Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mithenya-inī ĩo, ngoro cia and</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> acio igīthethūka mūno nĩ ũnd</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> wa njīra īo, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nao magīkiaria maundu
ma gūcambia Ngai, o na Musa, makiuga atīrī: </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwatū</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>rutire Misri tūüke tūkuire guku wero-inī nĩ kĩ?</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Niündū-ri, gūkű gūtikirī irio, na gūtirī maai, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na rĩ</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ủ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> ngoro citu nĩ inyikīte mūgate ūyũ utari kiene.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake Mwathani akīrehithirie andū acio nyamu-cia-thĩ ikūhenia o ta mwaki, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nacio ikimarũma; 
nao andũ aingī a Israeli magīkua. </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>And</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> acio magīgīthii kwi Musa, makimwira atiriri: </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩtwīhĩtie nī ūnd</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> nĩ täcambītie Mwathani, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o nawe tūgagūcambia; hoya Mwathani, nĩ getha atuthengerie nyamū ici-cia-thi.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake Musa agikīmahoera. Nake Mwathani ağīkiira Musa atirī: </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Withondekere nyamu-ya-thī kūhenia
ta mwaki, </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>umiikīre igūrū rĩa mūtī wa kibebero; </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na gugikinye atiri, ati mūndu o </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wothe urīa ūrūmītwo,
aamirora, akahonoka, </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Musa agīgīthondeka nyamū-ya-thī ya gīcango, </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akīmiikīra miūtī-inī wa kibebero
igūrű; </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na gugikinya atirī, ati rirà nyamū-ya-thĩ yarūma mūndū o na ürikū, </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>aarora nyamu-īo-ya-thĩ ya
gīcango-rī, akahonoka.</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nīcio ciugo cia Mwathani,</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>THABURI YA GÜCOKERŪO
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846>Thaburi 
78:1-2; 34-35; 36-37: 38</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>ICOKIA; </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Mwathani, nīwe ūhonokia witü.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>1. Kirindi giitu, ta tegai matu müigue kīrira giakwa; </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>inamiririai matü manyu müigue ciugo iria kanua gakwa gekwaria, </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ng</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>tumüra kanua njiarie na ngerekano; njitūrūre thimo icio cia maũndū ma tene</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>ICOKIA; </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Mwathani, nīwe ūhonokia witü.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>2. Riria aamoraga-ri, hĩndi ĩo magacoka kümūürīriria, </s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>magakīhünduka magacoka kūrongoria Murungu na kīyo. </s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na makaririkana ati Ngai nĩwe ndūmba yao ya ihiga, magakiririikana</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ati murungu uria uri iguru muno niwe mumakuuri.</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>ICOKIA; </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Mwathani, nīwe ūhonokia witü.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>3. No nĩ kũgathima maamugathimagīra kanua, </s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nimĩ ciao nikumuheni mamuhenagia nacio.</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ni gutuika ngioro ciao itiakiindiriirie hari we, </s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na hari uhoro wa kirikaniro giake matiari a kwihokeka. </s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>ICOKIA; </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Mwathani, nīwe ūhonokia witü.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>4.Nake tondu wa uria ari wa matha mingi, </s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nikuhumbira aahumbagira waganu wao, akarega  Kumanina; </s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ii-ni ni kaingi eheririe marakara make , akaaga kwarahura maruru make mothe</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>ICOKIA; </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Mwathani, nīwe ūhonokia witü</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>.</k></s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>GITHOMO KĪA IGĪRI
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846>Afilipi 2: 6-11</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>GUTHOMA MAR</k></c></s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Ữ</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>A MA M</k></c></s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Ữ</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>THURE PAUL KŪRI ANDU A FILIPI</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>:</k></s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kristu Yesu, We-ri.o na aaikarite ahaanaine na Ngai, </s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndonire ati kūiganana na Ngai ni </s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>ndu wa 
gukumbatirio, </s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>no gwĩcuuma ecuumire, agīikara ahaanaine na ngombo, </s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agigītutka wa kühaananio na andu a gükũ thi,. </s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake aagikorūo ahaana ta mūndū-rī, akīinyihia we mwene, agigiathika, </s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o kinya aiuragwo o kūūragwo kūria kwa mūtharaba-ini . </s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na nĩ ündü wa uguo, Ngai nĩ aamutūugīririe mūno, </s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akimūtua riitwa o riria rikirīte maritwa mothe; </s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>niguo atī thĩinī wa rītwa ria Yesu maru mothe 
maturagio, </s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o kūria Igūru, o na gūku thĩ, o na ruungu rũa thĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na ningi ati nīmi ciothe ciumbūrage atī </s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu Kristū nīwe Mwathani, 
nĩ getha Ngai Ithe wit</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> agoocagwo.</s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>icio nīcio ciugo cia Mwathani,</s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>RÜIMBO RWA ALLELUYA
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846>Alleluya, Alleluya, </s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ithui ni twagūtīa Wee Kristu na ni tűgūgūkumia tondū ni </s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ūkūūrite thĩ na
Mutharaba waku Mutheru.</s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alleluya, Alleluya, </s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>GiTHOMO KĪA INJIRI
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846>John 3: 13- 17</s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>GŪTHOMA ÎNJIRI YA MŪTHURE JOHN:</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hindi Yesu akeera Nikodemo: 
Gütiri műndū ūrĩ aambata Igūrű, </s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tiga o ūrīa aikūrūkire akiuma Igūru,
nĩwe Mürũ wa mũndū, o uria ūtuúraga Igūrű. </s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na ta ūria Musa aahaicirie nyamu-ya-thĩ igūrū werū-ini,</s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>noguo Mürũ wa mūndũ e na bata ahaicio igūrű: </s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ getha mūndū o wothe witikītie agīe mūoyo wa 
tene na tene thiinī wake we. </s></f>"},{ID:70,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Amu Ngai, tondű wa üria endete kīríndī gia gūkū thĩ, 
rĩ aarutire Mūrū wake wa mūmwe, </s></f>"},{ID:71,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ni getha műndű o wothe ūmwīhokete ndakore, 
no agīe mūoyo wa tene na tene.</s></f>"},{ID:72,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injiri theru ya Mwathani.</s></f>"}],
Text:"THIGUKUŨ YA GÍTÍO KIA MUTHARABA  MÜTHERU"},{Guid:"z8vMimlGK02zWZ4x1Zekjw",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>KUTUKUZWA KWA MSALABA MWAKA C</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>SOMO LA KWANZA
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846>Hesabu 214b-9</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika kitabu cha Hesabu</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Siku zile: Niiani, watu walikata tamaa.
akawanungunikia Mungu na Musa,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa nini mmetutoa Misri tuje tufe huku jangwani? </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Maana hukua na mkate wala maji; tumechoka na chakula hiki dhaifu!\"</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana akawapelekea watu nyoka wa sarafi; watu wengi wa Israeli</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wakaangamia kwwa kuumwa nao. Watu wakamwendea Musa</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>aakamwambia,lumekosa kwa kumnung'unikia Bwana na wewe.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tuombee kwa Bwana atuondolee nyoka hawa.\"</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>basi Musa akawaombea watu. Bwana akamwambia Musa:</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tengeneze nyoka ya shaba, ukaiweke juu ya mti.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kila aumwaye akiiangalia, atakuwa mzima.\"</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Musa akaifanya nyoka ya shaba, akaiweka juu ya mti,</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kila aliyeumwa na nyoka,
alipoiangalia nyoka hiyo ya shaba, akawa mzima.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F> 
</k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846>Zaburi 78:1-2, 34-35, 36-37, 38 </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Usiyasahau matendo makuu ya Mungu.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Sikilizeni mafundisho yangu, enyi taifa langu;</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tegeni masikio kwa maneno ya kinywa changu.</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nitafumbua kinywa changu kwa mifano,</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nitatangaza mafumbo ya zamani. K.</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>K.</k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F> Usiyasahau matendo makuu ya Mungu.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alipowaua, ndipo walipomtafuta;</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wakaongoka na kumtafuta Mungu kwa bidii tena.</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakakumbuka ya kuwa Mungu ni mwamba wao,</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwamba Mungu Aliye Juu ni mkombozi wao. K</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Usiyasahau matendo makuu ya Mungu.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Lakini walimdanganya kwa kinywa chao,</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wakamwambia uongo kwa ulimi wao.</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Moyo wao haukuwa mnyofu kwake;</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wala hawakuwa waaminifu kwa agano lake. K.</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Usiyasahau matendo makuu ya Mungu.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mungu lakini aliye mwenye huruma, alifuta dhambi;
wala hakuwaangamiza.</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mara nyingi alizuia hasira yake,
akazuia kuachilia ghadhabu yake. K.</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>K.</k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F> Usiyasahau matendo makuu ya Mungu.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>SOMO LA PILI
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846>Wafilipi 2:6-11</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika barua ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Wafilipi</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kristo Yesu, ijapokuwa alikuwa namna ya Mungu,</s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hakuchukulia kwamba kuwa sawa na Mungu</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Iilikuwa jambo la kushikamana nalo.
Bali alijishusha mwenyewe,</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akatwaa umbo la mtumishi,
akawa ana mfano wa wanadamu,</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na alipoonekana ana umbo la mwanadamu,</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>alijinyenyekeza mwenyewe, akawa mtii mpaka mauti,</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yaani mauti ya msalabani.
Kwa sababu hiyo Mungu alimtukuza,</s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akampa jina lipitalo kila jina,</s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ili kwa jina la Yesu wote wapige magoti,</s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wote walioko mbinguni, duniani na kuzimu.</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na kila ulimi ukiri kwamba Yesu Kristo ndiye Bwana,</s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa utukufu wa Mungu Baba.</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>SHANGILIO LA INILI
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846>K Aleluya,</s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tunakuabudu, ee Kristo,
na tunakushukuru</s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa sababu kwa Msalaba wako
umeikomboa dunia yote.</s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>W. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>INJILI</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo la lnji takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Yohane</s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakati ule:
yesu alimwambia Nikodemo.</s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hakuna mtu aliyepaa mbinguni,
a veye aliyeshuka kutoka mbinguni,</s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndiye Mwana wa Mtu.
Na kama Musa alivyomwinua nyoka jangwani,</s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>vile vile yampasa Mwana wa Mtu kuinuliwa,</s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>ili kila amsadikiye awe na uzima wa milele</k></s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa maana jinsi hii Mungu aliupenda ulimwengu,</s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hata akamtoa Mwanawe wa pekee,</s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ili kila mtu amsadikiye asipotee,</s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>bali awe na uzima wa milele.</s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mungu hakumtuma Mwana wake ulimwenguni,</s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ili auhukumu ulimwengu,
bali ulimwengu uokolewe naye.”</s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f>"}],
