Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>GITHOMO KIA MBERE
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>Amos 8: 4-7.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>GUTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RIA KIRORI AMOS</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ta iguai ūhoro ūyũ, inyui mwendaga kūmerükia arīa akīa, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mūkenda gūtūma athini a būrüri magī-thire, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>m</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>kiugaga atīrī: l karügamo ka mweri karīhītüka rī, nĩguo t</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>ügakīendagie irio ? </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na thabatü  irīthira rī, tūkabangage ngano ? </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>O tūkīnyihagia eba ya gūthimaga irio, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na tūkaritūhia cekeri ya gūthima mbia, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na tūthūkie ratiri nīguo tūhenanagie; 
nī getha twīgürīre arīa ahūthũ na mbia, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nao arīa akīa tūkīmegūrire na nyamüga igirī, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na gwata o muura wa ngano tūkawendagie. </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani nĩ ehītīte akagweta mwiraho ūrīa Jakobu, akoiga atīrī: </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndirī hingo ngariganīrūo nī ciiko icio 
ciao ona kīmwe.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nĩcio ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>THABURI YA GUCOKERUO
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846>Thaburi 
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>113: 1-2; 4-5; 7-8 .</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>ICOKIA </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Goocai Mwathani ürīa ūteithagia athīīni.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>1.Goocai Mwathani! Mügoocei, </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>inyuī ndungata ici cia Mwathani, 
kīgoocei ritwa rīa Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Riitwa ria Mwathani rīrotūura rigathagwo kuuma rīu nginya tene na tene.</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>ICOKIA</k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F> Goocai Mwathani ürīa ūteithagia athīīni.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>2.Mwathani-ri, atūūgrīte igüru rīa ndūrirī ciothe,</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>riri wake nī mũhitūku o igūrū rīa igūrū.</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>No ūhaana ta Mwathani Ngai witū, </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ucio witūügiriire e kūu aikaire,</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>ICOKIA </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Goocai Mwathani ürīa ūteithagia athīīni.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>3.Güūkiria nĩ okīragia mūndū ūria mūhūthū, </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akamũruta tiri-inī, o ūcio mwagi-rī, </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Agakīmuoya akamūruta kiara-ini; </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agatūma aikaranagie na anene, </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o ro hamwe na anene a kirindi kiao</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>ICOKIA </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Goocai Mwathani ürīa ūteithagia athīīni.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>GITHOMO KIA IGIRI
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846>1 Timotheo 2: 1-8</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>GŪTHOMA MARUA MA MŪTHURE PAUL KŪRI TIMOTHEO</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwendwo wakwa, nĩ ündü wa üguo, 
ürīa ngwamba gūtaarana nĩ atīirī, </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>atī kühoyagwo mahoya </s></f><fArial Black><s1384>magüthaithanirira,</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ma kühoyanīra, na ma gücokeria Ngai ngatho, </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ni ündü wa andü othe : na makiria, 
ati kühoyagirüo athamaki, </s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na arīa othe maathanaga, </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ getha tūtūüre na ühoreri o na twikindīire, </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tügītīaga Ngai tütarī na itherü. </s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ondü ücio niguo mwega na wa gwītīkīrīika nī Ngai Muhonokia witū, </s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o we wendaga andü othe mahonokio na matuīke a kūmenya ühoro-wa-ma. </s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Amu kwi na Ngai o ro ümwe, 
na mūiguithania </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o ümwe wa küigwithania Ngaí na andū, </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nake nī mũndu, o Kristü Yesu, üria werutire atuīke wa gükūüra andű othe: </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>naguo üira wa ühoro ücio nĩ waheanirüo ihinda rīaguo rīrīa rīagīrīru rīakinya, </s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Naguo nĩ niĩ ndatuirűo mühunjia o na mūtūmwo waguo, ngwaria o ma, </s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndikūhenania), na ningī ngĩtuwo mürutani </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wa kürutaga Ndūriri ühoro wa gwitikia, </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na uhoro-wa-ma. Tondū wa üguo-rī, </s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ngwenda ati kündū guothe arume  mahoithagie arĩ o, </s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>makioyaga moko matheru na igūrū, </s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hatarī na marakara na kana ngarari. </s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nĩcio ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>RUIMBO RŪA INJIRI
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>2 Akorintho 8, 9 .</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alleluya, Alleluya. </s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu Kristū, ona arī gītonga, nĩ atūikire mūthiini , </s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ getha ithuĩ tūtuīke itonga nĩ ündū wa ūrīa wee arī mūthĩni. </s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alleluya,</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>GĪTHOMO KIA INJIRI
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>Luka 16: 1-13</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŪTHOMA INJIRI YA MŪTHURE LUKA :</s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hindī io Yesu nĩ erire arūmiriri ake</s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ni kwarĩ műndū warī gītonga, nake nĩ aarīĩ na mūrori wa indo ciake: </s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ūcio nake agīthitakwo kūrĩ we, atī nĩ aaitangaga indo ciake. </s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akīmwīta akīműūria atīrī: 
Uhoro ūcio waku njiguīte nĩ atīa?</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ta he ūhoro wa wira ūcio ndakūheire; </s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nī gūkorūo ndūngīhota gūikara ūkīroraga indo ciakwa.</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake mūrori ücio wa indo akiiüria atīrī: </s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ngügiīka atīa, kuona atī mwathani wakwa nĩ ekūnduta</s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wira-inī wa kūrora indo ? Ndirĩ na hinya wa kürīma; </s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ingīhoya mbia kūrĩ andū, ndaconoka. </s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Indĩ nĩ ndamenya ürĩa ngwīka, nĩ getha, </s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>rīrīa ngarutwo wira-inī wa kūrora indo, </s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>andū makanyamūkīra njikarage kwao. </s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Agigiīta andū arīa maarīĩ na thirĩ na mwathani wake moke o mūndū, o mūndū;</s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akīüria üria wa mbere atīri: Wee-rī, </s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wĩ na thirī üigana atīa wa mwathani wakwa? </s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake akimwira atīrī: 
Ni wa marebe magana merī ma maguta, </s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake akīmwīra atirī: 
Oya marūa maku ma thirī, üikare thĩ narua, </s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wandike atī nī igana rīmwe. </s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Agīcoka akiūria mündū ūngī atīrī: Nawe-rī, thirī waku</s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Üigana atīa ? Nake akiuga atīrī: </s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ wa makūnia igana rīmwe ma ngano, Nake akīmwira atīrī: </s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Oya marűa maku ma thirī, wandīke atinĩ makūnia mīrongo înana. </s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake mwathani wake akīgatha müroriindo </s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ūcio műüru nĩ ündű wa ūguo ekire na ūügī; </s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ gükorūo andü arīa a mahinda maya me na üügi, </s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o rűciaro-inī rüao, gükira andū arīa a ūtheri. </s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na niĩ ngūmwira atīrī: 
tumagai ndūgū </s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na andü na ütonga ürīa ütarī wa ūthingu ; </s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ getha wathira-rī, makamwamükīra </s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>müikarage ciikaro-inĩ iria
igatüüra tene na tene.</s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mũndũ wa kwîhokeka na indo nyinyi mũno, </s></f>"},{ID:70,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ūcio ehokeka na iria nyingī o nacio ; </s></f>"},{ID:71,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nake ūrīa ütarī
wa kwīhokeka na indo nyinyi mũno, </s></f>"},{ID:72,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ūcio ndangiihokeka o na iria nyingīĩ nacio. </s></f>"},{ID:73,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ni ũndŭ ūcio-rī,
mũngīkorūo mūtehokekete na ūtonga </s></f>"},{ID:74,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ürīa ūtarī wa ūthingu, nũ üngīmwihoka na űtonga urīa
ma? </s></f>"},{ID:75,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na ningī mũngīkorūo mūtehokekete na indo cia mūndū ūngī ,</s></f>"},{ID:76,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nũ üngīmūne iria cianyu inyui ene ? </s></f>"},{ID:77,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Gūtirī ndungata îngīhota gūtungatīra aathani erī; </s></f>"},{ID:78,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ ündű no kinya îthū</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>re ümwe, yende ū-ria üngī;</s></f>"},{ID:79,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kana iiguithanie na ūmwe, inyarare ürīa üngī. </s></f>"},{ID:80,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mütingīhota gūtungatīra Ngai o na ütonga.</s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s></f>"}],
Text:"KIUMIA KIA MIRONGO IRI NA ITHANO KIA MWAKA C
"},{Guid:"BQ5WyZLU1kGPmN2OJovnAA",Verses:[{
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>DOMINIKA YA ISHIRINI NA TANO MWAKA C</k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>SOMO LA KWANZA
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>Amosi 8:47</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika kitabu cha Nabii Amosi</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Sikilizeni 
haya, enyi 
mnaomkanyaga </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mnyonge,na 
kuwaangamiza ninyi mnaosema:</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>atu maskini 
wa nchi;
Sikukuu ya mwezi </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mwandamo itakwisha wakati gani,</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tupate kuuza ngano?
Nayo siku ya Sabato, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tupate kufungua ghala ya ngano?</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tutapunguza vipimo, tutapandisha bei.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tutageuza mizani ziwe za uongo!</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tutauza hata makapi ya ngano,
tupate </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kuwanunua watu maskini kwa fedha,</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na wanyonge kwa jozi ya viatu!”
Bwana ameapa kwa utukufu wa Yakobo:</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hakika sitasahau kamwe matendo yao.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>Zaburi 1 13:1-2,4-6,7-8(K. la na 7a)</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFFFF66><kFFFF3F3F>Msifuni Bwana, humwinua mnyonge kutoka mavumbini aleluya.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Enyi watumishi wa Bwana, sifuni,
lisifuni jina la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Jina la Bwana litukuzwe
tangu sasa na hata milele. K.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFFFF66><kFFFF3F3F>Msifuni Bwana, humwinua mnyonge kutoka mavumbini aleluya.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana ni mkuu juu ya mataifa yote;
utukufu wa Mungu ni juu ya mbingu.</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ni nani aliye kama Bwana,
Mungu wetu, aketiye juu kabisa,</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ainamaye atazame chini mbinguni na duniani? K.</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFFFF66><kFFFF3F3F>Msifuni Bwana, humwinua mnyonge kutoka mavumbini aleluya.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Humwinua mnyonge kutoka mavumbini,
kutoka jalalani humpandisha maskini,</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>amketishe pamoja na wakuu,
pamoja na wakuu wa watu wake. K.</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>K </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFFFF66><kFFFF3F3F>Msifuni Bwana humwinua mnyonge kutoka mavumbini aleluya.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>SOMO LA PILI
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>1 Timotheo 2:1-8</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika barua ya kwanza ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Timotheo</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mpendwa:
Kwanza kabisa </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ninayowaomba hasa ndiyo, dua na sala, </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Maombezi na shukrani zitolewe kwa ajili ya watu wote, </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa ajili ya wafalme na wote wenye mamlaka, </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tupate raha na utulivu kwa kuishi</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maisha ya uchaji wa Mungu na ya mwenendo mwema.</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hayo ni mema, tena yampendeza Mungu, mwokozi wetu, </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ambaye anataka watu wote </s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>waokolewe, na watambue yaliyo kweli.</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa maana kuna Mungu mmoja, na mpatanishi baina ya Mungu</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na wanadamu ni mmoja, ndiye nwanadamu Kristo Yesu,</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>huyo alijitoa mwenyewe </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kuwa fidia kwa ajili ya watu wote. </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndio ushuhuda nyakati zake.</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa hiyo nimewekwa mimi niwe mtangazaji na mtume, </s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tena mwalimu wa mataifa katika imani na ukweli.</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hayo maneno yangu ni kweli, </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>si uongo. Kila mahali mnaposali</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>napenda wanaume wainue mikono kwa utakatifu, si kwa hasira
na ubishi.</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>SHANGILIO LA INJILI
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>2 Wakorintho 8:9</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>W. Aleluya.
K. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>lijapokuwa 
Yesu Kristo 
alikuwa tajiri,
alijifanya fukara kwa ajili yenu,</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ili ninyi mpate kutajirika kwa ufukara wake.</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>W. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>INJILI 
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>Luka 16:1-13</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo la lnjili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Luka</s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakati ule:
yesu aliwaambia wafuasi wake, </s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tajiri mmoja alikuwa na karani naye alishitakiwa </s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwake kwamba anatapanya mali zake.</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akamwita, akamwambia, Je, nasikia nini juu yako? </s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Toa hesabu wa ukarani wako, kwa maana huwezi kuwa karani tena.”</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Karani huyo akasema moyoni mwake, Nifanyeje? Maana,</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>bwana wangu ananiachisha kazi ya ukarani. Kulima, siwezi,</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kuomba kama maskini naona haya. Najua la kufanya, </s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ili baada ya kutolewa katika ukarani, wanikaribishe nyumbani kwao.”</s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akawaita wadeni wa bwana wake mmoja mmoja, </s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akamwambia wa kwanza, “Una deni gani kwa bwana wangu?”</s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Naye akajibu, Mapipa mia ya mafuta.</s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Akamwambia, Twaa hati
yako ya deni; </s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kaa upesi, andika, hamsini. Kisha akamwambia
mwingine, </s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>‘Nawe una deni gani?” Akasema, ‘Mifuko mia ya ngano.”</s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akamwambia, Twaa hati yako ya deni, andika, themanini.”</s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana akamsifu karani mdanganyifu kwa sababu alifanya
werevu. </s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Maana wana wa dunia hii ni werevu katika mahusiano
yao kuliko wana wa mwanga. </s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nami nawaambieni, jifanyieni
rafiki kwa mali inayoharibika, </s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ili mnapoishiwa nayo wawapokee
katika makao ya milele.</s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Aliye mwaminifu kwa mambo madogo ni mwaminifu pia kwa mambo makubwa; </s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kadhalika asiye mwaminifu kwa mambo, madogo, </s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>si mwaminifu kwa mambo makubwa. </s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Basi kama hamwi waaminifu kwa mali isiyo haki, </s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nani atawakabidhi mali ya kweli</s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na kama hamwi waaminifu kwa mali ya mwingine,</s></f>"},{ID:70,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> 
nani atawapa  yenu wenyewe?</s></f>"},{ID:71,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hakuna mtumishi awezaye kutumikia mabwana wawili, </s></f>"},{ID:70,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ama atamchukia wa kwanza na kumpenda wa pili </s></f>"},{ID:71,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>au atamjali wa kwanza na kumdharau mwingine.</s></f>"},{ID:72,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hamwezi kumtumikia Mungu na fedha.”</s></f>"},{ID:73,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f>"}],
Text:"DOMINIKA YA ISHIRINI NA TANO MWAKA C
"},{Guid:"/NPNkW/6Kk6Iom3zHkaJUQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>JUMAA</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Güthoma kuuma Marūa ma Mbere 
ma Paulo kűrī Timotheo
(6:3-12)</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mũndū o na ũrikü angikorūo nĩarutanaga ürutani üngi,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>atetīkanītie na mohoro marĩa magīrīire, </s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o macio ma Mwathani witũ Yesu Kristü, 
o na ûrutani wake ürĩa</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ürũmanīriire na kwiamürīra Ngai, </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mũndū ūcio nikwigatha egathīte na ndarī ündũ oĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>no thuti arī nayo ya kūüranganagia ciüria itarī bata, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na gũkararanīria o ciugo theri; </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na nīho hoimaga ūiru na ngũi, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na gũcambania na gwĩküa maŭndũ moru, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kūgiana kwa andű arĩa marĩ na meciria
mathūku </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na matiganīte na ūhoro-ūria-wa-ma, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>magakigereria atī ūhoro wa </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwĩamũríra Ngai nĩ guo gűtũma mũndũ atonge. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na mũndū wa kwĩamūrīra Ngai hamwe na </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>küiganwo nĩ kīrīa mũndű arĩ nakīo, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>üguo níguo űtonga mũnene: </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nī ũndũ tűtiarehire kindũ gũkũ thĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na gūtiri kĩndū tũngīhota kūruta kuo; </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndĩ tũngĩgĩa na irio ma nguo, no tũiganwo nīcio. </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>No andū arīa mendaga gütonga, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ kūgũa magūaga magerio-inī o na műtego-iní, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>magathūkio nī merirïria maingĩ o ma ũrimű, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o marīa mathűkagia andū,</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>namo makamaninűkia magatūma </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>more biũ o ta mahorokerete thĩinĩ wamo. </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tondũ kwīriĩria mbia nĩ kīhumo kĩa </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maűru ma mĩthemba yothe; </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na andū amwe, tondũ wa kūhahanya mbia üguo, </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩmatwarīrīirio njĩra-inī njũru, </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>magagītigana na űrutani wa witikio, </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na gwĩtheca metheceete ngoro na kĩeha kĩingî. </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>No wee mũndũ wa Ngai, kĩũragīre maūndũ macio, </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ürűgamie ūhoro wa ūthingu, </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na wa kwĩaműrira
Ngai, na wa gwītīkia, </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na wendani, na ükirīriria na ühoreri.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Rūaga mbaara irĩa njega ya kürüïrīra </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maűndű maria
metīkītio, </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na wĩnyitīre muoyo ũrña ūtagathira, </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o űcio wetirűo ügīe naguo hĩndi ĩrīa </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>woimbūrire uumbüri o ûria
mwega aira aingĩ marī ho.</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nicio c</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ủ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>ugo cia Ngai.</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Thaburi ya gůcokerwo.
(Cfr. Psalm 48)</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icokia: Gūkena nĩ athĩni a ngoro;
tondű űthamaki wa Igūrũ nĩ wao.</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>1.Nĩ kĩ gītũmaga ndiītigīre matukū marīa moru,</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>rirīa njigīrīiirio ni aria aaganu,</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o arĩa mehokaga űtonga wao,</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>magakīīraha tondũ wa ūrīa maingīhĩtie indo?</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icokia: Gūkena nĩ athĩni a ngoro;
tondű űthamaki wa Igūrũ nĩ wao.</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>2.Gūtiri ũngīhota gwīkūrĩra mūrũ wa nyina,</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>atī arutĩre Ngai kĩndū kĩngĩmūkūūra;</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ ündū ûkūūri wa mĩoyo yao nĩ goro müno,</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>no ūtiganwo naguo o nginya tene;</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gūtingīhoteka at</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ỉ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> mundū ūcio atūũre muoyo,</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>atarī hingo atakonana na kuora.</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icokia: Gūkena nĩ athĩni a ngoro;
tondű űthamaki wa Igūrũ nĩ wao.</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>3.Ndūkanetigīre mũndū atonga,
na riri gwake weongerera;</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tondū akua ndarī kindū agathiĩ nakio,</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>riri ūcio wake ndagaīkūrũka naguo.</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icokia: Gūkena nĩ athĩni a ngoro;
tondű űthamaki wa Igūrũ nĩ wao.</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>4.Ona angītuika rîrīa aarī muoyo nīegathagiriria,</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o nawe andū magagīkūgathaga weka wega;</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gūthii agathiĩ o kürí riika rīria rĩa maithe,</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>macio matagacoka kuona ūtheri rīngĩ.</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icokia: Gūkena nĩ athĩni a ngoro;
tondű űthamaki wa Igūrũ nĩ wao.</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Rūimbo rwa Injiri</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Umüthĩ ndūkonie ngoro na ūthikiririe mügambo
wa Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Gūthoma Injiri ta ürīa yandikītwo nĩ Luka
(8:1-3)</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hindi io gūgīkinya ati Yesu niathiangaga</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akīhunguraga matūūra o na mĩci</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ỉ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>, </s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akahunjagia Uhoro-űrīa-Mwega wa
Uthamaki wa Ngai, </s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akīūheanaga kūrī andū. Nao arĩa ikūmi
na erī maarī hamwe nake, </s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na andū-a-nja amwe arīa
moimitwo nī ngoma njűru, </s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na arīa mahonetio mĩrimũ miüru
yao: </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ūmwe nĩ Mariamu üria wetagwo Mũmagidali, </s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩwe ürīa
woimirūo nĩ ndaimonomūgwanja. </s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na arīa angi Joana, műtumia wa Husa, </s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ürīa warī mūrori wa indo cia Herode, </s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Susana, na angĩ aingī arīa maamūtungatagīra na indo ciao.</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injiri theru ya  Mwathani.</s></f>"}],
