Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani ekuuga üü: Mütino, kaĩ nĩ arīa maikaraga kūu Sion-ī! </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>O na 
arīa maikaraga megangarite kirīma-inĩ gĩa Samaria. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ inyuĩ arīĩa makomagīra marīrī magemie na miguongo, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>magetambũrükagia itanda-inī ciao, 
magakīriaga tügondu tuumīte rūüru-inī, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na icaŭ ciumīte icegū-inī,; o arīa
mainaga nyĩmbo cia mwituīro </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>cia künyihia mūthenya makīinagia inanda cia mūgeto ;</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na magetumithĩria inanda cia kūinaga nacio, ta Davide; </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>arīa manyuaga ndibei na ciitīrīra, na makehakaga
maguta marīa mega mūno; </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>no rirī, matingīigua ruo nĩ ũndũ wa kūgurara kwa mbarī ya Josephu.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hakīrī üguo-rĩ, rĩu no hinya matahanīrio na arīa a kwamba gütahwo, </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ironja ria acio matūire
metambürűkagia rīthire.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nĩcio ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>THABURI YA GUCOKERŪO</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000> 
