146: 7: 8-9a: 9b-10</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>ICOKIA: </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Agunwo ní athiini a ngoro.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>1.Mwathani, o we ūtuagira andũ arīa agūmire matuiro ma kihooto; </s></f>"},{ID:19,Style:{Background:{Image:"Candle.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ūria ningi ūheaga arīa ahūtu irio, Mwathani-rī, arīa othe ni amohoraga.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>ICOKIA: </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Agunwo ní athiini a ngoro.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>2.Mwathani nī ahingūraga arīa atumumu maitho, </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani nĩ ainamūraga aria mekonotete</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani nĩ enda aria athingu; Mwathani-rī, nĩ amenyagirira ageni.</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>ICOKIA: </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Agunwo ní athiini a ngoro.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>3.Mwana wa ngoriai na mūtumia wa ndigwa, nīwe ūmanyitagīrira;
 </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nayo njira ya aria aaganu nĩ kūmīhotomia amīhotomagia,
 </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani egūtūűra athamakaga tene na tene, Ngai waku,</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wee Sion-rī, egūtūūra athamakaga nginya njiarūa na njiarũa,</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>ICOKIA: </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Agunwo ní athiini a ngoro.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:29,
