6: 11- 16.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>GUTHOMA MARŨA MA MŪTHURE PAUL MARIA MAANDIKIIRUO TIMOTHEO :</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwendwo wakwa, no wee mündü wa Ngai-ĩ, kīüragīre maűndú macio, </s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ürűmagie ühoro wa 
uthingu, na wa kwīamūrīra Ngai, </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na wa gwīitīkia, o na wendani, na ükirīriria, 
o na ühoreri, </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ruaga mbaara īrĩa njega ya kūrüirīra maündũ marīa metikītio, </s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na wīnyitīre muoyo úria ütagathira, </s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o ucio wetirūo ūgīe naguo hĩndĩ irĩa woimbürire uumbüri üria mwega, </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>aira aingī marī ho. Ndakwira
atīrirī na ma, twĩ mbere ya Ngai, </s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>üria wikagira indo ciothe muoyo, o na twĩ mbere ya Kristũ Yesu, </s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>we woimbūrire uumbüri ürīa mwega e mbere ya Pontio Pilato-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>atī ürūmagie rīathani rīu
wathitwo narīo, riikare rītathūkītio na rītacambïtio, </s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o nginya rīrīa Mwathani witü Yesu Kristü akonanio : nake nĩ kuonanio akonanio,</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ihinda rīake rĩakinya, nĩ ürīa wĩ Mwene-hinya-wothe we wiki na ürīa Mügathe, </s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o we Müthamaki wa athamaki na Mwathani wa aathani, </s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake nīwe wiki ūtūüraga muoyo ürīa ūtathiraga, </s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agatūüra ütheri-inī ürīa ütarī mūndü üngīhota kūükuhīhīria. </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Gūtiri műndű o na ürīkű wanamuona, o na kana ūngīhota kūmyona. </s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake arotīagwo na arogīa na wathani üria ütagathira. 
Nĩ g</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>tuīke guo.</s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nīcio ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>RUIMBO RUA INJIRI
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF0000><kFFF2F200>Luka 6, 21 .</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Alleluya, Alleluya.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani ekuuga ūū : 
Gükena-rĩ, nĩ inyuī mühűtaga rĩu; nĩ gükorűo
nĩ mügacoka kūhūnio. </s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Alleluya.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>GITHOMO KIA INJIRI
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF0000><kFFF2F200>Luka 16 : 19 - 31 .</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>GUTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE LUKA :</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hĩndī īo Yesu akīira Afariseo : </s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ kwarī mündũ warī gītonga weguīkaga nguo ndune na gatani mūthemba mwega mūno; </s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nake aatüire arīaga irio njega mīthenya yothe. </s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na rīrī, mündū wahoyaga thendi, wetagwo Lazaro, </s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ aaigagwo kihingo-inī kĩa mūciĩ wake, na aarī na ironda nyingī. </s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na nĩeriragīria kūrīa rūitīki rūrĩa rūoimaga metha-ini ya gītonga kīu; </s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ningī ngui nĩ ciokaga kürĩ we igacūnaga ironda ciake. </s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na gügikinya atī: atī ücio mühoi thendi nĩ aakuire, </s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agīkuuwo nĩ araika, akīigwo githũri- ini kīa Abraham; </s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gītonga nakīo gīgīkua gīgīthikwo. Nakīo gii kūu kwa-ngoma </s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gikiiguaga ruo rūnene-ĩ, gīgītiira maitho,īkīona 
Abraham arīküraya, </s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na Lazaro arī gīthūri-inī
gīake, Akanīrīra akiuga atīrī: </s></f>",IsDisplayed:0},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Abraham, Awa, njiguĩra tha, 
na ütüme Lazaro atobokie mūthia wa</s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kīara gīake maaī-inī, oke a’hehie rürīmī nĩ gükorűo nĩ </s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nduuragwo müno ndĩ rũrīrimbī-ini rürű rüa mwaki. </s></f>"},{ID:70,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nowe Abraham akiuga atīri: 
Mürű wakwa, </s></f>"},{ID:71,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ta ririkana atī ihinda rīrīa watūire muoyo kūrīa
thĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:72,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ wonaga indo ciaku njega, nake Lazaro akona iria njüru; </s></f>"},{ID:73,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>no rĩu, gükū-rĩ, ücio nĩ anyamarűragwo, nawe ügatuurūo mũno. </s></f>"},{ID:74,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ningī hamwe na üguo-rī, nĩ kürī mūkuru müriku müno wikirītwo gatagatī gaitū nawe, </s></f>"},{ID:76,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ getha arīa mangīenda kuuma gūkū mathii kürī wee matikahote; </s></f>"},{ID:77,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na mūndũ ndakanahote küringa oime kűu, oke gükū türi. </s></f>"},{ID:78,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nakīĩo gītonga gīkiuga atīri: Hakīri ūguo, </s></f>"},{ID:79,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Awa, ndagūthaitha ümūtüme kürĩ andű a nyümba ya awa; </s></f>"},{ID:80,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nī gükorűo nd</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ỉ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> na ariū a maitü atano; 
athiï akamoimbūrīre ühoro, </s></f>"},{ID:81,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ getha matikanae gūkinya o nao gükü kwĩ na ruo rünene üũ. </s></f>"},{ID:82,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nowe Abraham akiuga atīrī: </s></f>"},{ID:83,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Andū acio marī na Musa o na Irori; nĩ mamaigue o. </s></f>"},{ID:84,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nakīo gītonga gigicoka
gīkiuga atīri: Tiguo, Abraham, </s></f>"},{ID:85,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Awa; no rīrī, műndū angīthiï kürī o, oimīte kūrĩ arīa akuū, no merire. </s></f>"},{ID:86,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake akīmwīra atirī: Akorűo matingiigua Musa na Irori, </s></f>"},{ID:87,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>matingīringīrīrīka nī mũndū, o na angīkorūo nĩ küriüka ariükīte akoima küri arīa akuü.</s></f>"},{ID:88,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injiri theru ya Mwathani.</s></f>"}],Style:{Background:{Image:"Candle.jpg",Luminosity:-25}},
Text:"KIUMIA KIA MIRONGO IRĪ NA ITHATHATU KIA MWAKA C
"},{Guid:"BI5qZotMq02N2NEdWHbNOA",Verses:[{
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>DOMINIKA YA ISHIRINI NA SITA MWAKA C</k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>SOMO LA KWANZA
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFF2F200>Amosi 
</k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>6:1a, 4-7</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Somo katika kitabu cha Nabii Amosi</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana Mungu wa majeshi, asema hivi:
Ole wao wanoishi kwa raha katika Sioni.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na wale wanaokaa salama katika mlima wa Samaria.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ninyi mnaolala juu ya vitanda vya pembe
na kujinyosha juu ya masemadari</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ninyi mnaokula wana kondoo wa kundi, na ndama wanono wa zizi.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wanaimba nyimbo kwa sauti ya kinubi,
yenu;</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kujifanyia, kama Daudi, vyombo vya muziki;</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wanakunywa divai katika mabakuli, na kujipaka manukato mazuri,</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>lakini hawahuzuniki juu ya kabila la Yosefu.
Kwa hiyo sasa watahamishwa,</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hata watakuwa wa kwanza wa wenye kuhamishwa,</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na matamasha yao ya kiasherati yatakoma.”</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846>Zaburi 
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>146:7, &-9a, 9be-10 (K. lb)</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K;</k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Umsifu Bwana, ee nafsi yangu.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana huwarudishia haki waliodhulumiwa,</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>huwapa wenye njaa chakula.
Bwana huwafungua wafungwa. K.</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K; </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Umsifu Bwana, ee nafsi yangu.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana huyafumbua macho ya vipofu.
Bwana huwainua waliokandamizwa chini:</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana huwapenda wenye haki.
Bwana huwalinda wageni. K.</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K ;</k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Umsifu Bwana, ee nafsi yangu</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>.</k></s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana huwategemeza yatima na mjane,
bali huipotosha njia ya waovu.</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana atatawala milele,
Mungu wako, ee Sioni, kizazi hata kizazi! K.</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Umsifu Bwana, ee nafsi yangu.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>SOMO LA PILI
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>1 Timotheo 6:11-l6</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Somo katika barua ya kwanza ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Timotheo</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wewe uliye mtu wa Mungu, ujiepushe na mambo hayo. </s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Fuata uadilifu, uchaji wa Mungu, imani, upendo, subira na upole.</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Pambana katika mapambano ya imani. uutwae uzima wa milele.</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Huo ndio mwito wako, nawe ume fanya maungamo mazuri mbele ya
mashahidi wengi.</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na kuamuru mbele ya Mungu aliye asili ya kila uhai na mbele ya
Kristo Yesu, </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>aliyetoa ushahidi mzuri mbele ya Ponsio Pilato,</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>utimize agizo hili bila waa na bila lawama mpaka kutokea kwake
Yesu Kristo. </s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakati wake mwenye heri atalidokeza tokeo la yeye
aliye peke yake mtawala.</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mfalme wa wafalme, Bwana wa mabwana, Yeye peke yake hawezi
kufa. </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Amekaa katika mwanga usiosogeleka. </s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hakuna mwanadamu
aliyemwona, </s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wala awezaye kumwona. Heshima na enzi ya milele ni yake. Amina.</s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>SHANGILIO LA INJILI
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846>2 Wakorintho 8:9</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>K. Aleluya.
W. Aleluya.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. ljapokuwa Yesu Kristo alikuwa tajiri, alijifanya fukara </s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa ajili yenu,
ili ninyi mpate kutajirika kwa ufukara wake.</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>W. Aleluya.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>INJILI </k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000> 
Luka 16: 19-31</k></s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Luka</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakati ule: Yesu aliwaambia Mafarisayo,</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>“Palikuwa na mtu mmoja tajiri aliyezoea kuvaa nguo za rangi</s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ya zambarau na kitani safi na alijifurahisha </s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa kufanya sherehe
siku kwa siku. </s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mlangoni pake alilala maskini, jina lake Lazaro,
aliyejaa vidonda. </s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alitamani kushibishwa walau kwa makombo
yaliyoanguka kutoka meza ya yule tajiri. </s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakaja pia mbwa, wakamlamba vidonda vyake. </s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Siku moja yule maskini alikufa,
akachukuliwa na malaika kifuani kwa Abrahamu. </s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kisha yule tajiri naye akafa, akazikwa,na katika mateso yake Jehanamu, </s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>aliinua macho yake, akamwona Abrahamu kwa mbali, na Lazaro kifuani pake. </s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akapaza sauti, akalia, ‘Baba Abrahamu, unihurumie. </s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Umtume Lazaro achovye ncha ya kidole chake kwenye maji, apoze ulimi
wangu, </s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa maana nateswa sana katika moto huu.</s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Abrahamu akajibu, Mwanangu, kumbuka ya kuwa wewe ulipokea</s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mema yako wakati wa maisha yako duniani, bali Lazaro alipatwa
na mabaya; </s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>sasa huyu anatulizwa, bali wewe unateswa.
Na juu ya hayo, kuna shimo kubwa kati yetu na yenu, </s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hata kama watu wangetaka kuvukia kwenu, </s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hawawezi, wala wa kwenu
hawawezi kuvukia kwetu. </s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akasema, Basi, baba, ninakuomba
umtume Lazaro aende katika nyumba ya baba yangu, </s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maana nina ndugu watano, awaonye, wasije wakafika pia mahali hapa pa mateso.”</s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Lakini Abrahamu akasema,
Wanao Musa na manabii. Wawasikilize hao.’</s></f>"},{ID:70,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yeye akasema, Sivyo, baba Abrahamu,
bali mtu akienda kwao kutoka kwa wafu, </s></f>"},{ID:71,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>watatubu.’ Lakini yeye akajibu, Wasipowasikiliza Musa na manabii,</s></f>"},{ID:72,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hawatapokea ushuhuda wa mtu aliyefufuka katika wafu.”</s></f>"},{ID:73,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f>"}],Style:{Background:{Image:"Candle.jpg"}},
Text:"DOMINIKA YA ISHIRINI NA SITA MWAKA C
"},{Guid:"uNpIew067E+qlDtrOiNpqA",Verses:[{Style:{Background:{Image:"WhatsApp Image 2025-10-04 at 07.57.08_cb1061b1.jpg"}},
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>DOMINIKA YA ISHIRINI NA SABA MWAKA C</k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>SOMO LA KWANZA
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFF2F200>Habakuki </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF0000><kFFF2F200>1:2-3; 2:24</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Somo katika kitabu cha Nabii Habakuki</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ee Bwana, nikusihi hata wakati gani,
nawe hutaki kusikiliza? Nitalia Udhalimu”,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wala hutaki kuokoa. Kwa 
nini unanifanyizia nione uovu,</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>unanishurutisha kuangalia taabu.
Unyang’anyi na ujeuri ni mbele yangu,</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ugomvi 
na mabishano yametokea.
Hapo Bwana akanijibu akasema:</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Andika maono, uyachore wazi katika vibao,
ili mtu apate kuyasoma upesi.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwani maono haya yatatimia wakati uliowekwa;</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>saa iliyokusudiwa yatatokea, wala hayatadanganya.
Kama yanakawia, uyangojee:</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwani yatakuja hakika, wala hayatachelewa.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mtu mwovu atakuwa na roho yenye kupotoka,</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>lakini mtu mnyofu ataishi kwa imani yake.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFF2F200>Zaburi 
</k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF0000><kFFF2F200>95:1-2, 6-7abc, 7d-9 (K. 7d, 8a)</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Ingekuwa heri leo msikie sauti yake!
Msiifanye mioyo yenu kuwa migumu.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Njoni, tumpigie Bwana kelele za furaha;</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tumshangilie mwamba wa wokovu wetu.
Tuje mbele yake kwa shukrani,</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tumfanyie shangwe kwa nyimbo na zaburi. K.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Ingekuwa heri leo msikie sauti yake!
Msiifanye mioyo yenu kuwa migumu.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Njoni, tuabudu na kusujudu;
tumpigie magoti Bwana aliyetuumba.</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwani yeye ni Mungu wetu,
sisi tu watu wa malisho yake,</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kondoo wanaochungwa kwa mkono wake. K.</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Ingekuwa heri leo msikie sauti yake!
Msiifanye mioyo yenu kuwa migumu.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ingekuwa heri leo msikie sauti yake:</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>msiifanye mioyo yenu kuwa migumu kama huko Meriba</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kama baba zenu walivyokuwa siku ya Masa jangwani.</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Waliponijaribu, baba zenu waliponipima;</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ijapo walikwishaona matendo yangu. K.</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Ingekuwa heri leo msikie sauti yake!
Msiifanye mioyo yenu kuwa migumu.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>SOMO LA PILI
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF0000><kFFF2F200>2</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFF2F200> Timotheo </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF0000><kFFF2F200>1:6-8, 13-14</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Somo katika barua ya pili ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Timotheo</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mpendwa:
Ninakukumbusha, uiamshe neema ya Mungu iliyomo ndani yako</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa kuwekewa mikono yangu. Kwa maana Mungu hakutupelekea</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>roho ya woga, bali Roho wa nguvu na wa upendo na wa kushika kiasi.</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Basi, usione aibu kumshuhudia Bwana wetu, wala usione aibu kwa</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>sababu yangu mimi niliye mfungwa wake. Bali uvumilie pamoja</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nami kwa ajili ya Injili ukitegemea nguvu ya Mungu.</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mafundisho kamili uliyoyasikia kwangu yawe mfano wako katika</s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>imani na upendo uliomo katika Kristo Yesu. Amana nzuri hiyo</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>uitunze kwa nguvu ya Roho Mtakatifu anayekaa ndani yetu.</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>SHANGILIO LA INJILI
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFF2F200>1 Petro </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF0000><kFFF2F200>1:25</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Aleluya</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>. 
W. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Aleluya.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Neno la Bwana ladumu milele.
Ndilo neno mlilohubiriwa
katika habari njema.</s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>W. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Aleluya.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>INJILI 
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFF2F200>Luka </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF0000><kFFF2F200>17:5-10</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Luka</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakati ule: Mitume walimwambia Bwana, “Tuongezee imani.”</s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana akasema, Mngekuwa na imani kiasi cha punje ya haradali,</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mngeuambia mkuyu huu, Ng’oka, kapandikizwe baharini,’ nao
ungewatii.</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nani kati yenu mwenye mtumishi wa kulima au kuchunga ng’ombe</s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>atamwambia anaporudi kutoka shambani, Njoo uketi ule chakula?”</s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Je, hatamwambia, Niandalie chakula, jifunge kanzu, nitumikie</s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mpaka nitakapomaliza kula na kunywa, ndipo utakula na kunywa
wewe?”</s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Je, atamshukuru mtumishi kwa sababu amefanya
aliyoamriwa?</s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nanyi pia, mkishafanya yote mliyoamriwa, semeni,</s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Sisi ni watumishi wasio na faida;
tumefanya tu tuliyopaswa kufanya.”</s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f>"}],Style:{Background:{Image:"WhatsApp Image 2025-10-04 at 07.57.08_cb1061b1.jpg"}},
Text:"DOMINIKA YA ISHIRINI NA SABA MWAKA C
"},{Guid:"eZ18bwf7GkyK8Vx1icjB5A",Verses:[{
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>DOMINIKA YA ISHIRINI NA NANE MWAKA C</k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA KWANZA
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF0000><kFFFFFF66>2 </k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846>Wafalme </s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF0000><kFFFFFF66>5:14-17</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika kitabu cha pili cha Wafalme</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Siku zile: Naamani [jemedari wa jeshi la mfalme wa Aramu]
alishuka, akajizamisha katika Yordani mara saba kadiri ya neno
la Elisha mtu wa Mungu. Mara nyama ya mwili wake ikarudi kuwa kama nyama ya mwili wa mtoto mdogo, akawa ameponywa ukoma.
Hapo akamrudia yule mtu wa Mungu, yeye na msafara wake wote.
Alipofika, akasimama mbele yake na kusema, “Sasa nimetambua
kuwa hakuna Mungu duniani kote, ila katika Israeli.
na Basi, nakusihi, upokee zawadi ya mtumishi wako.”
“Kama aishivyo Bwana, ninayemtumikia, sitapokea kitu,” akajibu Elisha.
Naamani akamshurutisha, lakini yeye alizidi kukataa. Naamani akasema, “Kama umekataa, basi umruhusu mtumishi wako achukue udongo kadiri ya mzigo wa nyumbu wawili, kwa maana mtumishi
wako hatatolea tena miungu wengine sadaka ya kuteketezwa wala dhabihu, isipokuwa kwa Bwana peke yake.”
Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA
Zaburi 98:1, 2-3ab, 3cd4 (K. 2b)</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Bwana ameifunua haki yake mbele ya macho ya mataifa.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwimbieni Bwana wimbo mpya,
kwa maana amefanya mambo ya ajabu.
Mkono wake wa kuume, na mkono wake mtakatifu.
umemletea ushindi. K.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Bwana ameifunua haki yake mbele ya macho ya mataifa.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana ameujulisha ushindi wake;
mbele ya macho ya mataifa ameifunua haki yake.
Amekumbuka wema na uaminifu wake
kwa nyumba ya Israeli. K.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Bwana ameifunua haki yake mbele ya macho ya mataifa.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Misho yote ya dunia
imeuona wokovu wa Mungu wetu.
Mshangilieni Bwana, nchi yote;
pigeni kelele za furaha; imbeni zaburi. K.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Bwana ameifunua haki yake mbele ya macho ya mataifa.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA PILI
2 Timotheo 2:8-13</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika barua ya pili ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Timotheo</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mpendwa: Kumbuka ya kuwa Yesu Kristo wa ukoo wa Daudi amefufuka katika wafu kadiri ya Injili yangu.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa ajili yake navumilia mateso, hata
nikifungwa minyororo kama mvunja sheria.</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Mungu halifungwi. Kwa hiyo navumilia yote kwa ajili ya wateule, ili nao wapate wokovu katika Kristo Yesu, ndio utukufu wa milele.</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno hili linasadikika: 
Tukifa pamoja na Kristo, tutaishi pia pamoja naye.
Tukivumilia pamoja naye, tutatawala pamoja naye.o
Tukimkana yeye atatukana.
Hata tukiacha kumwamini,
yeye ni mwaminifu daima,
kwani hawezi kujikana mwenyewe.</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SHANGILIO LA INJILI
Wathesalonike 5:18</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Aleluya.
W. Aleluya.
K. Fanyeni shukrani katika yote:
hayo ndiyo atakayo Mungu
kwenu katika Kristo Yesu.
W. Aleluya.
INJILI
Luka 17:11-19</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Luka</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakati ule: Yesu alikuwa njiani kwenda Yerusalemu, alipita kati ya
Samaria na Galilaya.
Alipoingia kijiji kimoja watu kumi wenye ukoma walikutana naye.
Wakasinmama mbali kidogo, wakapaza sauti, wakasema,
“Yesu, Mwalimu! Utuhurumie!” Alipowaona, akawaambia,
“Nendeni, mkajionyeshe kwa makuhani.”
Basi walipokuwa wanakwenda walitakasika.
Mmoja wao alipoona ameponywa
akarudi akimtukuza Mungu kwa sauti kubwa;
akamwangukia kifudifudi miguuni pake, akamshukuru.
Naye alikuwa Msamaria.
Yesu akajibu, akasema, “Je, si wote kumi waliotakaswa?
Wale tisa wako wapi?
Hakupatikana mtu aliyerudi kumpa Mungu utukufu ila mgeni huyu?”
Akamwambia, “Simama, nenda zako; imani yako imekuponya.”</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Bwana</s></f>"}],
Text:"DOMINIKA YA ISHIRINI NA NANE MWAKA C"},{Guid:"deunmZ7f20umN/lAC4RfPw",Verses:[{Style:{Background:{Image:"WhatsApp Image 2025-10-04 at 07.57.08_80a6444a.jpg"}},
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>KIUMIA KĨA MĨRONGO ĪRĪ NA MŪGWANJA KIA MWAKA C</k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>GĪTHOMO KIA MBERE
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFF2F200>Habakuk 
</k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>1:2-3. 2: 2-4.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>GUTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RIA KIRORI HABAKUK:</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>I Mwathani, nĩ nginya hīndī i ngūtūüra ngūkayagĩra na ndünjigue? </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndüire ngūkayagīra nĩ ündū
wa maūndū ma ühinya, nawe ükaaga kūhonokania. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Utümaga ndĩonere gūgīkwo üüru, na </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ükandekereria nyonage maūndū ma ūremi nĩ ündü kī? </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩündū-rī, ühoro wa gūtahwo na wa ühinya nocio itűire mbere yakwa, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kügurumükanīrűo na ngiano, o na ngarari.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake Mwathani akīnjokeria ühoro, akīnjīra atīri:</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Andika kīoneki gīkī mbaū-inī igūrü na ndemwa
nene, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nī getha ithomeke wega iteküriga arīa megūcithoma o magīteng’era. </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nii ündū-rī, kīoneki gīki nīĩ kia ihinda rīřīa gīathĩřĩirio, </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>narîo ihinda rīu rīhikīte rīkinye, naguo ühoro wakīo ndür</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ỉ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> nganja; </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na kingīonwo ta gīgüikara müno gīgīkahingio-ri, </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wee 
gīta o gükirirīria ügīetereire, nĩ undu 
ti-itheru gītiri hingo gītakahingio, </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na gītigatīrio, Atiriri, ngoro ya üria müüru nĩ ta </s></f>"},{ID:18,Style:{Background:{Luminosity:-20}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gütua ithuite
mikwa, na ti njerekereru thīini wake; </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>no mũndŭ ürīa műthingu agatüürio muoyo nĩ ündũ wa
gwitikia gwake.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nīcio ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>THABURI YA GÜCOKERŪO
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFF2F200>Thaburi 
</k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>95: 1-2; 6-7; 8-9.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>ICOKIA : </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Mwathani, tūhotithie gūthikīrīria mügambo waku.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>1.Ukani, tūkūngūiye Mwathani tūkenete, tūkīanīrīre ndūmba iitũ ya ihiga, </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yo nyene ūhonokio  witu,. Nĩ tūkinye ūthi</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>-inî wake twī na ngatho, </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tũmwanirie na gikeno tükiinaga nyîmbo cia thaburi.</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>ICOKIA : </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Mwathani, tūhotithie gūthikīrīria mügambo waku. </k></c></s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>2.Giükeni, tūmūthathaiye, tūmūinamirire; </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ni tūturirie Mwathani ndu, o ūcio Mūtūūmbi, </s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ni gūkorūo we niwe Ngai witū, na nî ithui kirindi gīake kwirithiria, </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ni ithu</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ỉ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> ng’ondu iria atungataga na guoko gwake,</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>ICOKIA : </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Mwathani, tūhotithie gūthikīrīria mügambo waku</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>. </k></s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>3.Umūthi, na arī korūo mwetikira kūigua mūgambo wake! </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tigai kū</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>mia ngoro cianyu, ta ūria</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mwekire kūu Meriba, mūthĩ ta ūrīa mwari Masa, </s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kūu werū-ini; hindi iria maithe manyu </s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maangeririe, 
makindoria, na magīkīona wiko wakwa.</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>ICOKIA : </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Mwathani, tūhotithie gūthikīrīria mügambo waku. </k></c></s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>GĪTHOMO KĪA IGĨRI
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>2</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFF2F200> Timotheo</k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200> 
1: 6-8,13- 14.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>GŨTHOMA MARUA MA MŨTHURE PAUL MARIA MAANDĪKĪIRŪO TIMOTHEO</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwendwo wakwa, nĩ ngũküririkania atī ühuhagīrīrie </s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kīheo kīrīa üheetwo nĩ Ngai kiumanīte na Wega wake, </s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>O kīu wagīire nakīo na ūndű wa ürīa ndakūigīrīire moko. </s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Amu-rī, Ngai ndaigana gūtühe muoyo wa gūtūma tūiguage guoya, </s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>no makīria nĩ wa gütwīkīra hinya na wendani na üügī wa ngoro. </s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hakīrī üguo-rī, ndűkanaconoke ükiumbüra ühoro wa Mwathani witū, </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kana ūconoke nī ündū wakwa nīĩ njohetwo nī ündū wake; </s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>no riri, itikira künyariranīrio na nii ni ündü wa Uhoro-ürīa-Mwega, </s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kūringana na üria üheagwo hinya nĩ Ngai.</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Rümagia wega mohoro marīa maagīrīru monanīrīirio o mbere, </s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o mara waiguire na niĩ, wĩ na wĩtīkio 
na wendani, 
o iria irĩ thĩin</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>i</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> wa Kristū Yesu. </s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Menyagīrīra wega ündū ürĩa mwega 
waigirűũo kürī 
wee ūüramatage, </s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ügīteithagio nĩ Muoyo Mütheru ürīa ütüüraga thĩinī witü.</s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nicio ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>RUIMBO RŪA INJIRI
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>1</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFF2F200> John </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>5, 4.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>Alleluya, Alleluya.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kīrīa gĩothe gīciarītwo nĩ Ngai nĩ gītoragia ūhoro wa gükü thĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>naguo ũtoria 
ürīa ūtoretie ühoro wa thĩ nĩ atīrīrī: nī gwīitīkia witü. </s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>Alleluya</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>GITHOMO KĪA INJIRI
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFF2F200>Luka </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>37: 5-10.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>GUTHOMA INJIRI YA MŪTHURE LUKA :</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hindī io, atumwo makīira Mwathani atīrī: Tuongerere wītikio. </s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake Mwathani akiuga atīrĩ :
Müngīkorūo mūrī na wītīkio </s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>üiganaine na kahĩndī ga karatari-rī, mwera mūkūyū ūyũ atīrī:</s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Küürüka, ükehande iria-inī riria inene, naguo no ümüigue. </s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na nĩ mündū ürīkũ wanyu üngīkorūo
ari na ndungata ikūümūcimbīra na müraű, </s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kana ikamürīithīrĩa mbüri, nayo yainūka yumīte mügūnda, </s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akamira atīrī: Üka o rīu, üikare metha-inĩ ürīe irio ? </s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Githĩ ndangīmīira atīrī: Thondeka irio, ndie; na wihotore, ündehere irio, </s></f>"},{ID:70,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o nginya ndiīkorūo ndīkītie kürīa na kūnyua; </s></f>"},{ID:71,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na thutha ücio, 
wee ücoke ürīe na ünyue ? 
Anga nĩ egűcokeria ndungata io </s></f>"},{ID:73,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ngatho nīi ündū nĩ mkīte maündū marīa yathītwo ? </s></f>"},{ID:74,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Noguo o na inyui-rī, mwarīkia gwika maūndũ </s></f>"},{ID:75,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>marīa mothe mwathītwo,
ugagai atīrī: 
Türīndungata itari uumithio; </s></f>"},{ID:77,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ twikīte o maündū marīa twagiriirüo nĩ gwīka.</s></f>"},{ID:78,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s></f>"}],Style:{Background:{Image:"WhatsApp Image 2025-10-04 at 07.57.08_80a6444a.jpg"}},
