Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GiTHOMO KIA MBERE
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>2</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846> Athamaki 
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>5: 14 - 17.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>GŪTHOMA KUUKA IBUKU RĪA KERI RIA ATHAMAKI :</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Matuküinī macio, Naaman agīgīikürüka, agīītobokia </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>metobokia mügwanja Jordano o ta oguo</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mūndū ücio wa Ngai oigīte; naguo mwiri wake ükimūcokerera </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ükīhaana o ta mwirī wa kaana kanini, agīgīthera, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake akīhündūka, agīcoka he mündū ücio wa Ngai, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>we mwene, o na gīkundi gīake gīothe, agīkīrügama mbere yake, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akiuga üú: Tiitherü rĩu ndĩ kūmenya atī gūtirī Ngai üngī gükū thĩ guothe, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tiga o gükū Israeli ; na tondū ücio ndagūthaitha wītikīre atī niī, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndungata yaku,ngühe nduhi. Nowe akiuga atīrĩ: 
Ota ürĩa Mwathani atūűraga muoyo, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o we ürīa nii ndügamaga mbere yake rī, ndirī kīndū ingīamūkīra. </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake Naaman agīkīmūringīrīria mūno oe, no akīrega.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake Naaman akiuga atīiri: Kūngīkorūo ti üguo-rī, </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndagūthaitha üreke nīī, ndungata yaku, ‘heo tiri, mĩrigo iirī ya nyümbū; </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ ündūrī, niĩ ndungata yaku, gwata rīu, ndikarutīra ngai ingī ihaki rĩa njino, </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kana igongona rĩa mūthemba o na ürīkū, tiga o Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nīcio ciugo cia Mwathani,</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>THABURI YA GUCOKERŪO
Thaburi 
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>98: 1; 2-3a; 3b4.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>ICOKIA : </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Ühonokania wa Mwathani nĩ wa kūhonokia andü othe.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ī kiarūkei kūinīira Mwathani ruimbo rūerū,</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tondū nīĩ ekīte maūndū ma magegania gwake kwa ürio, gwake mwene, nikuo kūmūhonokanirie, </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o kuo gīcoka kīu grake gītheru.</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA : </s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Ühonokania wa Mwathani nĩ wa kūhonokia andü othe.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>2.Mwathani nĩ atūmīte ūhonokania wake ūmenyeke wega; </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ūthingu wake ni aūguūririe maitho inī ma ndūriri, </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kūririkana ni akīririkanite ūtugi wake o na wihokeku wake, iria onagia nyũmba ya Israeli.</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>ICOKIA : </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Ühonokania wa Mwathani nĩ wa kūhonokia andü othe.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>3. Uhonokania wa Ngai witū-rī, ituri ciothe cia thĩ riu nī ciwonete. </s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Inyĩ and</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> othe a thī, anirirai Mwathani na gīkeno; </s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tumūkai, mūkūngūiye; i-ni, mūkīmūgooce na nyīmbo.</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA : </s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Ühonokania wa Mwathani nĩ wa kūhonokia andü othe.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĪTHOMO KIA IGĪRĪ
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>2 Timotheo </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>2: 8- 13.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>GŪTHOMA MARŪA MA MŪTHURE PAUL MARĪA MAANDĪKIIRUO TIMOTHEO</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwendwo wakwa, tūüra üririkanaga Yesu Kristü, </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>we wariükire akiuma kūrī arīa akuũ, na aarī wa rūciaro rũa Davide, </s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o ta ürīa kwonanagio nĩ Ohoro-ürīa - mwega ndüire “hunjagia. Uhoro ūcio - ī,</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nīguo ndüire “nyariragīrūo, o nginya ngaya kuohwo ta ndĩ műgeri ngero; </s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Índi Ohoro wa Ngai ti muohe, Tondü wa üguo-rī, ngiragīrīria maündű mothe </s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ ündū wa andū arīa athure, nĩ getha o nao makahonokio na ühonokio </s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ūrīa uumaga gwĩ Kristũ Yesu, na magīe na riri ürīa ütagathira. </s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ohoro üyū nĩ wa kwīhokeka, atīrī: Tüngīkorūo nĩ twakuire hamwe nake, </s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ tügatüüra muoyo hamwe nake : na tũngīkirīriria-rī, </s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ tügacoka gūthamaka hamwe nake : īndī tüngīmūkaana-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o nake aaya gütükaana na ithuī: na tūngĩaga kwihokeka-rī, </s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>we mwene atüüraga arīo mwīhokeku; nĩ ündū ndangīhota gwīkaana ürīa atariï.</s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nīcio ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>RŪIMBO RŪA INJIRI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>1</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846> Peter </s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>2, 9.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Alleluya, Alleluya.</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846> </s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Inyuī mūrī rüruka rūthurītwo, na thiritū ya athīnjīri-Ngai </s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ya nyūmba ya mūthamaki, mürī rürīrī rūtherű : 
mūhunjanagirie mawega make, </s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>we wamwītire muume nduma-inī
mūtonye ütheri-inī wake. </s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Alleluya.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GITHOMO KIA INJIRI
Luka </s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>17: 11 - 19.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŪTHÒMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE LUKA :</s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na gügīkinya atīri, hĩnđi Īrĩa maathiaga Jerusalem, </s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agītuikanīria Samaria na Galilea. Na agītonya mūcií ümwe, </s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agītūngwo nĩ arūme ikūmi marūarīte mangū, </s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na maarügamīte haraya: makīanīrīra
na mūgambo münene, makiuga atīrí: </s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu mũnene witū, tūigwīre tha. Nake aamona akīmera atīrī:</s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Thiĩi mükeyonanie kürī asacerdoti. Na gügītuika atīrī, </s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hĩndī íiria maathiaga, makīhonio magīthera. </s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na ümwe wao ona atī nĩ ahonetio, </s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akīhűndūka agīkumagia Ngai na mügambo mūnene; </s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agīturumithia üthiü thĩ o magūrü-inī ma Yesu, </s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akimūcokagīria ngatho: nake aarī Müsamaria.</s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake Yesu agīcokia akiuga atīrī: Githī othe ikümi matinatherio ? </s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kaï acio angī kenda marī ha ?</s></f>"},{ID:70,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Githī gütinakorūo mūndū wao Ücokete gūkumia Ngai, tiga ūyü mūgeni ?</s></f>"},{ID:71,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake akīmwira atīrī: Okīra withiire; gwītikia gwaku nīkuo gwatūma ühone.</s></f>"},{ID:72,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injiri theru ya Mwathani,</s></f>"}],Style:{Background:{Image:"WhatsApp Image 2025-10-04 at 07.57.08_80a6444a.jpg"}},
