YA MWAKA C</k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA KWANZA
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>2 Wafalme 5:14-17</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika kitabu cha pili cha Wafalme</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Siku zile: Naamani [jemedari wa jeshi la mfalme wa Aramu]</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>alishuka, akajizamisha katika Yordani mara saba kadiri ya neno</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>la Elisha mtu wa Mungu. Mara nyama ya mwili wake </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ikarudi kuwa kama nyama ya mwili wa mtoto mdogo, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akawa ameponywa ukoma.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hapo akamrudia yule mtu wa Mungu, yeye na msafara wake wote.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alipofika, akasimama mbele yake na kusema, “Sasa nimetambua</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kuwa hakuna Mungu duniani kote, ila katika Israeli.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na Basi, nakusihi, upokee zawadi ya mtumishi wako.”</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>“Kama aishivyo Bwana, ninayemtumikia, sitapokea kitu,” akajibu Elisha.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Naamani akamshurutisha, lakini yeye alizidi kukataa. Naamani akasema, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>“Kama umekataa, basi umruhusu mtumishi wako achukue udongo </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kadiri ya mzigo wa nyumbu wawili, kwa maana mtumishi</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wako hatatolea tena miungu wengine sadaka ya kuteketezwa </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wala dhabihu, isipokuwa kwa Bwana peke yake.”</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA
Zaburi 
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>98:1, 2-3ab, 3cd4 (K. 2b)</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. </s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Bwana ameifunua haki yake mbele ya macho ya mataifa.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwimbieni Bwana wimbo mpya,
kwa maana amefanya mambo ya ajabu.</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mkono wake wa kuume,  Na mkono wake mtakatifu. umemletea ushindi. K.</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. </s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Bwana ameifunua haki yake mbele ya macho ya mataifa.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana ameujulisha ushindi wake;
mbele ya macho ya mataifa ameifunua haki yake.</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Amekumbuka wema na uaminifu wake
kwa nyumba ya Israeli. K.</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. </s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Bwana ameifunua haki yake mbele ya macho ya mataifa.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Misho yote ya dunia
imeuona wokovu wa Mungu wetu.</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mshangilieni Bwana, nchi yote;
pigeni kelele za furaha; imbeni zaburi. K.</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. </s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Bwana ameifunua haki yake mbele ya macho ya mataifa.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA PILI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>2 Timotheo 2:8-13</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika barua ya pili ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Timotheo</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mpendwa: Kumbuka ya kuwa Yesu Kristo </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wa ukoo wa Daudi amefufuka katika wafu kadiri ya Injili yangu.</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa ajili yake navumilia mateso, </s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hata nikifungwa minyororo kama mvunja sheria.</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Mungu halifungwi. Kwa hiyo navumilia yote kwa ajili ya wateule, </s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ili nao wapate wokovu katika Kristo Yesu, </s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndio utukufu wa milele.
Neno hili linasadikika: </s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tukifa pamoja na Kristo, tutaishi pia pamoja naye.</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tukivumilia pamoja naye, tutatawala pamoja naye.</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tukimkana yeye atatukana.
Hata tukiacha kumwamini,</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yeye ni mwaminifu daima,
kwani hawezi kujikana mwenyewe.</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SHANGILIO LA INJILI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Wathesalonike 5:18</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. </s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Aleluya.
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846>W. </s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Aleluya.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Fanyeni shukrani katika yote:
hayo ndiyo atakayo Mungu
kwenu katika Kristo Yesu.</s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>W. </s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Aleluya.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>INJILI
Luka </s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>17:11-19</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Luka</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakati ule: </s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu alikuwa njiani kwenda Yerusalemu,</s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Alipita kati ya
Samaria na Galilaya.</s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alipoingia kijiji kimoja watu kumi wenye ukoma walikutana naye.</s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakasimama mbali kidogo, wakapaza sauti, wakasema,</s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>“Yesu, Mwalimu! Utuhurumie!” Alipowaona, akawaambia,</s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>“Nendeni, mkajionyeshe kwa makuhani.”</s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Basi walipokuwa wanakwenda walitakasika.</s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mmoja wao alipoona ameponywa</s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akarudi akimtukuza Mungu kwa sauti kubwa;</s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akamwangukia kifudifudi miguuni pake, akamshukuru.</s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Naye alikuwa Msamaria.
Yesu akajibu, akasema, </s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>“Je, si wote kumi waliotakaswa?
Wale tisa wako wapi?</s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hakupatikana mtu aliyerudi kumpa Mungu utukufu ila mgeni huyu?”</s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akamwambia, “Simama, nenda zako; imani yako imekuponya.”</s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Bwana</s></f>"}],Style:{Background:{Image:"WhatsApp Image 2025-10-04 at 07.57.08_80a6444a.jpg"}},
Text:"DOMINIKA YA ISHIRINI NA NANE YA MWAKA C"},{Guid:"kxvX65ShNUGrSTOIlcf/RA",Verses:[{Style:{Background:{Image:"KIUMIA.jpg",Luminosity:0}}},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĪTHOMO KIA MBERE
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Thama 17: 8- 13.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:3,Style:{Background:{Transition:4,Duration:10000}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>GŪTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RIA THAMA:</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846> </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Matukü-inī macio, Aamalek magīūka, 
makīhűranīra na andű a Israeli kūu Refidim. </s></f>"},{ID:5,Style:{Background:{Transition:0}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake Musa akiira Joshua atīri:
Tūthurīre andū, műthiĩ mūkahūrane. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nà Aaamalek; 
rūciŭ nĩguo niï na nii ngathi?</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kūrügama kīrīma igūrũ ngwatīte rüthanju rũa Ngai na guoko. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Joshua agīgiīka o ta üguo erītwo nī Musa, agīkīhūrana na Aamalek;</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nao Musa marī na Haaron na Hur, magithii kĩrīma-inī kiu igūrū, </s></f>"},{ID:10,Style:{Background:{Transition:5}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na gūgīkinya atīri: atī hĩndī îrīa 
Musa aambararia guoko gwake na igūrŭ, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>andū a lsraeli makahootana, na rīrīa aagüithia</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>guoko gükarora thĩ, hĩndi io Aamalek nao makahootana.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>No rīrī, moko ma Musa makīnoga ; </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>andü magīkīoya ihiga makīmūigīra thĩ, akīrīikarira ; </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na Haaron na Hur makīmūnyita moko mamaambararītie na igürü, </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ümwe akamūnyita guoko kümwe, 
nake urīa üngī akamünyita guoko kürĩa küngī: </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>namo moko make magīikara o ro uguo 
marumetio o nginya hĩndī irĩa riūa riathüire.   </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nĩcio ciugo cia Mwathani,</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>THABURI YA GŪCOKERÜO
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Thaburi 
121: 1-2; 3-4; 5-6:-8.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA : </s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Uteithio witũ umanaga kwa Mwathani</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846>.</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ ngūtiira maitho ndorererie irīma-inīi: i ūteithio wakwa ūgūkiuma na kū? </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Uteithio wakwa-rī, uumaga kwi Mwathani, üria wombire igūrū na thĩ,</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>ICOKIA : </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Uteithio witũ umanaga kwa Mwathani.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>We ndarī hĩndī angīreka kūgūrū gwaku gūtirūke: </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ūcio mūmenyereri waku ndarī hingo angīcūnga. </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mūmenyereri wa Israeli-rī, 
ndari hingo angicūnga kana ahĩtwo ni toro.</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>ICOKIA : </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Uteithio witũ umanaga kwa Mwathani.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>3. Mwathani niwe mūkumenyereri; Mwathani-ri, </s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ni kiigunyi harī wee, mwena waku wa ūrio.</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mūthenya, wee ndūngīringīka ni riūa, 
kana ūtukū ūringīke nī mweri.</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA : </s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Uteithio witũ umanaga kwa Mwathani.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>4. Uüru wothe nī Mwathani ūikūriragīra; 
muoyo waku nī arīu</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>menyagīrîra, </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ukiumagara ūthi, na ūgīcoka na mūcii, </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani no arikumenyagirira, 
kuuma rīu nginya tene na tene.</s></f>"},{ID:35,Style:{Background:{Transition:3}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA : </s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Uteithio witũ umanaga kwa Mwathani.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:36,Style:{Background:{Transition:3}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>GITHOMO KIA IGIRĪ
</k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>2 Timotheo 
3: 14–2</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>GŪTHOMA MARUA MA MUTHURE PAUL MARIA MAANDIKIIRUO TIMOTHEO:</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwendwo wakwa, tù</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>ra ürūmītie maūndũ marĩa wirutīte, </s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ükamamenya wega atī ma ma; </s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>niĩ üui
arīa werutire maündu macio harī o, </s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ükamenya atī gwata hĩndi irĩa warī kaana, ütűire űmenyete</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Maandīko marīa matheru,o marīa mahotaga gükūűhĩgia, </s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nīguo ükahonokio nĩ ündū wa kwīhoka Kristū Yesu. </s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Uhoro o wothe wandikītwo Maandiko-inī nĩ </s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wekīrirūo nĩ Ngai ngoro-inī ya műwandīki, </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na wĩ na kīguni ühoro-inī wa kürutana, na wa kūmenyithia andũ üüru wao, </s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na wa kūmakaania, o na wa kūmamenyeria </s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mītūũrīre irīa îringaine na ūthingu; </s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ getha mündũ wa Ngai atuike mūkinyanīru o gukinyanīra, </s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na aikarage athagathagītwo küna, nîguo arutage wira üria wothe mwega.</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndakwīra atīri na ma, Ngai arī ho, o nake Kristü Yesu,</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o we ürīa ügacirithia andü arīa marī muoyo o na arīa makuīte, </s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na nĩ ündü wa üria akaguüranīrio na athamakage, atĩrī, kīhunjagie Uhoro wa Ngai, </s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na wīkagīre kīyo hĩndi iria njagiriru o na irĩa itarī njagīrīru; </s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ningī rūithagīria andü úüru wao, na ümakaanagie, </s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ũmahatagīririe, ūgīkiragīrīria müno o ükĩrutanaga.</s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nīcio ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>RUIMBO RUA INJIRI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Aheberea 4, 12.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Alleluya, Alleluya. </k></c></s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mügambo wa Ngai wĩ muoyo, na wĩ na ũhoti, 
na nĩ ühiühaga gūkūürana meciria ma ngoro. </s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Alleluya.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>GITHOMO KIA INJIRI
</k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Luka 18: 1 -8.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>GÜTHOMA INJIRI YA MUTHURE LUKA :</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hind îo Yesu akīhe arutwo ake ühoro na ngerekano, </s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akamarute atī nĩ maagīriirūo nĩ kühoyaga</s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ngai hingo ciothe mategūtirika; akiuga atīrī: </s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Itüüra rimwe nĩ kwari mütuanīri cira ürīa ütetigagīra Ngai, </s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kana agaconokera mūndü: na rĩĩ, itūüra-ini rīu kwarī műtumia wa ndigwa; </s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>riake nĩathiaga harī we kaingī, akamwira atīri: </s></f>"},{ID:70,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndihiria kürĩ mündü üria türi üth</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> nake. </s></f>"},{ID:71,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake akīrega ihinda : no thutha agīcoka akīira na ngoro atīri: </s></f>"},{ID:72,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>O na itetigagīra Ngai, na ndiconokagīra mūndū, </s></f>"},{ID:73,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>indī tondü m</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>tumia üyū wa ndigwa nî andangaga-rī, nĩ ngũmürīhīria, </s></f>"},{ID:74,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ getha atige künogagia nĩ güükaga haha hingo ciothe. </s></f>"},{ID:75,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake Mwathani akiuga atīri: lguai üria műtuanīri cira ūücio müüru oiga. </s></f>"},{ID:76,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Githĩ nake Ngai ndangīrihĩria and</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> ake arīa athurĩire, </s></f>"},{ID:77,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o arīa mamūkayagīra m</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>thenya o na ütukū, o na angīmaikaria ihinda? </s></f>"},{ID:78,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ngümwira atīri, nĩ arīmarīhiria narua, No riri, </s></f>"},{ID:79,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>rirĩa Mürü wa mündũ agoka, anga nĩ agakora andü metīkītie gükü thĩ?</s></f>"},{ID:80,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injiri theru  ya Mwathani,</s></f>"}],Style:{Background:{Image:"WhatsApp Image 2025-10-04 at 07.57.08_80a6444a.jpg",Transition:0,Duration:7009}},
Text:"KīUMIA KīA MīRONGO īRī NA KENDA KīA MWAKA C"},{Guid:"UWK5aauPSEeX2W2G603Hkg",Verses:[{Style:{Background:{Image:"DOMINIKA.jpg",Luminosity:0}}},{ID:2,Style:{Background:{Image:"WhatsApp Image 2025-10-04 at 07.57.08_80a6444a.jpg",Luminosity:0}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA KWANZA
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Kutoka 17:8-13</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika kitabu cha Kutoka</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Siku zile: 
Waamaleki walitokea 
wakashambulia Israeli huko Refidim.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Basi Musa akamwambia Yoshua, “Chagua watu, na kesho asubuhi, utoke kupigana na Amaleki. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mimi nitasimama juu ya kilima, na ile fimbo
ya Mungu itakuwa mkononi mwangu.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>“Yoshua akafanya kama alivyoambiwa na Musa, akatoka kupigana na Amaleki.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Musa, Haruni na Huri wakawa wamepanda juu ya kilima.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ikawa, Musa alipoinua mikono yake, Israeli ilishinda. </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alipoiacha mikono kushuka, Amaleki ilishinda. </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa kuwa mikono ya Musa ilichoka, walitwaa jiwe, wakaliweka chini yake. </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akaketi juu yake, Haruni na Huri wakaitegemeza mikono yake, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mmoja upande huu, na mwingine upande huo. </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na hivi mikono ya Musa haikulegea tena mpaka jua lilipokuchwa. </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yoshua akamshinda Amaleki na watu wake kwa makali ya upanga.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Zaburi 
121:1-2, 3 4. 5-6, 7-8 </k></c></s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Msaada wetu kwa jina la Bwana,
aliyezifanya mbingu na dunia.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ninainua macho yangu niitazame milima.
Msaada wangu utatoka wapi?</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Msaada wangu watoka kwa Bwana,
aliyezifanya mbingu na dunia. K.</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Msaada wetu kwa jina la Bwana,
aliyezifanya mbingu na dunia.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Asiuache mguu wako uteleze,
asisinzie yule anayekulinda.</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Naam, hatasinzia, wala hatalala usingizi
Mlinzi wa Israeli. K.</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>K.</k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F> Msaada wetu kwa jina la Bwana,
aliyezifanya mbingu na dunia.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana ni mlinzi wako, Bwana ni uvuli wako
mkono wako wa kulia.</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mchana jua halitakuchoma,
wala mwezi usiku. K</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Msaada wetu kwa jina la Bwana,
aliyezifanya mbingu na dunia.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana atakukinga na uovu wowote,
atalinda roho yako.</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana atakulinda unapotoka na unaporudi,
tangu sasa na hata milele.K.</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Msaada wetu kwa jina la Bwana,
aliyezifanya mbingu na dunia.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA PILI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>2 Timotheo 3:144:2</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Somo katika barua ya pili ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Timotheo</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mpendwa: Wewe uyashikilie uliyofundishwa na kuyaamini;</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>umewajua waliokufundisha.
Tangu utoto wako umeyajua Maandiko Matakatifu.</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nayo yana uwezo wa kukupatia hekima upate</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kuokoka kwa nguvu ya imani iliyomo katika Kristo Yesu.</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kila andiko lililotungwa kwa pumzi ya Mungu lafaa pia kwa kufundisha. </s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kukanusha makosa, kuwaongoza watu na kuwazoeza njia ya uadilifu.</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hivyo mtu wa Mungu anatengenezwa na kutayarishwa kufanya kila tendo jema.</s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nakusihi sana mbele ya Mungu na Kristo </s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu atakayekuja kuwahukumu wazima na wafu, </s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kwa ujio wake na ufalme wake:
litangaze neno, sisitiza, </s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hakikisha, onya, himiza kwa uvumilivu wote na elimu.</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SHANGILIO LA INJILI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Waebrania 4:12</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Neno la Mungu ni hai, lina nguvu;
laweza kupambanua nia na maono ya mioyo.</s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>W. Aleluya.
W. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>INJILI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Luka 18:1-8</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo a Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Luka</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakati ule: Yesu aliwafundisha kwa mfano ya</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwamba ni lazima kusali daima bila kuchoka. </s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alisema, “Katika mji mmoja kulikuwa na hakimu</s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>asiyemcha Mungu wala kumjali mtu.</s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na katika mji huo kulikuwa na mama mjane, </s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>naye alimwendea tena na tena akisema, </s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>‘Nipatie haki kwa adui yangu.
Siku nyingi hakutaka, kisha akajiambia,</s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ingawa simchi Mungu wala simjali mtu, 
kwa kuwa mjane huyu ananisumbua </s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nitahakikisha amepata haki yake, 
ama sivyo atacndelea kuja hadi anichoshe.”</s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana akaendelea kusema,
“Sikilizeni asemayo hakimu mbaya. </s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na Mungu, je, hatawapatia haki
wateule wake wanaomlilia mchana na usiku?</s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Je, atakawia kuwasaidia?
Nawaambieni, atawapatia haki upesi.</s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Lakini Mwana wa Mtu atakapokuja, je, atapata imani duniani?</s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f>"}],
Text:"DOMINIKA YA ISHIRINI NA TISA MWAKA C
"},{Guid:"JD33MzloT02yG/HVfTXKVw",Verses:[{Style:{Background:{Image:"SACRED HEART GAKIRA CATHOLIC CHURCH  KIUMIA 2.png",Luminosity:0}},
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFF3F3FFF><kFFFF0000>.</k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GITHOMO KIA MBERE
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Sirach 35: 12 - 14. 16-19</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GUTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RIA SIRACH:</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani nĩ m</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>thamaki na ndakoragwo akīrora ngürani ya andu, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ aroraga andű othe na maitho mamwe, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na nĩ aiguaga ihoya ria mundú muhatīririe. </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ni aiguaga ihoya ria mwana wa ngoriai na rĩa műtumia wa ndigwa. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mündů üria ütungataga Ngai wega nĩ akamükīrūo</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na tha, na ihoya riake nĩ rígakinya matu-inī. </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ihoya rīa mũndú műhoreri nĩ rigakinya matu-inī, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ndagakorūo na gīkeno rītakinyīte o kūu matu-inī. </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na ndangītiga kūhoya Ngai ürīa ürī igūrű atamüiguite.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nīcio ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>THABURI YA GUCOKERUO
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Thaburi 34: 1-2; 15-1 6; 18 na 22.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA : </s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Mwathani athikagīriria mahoya ma mũndū mūthíni.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>1.Nĩndirigathaga Mwathani o hingo ciothe; </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kanua gakwa kūmūkumia gatirī hĩndī gatarīmūkumagia,</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> 
Mwathani nowe ngoro yakwa í rirahagira: </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>aria ahoreri mariiguaga ūguo magakena.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA : </s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Mwathani athikagīriria mahoya ma mũndū mūthíni.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>2.Maitho ma Mwathani merekeire na kuri aria athingu, </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na matu make magategerūo kiriro kíao,</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Arīa mekaga ūūru-rī, ūthiű wa Mwathani ni kumomira momiire, </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>atī ang’ūrie riitwa rīao ritikaririkanwo gūkū thi.</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA : </s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Mwathani athikagīriria mahoya ma mũndū mūthíni.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>3. Mwathani nĩ akoragwo hakuhi na aria athuthīku ngoro; </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>acio maherete muoyo-rī, agakímahonokia, </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani nĩ gūkūūra aku</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>raga ngoro cia ndungata ciake; </s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>arīa marahagīra harī we gūtirī ūngituwo mwīhia,</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA : </s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Mwathani athikagīriria mahoya ma mũndū mūthíni.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GITHOMO KIA IGIRI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>2 Timotheo 4: 6 -8. 16- 18,</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GUTHOMA MARUA MA MUTHURE PAUL MARIA MAANDIKIIRUO TIMOTHEO :</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwendwo wakwa, thakame yakwa nī yambīrīirie güitwo ítuīke ya igongona, </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na hingo yakwa nī nginyu ndímeherere. </s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ni ndūite mbaara īra njega, nakīo </s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kīhītahītano gīakwa-rī, nĩ nginyīte gīturi gīakio.</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>naguo ürutani ürīa wa Witikio-rī, nĩ ndũire ndiűmenyereire. </s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Gwata rīĩu nĩ njigiirűo thũmbĩ íria ya üthingu, </s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o īrīa Mwathani, we mütuanīri cira na kīhooto, aka”he Müthenya ücio: na to nií nyiki, </s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>no ningī ahe andū othe arīa magakorűo </s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>matanyīte kügu</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>ranīrio gwake me na wendo.</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Rīrīa ndatwarirűo cira-inī ria mbere-rī, hatirī</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mündū o na ümwe wandūgamīrīire: ni kūndiganīria</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maandiganīirie othe. Maroaga g</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>tarīrūo ūndü ücio ! </s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>No Mwathani nīwe wandūgamīrīire akĩnjīkīra
hinya, </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ni getha ndümirīri íria ya Ngai īhunjio imemereke wega na </s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ūndũ wakwa, nao andű othe a Ndūrirī mamiigue: </s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ngīgītunyūkithio kanua-inī ka mürüthi ücio. </s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake Mwathani nīwe ükandunyűkithia
ündū-inī ürīa wothe mūüru, </s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na a’honokie nīguo ngakinya üthamaki-inī wake wa lgūrū: </s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nake we arogoocagwo mĩndī na mĩndī. Nĩ gütuîke guo</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>icio nicio ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>RUIMBO RUA INJIRI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Mathayo 11, 25.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Alleluya, Alleluya, </k></c></s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Awa, Mwathani wa lgūrü o na thĩ, ndakūgatha nĩ ündũ </s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ üguüríirie tűkenge maūndű ma Üthamaki waku. </s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Alleluya.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GITHOMO KIA INJIRI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Luka 18: 9- 14.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GUTHOMA INJIRI YA MÜTHURE LUKA :</s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hĩndī ío, Yesu akīarīria andü ngerekano îno ní ündu wa andū amwe: </s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nanī o arīa metuaga athingu magīcambagia arīa angī.</s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>And</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ủ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> erī nĩ maambatire magīthií ihoero makahoe Ngai : </s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ümwe aarī Mũfariseo, nake ürīa üngī aarī Müpublikano. </s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake Müfariseo ücio akīrügama, akīhoya üű na mwiirowa ngoro: </s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ngai, nĩ ndakūgatha ní ündū ndihaanaine </s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na andū arīa angī; tondú o nĩ aría-ma, </s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ti athingu na nĩ itharia; 
o na tondū ndihaana ta műndū űyũ mūpublikano,</s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Niĩ-ri, ndihingaga kūrīa irio kerī o kiumia; na nĩ ndutaga gīcunjí gīa ikümi kĩa indo ciothe iria nyonaga, </s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>No műndü ũcio  mwītia mbia cia igoti, arügamīte o haraya, </s></f>"},{ID:70,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndaigana o na gūtiira maitho make na Igürū, </s></f>"},{ID:71,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>no kwihora ehürahürire gīthüri, akiuga atīri: </s></f>"},{ID:72,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ngai, njiguīra tha, nií mündũ mwīhia., Ngũmwĩra atīrī: </s></f>"},{ID:73,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mündŭ ucio nĩ aaikürűkire akīinüka gwake mücií atuītwo mūthingu gükira ücio üngī: </s></f>"},{ID:74,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ gükorüo o mũndu üría witüügagīria nī akanyihio; no ürīa wīnyihagia nĩ agatüügīrio.</s></f>"},{ID:75,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injiri theru ya Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:76,Style:{Background:{Image:"SACRED HEART GAKIRA CATHOLIC CHURCH  KIUMIA.png",Luminosity:5}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFF3F3FFF>.</c></s></f>"}],Style:{Background:{Image:"WhatsApp Image 2025-10-04 at 07.57.08_dd6cdcec.jpg"}},
Text:"KIUMIA KIA MIRONGO ITATÜ KĨA MWAKA C
"},{Guid:"6xBF91IBa0Wjir0MY36yOg",Verses:[{Style:{Background:{Image:"SACRED HEART GAKIRA CATHOLIC CHURCH DOMINIKA.png",Luminosity:5}},
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFF3F3FFF><kFFFF0000>.</k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA KWANZA        
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Yoshua bin Sira 35:12-14, 16-18 </k></c></s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika kitabu cha Yoshua bin Sira.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana ni Mungu wa haki, wala hakuna kwake sifa ya upendeleo. </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hatampendelea mtu dhidi ya maskini, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>naye atasikiliza ombi la aliyetendewa vibaya. </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Anaijali dua ya yatima, na mjane akiwa anamwaga maneno.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwenye kuabudu inavyoridhisha, atapokelewa; </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ombi lake litafika hadi mawinguni. </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Sala ya mnyenyekevu hupenya mawingu; </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>bila kumkaribia Mungu na kuwa kwake, haifarijiki. </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Haitakaa pembeni mpaka Aliye Juu atakapoijia </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kuwaamulia wenye haki na kufanya hukumu. </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Naye Bwana hatachelewa, kama aendae vitani hatakuwa mvumilivu kwao.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA	
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Zaburi 34</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. </s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Mnyonge alilia, naye Bwana akamsikiliza.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nitamtukuza Bwana kila wakati; sifa zake zi kinyuani mwangu daima. </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nafsi yangu itajisifu katika Bwana wanyonge wasikie na kufurahi.  (K)</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>(K) </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Mnyonge alilia, naye Bwana akamsikiliza.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Uso wa Bwana ni juu ya watendao mabaya ili afute kumbukumbu yao duniani. </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wanyofu waliita, Bwana akasikia akawaopoa katika shida zao zote.  (K)</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>(K) Mnyonge alilia, naye Bwana akamsikiliza.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana yu karibu nao waliopondeka moyo, huwaokoa wenye kuvunjika moyo. </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana huwakomboa watumishi wake waaminifu; </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wote waliomkimbilia Mungu, hawatapatilizwa kamwe.  (K)</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>(K) Mnyonge alilia, naye Bwana akamsikiliza.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA PILI	       
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>2 Timotheo 4:6-8, 16-18</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika barua ya pili ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Timotheo.</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mpendwa: Mimi nipo katika kutolewa sadaka, na wakati wa kufa kwangu umekaribia. </s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nimevipiga vita vilivyo vizuri, nimeumaliza mwendo, nimeilinda imani. </s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nimewekewa taji la uadilifu atakayonipa siku ile Bwana, hakimu wa haki, </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>lakini si mimi peke yangu, ila na wale wote wanaotarajia ujio wake. </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nilipojitetea mara ya kwanza, hakunisaidia mtu hata mmoja. </s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wote waliniacha. Lakini wote wasihesabiwe kosa hilo. </s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Basi, Bwana alinisaidia na kunipa nguvu, kusudi kwa kazi yangu ujumbe usambae, </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na watu wa mataifa wote wapate kusikia. Hivyo nikaokolewe katika meno ya simba.</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> 
Bwana ataniokoa katika kila jambo baya na kuniingiza </s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>salama katika ufalme wake wa mbinguni. </s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yeye atukuzwe milele na milele. Amina. Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SHANGILIO LA INJILI</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>K.Aleluya.
W.Aleluya.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K.Mungu ameipatanisha dunia naye katika Kristo, 
akaliweka neno la upatanisho ndani yetu. </s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>W.Aleluya.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>INJILI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Luka 18:9-14</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Luka.</s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakati ule: Yesu aliwaambia mfano huu baadhi ya watu </s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>waliojiona kama waadilifu na kuwadharau wengine, </s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>“Watu wawili walipanda kwenda hekaluni kusali. </s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mmoja alikuwa Farisayo, mwingine mtoza ushuru. </s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yule Farisayo akasimama, akasali hivi moyoni mwake, </s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>‘Ee Mungu, nakushukuru kwa sababu mimi </s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>si kama watu wengine wanyang’anyi, wasiofanya haki, </s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wavunja ndoa Wala kama huyu mtoza ushuru. </s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nafunga mara mbili kila juma na kutoa zaka moja ya kumi ya mapato yangu yote.’</s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mtoza ushuru alisimama mbali, wala hakuthubutu </s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kuinua macho yake mbinguni, bali alijipiga kifua akisema, </s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>‘Ee Mungu, uniwie radhi mimi mkosefu.’ </s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nawaambieni, huyu mtoza ushuru alishuka kwenda nyumbani </s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hali amehesabiwa haki, lakini yule mwingine hapana; </s></f>"},{ID:61,Style:{Background:{Luminosity:-55}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa maana kila ajikwezaye atashushwa, 
lakini ajishushaye atakwezwa.” </s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:63,Style:{Background:{Image:"SACRED HEART GAKIRA CATHOLIC CHURCH DOMINIKA.png",Luminosity:5}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFF3F3FFF>.</c></s></f>"}],Style:{Background:{Image:"WhatsApp Image 2025-10-04 at 07.57.08_dd6cdcec.jpg"}},
Text:"DOMINIKA YA THELATHINI MWAKA C
"},{Guid:"bAR++TWA4UySifXNQOPQhw",Verses:[{Style:{Background:{Image:"basilica.jpg",Luminosity:0}}},{ID:2,
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>KUTABARUKIWA
BASILIKA LA LATERANI</k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA KWANZA
Ezekieli 47:1-2, &-9, 12</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika kitabu cha Nabii Ezekieli</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Siku zile: Malaika alinirudisha kwenye maingilio ya nyumba ya hekalu, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na tazama, maji yalikuwa yakitoka chini ya kizingiti
cha nyumba, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>upande wa mashariki, kwa maana, nyumba ilielekea mashariki. </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Maji yalikuwa yakiteremka toka chini ya upande
wa kulia wa nyumba, kusini mwa altare. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Malaika akanileta nje,kwa njia ya mlango wa kaskazini, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akanizungusha kwa njia ya nje mpaka mlango ulio upande wa mashariki;</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> na tazama, maji yalitoka upande wa kulia. Akaniambia, 
“Maji haya yanakwenda upande wa mashariki, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yanateremka katika Araba na kuingia katika bahari na maji yake ya chumvi yatasafishwa. </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kila mahali utakapofika mto huu, viumbe vyote vyenye uzima vilivyopo vitaishi: </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>samaki watakuwamo wengi sana. Maji hayo yanapofika, huponya na kuzidisha uzima popote mto upitapo. </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kando ya mto, kila ng'ambo, miti ya matunda ya kila namna itaota, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na majani yake hayatakauka, wala matunda yake hayatakosekana.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Miti itazaa matunda mapya kila mwezi kwa sababu ya maji yale yaliyotokea patakatifu. </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nayo matunda yake yatakuwa chakula, na majani yake yatakuwa dawa.\"</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Zaburi 46:2-3, 5-6, 8-9 (K.5a)</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Maji ya mto yaufurahisha mji wa Mungu.</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mungu ni kimbilio na nguvu yetu,
msaada ulio tayari daima wakati wa shida.</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa hiyo hatuogopi kitu, ijapoyeyuka nchi,
na milima ijapoanguka katikati ya bahari. K.</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Maji ya mto yaufurahisha mji wa Mungu.</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kuna mto ambao mikondo yake yaufurahisha mji wa Mungu.
makao matakatifu ya yule Aliye Juu.</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mungu yupo katikati yake; nao hautatikisika;
Mungu huuletea msaada alfajiri na mapema. k</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Maji ya mto yaufurahisha mji wa Mungu.</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana wa majeshi yu pamoja nasi;
Mungu wa Yakobo ni ngome yetu.</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Njoni, tazameni matendo yake Bwana,
maajabu aliyoyafanyia duniani. K.</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Maji ya mto yaufurahisha mji wa Mungu.</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA PILI
1 Wakorintho 3:9e-11, 16-17</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika barua ya kwanza ya Mtakatifu Paulo
kwa Wakorintho</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndugu zangu: Ninyi ni jengo la Mungu. Kwa kadiri ya neema ya Mungu </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>niliyojaliwa nimepata kuwa mjenzi bingwa na nimeweka msingi. Mtu mwingine anajenga juu yake. Lakini</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yeyote anayejenga juu yake aangalie namna anavyojenga.</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Maana hakuna anayeweza kuweka msingi mwingine, ila ule uliokwishawekwa, </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndiye Yesu Kristo. Je, hamjui ya kuwa ninyi ni hekalu la Mungu, </s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na Roho wa Mungu anakaa ndani yenu?
Kama mtu akiliharibu hekalu la Mungu, </s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mungu atamharibu.Kwa maana hekalu la Mungu ni takatifu, nalo ni ninyi.</s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SHANGILIO LA INJLI
2 Nyakati 7:16</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Aleluya.
W. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Nimechagua na kuitakasa nyumba hii, asema Bwana; ili jina langu likae hapa milele.</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>W. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>INJILI
Yohane 2:13-22</s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Yohane</s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Pasaka ya Wayahudi ilikuwa imekaribia. Yesu alipanda kwenda Yerusalemu. </s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akaona pale hekaluni watu wakiuza ng’ombe,
kondoo, </s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na njiwa, pia wabadilisha fedha wamekaa mezani pao. Akafanya mjeledi kwa kamba, </s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akawafukuza wote katika hekalu pamoja na kondoo na ng’ombe. </s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akamwaga fedha za wabadilisha fedha, akapindua meza zao, akawaambia wauza njiwa, </s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ondoeni vitu hivi, msiifanye nyumba ya Baba yangu
kuwa nyumba ya biashara.</s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>“ Wafuasi wake wakakumbuka ya kuwa imeandikwa, Wivu wa nyumba yako unaniua.”</s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hapo Wayahudi wakamrudia na kumwambia, “Je, utaweza kutuonyesha ishara gani inayokuruhusu kufanya hayo?” </s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu akajibu, akawaambia, “Livunjeni hekalu hili, nami nitalijenga tena kwa siku tatu,</s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>“ Wayahudi wakamwambia, “Miaka arobaini na sita ilitakiwa kujenga hekalu hili, </s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na wewe utalijenga kwa siku tatu? “Lakini yeye alikuwa anazungumzia hekalu la mwili wake, </s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Baada ya ufufuko wvake katika wafu, wafuasi Wake wakakumbuka ya kuwa alisema hayo, </s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na wakayasadiki Maandiko na maneno aliyokuwa anmeyasema Yesu.</s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:61,Style:{Background:{Image:"basilica.jpg",Luminosity:-5}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>.</s></f>"}],Style:{Background:{Image:"WhatsApp Image 2025-10-04 at 07.57.08_80a6444a.jpg"}},
Text:"KUTABARUKIWA BASILIKA LA LATERANI 9 Novemba "},{Guid:"5oPtgC7nZUSD4d6UvOO7DQ",Verses:[{Style:{Background:{Image:"basilica.jpg",Luminosity:-5}}},{ID:2,Style:{Background:{Image:"Candles.jpg",Luminosity:-5}},
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>GITHOMO KIA MBERE</k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>EZEKIELI 47:1-2;8-9;12</k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Thuutha ücio, mũndi ücio akindwara akīnjookia o mūromoinī wa Hekaarű. </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na riri, maai maatherükaga na kūu rungu rwä mūromo ūcio </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>magatherera maroreete mwena wa irathĩro tondū Hekarű yaroreetie ūthiũ wayo mwena ūcio.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Maai macio maathereraga moimiite mwena wa na kianda wa Hekaarű </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>makahitūkira mwena wa mühuro wa kīgongoona. </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mundū ücio akīnduta hau njainī ya Hekaarū aangereirie </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kīhingoinĩ kĩa na rūgongo Agithiūrūrukagi akinginyia kihingoini kīa mwena wa na irathiro. </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na riiri, kwarī na karũi gaathereraga koimīte mwena wa na kĩanda wa kĩhingo kiu.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akīnjĩra atīrĩ, Maai maya mathereraga magatuikania bũrũri ũria ũri mwena wa irathīro,</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>magacooka meerekeire gituamba kīa Jorodani magaikūrūka makeitirĩra iria ria Cumbi. </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Meitirira iria ria Cumbi matumaga maai maario mathirwo ni cumbi magatuika meega. </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kūria guothe rũúi rüürū rūthereragira nīkūrikaragwo nĩ nyamũ na thamaki ciá mĩthemba yothe. </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Rūűi rūũrű i nĩrūrītūmaga maai ma iria rĩa Cumb</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ỉ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> mathirwo nio cumbi: </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maagire Kūriĩa guothe rürihitūkagīra nīrūrikühotithagia kūgia na ciũmbe irī muoyo.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hügúrurüini cia rū</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>ï rūūrü mirimo yerī ni ikūrīkūraga miti ya mīthemba yothe ya matunda ma kūrīio. </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Miti iyo mathangũ maayo  matirih</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ọ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>ohaga i na ndiri hindi iriagaga matunda. </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Irīkoragwo na matunda mangirīo mweri o mweri, tondū maai ma rũũi rũűrũ</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>marītherūkaga kuuma o Hekaarū thĩini, Matunda ma mĩti iyo marītuikaga irio cia kürio, </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>namo mathangũ maayo magatuika nd</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ạ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>awa cia kuhonania </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>icio nicio ciugo cia Mwathan</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>THABURI YA GUCOKERWO.</k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>THABURI: 46: 2- 9</k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>(Icokia)  </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Ni hari ruui  ruria  turuui twaruo tukenagia ituura  ria Ngai, mucii uria  mutheru wa uria uri iguru muno.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tondu ucio tutingitigira o na thi ingithingitha, kana irima igue iriaini, </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na o maai maario marurume na mahuyuke,  o na kana irima ithingithio ni hinya wa mo. </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>(Icokia) </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F> Ni hari ruui  ruria  turuui twaruo tukenagia ituura  ria Ngai, mucii uria  mutheru wa uria uri iguru muno.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ni hari ruui ruria turuui  twarwo tukenagia ituura ria Ngai, mucii uria mutheru wa Uria uri Iguru Muno.</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ngai ari thiini  wa ituura riu na ritikaaharaganio o na ri; kirooko tene nirio Ngai ariukaga kuriteithia. </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>(Icokia)  </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Ni hari ruui  ruria  turuui twaruo tukenagia ituura  ria Ngai, mucii uria  mutheru wa uria uri iguru muno.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mabururi nimambararukiite, moothamaki nimathingithie; </s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>thi no kumumuthuka iramumuthuka Ngai aguuthuka.</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani Ngai Mwene Hinya Wothe ari hamwe na ithui; </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ngai wa Jakubu ni we handu haitu ha gwitharira. </s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>(Icokia)  </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Ni hari ruui  ruria  turuui twaruo tukenagia ituura  ria Ngai, mucii uria  mutheru wa uria uri iguru muno.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ukaai muone uria Mwathani eekiite muone maundu ma magegania maria eekiite guuku thi, </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Aniinaga mbaara thi yothe, akoinanga moota, akaananga matimu, na agacina ngo na mwaki.</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>(Icokia)  </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Ni hari ruui  ruria  turuui twaruo tukenagia ituura  ria Ngai, mucii uria  mutheru wa uria uri iguru muno.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>GITHOMO KĨA IGIRI.</k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>1 AKORINTHO 3: 9 -1.</k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tondu ithui turutithanagia wira na Ngai, na inyui  ni inyui  mugunda wa Ngai. </s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Inyui  ni inyui mwako wa Ngai. Kuringana na wega uria ndaheirwo ni Ngai, </s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ta  mwakithia uria  muugi nii ndaakire muthingi, naake mundu ungi niaraaka  iguru riaguo.  </s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>No mundu o wothe niakimenyagirire  egwaka iguru  riaguo  atia. </s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Gutiri  muthingi ungi  mundu angiaka tiga  uria uriikiitie  gwakwo ni Ngai, </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na Jesu Kristu  ni we muthingi  ucio.  Mundu no aake iguru  </s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ria muthingi ucio na thahabu kana betha, kana  mahiga ma goro, </s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kana mbaau, kana  nyeki o na kana ruua. No riiri, </s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wira  wa mundu o mundu  niukaamenyeka  hindi iria Muthenya wa Kristu ugaatuma wira ucio wonekane. </s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Amu muthenya  ucio mwaki niukaamenyithania wira wa  o mundu; </s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wira ucio ukaagerio na mwaki niguo umenyeke uria uhaana. </s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Angikorwo kiria mundu aakire iguru ria muthingi ucio nigigeetiiria mwaki, </s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>niakaamukira mucaara. No angikorwo kiria  giakirwo nigikaahia, </s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>uria wagiakire niagathie hathara , no we mwene niakaahonoka o ta ria mundu angihonoka agereire mwakiini. </s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Atiriiri, kai mutooi ati inyui muri Hekaaru ya Ngai, na ati Roho wa Ngai </s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>aikaraga thiini wanyu? Hakiri uguo-ri, mundu angithuukia Hekaaru ya Ngai, </s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ngai naake niakaamuthuukia  ni gukorwo Hekaaru ya Ngai ni theru, na inyui ni inyui Hekaaru iyo.</s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>Ciugo cia Mwathani</k></s></f><u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>.</k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>RŨIMBO RWA INJIRI.</k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Maũndũ ma matuku ma tene 2: 7-16.</k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Alleluia,  
Alleluia.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ni undu-ri, nindimithuuriite na  ngamiamura ituike  ituike handu haria </s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>marithathaayagiria  tene na tene. Nindirimimenyagirira na ndimigitagire hindi ciothe. </s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>INJIRI
Johana 2:13-22</k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na rīiri, tondū thigükű ya Ayahudi ya Bathaka niyakuhīriirie, </s></f>"},{ID:22,Style:{Background:{Image:"Candles.jpg",Luminosity:-5}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Jesű akīambata Jerusalemu Nakuo thiinĩ wa Hekaarũ agikora andũ </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>meendagia ng'ombe, ng'ondu, nà ndutuura,
o na angi maacenjagia mbeeca maikarīite thĩ kuo. </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Naake oona űguo, agīthondeka műcarica wa ndigi, akimaingata kuuma kūu Hekaarű Oothe, </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na ng'ondu na ng'ombe, nacio mbeeca cia arīa maacenjagia agīcihurunja, na akīng'aūrania meetha ciao.</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nao arĩa meendagia ndutuura akimeera atiri, \"Eheriai ndutuura icio gũűkũ! </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tigaai gūtua nyũmba ya Awa ndūũnyū!\" Hindi iyo arutwo aake </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>makiririkana űria Maandīko moigīite atirī, </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Kiyo kiria ndĩ nakão kĩa nyūmba yaku nikio gikaandia.</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\" ningi Nao atongoria a Ayahudi makiūria Jesű atīrĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ kiama kīrīkũ ūngītūringīra gia gūtuonia ati nīwagīriírwo nīgwīka ūguo weka?\" </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Naake akīmacookeria atiri, \"Thariai Hekaarű ino, na ningūmiaka ríngi na mithenya itatū.\"</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nao makimūüria atīri, \"Hekaarü ĩno yakirwo na mĩaka </s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mirongo ina na itandatü ní yo üroiga ati ni</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>kūmiaka na mithenya ītatü</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>No Jesű aaragia ühoro wa Hekaarũ ya mwirī wake. Na rĩri, riria aariokire akiuma küri arīa akuũ </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>arutwo ake nimaaririkanire atī nioigīte uguo.
Magíígitikia maandíko na úría Jesu oiigíte.</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s></f>"},{ID:35,Style:{Background:{Image:"basilica.jpg",Luminosity:0}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>.</s></f>"}],Style:{Background:{BodyRect:"0,0,10000,9300"}},
Text:"KURATHIMWO IHOERO RIA LATERAN BASILICA – NOVEMBA 9"},{Guid:"A5bx664f2U298tZudKtNdw",Verses:[{Style:{Background:{Image:"kik.jpg",Luminosity:0}}},{ID:2,
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>KIUMIA KĨA MIRONGO ITATŨ NA ITHATÜ KIA MWAKA C</k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GITHOMO KIA MBERE
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Malaki 4; 1-2a.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GUTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RIA KIRORI MALAKI :</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani ekuuga atīrī: Tondū rīrī, müthenya ūcio ndūrī hingo ütagakinya, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>naguo ūkagerekanio na icua rīa mwaki ūrīa wakanīte müno; </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nao andű othe etīi na arīa mekaga waganu magatuīka ta maragara; </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>naguo műthenya ücio wakinya nĩ magacinwo mathire biü, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na maagithio kīene o ta muti üria ūtigītwo ūtarī na mĩri kana honge; </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>üguo nīguo Mwathani Münene wa Ita oiga. </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>No rirī, inyuĩ mwitigagīra rīĩtwa rīakwa nĩ műkamūrīkīrūo nĩ </s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>rīa wītagwo Riűa-rĩa–Wega.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nīcio ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>THABURI YA GUCOKERUO
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Thaburi 98: 5-6; 7-8; 9</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>ICOKIA: </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Mwathani nĩ agūka gūthamakīra andu.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>1. Inirai Mwathani mūkimūgoocaga na inanda cia mūgeto; </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>inanda-nī, o na mūgambo wa küina thaburi,</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Inai na tur</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ụ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>mbeta, na ugambi wa coro, mukianirire </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na gīkeno mwī mbere ya Mūthamaki o we Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>ICOKIA: </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Mwathani nĩ agūka gūthamakīra andu.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>2.Iria rirīa inene ni rirurume, gwata kīrīa giothe kiriiyūire; maburūri o namo, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o gwata aria matuūraga kuo; njuí nacio ni ikīhūre hi, o nacio irima ikūngūiye ciothe ni ūrīa ikenete.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>ICOKIA: </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Mwathani nĩ agūka gūthamakīra andu.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>3. Ni gwikwo ūguo mbere-inī ya Mwathani, tondū nīĩ egūüka gūthamakīra thi; </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>arīthamakagīra mab</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>rūri na ūthingu, atuithanagie irīndi o ūrīa kwerekereire.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>ICOKIA: </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Mwathani nĩ agūka gūthamakīra andu.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GiTHOMO KIA IGĪRĪ
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>2 Athesalonika 3: 7-12.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŪTHOMA MARUA MA MUTHURE PAUL KŪRĪ ANDU A THESALONIKA:</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ariu a Ithe witu, nĩ gükorūo nĩ müui inyuene ürīa mwagīrirüo nĩ kwīgerekanagia na ithuī: </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>amu tũtiatūüraga ta andů matarī kīhaarīro hĩndī iria twatüire na inyuī, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na kana tükarīa irio cia mũndü ona üriku tühū; 
no nī küruta </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>twarutaga wira wa hinya ütukű na mūthenya tükīinogagia, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ getha tütikae küritühīra mündū o na ümwe wanyu,</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na riri, ti atī tütirī na kīhooto gīa kümūritühīra, no ni küruta twarutaga </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wīra üguo nĩ getha tūtuīke cionereria küri inyui,</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nīguo mütüūre mwigerekanagia na ithui. </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ni ündū-rī, o na hĩndĩ irĩa twatūire hamwe na inyuī, </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ündü ūyū nīguo twamwathaga ati Mündu o na Urīkũ angīrega küruta wīra-rī, </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na kürĩa nĩ atigage kürīa. Amu nĩ tũiguaga atī nĩ kuri</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>andù amwe anyu matūüraga ta andū matarī kīhaarīro, </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>matarī na wira marutaga, no gwitonyereria metonyagiriria maūndu-inī ma andű arīa angī. </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Acio nĩo tũgwatha na tūkamahatīriria, twi th</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ỉ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>inĩ wa Mwathani Yesu Kristü, </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>atī marutage wira makindīirie, na marīage o irio ciao ene.</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nīcio ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>RUIMBO RUA INJIRI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Mathayo 24: 42. 44.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Alleluya, Alleluya. </k></c></s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wihūgagei na ikaragai mwīharīirie nī gükorūo m</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>tiüi
müthenya ūrīa Mwathani agoka. </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Alleluya.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GITHOMO KIA INJIRI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Luka 21: 5-19.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GUTHOMA INJIRI YA MUTHURE LUKA:</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hĩndī io, rirīa amwe maaragia ühoro wa hekarü, ürīa yagemetio na mahiga mathaka,</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na iheo iria andū maarutiire Ngai, akiuga atīri: Ha ühoro wa indo ici mükuona-rī, </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>matukū nī magoka rirīa hatagatigario ihiga o na rīmwe rīikarīte igürű rīa rīria rīngī, </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ritagúithitio. Nao makīmūüria atīrī: Mwonania, riria maündü macio magagīkinya nĩ rī? </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na kīmenyithia nĩ kīrikü riria makagwata gükinya ?</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake akiuga atīrī: Wimenyagīrīrei műtikanahītithio : nĩ gükorūo andũ aingi?</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ magoka magiītuaga riitwa rĩakwa, makiugaga atīrī: Nii nĩ nii we, na makoiga atīrī: </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ihinda nĩ rikiriī gükinya, mūtikanamarümīrīre. Na rĩrīa m</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>ükaigua ühoro wa mbaara, </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na wa ngüī, műtikanetigīre: nī gükorūo maündū macio matirī </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hingo matagakinyao mbere; indī ithirîĩro ti rĩa ihinda oro riu.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hindi io akīmera atīrī: O rüriri nī rūgokīrīra rürīa rüngī, na o üthamaki üükīrire ürīa üngī: </s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na nĩgūkagīa ithingithia nene; o na kündũ na kũndūnĩ gükagīa na ng'aragu, </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na mĩrimů miüru îria irehage müthiro; na nĩ gükagīa na imakania cia gűt</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ủ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>a andú nda, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na ciama nene ciumīte matu-inī. No maündü macio matanakinya-rī, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>andū nī makaműnyita na mamũnyarire, makimüneanaga mürwarūo thinagoga-inĩ na korokoro inī; </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na nĩ mügatwarűo kūrī athamaki nĩ ūndū wa rīītwa rīakwa, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nario ihinda rīu rigatuika ihinda rĩanyu rĩa üira. </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hakīrī üguo-rī, tuai na ngoro cianyu atī m</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>tigeciria o mbere ürīa mügacokia ühoro: </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ gükorūo nii nĩ ngamühe miario o na ūūgi, iria thũ </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>cianyu ciothe itakahota gwītiiria kana gükararia, </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>No rĩrī, mükaneanwo ni andu, o gwata aciari anyu, o na arīa mürĩ a nyina ūmwe nao, </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na arīa a mīhinga yanyu, o na arata anyu; na amwe anyu nĩ makamoragithia, </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na nĩ mügathüürűo nĩ andű othe nĩ ündūũ wa riitwa riakwa. No rĩrī, </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na rücuirī rüanyu rüa mütwe, gůtirī rükora. 
Nĩ </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gükirīriria kwanyu gūgatūma mühonokie mīoyo yanyu:</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injiri theru ya Mwathani,</s></f>"},{ID:28,Style:{Background:{Image:"kik.jpg",Luminosity:0}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>.</s></f>"}],Style:{Background:{Image:"WhatsApp Image 2025-10-04 at 07.57.08_ddf7796b.jpg"}},
Text:"KIUMIA KĨA MIRONGO ITATŨ NA ITHATÜ KIA MWAKA C"},{Guid:"xxn/VoyJs0ibPwviREeMhA",Verses:[{Style:{Background:{Image:"DO.jpg",Transition:3,Luminosity:0}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846></s></f>"},{ID:2,Style:{Background:{Transition:3}},
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>DOMINIKA YA THELATHINI NA TATU MWAKA C</k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:2,Style:{Background:{Transition:2}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA KWANZA
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Malaki 3: 19-20a</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika kitabu cha Nabii Malaki</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tazama, siku inakuja,inawaka kama tanuri.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Watu wote wenye kiburi,na yeyote atendaye uovu,</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>watakuwa kama makapi. Na siku ile inayokuja itawateketeza, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ambapo haitawaachia shina wala tawi.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Lakini kwenu ninyi mnaoliheshimu jina langu,</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>jua la haki litawatokezea, jua lenye kuponya katika mbawa zake.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Zaburi 98:5-6, 7-8, 9a, 9</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Bwana anakuja kuwahukumu mataifa kwa haki.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwimbieni Bwana kwa kinubi,
kwa kinubi na sauti ya vinanda.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa tarumbeta na sauti ya baragumu
shangilieni mbele ya Mfalme, Bwana. K.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Bwana anakuja kuwahukumu mataifa kwa haki.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bahari na ivume na vyote viljazavyo,
dunia yote na wote wakaao ndani yake.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mito na ipige makofi,
milima na iimbe pamoja kwa furaha.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mbele ya Bwana, kwa kuwa anakuja,
kwa kuwa anakuja kuihukumu nchi. K</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Bwana anakuja kuwahukumu mataifa kwa haki.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Atauhukumu ulimwengu kwa haki,
na mataifa kwa adili. K.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Bwana anakuja kuwahukumu mataifa kwa haki.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA PILI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>2 Wathesalonike 3,7-12</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika barua ya pili ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Wathesalonike</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndugu zangu: Mwajua wenyewe jinsi iwapasavyo kutuiga sisí.</s></f>"},{ID:15,Style:{Background:{Duration:0}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Maana hatukukaa kwenu kwa uzembe. Kamwe hatukula kwa mtu</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yeyote bila kumlipa. Bali tulifanya kazi usiku na mchana kwa</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kujikakamua mpaka kuchoka, kusudi tusimuelemee mtu wa</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwenu, hata mmoja. Si kama hatungalikuwa na haki ya kufanya hayo, </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>lakini tulitaka sisi wenyewe tuwe mfano kwenu mtufuate. </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa maana tulipokaa kwenu tuliwapa kanuni hii: asiyetaka</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kufanya kazi, asile. Maana tumesikia kwamba baadhi yenu ni</s></f>"},{ID:22,Style:{Background:{Transition:20}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wavivu, hawafanyi kazi, bali bali huwadoea watu wengine.</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hao tunawaonya na kuwasisitiza katika Bwana Yesu Kristo,</s></f>"},{ID:24,Style:{Background:{Duration:8110}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wafanye kazi kwa utulivu wapate kula chakula wanachostahili wenyewe.</s></f>"},{ID:15,Style:{Background:{Image:"WhatsApp Image 2025-10-04 at 07.57.08_ddf7796b.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SHANGILIO LA INJILI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Luka 21:28</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:17,Style:{Background:{Transition:0}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Aleluya.
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>W. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Aleluya.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Simameni, inueni vichwa vyenu,
kwa maana ukombozi wenu unakaribia.</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>W. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Aleluya.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>INJILI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Luka 2,15:19</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Luka</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakati ule: 
Baadhi ya watu walipokuwa wakiongea habari za hekalu, </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hasa mawe mazuri na mapambo ya wakfu.</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu akasema,
\"Haya yote mnayoyaona, siku sitakuja ambapo jiwe halitaachwa</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>juu ya jiwe. Yote yatabomolewa.\"
Wakamwuliza wakisema, </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>“Mwalimu, hayo yatakuwa lini? 
Na iko ishara gani inayodokeza mwanzo wa kutimia hayo?\"</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akasema, “Angalieni msije mkadanganywa, kwa maana wengi</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>watakuja kwa jina langu, wakisema, Mimi ndiye,' tena Wakati</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>umewadia. Msiwafuate hao. Mtakaposikia habari za vita na</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>misukosuko, msihangaike, kwa maana hayo hayana budi kutendeka</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwanza, lakini si mwisho bado,\"</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kisha akawaambia, Taifa litashambulia taifa, na ufalme utashambulia ufalme.</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kutakuwa na matetemeko makubwa ya nchi huko na huko,</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na maradhi na njaa na matisho na ishara kubwa kutoka uwinguni.</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Lakini kabla yakutendeka hayo yote, watawakamata ninyi na</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kuwadhulumu, watawapeleka katika sinagogi na kuwatia gerezani,</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na mtapelekwa mbele ya wafalme na magavana kwa ajili ya jina</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>langu. Hivyo mtapata nafasi ya kushuhudia.</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Basi, jikazeni mioyo yenu: msifikirie kabla yake namna ya</s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kujitetea. Kwa maana mimi nitawapa kauli na hekima, ambayo adui</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kushindana nayo wala kuipinga. wenu wote hawataweza Lakini </s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mtatolewa na wazazi na ndugu na jamaa na marafiki,</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nao watawaua baadhi yenu. Na mtachukiwa na watu wote kwa</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ajili ya jina langu. Lakini hata unywele mmoja wa vichwa vyenu</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hautapotea. Kwa uvumilivu wenu mtaziokoa nafsi zenu.\"</s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:47,Style:{Background:{Image:"DO.jpg",Luminosity:0}},
