Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>GITHOM0 KIA MBERE
2 Samweli 5: 1-3.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GUTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RIA KEERI RIA SAMWELI:</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Matukū-inī macio, mihīriga yothe ya Israeli igigīthii he Davide o kũu Hebron, îkīmwarīria,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>íkimwira atīrī: Türí a m</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>thimo ümwe nawe, o na a mwirī ümwe. Tene hĩndī iria Saul aarī</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mūthamaki wa gũt</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>thamakīra-rī, wee nīwe watongoragia mbūtũ cia Israeli igīthii ita, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na ikīinüka; nake Mwathani agīkwira atii: We nīwe ürīrithagia andű akwa Israeli, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na nīwe ügatuíka mūtongoria wa Israeli,
Tondū ücio athuri othe a Israeli magīthií</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>magikinya he müthamaki o kūu Hebron; nake Davide ücio mūthamaki akīrikanīrira nao kũu</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hebron mbere ya Mwathani; nao magīgí itīriria Davide maguta atuíke müthamaki wa güthamakīra Israeli,</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nīcio ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>THABURI YA GUCOKERŪO
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Thaburi 122: 1-2; 3-4; 5-6.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>ICOKIA: </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Thayű nĩ ürīküragwo üharia Mwathani arī.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>1. Nĩgūkena ndirakenire maanjıra tūthii nyümba-ini ya Mwathani, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Magūrū maitũ rĩu nĩkuo marūngi, ihingo ciaku na thinī, wee Jerusalemu,</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>ICOKIA: </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Thayű nĩ ürīküragwo üharia Mwathani arī.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>2. Jerusalemu, o wee wakitwo ta gitūüro gitumaine o wega., </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nīkuo mihiriga îthiaga ikīambatagirira,
mihĩrīga oio ya Mwathani: </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ni üira harī Israeli, igithiaga kuo gūcokeria rütwa rīa Mwathani ngatho.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>ICOKIA: Thayű nĩ ürīküragwo üharia Mwathani arī.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>3. Nĩgūtuíka nīkuo kwaigītwo iti iria cia cira, itī cia ūnene, </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o iria cia mbarī ya Davide. Kihoerei Jerusalemu thayü; </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>arīa wee makwendete-tī, marotūūra magaaciīrūo.</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA: </s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Thayű nĩ ürīküragwo üharia Mwathani arī.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GİTHOMO KIA IGIRI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Akolosai 1: 12 - 20.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GUTHOMA MARUA MA MÜTHURE PAUL KURI ANDU A KOLOSAI :</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ariŭ a ithe witū, mūcokagīrie Ithe witü ngatho, we ūtūtuïte andū aiganĩru </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>a kügayanīrio igai hamwe na andŭ arīa aamūre, kürīa kwĩ na ütheri, </s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake nīwe watūhonokirie agītūruta watho-inī wa nduma</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agītūthamīrīria üthamaki-inī wa Müriū üría endete müno, </s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ücio nīwe watūkūürire, nĩ gütūrekera mehia mait</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ủ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>. </s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake niwe mühianīre wa ürĩa Ngai ahaana, o we ütunekaga, </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na nĩwe waambire kūrigithathwo indo ciothe itaanombwo. </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tondũ rĩrĩ, indo ciothe ikīúmbwo nĩ ciombirūo na ündű wake, iria irī igūru,o nacio iria irī thĩ; </s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>iria cionekaga o na iria itonekaga; o na ciatuīka ní itī cia ünene kana ene wathani, </s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kana műthamaki, o na kana mahinya, ciothe-rī, nĩ kūümbwo ciombirūo na ũnd</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> wake, nīguo ituike ciake. </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake we nīwe ütūire o ho mbere indo ciothe itaanagīa, nacio ciothe itűűraga inyitanītio nīwe. </s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ningĩ nĩwe Mütwe wa mwirī, arī guo Kanitha: nake nīwe wa kīambīrīria, </s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na nīwe irigithathi rīa andű arĩa maanakua; 
nĩ getha maūndū-inī mothe atuike nowe wa mbere.</s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ gūkorūo üiyűru wothe wa Ngai nĩ wetikīrire gūtūüra thĩinī wake; </s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nīguo atī na ündũ wake maűndũ mothe macoke kūiguithanio na Ngai, nĩ ündũ wa ürīa aarehire thayū </s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ündű wathakame iria yaitirūo Mütharaba-inī wake; mo mothe-rī, maiguithanio na Ngai no ũndū wake, </s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na mangītuīka nĩ ma gūkü thĩ, o na kana ma Igūrű.</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nicio ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>RUIMBO RUA INJIRI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Marko 11,10 .</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Alleluya, Alleluya.</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F> </k></s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kürathimwo-rī, nĩ ūrīa ūgūūka na riītwa rĩa Mwathani :
Kürathimwo-rĩ, nĩ üthamaki ūrīa ügūüka. </s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Alleluya.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GITHOMO KIA INJIRI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Luka 23: 35 -43.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GUTHOMA INJIRI YA MUTHURE LUKA :</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hindī io, kīrīndī nĩ kĩarūgamīte o gīkīirorera. Anene o nao makīmüthekerera, makiuga atīrī: </s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩaahonokagia andű angī; nĩ akīhonokie we mwene, angīkorūo nīwe Kristū wa Ngai, ürīa wake m</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>thure.</s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Athigari nao makīmūnyürūria, magīthiĩ harī we makīműtwarīrira thiki, makīmwīra atīrī :</s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akorűo wee nīwe müthamaki wa Ayahudi, wihonokie. Na nĩ haarī marūa maridīkītwo igürū rīake,atīirī: </s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Úyũ nĩwe Müthamaki wa Ayahudi. Na mündū ümwe wa acio ageri ngero maacuurītio mitiinī akīmũruma,</s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akiuga atīrī: Githĩ tiwe Kristü ? Wihonokie wee mwene, na ütühonokie ithui.</s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake üria ūngī agīcokia akīmūkaania, akīmüüria atīrí: Anga o na Ngai ndüngīmwītigīra, kuona atí wee o</s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nawe nī űtuĩríirüo ituīro o take ? Na ithui-rī, nī kīhooto tütuĩríirüo nakīo : </s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>amu nĩ küihio tūkürīhio maūndű marīa twaneka : no mũndū üyű-rī, </s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndarī ündü müüru ekīte. Nake akiuga
atīrī : </s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu, itikira gükandirikana rīrīa ūgoka ügwatīte üthamaki waku. </s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake akīmwira atīrī : Ngũkwira na ma, atī üműthĩ ni. üiikara hamwe na niĩ lkenero-ini.</s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injiri theru ya Mwathani.</s></f>"}],Style:{Background:{Image:"WhatsApp Image 2025-10-04 at 07.57.08_dd6cdcec.jpg"}},
