Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika kitabu cha pili cha Samueli</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Siku zile:
Makabila yote ya Israeli yalimwendea Daudi huko Hebroni
na kusema,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tazama, sisi hapa ni mfupa wako, na nyama yako. Hapo zamanií Sauli</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>alipokuwa mfalme wetu, wewe uliwaongoza Waisraeli kuingia na
kutoka vitani.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na Bwana akakuambia: Wewe utawalisha watu wangu Israeli,</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nawe utakuwa mkuu juu ya Israeli.”
Basi, wazee wote wa Israeli wakamwendea mfalme huko Hebroni,</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>naye mfalme Daudi akafanya nao mapatano huko Hebroni mbele ya</s></f>"},{ID:10,
