Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakati ule: Wakubwa wa watu walimdhihaki Yesu, wakisema.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>“Aliwaokoa wengine, sasa ajiokoe mwenyewe, kama ni Kristo,</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mteule wa Mungu.”
Askari pia walimdhihaki. Walimjongea na kumletea siki.</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakisema, “Kama wewe ni Mfalme wa Wayahudi,
jisalimishe mwenyewe.</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Juu yake palikuwa na hati: “Huyu ndiye Mfalme wa Wayahudi.”</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mmoja wa wale wahalifu waliotundikwa alimtukana akisema,</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>*Je, wewe si Kristo? Basi, jiokoe mwenyewe na sisi pia.”</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Lakini mwingine akajibu, akamgombeza na kusema,</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>“Je, hata wewe uliyehukumiwa sawa na yeye humjali Mungu?</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Sisi kwa haki, tunapokea tuliyostahili kwa makosa yetu;</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>huyu lakini hakutenda mabaya.”
Akasema,</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>“Ee Yesu, unikumbuke mimi utakapoingia katika ufalme wako.”</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu akamjibu,
“Amin, nakuambia, leo utakuwa pamoja nami peponi.”</s></f>"},{ID:20,
