Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>KIUMIA GIA ITHATHATU KIA IRIUKIRO MWAKA C</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĪTHOMO KIA MBERE</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Atūmwo 15: 1-2, 22-29.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŪTHOMA KUMA IBUKU RĨA ATŪMWO</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Matukū-ini macio, andū amwe nĩ mokire moimīte </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Judea makarutaga ariű a Ithe witũ atīri: Mũngi-aga  </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kūrua kūringana na mūtugo ürīa Musa aatūtigīire, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mütingīhota kūhonokio. Nao Paul na Barna-ba </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maarīkia gükararania nao makīüranganagia ündü ucio nao mũno, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gugītuwo ati Paul na Barnaba</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>marī na amwe angī a thiritũ yao, maambate mathii </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Jerusalemu kūrī atūmwo o na athuri nĩ ündū wa</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ühoro ücio moranganagia.
Na hĩndī io-rī, atūmwo na athuri o na andű othe a </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kanitha makīona arī wega mathure andü amwe</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>a thiritū yao, mamarekie Antiokia hamwe na Paul na Barnaba. </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nao nĩ aya, Juda ürīa wetagwo Barna-ba, </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na Sila, arīa maarī atongoria thiritū-inī ya ariű a Ithe witū. </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Magīkīandika marűa ma gūtwarūo nĩo, makiuga ūű: </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ithuĩ atūmwo na athuri a thiritū ya ariū a lthe witū, </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ twamügeithia inyui ariū a Ithe witũ m</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>tarī Ayahudi, </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mūtüire Antiokia, na Suriata, na Cilicia. </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Atīrirī, nī tūkīiguīte atī andü amwe arīa moimire </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kūrī ithuĩ nĩ mamürigithītie ühoro na ndeto ciao, </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>makahotomia meciria mangoro cianyu, 
o na gűtari ündű twamaathire naguo. </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na twakīrīkia küiguanīra ühoro, 
nĩ twonire a-rĩ wega t</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>thure andű amwe, </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tũmarekie küri inyui hamwe na 
Barnaba na Paul arīa twendete mű-no; </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nao nīo andű metwarīrīire ügwati-ini wa </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kūūragwo nī ündũ wa rīitwa rīa Mwathani witü Yesu  Kristü. </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tondū ūcio nĩ twarekia Juda na Sila,</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nao nĩ mekūmwīra na kanua o ene maündū o ro
maya türaandīka. </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tondü atiri: Muoyo Mütheru, o na ithuī, 
nĩ tuonete arī wega tūtikamüigīrire </s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mürigo ükīrīte maündū maya matangītigīka; </s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>namo nĩ maya, atī mūthemage kindü kīrĩa gīothe
kīhakīirūo mihianano, na thakame, </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na nyama cia nyamű iria ciitītwo, o na ümaraya. </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na rīri, mũn-gīīamüra müthemage maűndű macio, mweka wega. </s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tigwoi na ühoro.
icio nicio ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>THABURI YA GUCOKERUO</s></f>"},{ID:37,
