Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA:
Ndūrirī ciothe, mūgoocage Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ngai arotūkinyiria wega wake, agītūrathime,</s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> 
arotūma uthi</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> wake utuure ūtwariire,</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Niguo njira yaku, Ngai, īmenyūo gukū thi, </s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ūhonokania waku ūkīoneke ndūriri-ini ciothe,</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA:
Ndūrirī ciothe, mūgoocage Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndũriri  gūkena ni ikene, o na ikūnguyagie ni gūkena, </s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tondū wee uriciragira irindi o uria kwerekereire, </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndūriri cia gūku th</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ỉ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> </s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>tuike mūtongoria wacio,</s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA:
Ndūrirī ciothe, mūgoocage Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Irindi cia thi, Ngai, irogūcokeria ngatho; </s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ūrogathagvo nĩ ndūriri cia thĩ ciothe.</s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kurathima Ngai no arītūrathimaga; </s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ituri ciothe cia th</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ỉ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> igītuike cia kūmwitigira.</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA:
Ndūrirī ciothe, mūgoocage Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GITHOMO KIA IGIRI</s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kuguürīrio 21: 10-14, 22-23.</s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Müraika akīndūara na muoyo igūrū rīa kīrīma kīnene, </s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gītūúgīru ma, akīnyonia itūüra rirīa itheru, </s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Jerusalemu, rīgīīkūrūka rīkiuma Igūrű kwi Ngai, </s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>rirī o na riri wa Ngai. Mūtherere warīo </s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wahanaga ta wa kahiga ke goro mūno, </s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o ta karīa getagwo njathibi, gakengu o ta gīcicio. </s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na riĩ na rűirigo rünene rūa mahiga, </s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>rūraya na igūrū, rüĩ na mĩromo ikūmi na iirĩ , </s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na mĩromo īo igaikario nī araika ikümi
na erī; </s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ningi ikaandīkwo marīītwa, </s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na nĩmo marīītwa ma mĩhīrīga irīa ikümi na iiri ya ciana cia
Israeli: </s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mwena wa irathīro ria riũa kwarī mīromo itatü; </s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na mwena wa gathigathini, mīromo îtatu;</s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na mwena wa gūthini, mīromo itat</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> na mwena wa ithüīro rĩa riūa, </s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mīromo itatū. 
Naruo rürigo rũu rūa itüüra </s></f>"},{ID:70,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>rũarī na itina ikūmi na igīrī, 
na igürű riacio kagīa </s></f>"},{ID:71,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na marīitwa ikūmi na merī </s></f>"},{ID:72,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ma atümwo arīa ikūmi na erī a Gatūrūme.</s></f>"},{ID:73,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na g</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>tirī hekarū ndonire kuo, 
nĩ gükorūo </s></f>"},{ID:74,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani Ngai Mwene-Hinya-Wothe, </s></f>"},{ID:75,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o nake Gatūrüme, nĩo hekarũyakuo. </s></f>"},{ID:76,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Narīo itūūra rĩu rītibataragio nĩ riüa, </s></f>"},{ID:77,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kana mwèri, iriarīre, 
nĩ gūkorūo </s></f>"},{ID:78,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>riri wa Ngai
nīguo ürīmūrīkagīra, </s></f>"},{ID:79,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na tawa wakuo nĩ ücio Gatürűme.
Icio nicio ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:80,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>RUIMBO RUA INJIRI
John 14, 23.</s></f>"},{ID:81,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alleluya, Alleluya. </s></f>"},{ID:82,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani ekuuga: 
Mündű aakorűo nĩ anyenda, </s></f>"},{ID:83,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>arīmenyagīrira uuge wakwa;
nake Awa nĩ arīmwendaga, </s></f>"},{ID:84,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na nĩ tūrīüka kürī we, tūtūűranie nake, Alleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:85,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GITHOMO KIA INJIRI
John 14: 23- 29.</s></f>"},{ID:86,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GUTHOMA INJIRI YA MUTHURE JOHN :</s></f>"},{ID:87,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hindī To Yesu agīcokeria arümīrīri ake: </s></f>"},{ID:88,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mündű aakorūo nī anyenda, arīmenyagīrĩra uuge wakwa; </s></f>"},{ID:89,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nake Awa nĩ arīmwendaga, na nĩ türiuka kürĩ we, </s></f>"},{ID:90,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tūtüüranie nake, Üria ütanyenda ndamenyagirira</s></f>"},{ID:91,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ciugo ciakwa naguo ühoro ürīa műiguaga ti wakwa, </s></f>"},{ID:92,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ wa Ithe witü ürīa wandekirie.</s></f>"},{ID:93,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Maündū macio ndimwīrite tũri o na inyuí. </s></f>"},{ID:94,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>No rirī, müteithia ūcio Muoyo Mutherü, </s></f>"},{ID:95,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>üria ükarekio ni Ithe witū na rīītwa rīakwa, </s></f>"},{ID:96,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>we akaműruta maündū mothe, </s></f>"},{ID:97,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na amūririkanagie mohoro mothe marīa
ndanamūhe. </s></f>"},{ID:98,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Thayũ nĩguo ndamūtigīra; 
thayű wakwa nīguo ndaműhe; </s></f>"},{ID:99,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ti ta ūrīa küheanagwo nĩ andū a gūkũ thĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:100,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ti üguo ndaműhe. 
Mütigatangīke ngoro, </s></f>"},{ID:101,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kana mūgīe na guoya. 
Ni  mwaigua ūguo ndamwīra atī: </s></f>"},{ID:102,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ gūthiĩ ngūthĩi, na nĩ ngūũka kūrī inyuĩ. </s></f>"},{ID:103,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mũngīnyendete, nĩ mūngīakena, 
niī ündũ ng</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>thĩĩ gwĩ Ithe witũ; </s></f>"},{ID:104,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>amu Ithe witũ nĩ münene kūrī Nī. 
Na rĩu nĩ ndamūhe ühoro ūtanakinya, </s></f>"},{ID:105,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>atī nīguo warīkia gükinya, mügetīkia .</s></f>"},{ID:106,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injiri theru ya Mwathani.</s></f>"}],
