Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Katika kitabu changu cha kwanza, Theofilo,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> nilisimulia yote aliyofanya na kufundisha </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu toka mwanzo mpaka siku alipowapa mitume aliowachagua </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agizo kwa nguvu ya Roho Mtakatifu na kuchukuliwa mbinguni. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwao pia alijionyesha kwa uthibitisho mwingi ya </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kuwa yu hai baada ya mateso yake, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa muda wa siku arobaini aliwatokea na </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kusema nao juu ya ufalme wa Mungu.
Alipokuwa mezani pamoja nao,</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> aliwaamuru wasitoke Yerusalemu, bali waingoje </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"ahadi ya Baba, mliyosikia kutoka kwangu; </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yaani Yohane alibatiza kwa maji, bali ninyi </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mtabatizwa kwa Roho Mtakatifu baada ya siku chache.\"</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hapo wale waliokusanyika wakamwuliza, \"Bwana, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>je, wakati huu ndipo utakaporudisha upya ufalme wa Israeli?\"</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akawajibu,
\"Si shauri lenu kujua nyakati kamili </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>alizoweka Baba kwa uwezo wake.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Lakini mtapokea nguvu ya Roho Mtakatifu atakayewashukia, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na mtakuwa mashahidi wangu Yerusalemu,</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> na katika nchi yote ya Yudea, Samaria, na hata miisho ya dunia.\"</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Baada  ya maneno hayo, akainuliwa, mbele ya macho yao, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na wingu likampokea wasimwone tena.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Walipokazia bado macho juu mbinguni alikoenda yeye, </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>watu wawili wenye mavazi meupe walisimama
ghafula pembeni mwao. </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakasema, 
“Enyi watu wa Galilaya,</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> mbona mmesimama na kutazama juu mbinguni? </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Huyu Yesu aliyechukuliwa mbinguni kutoka kwenu </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>atakuja tena jinsi hiyo hiyo mlivyomwona akipaa mbinguni.\"</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Zaburi 
47:2-3, 6-7, 8-9 (K. 6)</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>(K) Mungu amepanda juu kwa kelele za shangwe; 
Bwana, kwa mlio wa baragumu.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Enyi watu wote, pigeni makofi;
mshangilieni Mungu kwa kelele za furaha.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwani Bwana Aliye Juu ni wa kutisha,
ni mfalme mkuu wa dunia yote. (K)</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>(K) Mungu amepanda juu kwa kelele za shangwe; 
Bwana, kwa mlio wa baragumu.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mungu amepanda juu kwa kelele za shangwe;
Bwana, kwa mlio wa baragumu.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwimbieni Mungu sifa, mwimbieni sifa;
mwimbieni mfalme wetu, mwimbieni sifa. (K)</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>(K) Mungu amepanda juu kwa kelele za shangwe; 
Bwana, kwa mlio wa baragumu.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Maana Mungu ni mfalme wa dunia yote;
imbeni wimbo wa shangwe.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mungu atawala juu ya mataifa;
Mungu ameketi katika kiti chake kitakatifu. (K)</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>(K) Mungu amepanda juu kwa kelele za shangwe; 
Bwana, kwa mlio wa baragumu.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA PILI
Waebrania 9:24-28</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika barua kwa Waebrania</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kristo hakuingia mahali patakatifu palipojengwa kwa mikono, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yaani mfano wa mahali patakatifu halisi, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>bali ameingia katika mbingu ya kweli,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> ili sasa amjongee Mungu badala yetu. </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wala hakuingia humo aJitoe mara nyingi kama kuhani mkuu </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>anayeingia mahali patakatilu kila mwaka </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mara moja akichukua damu isiyo yake. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kama ingekuwa hivyo, ingempasa </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kuteswa mara nyingi tangu mwanzo wa dunia.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Lakini sasa, mwisho wa nyakati ametokea </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mara moja tu aifute dhambi kwa sadaka yake.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na kama wanadamu walivyoamriwa </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kufa mara moja na baadaye kuhukumiwa, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndivyo Kristo alivyotolewa mara moja tu </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ili kuziondoa dhambi za wengi.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mara ya pili atatokea, si kwa sababu ya dhambi, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ila kwa ajili ya kuwaokoa wenye kumngojea.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Basi ndugu, tunayo fahari ya kuingia mahali patakatifu kwa damu
ya Yesu. </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yeye ametufungulia njia mpya iletayo uzima, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndiyo njia
ya pazia, yaani ya mwili wake.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tunaye \"Kuhani mkuu aliyewekwa juu ya nyumba ya Mungu.\"</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa hiyo tujongee kwa mioyo minyofu na imani kamili, maana</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mioyo yetu imenyunyiziwa na kusafishwa dhamiri mbaya, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na
miili yetu imeogeshwa katika maji safi. </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na tuyashikilie matumaini
tunayoungama bila kusitasita, </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa maana yeye aliyetoa ahadi
ni mwaminifu.</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SHANGILIO LA INJILI
Mathayo 28:19a, 20b</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Aleluya.
W. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nendeni, mkayafanye mataifa yote kuwa wafuasi,</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tazama, nipo nanyi siku zote mpaka mwisho wa dahari.</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>INJILI
Luka 24:46-53</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Luka</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakati ule: Yesu aliwaambia wafuasi wake, </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Ndivyo ilivyoandikwa
kwamba Kristo atateswa na kufufuka katika wafu siku ya tatu.</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kwa jina lake ihubiriwe toba na maondoleo ya dhambi kwa</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mataifa yote, kuanzia Yerusalemu. Ninyi ni mashahidi wa mambo
hayo. </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Angalieni, mimi ninawatumia ahadi ya Baba yangu. </s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Lakini
ninyi kaeni mjini hata mvikwe nguvu toka juu.\"</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Toka hapo akawapeleka Bethania, akainua mikono yake,
akawabariki. </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tazama, katika kuwabariki alijitenga nao,
akachukuliwa mbinguni. </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakamwabudu, kisha wakarudi
Yerusalemu kwa furaha kubwa. </s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na daima walikuwa hekaluni
wakimsifu Mungu.</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f>"}],
