Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MATHAYO:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na rĩrĩ, hĩndĩ ĩrĩa  Yesu aciarĩirũo Bethlehemu, itũũra rĩa Judea,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>matukũ ma mũthamaki wetagwo Herode, gũgĩũka andũ ogĩ </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>a njata Jerusalem, moimire kũrĩa irathĩro-inĩ, makĩũria atĩrĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>“Ũrĩa ũciarĩtwo e mũthamaki wa Ayahudi, arĩ ha?”</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tondũ nĩ twonire njata yake kũrĩa irathĩro-inĩ, na nĩ tũũkĩte </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>tũmuturirĩe ndu tũmũgooce.  Na rĩrĩa Herode, ũcio ,mũthamaki, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>aaiguire ũhoro ũcio akĩĩgua ũũru, we mwene o na Jerusalem </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>guothe hamwe nake. Agĩkĩũngania athĩnjĩri Ngai arĩa anene othe na </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>aandĩki-marũa a kĩrĩndĩ, akĩmoria harĩa Kristũ agaciarĩrũo. </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nao makĩmwĩra, Nĩ Bethlehem, itũũra rĩa Judea, tondũ nĩ </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kwandĩkĩtwo nĩ mũrathi ũũ: Nawe Bethlehem,</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o kũu bũrũri wa Judea, tiwe ũrĩa mũnyinyi  mũno wa aathani a Juda: </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>tondũ rĩ, nĩ kũrĩ wee gũkoima ũrĩa agaathanaga, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o ũrĩa ũkarĩithagia andũ akwa Israeli”. Hĩndĩ ĩo Herode agĩĩta andũ </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>acio ogĩ a njata na hitho, 
agĩtuĩria wega kũrĩ o hĩndĩ ĩrĩa njata </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>yonekire. Akĩmatũma Bethlehem, akĩmera, thiĩi, </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mũgatuĩrie wega ũhoro wa gakenge kau, na mwakona, cokai mũhe </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũhoro, nĩ getha na niĩ thiĩ ngagaturĩrie ndu ndĩkagooce. Nao </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>maaigua ũrĩa mũthamaki ũcio aamerire,</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> magĩĩthiĩra; na rĩrĩ, njata ĩrĩa monire o kũrĩa irathĩro-inĩ ĩkamathiĩ mbere, o nginya ĩkĩrũgama igũrũ rĩa harĩa gakenge kau kaarĩ</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>.  Nao mona njata ĩo, magĩkena gĩkeno kĩnene mũno. </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Magĩtonya nyũmba, makĩona gakenge karĩ na nyina Maria, </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Makĩĩgũithia thĩ, magĩkagooca.  Makĩohora indo ciao cia goro na cio ciarĩ thahabu, ũbani na manemane. </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Na tondũ wa gũkanio nĩ Ngai na kĩroto, atĩ matigacokere kũrĩ Herode, magĩcoka bũrũri wao na njĩra ĩngĩ.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s></f>"}],
Text:"THIGUKUU YA EPIPHANIA MWAKA C"},{Guid:"VwwfQTLvREGga09Y7LLXbA",Verses:[{
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1384>KIUMIA KIA MBERE GIA KWADRAJESMA MWAKA C</s></f></u>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE
Deuter. 26:4-10</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA GŨCOKERITHIA MAATHANI: </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Musa agĩgĩĩta kĩrĩndĩ na akĩmera atĩrĩ: Mũthĩnjĩri </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ngai aiyũkie kĩondo kĩu, akĩruta guoko gwaku,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> akĩige thĩ o hau mbere ya kĩgongona kĩa Mwathani Ngai waku.  </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nawe hĩndĩ ĩo ũgagĩcokia uugĩre  o hau mbere ya Mwathani Ngai waku atĩrĩ:</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Baba aarĩ Mũsuriata worũraga; nake agĩgĩikũrũka agĩthiĩ Misri, agĩtũũra kuo e mũgeni, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>andũ ake marĩ anyinyi mũno magĩtarũo; nao magĩkĩingĩhĩra kuo </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>magĩtuĩka rũrĩrĩ rũnene, na rũĩ  hinya, na rũa andũ aingĩ mũno; </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nao andũ a Misri magĩtũhinyĩrĩria, na magĩtũnyarira, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>magĩtũigĩrĩra mawĩra ma hinya mũno matũtuĩte ngombo ciao:</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ithuĩ tũgĩgĩkaĩra Mwathani Ngai wa maithe maitũ; </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nake Mwathani akĩigua gũkaya kũu gwitũ, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nake akĩona ũrĩa tũranyarirũo, o na wĩra ũrĩa tũrarutithio wa hinya, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na kũhinyĩrĩrio kũrĩa tũrahinyĩrĩrio;</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> nake Mwathani agĩtũruta Misri,  na njara irĩ hinya, o na guoko gũtambũrũkĩtio, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hamwe na maũndũ ma kũguoyohania mũno, na kũringa ciama,</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> o na maũndũ ma kũgegania; nake nĩ atũrehete kũndũ gũkũ, agatũhe bũrũri ũyũ,</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> o bũrũri wĩ bũthi wa iria, o na ũũkĩ.  Na atĩrĩrĩ, wee Mwathani, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>rĩu nĩ ndakũrehere maciaro ma mbere ma thĩ ĩno ũheete. </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Nawe ũkĩmaige thĩ mbere ya Mwathani Ngai waku, </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũcoke ũinamĩrĩre mbere ya Mwathani Ngai waku, ũmũhoe.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Thaburi 
</s></f><fArial Black><s1384>91:1-2,10-11,12-13;14-15</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
Tũũrania na ithuĩ, Mwathani, magerio-inĩ maitũ.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ũrĩa ũtũire ahithĩtwo ũhitho-inĩ wa Ũrĩa-wĩ-Igũrũ-mũno </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>arĩikaraga kĩĩgunyĩ-inĩ kĩa Mwene-Hinya. </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ngũkiuga atĩrĩ, ũhoro wa Mwathani, atĩ, nĩwe irahĩro rĩakwa </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o gwata gĩikaro gĩakwa kĩirigĩre nĩwe Ngai wakwa, ũrĩa ndĩĩhokete.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
Tũũrania na ithuĩ, Mwathani, magerio-inĩ maitũ.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Gũtikĩrĩ ũũru o na ũrĩkũ ũgakũnyita, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gũtirĩ itũhũhũ rĩngĩthengerera hema yaku.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ gũkorũo  nĩ agaatha araika ake nĩ ũndũ</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>waku, makũmenyagĩrĩre ikĩro-inĩ ciaku ciothe.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
Tũũrania na ithuĩ, Mwathani, magerio-inĩ maitũ.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Marĩgũkuuaga ndayaya na hĩ ciao, ndũkae gũkahĩngwo kũgũrũ nĩ ihiga.  </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ũgakinyĩrĩria mũrũthi,</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> o na nduĩra; ngatia ĩrĩa nyanake, o gwata</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndamathia-rĩ, ũitereme na magũrũ. </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
Tũũrania na ithuĩ, Mwathani, magerio-inĩ maitũ.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kuona nĩ anyitĩtie wendo harĩ niĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tondũ ũcio nĩ ndĩĩmũhatũraga hatĩ-inĩ; </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndĩĩmũigaga handũ haraya na igũrũ,</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> nĩ ũndũ nĩ amenyete rĩĩtwa rĩakwa.  </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Arĩngayagĩra, 
na niĩ ngamwamũkĩria; </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ ndĩrĩikaraga nake hingo ya mĩnyamaro,</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> ndĩrĩmũtharaga harĩ yo, na kũmũtĩithia ndĩmũtĩithie.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
Tũũrania na ithuĩ, Mwathani, magerio-inĩ maitũ.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA 
         IGĨRĨ					                            </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Aroma 10:8-13</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A ROMA:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, ũhoro ũcio uugaga atĩa? Uugaga atĩrĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>atĩ uuge ũrĩa mũreheirũo-rĩ, ũrĩ o hakuhĩ nawe,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> o kanua-inĩ gaku na ngoro-inĩ yaku.  </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Naguo uuge ũcio nĩ ũrĩa wa wĩtĩkio, o ũrĩa ithuĩ tũhunjagia. </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Tondũ-rĩ, ũngiumbũra na kanua gaku atĩ Yesu nĩwa Mwathani, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na gwĩtĩkia wĩtĩkie na ngoro yaku atĩ Ngai nĩ aamũriũkirie oime kũrĩ arĩa akuũ, no ũhonoke:</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> nĩ gũkorũo nĩ ngoro mũndũ etĩkagia nayo agagĩtuwo mũthingu, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na nĩ kanua oimbũraga  nako agakĩhonoka.  Tondũ Maandĩko mekuuga atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mũndũ o wothe ũmwĩhokete rĩ, ndarĩ hĩndĩ agaconorithio.  </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Amu ũhoro wa gũthurania Mũyahudi na Mũyunani gũtirĩ:</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ gũkorũo Mwathani o ro ũcio nowe Mwathani wa andũ othe, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na aikaraga o agĩtanahagĩra othe arĩa mamũkayagĩra.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ ũndũ nĩ haandĩke atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mũndũ o wothe ũgakaĩra rĩĩtwa rĩa Mwathani nĩ akahonoka.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI
Mathayo 4:4
	</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Rũgoco gwaku, Mwathani, Mũnene wa ũkumio ũtarĩ mũhaka. </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ti mũgate wiki ũtũũragia mũndũ muoyo, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>no kiugo o gĩothe kĩrĩa kiumaga kanua ka Ngai.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Rũgoco gwaku, Mwathani, Mũnene wa ũkumio ũtarĩ mũhaka.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI
Luka 4:1-13</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE LUKA:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hĩndĩ ĩo Yesu akiuma kũu Jordano aiyũrĩtwo nĩ Muoyo </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mũtheru, agĩtwarũo nĩ Muoyo werũ-inĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>aikare kũu matukũ mĩrongo ĩna, akĩgeragio nĩ shaitani.  </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na matukũ macio ndaarĩaga kĩndũ o na kĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>namo maathira, akĩhũta.  Nake shaitani akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ongorũo wee nĩwe Mũrũ wa Ngai, ĩra ihiga rĩrĩ rĩtuĩke mũgate. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake Yesu akĩmũcokeria akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ũhoro nĩ wandĩkĩtwo atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ti mũgate wiki ũtũũragia mũndũ muoyo. </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ningĩ agĩcoka akĩmũtwara kĩrĩma igũrũ, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akĩmuonia mothamaki mothe ma thĩ o kahinda kanini ma.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake shaitani agĩcoka akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wathani wa gwathaga kũu guothe nĩ ngũkũhe, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na mwago wakuo:</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ ũndũ kũheo nĩ heetwo niĩ: na mũndũ o ũrĩa ingĩenda kũhe, ndamũhe.   </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio-rĩ, ũngĩĩtĩkĩra kũndurĩria ndu o haha ndĩ, ũhoe,</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũcio wothe nĩ ũgũtuĩka waku.  </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake Yesu akĩmũcokeria akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ũhoro nĩ wandĩkĩtwo atĩrĩ:</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Turagĩria Mwathani Ngai waku ndu ũmũhoyage, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ũmũtungatagĩre o we wiki.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Agĩcoka akĩmũtwara Jerusalemu, 
akĩmũrũgamia o igũrũ </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gathũrũmũndũ-inĩ ka hekarũ, akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ongorũo wee nĩwe Mũrũ wa Ngai, wĩtungumanie thĩ uumĩte haha: </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ gũkorũo ũhoro nĩ wandĩkĩtwo atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ agaatha araika ake nĩ ũndũ waku, nĩ getha magũikaragie: </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ningĩ atĩrĩ: Nĩ magakwanĩrĩria na moko mao, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndũkae kũgũthwo kũgũrũ nĩ ihiga.  Nake Yesu </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akĩmũcokeria atĩrĩ: Ningĩ nĩ kwĩranĩtwo atĩrĩ:</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndũkanagerie Mwathani Ngai waku.  
Nake shaitani aarĩkia </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kũmũgeria magerio macio mothe, agĩtigana nake ihinda.</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s></f>"}],Style:{Background:{Image:"Bible.jpg",Luminosity:-40}},
Text:"KIUMIA KIA MBERE GIA KWADRAJESMA MWAKA C"},{Guid:"EXTieS4wL0y5uXnzatMSDw",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>KIUMIA KIA ITHATU KIA WINYEREREKIA MWAKA C </s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE			             	         Thama 3: 1-8,13-15</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA THAMA:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Mĩthenya-inĩ ĩo, Musa nĩ gũkorũo aakorirũo akĩrĩithia ndĩithia ya mũthoniwe jethero mũthĩnjĩri </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ngai wa Madian, nake akĩmĩtwara mbarĩ ĩrĩa ĩngĩ ya werũ wakuo, </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>agĩkinya  kĩrĩma-inĩ kĩa Ngai na kũu Horeb.  Nake mũraika wa Mwathani akĩmuumĩrĩra arĩ rũrĩrĩmbĩ-inĩ rũa mwaki ruoimaga kĩhinga-inĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>agĩcũthĩrĩria, na atĩrĩ, kĩhinga kĩu nĩ mwaki gĩakanaga, na gĩtingĩhĩa.  Nake Musa akiuga atĩrĩ: Rĩu nĩ ngũkerũra naho, nĩ getha nyone kĩũndũ gĩkĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>‘menye kĩrĩa gĩkũgiria kĩhinga kĩhĩe.  Nake Mwathani ona atĩ egũkerũra naho nĩguo one wega-rĩ, we Ngai agĩkĩmwĩta e kĩhinga-inĩ kĩu thĩ-inĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>akiuga atĩrĩ: Musa, Musa.  Nake agĩcokia atĩrĩ: Niĩ ũyũ.  Agĩkiuga atĩrĩ: Menya ũkuhĩhĩrie haha; amba ũrute iratũ ciaku magũrũ,</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076> nĩ gũkorũo hau ũrũngiĩ nĩ handũ hatheru.  O na ningĩ agĩcoka akiuga atĩrĩ: Nĩ niĩ Ngai wa thoguo, Ngai wa Abraham, Ngai wa Isaka,</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076> Ngai wa Jakobu.  Nake Musa akĩhitha ũthiũ tondũ nĩ etigagĩra gũcũthĩrĩria Ngai.  Nake Mwathani akiuga atĩrĩ:</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076> Ti-itherũ nĩ nyonete mĩnyarirĩko ya andũ akwa arĩa marĩ Misri, na ngaigua kĩrĩro kĩao nĩ ũndũ wa akaburũ akuo, tondũ nĩ njũĩ maruo marĩa marĩ namo; </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>na niĩ ngĩikũrukĩte nĩguo ndĩmateithũre moko-inĩ ma andũ a Misri, ndĩmarute bũrũri ũcio, ndĩmahire bũrũri mwega mwariĩ, wa bũthi wa iria na ũũkĩ.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nake Musa akĩũria Ngai atĩrĩ: Rĩrĩa ngakinya kũrĩ ciana cia Israeli, ndĩciĩre ũũ: Ngai wa maithe manyu nĩwe ũndeketie kũrĩ inyuĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>nacio injũrie atĩrĩ: Agĩĩtagwo atĩa? Ngagĩciĩra atĩa hihi? Nake Ngai akĩĩra Musa atĩrĩ: Niĩ ndũire o ta ũrĩa ndũire; agĩcoka akiuga atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Ĩra ciana cia Israeli ũũ, atĩ ũrĩa wĩtagwo Niĩ ndũire, nĩwe ũndũmĩte kũrĩ inyuĩ.  O na ningĩ Ngai akĩĩra Musa atĩrĩ: Ĩra ciana cia Israeli ũũ, </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>atĩ Mwathani, o we Ngai wa maithe manyu, o we Ngai wa Abraham, Ngai wa Isaka, Ngai wa Jakobu, nĩwe ũndũmĩte kũrĩ inyuĩ,; </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>rĩu nĩrĩo rĩĩtwa rĩakwa tene na tene, na norĩo kĩririkania gĩakwa o nginya njiarũa na njiarũa.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                     Thaburi 103:1-2;3-4 8 na 10;12-13</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ICOKIA	
Mwathani nĩ wa matha maingĩ, na nĩ muuma andũ mũno</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Ngoro yakwa, gatha Mwathani; gwata kĩrĩa o gĩothe gĩĩ thĩinĩ wakwa nĩ kĩgathe rĩĩtwa rĩake rĩamũre. </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076> Ngoro yakwa, kĩgathe Mwathani, na ndũkariganĩrũo nĩ wega o na ũmwe marĩa agwĩkaga. </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ICOKIA	
Mwathani nĩ wa matha maingĩ, na nĩ muuma andũ mũno</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Arĩ we ũkuohagĩra waganu waku wothe, ndũari ciaku ciothe o nacio nowe mũkũhonia; </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>o we mũkũũri muoyo waku harĩ irima rĩa gĩkuũ, na nowe mũgwĩki maũndũ ma ũtugi na ma matha maingĩ, ta arĩ thũmbĩ aragwĩkĩra ya ũnene.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ICOKIA	
Mwathani nĩ wa matha maingĩ, na nĩ muuma andũ mũno</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Mwathani nĩ wa matha maingĩ nĩ muuma-andũ mũno; ndahiũhaga kũrakara, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>na e na ũtugi mũingĩ.  Ndatwĩkĩte ta ũrĩa mahĩtia maitũ maagĩrĩirũo, kana agatũcokeria kũringana na ũrĩa waganu witũ ũigana.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ICOKIA	
Mwathani nĩ wa matha maingĩ, na nĩ muuma andũ mũno</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>O ta ũrĩa irathĩro kũraihanĩrĩirie na ithũĩro, no taguo atũthengeirie mehia maitũ matũraihĩrĩrie.  </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076> O ũrĩa mũthuri aiguagĩra ciana ciake tha, noguo Mwathani aiguagĩra arĩa mamwĩtigĩrĩte.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ICOKIA	
Mwathani nĩ wa matha maingĩ, na nĩ muuma andũ mũno</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ
1 Akorintho 10: 1-6,10-12</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A KORINTHO:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Amu rĩrĩ, ariũ a Ithe witũ ndikwenda mwage kũmenya atĩ </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>maithe maitũ arĩa a tene, othe maaikaraga mahumbĩirũo nĩ itu </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>rĩrĩa, na magĩtuĩkania othe maaĩ-inĩ ma iria rĩrĩa; othe </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>magĩgĩtuĩka ta makĩbatithĩtio matuĩke andũ a Musa, marĩ itu-inĩ </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>rĩu o na iria-inĩ rĩu; 
na magĩtũũra marĩaga irio o imwe othe, iria </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>cia muoyo, na makanyuaga gĩa kũnyua o kĩmwe othe, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>o kĩrĩa gĩa muoyo; nĩ gũkorũo maanyuaga maaĩ moimĩte </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ndũmba-inĩ ya ihiga yarĩ ya muoyo ĩrĩa yarũmanagĩrĩra  nao, nayo ndũmba</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ĩo ya ihiga nĩ Kristũ.  
No rĩrĩ, arĩa aingĩ mũno-rĩ, Ngai ndaigana </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>gũkenio nĩo; amu nĩ kũng’aũranio mang’aũranĩirio nĩwe werũ-inĩ.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Rĩu-rĩ, maũndũ macio maatuĩkire ta igerekanio cia ũhoro witũ,</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>nĩ getha ithuĩ tũtikanatuĩke  erirĩria a maũndũ moru ta ũrĩa andũ </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>acio maameriragĩria.
O na mũtigatete, ta ũrĩa andũ acio </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>amwe maatetire, na magĩkĩninwo nĩ ũrĩa mũninani.  </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Na rĩrĩ, maũndũ macio mothe monĩre maarĩ ta igerekanio,</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>na makĩandĩkwo matuĩke ma gũtũtaara ithuĩ, o ithuĩ </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>tũkinyĩrĩirũo nĩ marigĩrĩrio ma mahinda maya ma ndũire.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Tondũ ũcio-rĩ, mũndũ ũkwĩĩra atĩ nĩ ehandĩte </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ki, nĩ emenyagĩrĩre ndakae kũgũa.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI
Mathayo 4:17
	</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Rũgoco na gĩtĩo gwaku, Mwathani Yesu.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Mwathani akiuga atĩ: Wĩrirei; tondũ ũthamaki wa Igũrũ nĩ ũkuhĩhĩirie.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Rũgoco na gĩtĩo gwaku, Mwathani Yesu.</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI
Luka 13:1-9</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE LUKA:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Hĩndĩ ĩo nĩ haarĩ andũ amwe ho maamwĩrire ũhoro wa Agalilea arĩa </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Pilato aatukanirie thakame yao na ĩrĩa ya nyamũ ciao cia magongona. </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Nake akĩmacokeria akĩmoria atĩrĩ: Githĩ mũgwĩciria atĩ Agalilea </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>acio maarĩ ehia gũkĩra Agalilea  othe, kuona atĩ nĩ maanyaririrũo </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ũguo? Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ: Tiguo: no rĩrĩ, mũngĩaga kwĩrira, inyuothe </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>mũkaninwo o tao. Kana andũ acio ikũmi na anana-rĩ, o arĩa </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>maagũĩrĩirũo nĩ nyũmba ĩrĩa ndaya na igũrũ kũu Siloe, ĩkĩmoraga,</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>githĩ mũkĩũĩ atĩ nĩ maahĩtĩtie gũkĩra andũ othe arĩa maatũire </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Jerusalemu? Ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ: Tiguo: no rĩrĩ, mũngĩaga kwĩrira, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>inyuothe mũkaninwo o tao.  Nake akĩaria na ngerekano ĩno,</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>akiuga atĩrĩ: Mũndũ ũmwe aarĩ na mũkũyũ wahandĩtwo </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>mũgũnda wake wa mĩthabibũ; nake agĩũka gũcaria maciaro </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>mũtĩ-inĩ ũcio, akĩmaaga.  Agĩcoka akĩĩra mũcehi wa mĩthabibũ, atĩrĩrĩ:</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>rĩu nĩ mĩaka ĩtatũ njũkaga gũcaria  maciaro mũkũyũ-inĩ ũyũ, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>o ngĩmaagaga: ũũteme, wĩkagĩra mũgũnda kiura nĩkĩ? Nake mũcehi </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>agĩcokia akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Mwathani, reka ũikare mwaka ũyũ o naguo, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>o kinya ndĩũrĩmĩre, na ndĩũitĩrĩrie thumu: na thutha wa ũguo, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>ũgĩciara, nĩ wega; na ũngĩaga gũciara, no ũtemwo.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s></f>"}],
Text:"KIUMIA KIA ITHATU KIA WINYEREREKIA MWAKA C"},{Guid:"sPdrD3katUqD2/T6ltQ7TA",Verses:[{Style:{Background:{Image:"Bible.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Githomo kia mbere
 (Joeli 2: 12-18)</s></f>"},{ID:3,Style:{Background:{Image:"Bible.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani ekuga uu: </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Njokererai na ngoro cianyu ciothe, na mwihinge kūrīa irio, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mũkirīraga maithori 
mūgwatitwo ni kieha. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tembürangai ngoro cianyu, 
na mūtigatembūrange </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o nguo cianyu ciiki, 
mūcokerere mwathani Ngai wanyu; </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ ũndū we ni mwega, na ning</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ỉ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> n</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ỉ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> wa tha, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ndahiûhaga kūrakara, no niaiyûirüo ni ūtugi, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akericükagwo agatiga gwika andü üūru. </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nũ ūũi kana niangigarūrūka ericūkwo, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>atige aatũrathima, 
atûhe indo cia kürutagira </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani  Ngai wanyu 
magongona ma mûtu, </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ona ma indo iria irutagwo cia kūnyuwo?</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Huhai karumbeta kūu Zayuni mūraarīrie gīathi kiamüre </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gia kwihinga kūria irio; îtanai müraarīrie </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gitüngano gikonii andū othe; cokanīririai andū, </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na mwamūre kirindi kianyu mūgitherie; 
mūcokaniririe athuri akūrů, </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ciana, o na tũkenge; 
mühikania nioimagare </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>oime kanyūmba gake ka na thi-inii
o nake muhiki aume kiriri</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Athinjiri-Ngai, o acio atungatiri Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nimarire marüngii gatagati ka githaku </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kigongona, moige atiri, 
Caira andū aku, Wee Mwathani; </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>menya üreke ůgai waku ūmenwo, niguo ati andū aku moinwo thimo </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>a ndūriri moranie üū: Kai Ngai wao akiri ha?</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hindi io Mwathani agīkiirutanīria </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ni ündů wa bürūri wake, na akiiguira andü ake tha.  </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{Style:{Background:{BodyRect:"0,0,10000,9300"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Thaburi 
</s></f><fArial Black><s1384>51:1-2;10-11;12-15</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
Tuiguire tha Mwathani, tondu ni tuhititie</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nginyĩria wega waku, Ngai, kũringana na ũrĩa ũtugi waku ũigana; </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tondũ wa ũguo matha maku marĩ maingĩ-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tharia mehia makwa o gũtharia.  </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Thambia mũno, waganu wakwa ũthire, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>‘theria mahĩtia makwa maninũke.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
Tuiguire tha Mwathani tondu ni tuhititie</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Amu ni njui mehia makwa, o nii mwene mahitia makwa </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ngakimonaga o ro hingo ciothe.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wee niwe njihitie wee wiki ngeka uria wee wagwata kwaria ni </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kihooto uri nakio wee ugitua cira-ri, ugituike uri o mutheru</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
Tuiguire tha Mwathani tondu ni tuhititie</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ngai, nyũmbĩra ngoro ĩtarĩ na gĩko; </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>thĩinĩ wakwa cokia muoyo mwerũ, mwĩkindĩru.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndũkanyingate nyume harĩ wee, na ndũkana </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>‘thengerie muoyo waku mũtheru</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
Tuiguire tha Mwathani tondu ni tuhititie</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hũndũrĩra gĩkeno kĩrĩa kĩa ũhonokio waku, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ũndiirĩrĩre na muoyo mweyenderi.  </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani, tumura miromo yakwa, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kanua gakwa ni gagukionania kugoocwo gwaku.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
Tuiguire tha Mwathani tondu ni tuhititie</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GITHOMO KIA IGIRI</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>2 Akorintho 
5: 20 ; 6: 20</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GUTHOMA KUUMA MARUA MA MUTHURE PAUL KURI ANDU A KORINTHO:</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ariu a Ithe witu,tukiri arekio mareketio a kwaririria Kristu, </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o ta ari Ngai urathaithana na tunua twitu;</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>twamuthaitha ithenya ria Kristu atiri: </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>itikirai kuiguithanio na Ngai. </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ngai ni aatumire ucio utari hingo aamenyire wihia atuike </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o wihia ari we ithenya riitu,
ni getha ithui,ni undu wa uria </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>twi thiini wake,tutuike o uthingu wa Ngai.</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na tondu wa uria turi aruti wira hamwe nake,</s></f>"},{ID:23,
