Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Lakini walipomjia Yesu na kumwona amekwisha kufa,
hawakumvunja miguu,</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ila askari mmojawapo alimchoma ubavu kwa mkuki,
mara ikatoka damu na maji.</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Aliyeona hayo, ameyashuhudia, na ushuhuda wake ni kweli;</s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>naye anajua ya kuwa anasema kweli, ili ninyi pia mpate kusadiki.</s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Maana hayo yametendeka, ili andiko litimie lisemalo:</s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Hatavunjwa mfupa hata mmoja.\"
Tena andiko lingine lasema: </s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Watamtazama yule waliyemchoma.\"</s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Bwana</s></f>"}],
