</k></c></s></f></u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFD8D800>Mhubiri 1:2; 2:21-23</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika kitabu cha Mhubiri</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ubatili mtupu! Mhubiri anasema, Ubatili mtupu! Yote ni ubatili</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa sababu mwangalieni mtu aliyejikaza sana </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa hekima na
kwa elimu, akapata faida: </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>naye atamwachia mwingine asiyetaabika</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>katika kazi hiyo 
urithi wa mali yake: </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hilo pia ni ubatili na uovu mkuu
Kwa maana mtu atapata nini kwa taabu zake zote, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kwa bidii   ya moyo wake, aliyoshughulika nayo chini ya jua? </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Siku zake zote zimejaa mateso, kazi zake zina uchungu: hata usiku </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>moyo wake
haupumziki: hilo pia ni ubatili.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
