</k></c></s></f></u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFD8D800>Zaburi 90:3--4, 
5-6, 12-13, 14 na 17 (K.1)</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFFF0000>K.</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000> </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFD8D800><kFFFF0000>Wewe Bwana, umekuwa makao yetu toka kizazi hata kizazi.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>1.Unamrudisha mtu mavumbini,
ukisema, </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Rudini, enyi wanadamu!\"
Maana miaka elfu machoni pako</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ni kama siku ya jana iliyopita,
kama kesha la usiku. K.</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFD8D800><kFFFF0000>Wewe Bwana, umekuwa makao yetu toka kizazi hata kizazi.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>2.Unawaondoa wakawa kama usingizi asubuhi;
kama majani yanayotokomea.</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Asubuhi yana maua na kuwa mabichi:
jioni yanafifia na kukauka. K.</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFFF0000>K.</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000> </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFD8D800><kFFFF0000>Wewe Bwana, umekuwa makao yetu toka kizazi hata kizazi.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>3.Utufundishe kuzihesabu siku zetu vyema,
tujipatie moyo wenye hekima.</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Urudi, ee Bwana! Mpaka lini?
Uwahurumie watumishi wako! K. </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFD8D800>K.</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFD8D800> </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFD8D800><kFFFF0000>Wewe Bwana, umekuwa makao yetu toka kizazi hata kizazi.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>4.Utushibishe upesi kwa huruma yako,
nasi tutashangilia na kufurahi siku zetu zote.</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Uzuri wa Bwana Mungu wetu uwe juu yetu.</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kazi ya mikono yetu uistawishe!
Kazi ya mikono yetu uiimarishe! K.</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFFF0000>K.</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000> </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFD8D800><kFFFF0000>Wewe Bwana, umekuwa makao yetu toka kizazi hata kizazi.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>SOMO LA PILI
</k></c></s></f></u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFD8D800>Wakolosai 3:1-5,9-11</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika barua ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Wakolosai</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndugu zangu: Ikiwa mmefufuliwa pamoja na Kristo,</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> yatafuteni yaliyo juu anakokaa Kristo kuume kwa Mungu. </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Zingatieni yaliyo juu, si mambo ya duniani. </s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Maana mmekwisha kufa, na uzima wenu umefichika</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>pamoja na Kristo katika utukufu. </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Baadaye Kristo aliye uzima wetu atakapotokea, </s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ninyi pia mtatokea pamoja naye katika utukufu.</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa hiyo fisheni yaliyo ya kidunia ndani yenu kama uasherati,</s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>uchafu, ashiki, tamaa mbaya na choyo, yaliyo sawa na kuabudu</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Sanamu, Msiambiane uongo mkishauvua utu wa zamani pamoja na
matendo yake, </s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na mkishauvaa utu mpya na mkiwa mmetengenezwa</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>upya katika ujuzi kwa kadiri ya mfano wa mwumbaji wake</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ambapo hakuna tena Myunani wala Myahudi, </s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>aliyetahiriwa wala
asiyetahiriwa,</s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mgenı wala Mshenzi, </s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mtumwa wala mtu huru:
bali Kristo ni yote katika wote.</s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SHANGILIO LA INJILI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFD8D800>Mathayo 5:3</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>W. Aleluya.
K. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Heri walio maskini wa roho,
maana ufalme wa mbinguni ni wao.</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>W. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>INJILI
</k></c></s></f></u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFD8D800>Luka 12:13-21</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Luka</s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakati ule: Mtu mmoja katika umati alimwambia Yesu,</s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Mwalimu, mwanmbie ndugu yangu anigawie urithi.\"</s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akamjibu, \"Rafiki, nani 
ameniweka kuwa </s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hakimu au mwamuzi
katika mashauri yenu?\" </s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akauambia umati,
\"Angalieni, jihadharini na choyo zote, </s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa maana uzima wa mtu hautegenmei 
mali yake hata ikipita kiasi.\"</s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kisha akawasimulia mfano,
\"Shamba la mtu </s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tajiri lilizaa sana. 
Akawaza moyoni akasema,</s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>'Nitafanyaje kwa kuwa 
sina pa kuweka </s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mavuno yangu?\"
Akasema, Nitafanya hivi: </s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nitabomoa ghala zangu na kujenga
nyingine zilizo kubwa zaidi. </s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Humo nitaweka nafaka yangu yote
na mali yangu. </s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kisha nitajiambia, “Ee roho yangu, una vitu vingi,</s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ulivyojiwekea akiba kwa miaka mingi, basi, ustarehe, ule, unywe, uchangamke!\"</s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Lakini Mungu akamwambia:
Mjinga wewe, usiku huu wa leo roho yako itaitwa;</s></f>"},{ID:70,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na vitu ulivyojiwekea akiba, vitakuwa vya nani?</s></f>"},{ID:71,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hivi ndivyo itakavyokuwa kwa mwenye kujipatia </s></f>"},{ID:72,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hazina 
nyingi, na asiyejitajirisha kwa Mungu.\"</s></f>"},{ID:73,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f>"}],
