Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika kitabu cha Yoshua bin Sira</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ee mwanangu, utekeleze kazi zako kwa unyenyekevu,
nawe utapendwa kuliko anayetoa zawadi.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kadiri ulivyo mkubwa, ndivyo ujinyenyekeze;
nawe utapata neema mbele za Bwana.,</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Maana uwezo wa Bwana ni mkubwa;
naye hutukuzwa na wanyenyekevu.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yaliyo magumu mno kwako, usiyatafute, nayo yenye nguvu kuliko</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wewe usiyachunguze. Moyo wa mwenye akili utazitafakari mithali</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na sikio sikivu ni tamaa ya mwenye hekima.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
