Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Ee Mungu,kwa wema wako uliwahifadhi walioonewa.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>1.Watu wema wanafurahi;
Baba wa yatima, mlinzi wa wajane</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mbele ya Mungu wanachangamka wanashangilia kwa furaha.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwimbieni Mungu, lisifuni jina lake;
jina lake ni Bwana. K.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Ee Mungu,kwa wema wako uliwahifadhi walioonewa</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>.</k></s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>2.Baba wa yatima, mlinzi wa wajane</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndiye Mungu katika makao yake matakatifu,</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>walio pweke, Mungu huwaifadhi,
huwatoa wafungwa na kuwafanikisha. </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Ee Mungu,kwa wema wako uliwahifadhi walioonewa.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ulirejesha ardhi, ee 
Mungu; urithi 
wako ulipolegea, 
wewe uliutia nguvu.</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Watu wako wanakaa 
humo, mahali hapo ulimtengenezea mnyonge,</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kumjalia mvua nyingi ya baraka, ewe Mungu.</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Ee Mungu,kwa wema wako uliwahifadhi walioonewa</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>.</k></s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>SOMO LA PILI
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>Waebrania 12:18-19.22-24a</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika barua kwa Waebrania</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndugu zangu:
Hamjakaribia mlima uwezao kuguswa wala moto uwakao, </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wala
giza wala tufani, wala mvumo wa tarumbeta, </s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wala sauti ya maneno
iliowasababisha </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wasikilizaji kuomba 
isiendelee kusema nao.</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>lakini mmeukaribia Mlima sioni, mji wa Mungu aliye hai,</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yerusalemu ya ,mbinguni kwenye maelfu ya </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>malaika na mkutano
wa sherehe. </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na mmejiunga na jamii ya wazaliwa wa kwanza</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ambao majina yao walioandikwa mbinguní,</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na Mungu aliye
hakimu wa wote, pia na roho za waadilifu waliokamilika,</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kadhalika na Yesu, mpatanishi wa agano jipya.</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>SHANGILIO LA NJILI
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>Mathayo 11;29ab</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Aleluya. W. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Mjitwike nira yangu na kujifunza kwangu,
asema Bwana, </s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa maana mimi ni mpole
na mnyenyekevu wa moyo.</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>W. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>INJILI
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>Luka 14:1, 7-14</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Luka</s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Siku ya Sabato (Yesu] aliingia nyumba ya mkubwa mmojawapo
wa Mafarisayo ale chakula, </s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nao wakawa wakimchunguza kwa
makini.</s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akawaambia waalikwa mfano alipoona jinsi walivyojichagulia viti
vya heshima.</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>“Unapoalikwa na mtu harusini, usiketi katika</s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Labda mtu mwenye cheo kikubwa zaidi kuliko wewe amealikwa</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Naye aliyewaalika wewe na yeye asije akakuambia, ‘Mpe nafasi huyu.</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hapo utaanza kuona aibu na kushika mahali pa mwisho. </s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bali, ukialikwa, nenda kakae mahali pa mwisho, ili yule aliyekualika </s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Aje kukuambia, ‘Rafiki, kaa mbele zaidi.”</s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hapo utapata heshima mbele ya wote wenye kukaa mezani pamoja nawe. </s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa maana kila ajikwezaye atashushwa, na kila ajishushaye atakwezwa,”</s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kisha akamwambia na yule aliyemwalika,</s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>“Ufanyapo karamu kwa chakula cha mchana au jioni, usiwakaribishe</s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>rafiki zako, wala ndugu zako, wala jamaa zako, wala jirani zako</s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wenye uwezo, wasije wakakualika pia na kukulipa sawa kwa sawa</s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bali unapofanya karamu,</s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>uwaite maskini, vilema, viwete na vipofu; nawe utakuwa na heri.</s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa sababu hawana cha kukulipa.</s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa maana utalipwa katika ufufuko wa waadilifu.”</s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f>"}],
