Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE
Atũmwo 2:1-11</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU 
RĨA ATŨMWO:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na mũthenya wa Pentecoste wakinya-rĩ, acio othe magĩkorũo </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>marĩ o handũ hamwe. Na hĩndĩ o ĩo hagĩũka mũgambo uumĩte </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Igũrũ, ta wa rũhuho rũnene rũkĩhuhũkania,ũkĩiyũra nyũmba </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yothe ĩrĩa maaikaire thĩ; nao makiumĩrĩrũo nĩ nĩmĩ ciatariĩ ta </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩnĩmbĩ cia mwaki igayũkanĩte, 
nacio igĩikara igũrũ rĩa mũndũ </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o mũndũ. Nao othe makĩiyũrũo nĩ Muoyo Mũtheru, magĩitĩka </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gũthioma thiomi ingĩ o ta ũrĩa Muoyo aamahotithirie kwaria.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na hĩndĩ ĩo kũu Jerusalemu nĩ gwaikarĩte Ayahudi aigua-Ngai </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>moimĩte ndũrĩrĩ-inĩ ciothe cia thĩ. 
Na rĩrĩa mũgambo ũcio waiguirũo-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>andũ a kĩrĩndĩ  magĩcokanĩrĩra, 
makĩhagaiga tondũ o mũndũ o mũndũ </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ aamaiguaga makĩaria na mwarĩrie wa kwao kĩũmbe. </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nao othe makĩmaka makĩgegeara, makĩĩrana atĩrĩ: Githĩ aya othe </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maraaria ti a Galilea? 
Nao makĩaria-rĩ, nĩ kĩ gĩgũtũma </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tũmaigue makĩaria na mĩarĩrie iitũ, o mũndũ na mwarĩrie wake wa kũrĩa </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>aaciarĩirũo? Aparti na Amedi na Aelamiti, o na arĩa matũũraga </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mesopotamia, na Judea na Kapadocia, na Ponto na Asia, na Frijia na Panfilia, </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na Misri na ndwere cia Lĩbia iria irĩ gũkuhĩ na Cirene, na ageni moimĩte </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Roma, arĩa Ayahudi, o na arĩa megarũrĩte magatuĩka Ayahudi, </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na andũ a Creta na Aarabu, 
ithuothe-rĩ, tũkũigua </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>andũ aya makĩaria na mĩarĩrie iitũ </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maũndũ marĩa manene mekĩtwo nĩ Ngai.</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani
(NGAI AROCOCWO)</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO
                                 
Thaburi 
104: 1. 24; 29,30; 31. 34.</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA: Thĩ yothe, Mwathani, nĩ ĩiyũrĩtwo nĩ Muoyo waku.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ngoro yakwa, gatha Mwathani. Ĩ Mwathani, Ngai wakwa, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wee ũrĩ mũnene mũno; wĩguĩkĩte ũtĩĩku, o na ũkaru.  </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ĩ Mwathani, nĩ maingĩ atĩa mawĩra marĩa ũrutĩte! O mothe ũmarutĩte </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na wara; thĩ nĩ kũiyũra ĩiyũire ũrĩmi waku.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA: Thĩ yothe, Mwathani, nĩ ĩiyũrĩtwo nĩ Muoyo waku.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ningĩ ũkahitha ũthiũ, cio igagĩcanjama; ũcokagĩra mĩheehũ </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yacio, igakua, igacoka rũkũngũ-inĩ gwacio.
Gũtũma ũtũmaga </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>muoyo waku, nacio igakĩgĩa; ũthiũ wa thĩ ũgakĩwanakahia.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA: Thĩ yothe, Mwathani, nĩ ĩiyũrĩtwo nĩ Muoyo waku.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Riri wa Mwathani ũrotũũra tene o na tene; Mwathani arokenagĩra mawĩra </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>marĩa arutĩte. Macũrania makwa marogĩa na mũrĩo harĩ we: niĩ-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ Mwathani ndĩrĩkenaga nĩ ũndũ wake.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA: Thĩ yothe, Mwathani, nĩ ĩiyũrĩtwo nĩ Muoyo waku.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ
1 Akorintho 12:3-7. 12-13</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ AKORINTHO:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, gũtirĩ mũndũ 
ũngĩhota kuuga atĩ Yesu nĩwe </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani atarĩ na Muoyo Mũtheru. 
Na rĩrĩ, iheo iria iheanagwo </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ciumanĩte na Wega wa Ngai nĩ 
mĩthemba-mĩthemba, no rĩrĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Muoyo mwene cio no ũmwe. Mĩtungatĩre o nayo nĩ mĩthemba-mĩthemba, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na Mwathani mwene yo no ũmwe. O nayo mĩĩkĩre ya maũndũ </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ ĩtiganĩte mĩthemba, ĩndĩ Ngai no ũmwe, ũcio 
wĩkithagia maũndũ </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>macio mothe thĩinĩ wa andũ othe. 
No rĩrĩ, mũndũ o mũndũ aheagwo </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũndũ wake ũrĩa wonanagia atĩ arĩ na Muoyo nĩ getha 
ũndũ ũcio ũgune </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>andũ othe. Amu – rĩ, o ta ũrĩa mwĩrĩ wa mũndũ ũrĩ na ciĩga nyingĩ, na mwĩrĩ </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũcio no ũmwe, nacio ciĩga ciothe ciaguo,
o na ciatuĩka </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ nyingĩ, no mwĩrĩ o ũmwe-rĩ, ũguo no taguo ũhoro wa Kristũ ũtariĩ.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ gũkorũo ithuĩ twabatithirio ithuothe nĩ ũndũ wa Muoyo o ũmwe tũtuĩke mwĩrĩ </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o ũmwe, tũrĩ Ayahudi, kana tũrĩ Ayunani, o na kana twĩ ngombo kana </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tũtarĩ ngombo; na ithuothe tũgĩkĩnyuithio Muoyo o ũmwe.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani.
(NGAI AROGOCWO) </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>RUIMBO RWA INJIRI</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI
John 20: 19-23</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE JOHN:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mũthenya o ũcio wa kwambĩrĩria kiumia, gũkinyĩte hwai-inĩ, na mĩrango </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ĩkahingwo kũu arutwo maarĩ, nĩ ũndũ wa gwĩtigĩra Ayahudi,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu agĩũka akĩrũgama gatagatĩ-inĩ, akĩmera atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Gĩai na thayũ. Na aarĩkia kuuga ũguo, akĩmonia hĩ ciake  </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na mbaru. Nao arutwo mona Mwathani magĩkena.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu agĩkĩmera rĩngĩ atĩrĩ: Gĩai na thayũ; o ta ũrĩa Ithe witũ </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>aandekirie niĩ, noguo ndamũrekia inyuĩ. Na aarĩkia kuuga ũguo </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akĩmaheeherera, akĩmera: Iyũkiai Muoyo Mũtheru; andũ arĩa othe </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mwarekera mehia mao, nĩ maarekerũo; arĩa othe mwarega </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kũrekera mehia mao, megũikara matarekeirũo.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injiri theru ya Mwathani
(NITWAGUKUMIA WEE KRISTU)</s></f>"}],
Text:"KIUMIA KIA PENTEKOSTE MWAKA C"},{Guid:"pOU+r9eVl0aIG6DN8qIQTA",Verses:[{Style:{Background:{Image:"skyground1.jpg"}},
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFFFF66><kFFFF3F3F>DOMINIKA YA ISHIRINI NA TATU MWAKA C</k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFFFFF66><kFFFF3F3F>SOMO LA KWANZA
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846>Hekima ya Sulemani 
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>9:13-18b</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Samo katika kitabu cha Hekima ya Sulemaní</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>Nani kati ya wanadamu aweza kujua mashaurí ya </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFFFF66><kFFFF3F3F>Mungu</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>?</k></s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFF2F200> Au tafakari atakayo Bwana?</k></s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwani mawazo ya wenye kufa yana
woga, na fikra zetu zina hatari.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Maana, mwilí uharibikao huilemea</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>roho na hema ya udongo hukandamiza akili yenye kujaa mawazo.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ni vigumu kwetu kuyapambanua mambo ya duniani,</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ní kazi ngumu kuyaona yaliyo mikononi mwetu: </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>basi, yale yaliyo mbinguni nani atayachunguza? </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nani aliweza kuyajua mashauri yako, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>isipokuwa wewe ulimpa Hekima, </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kumpelekea roho yako
takatifu kutoka juu? </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndivyo yalivyonyoshwa mapito ya walio juu
ya nchi </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nao wanadamu walifundishwa mambo yanayokupendeza.</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFFFFF66><kFFFF3F3F>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFF2F200>Zaburi 
</k></s></f><fArial Black><s1384><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>90:34. 5-6, 12-13. 14 
na 17 (K 1)</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFFFF66><kFFFF3F3F>Wewe Bwana, umekuwa makao yetu toka kizazi hata kizazi.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>1.Unamrudisha mtu mavumbini,
ukisema, \"Rudini, enyi wanadamu!\"</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Maana miaka elfu machoni pako</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ni kama siku ya jana iliyopita,
kama kesha la usiku. K.</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFFFF66><kFFFF3F3F>Wewe Bwana, umekuwa makao yetu toka kizazi hata kizazi.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>2.Unawaondoa; wakawa kama usingizi asubuhi;
kama majani yanayotokomea.</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>asubuhi yana maua na kuwa mabichi;
jioni yanafifia na kukauka. K.</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFFFF66><kFFFF3F3F>Wewe Bwana, umekuwa makao yetu toka kizazi hata kizazi.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>3.Utufundishe kuzihesabu siku zetu vyema,
tujipatie moyo wenye hekima.</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Urudi, ee Bwana! Mpaka lini?
Uwahurumie watumishi wako! K.</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFFFF66><kFFFF3F3F>Wewe Bwana, umekuwa makao yetu toka kizazi hata kizazi.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>4.Utushibishe upesi kwa huruma yako,
nasi tutashangilia na kufurahi siku zetu zote.</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Uzuri wa Bwana Mungu wetu uwe juu yetu.</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kazi ya mikono yetu uistawishe!
Kazi ya mikono yetu uiimarishe! K.</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFFFF66><kFFFF3F3F>Wewe Bwana, umekuwa makao yetu toka kizazi hata kizazi</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFFFFF66><kFFFF3F3F>SOMO LA PILI
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFF2F200>Filemoni 
</k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>9b-10, 12-17</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika barua ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Filemoni</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mpendwa: Mimi Paulo, mzee, 
na sasa nikiwa nimefungwa gerezani</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa ajili ya Kristo Yesu. </s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ninakusihi kwa ajili ya mwanangu Onesimo
niliyemzaa nikíwa kifungoni. </s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Namrudisha kwako. Umpokee
kana kwamba ni moyo wangu. </s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ningalipenda akae kwangu na
kunitumikia badala yako </s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa muda wa kufungwa kwangu kwa ajili
ya Injili.</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Lakini pasipo ukubali wako sikutaka kufanya kitu, </s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kusudi tendo
lako jema lifanyike kwa hiari bila shuruti. </s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Labda kwa sababu
hii alitengana nawe kwa kitambo ili umpokee kwa daima, </s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>si kama mntumwa tena, bali zaidi ya mtumwa, </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yaani kama ndugu
mpendwa. </s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa namna ya pekee kwangu mimi ni ndugu lakini</s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>bila shaka kwako ni zaidi yaani yote katika mwili na katika Bwana. </s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Basi, ukinijali mimi kama mwenzio, umpokee yeye kama mimi.</s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFFFFF66><kFFFF3F3F>SHANGILIO LA INJILI
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846>Zaburi 
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>119:135</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Aleluya.
W. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Umwangazie mtumishi wako uso wako, </s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ee Bwana,
na unifundishe kanuni zako.</s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>W. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFFFFF66><kFFFF3F3F>INJILI
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFFFFFF><kFFF2F200>Luka</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200> 
14:25-33</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Luka</s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakati ule:</s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Watu wengi sana walifuatana na Yesu, akawageukia, akawaambia,</s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mtu akija kwangu bila ya kuwachukia baba na mama yake,</s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mke na watoto, ndugu zake, na hata nafsi yake mwenyewe,</s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hawezi kuwa mfuasi wangu. </s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mtu asiyechukua msalaba wake na
tanifuata, hawezi kuwa mfuasi wangu.</s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nani kati yenu anayenuia kujenga mnara haketi kwanza na</s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kuhesabu gharama kama mali yake yatosha kwa kuumaliza? </s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Asije
akaweka msingi, halafu akashindwa kumaliza, </s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hata watu wote
wanaoona wakaanza </s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kumcheka, wakisema, 
‘Mtu huyu alianza</s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kujenga, akashindwa kumaliza.</s></f>"},{ID:70,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Au mfalme gani anayetaka kwenda vitani apigane na mfalme</s></f>"},{ID:71,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mwingine haketi kwanza na kufanya shauri, </s></f>"},{ID:72,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kama ataweza na
askari elfu kumi kumshambulia</s></f>"},{ID:73,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> yule anayemjia na askari elfu
ishirini? </s></f>"},{ID:74,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kama sivyo, anatuma ujumbe kwake, angali mbali bado,</s></f>"},{ID:75,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>amwulize masharti ya amani.
Vivyo hivyo kila mmoja wenu </s></f>"},{ID:76,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>asiyeacha vyote alivyo navyo,
hawezi kuwa mfuasi wangu.”</s></f>"},{ID:77,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f>"}],Style:{Background:{Image:"skyground1.jpg"}},
Text:"DOMINIKA YA ISHIRINI NA TATU MWAKA C
"},{Guid:"lg+e16PfFEOCOay4mJbIGw",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>KIUMIA KIA ITHATHATU MWAKA C</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE
Jeremiah 17:5-8</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA MŨRATHI JEREMIA: </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hĩndĩ ĩo Mwathani ekuuga ũũ: Atĩrĩrĩ, kũgwatwo nĩ kĩrumi-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ mũndũ ũrĩa wĩhokaga andũ a gũkũ thĩ, o na kana </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akehotora ehokete hinya  wao, ngoro yake ĩgatirika Mwathani. </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nĩ gũkorũo agatuĩka  o ta kamũtĩ kĩng’ang’ĩtie werũ-inĩ   </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kũrĩa gũtarĩ wega o na ũrĩkũ ũngĩmũkinyĩra,
no egũtũũra </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kũndũ kũũmũ kwĩ nyota werũ-inĩ, o rũng’ũrĩ rũa cumbĩ </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>rũtatũũragwo nĩ andũ.
No rĩrĩ, gũkena-rĩ, nĩ mũndũ ũrĩa </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wĩhokaga Mwathani, na agatua  Mwathani mwĩhoko wake.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nĩ ũndũ agatuĩka o ta mũtĩ ũhandĩtwo hũgũrũrũ-inĩ cia maaĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũrĩa ũtambagia mĩri yaguo gũkuhĩ na rũũĩ; 
na rĩrĩa kwagĩa </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũrugarĩ wa riũa-rĩ, mũtĩ ũcio ndũngĩhoha, no ithangũ rĩaguo </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>rĩgũtũũra rĩrĩ iruru; na rĩrĩ, mũtĩ ta ũcio ndũrĩ ũndũ ũgĩũtanga mwaka </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wa wathima, na ndũngĩtiga gũciara maciaro.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                                 Thaburi 1:1-2;3;4 na 6</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA: Gũkena-rĩ, nĩ mũndũ ũrĩa arĩĩhokaga o Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Gũkena-rĩ, nĩ mũndũ ũrĩa ũtatwaranaga  na ũtaaro wa arĩa aaganu, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na ndarũgamaga njĩra-inĩ ya arĩa mehagia, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kana agaikaraga gĩtindo-inĩ kĩa andũ arĩa atendi.  No rĩ’, nĩ kĩrĩra kĩa </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani ekenagĩra nĩkĩo; na kĩrĩra kĩu gĩake </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akerurumagia ũhoro wakĩo mũthenya o na ũtukũ.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA: Gũkena-rĩ, nĩ mũndũ ũrĩa arĩĩhokaga o Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Agakĩhaanaga ta mũtĩ wahandirũo mĩtaro-inĩ ya maaĩ, aciaraga maciaro </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>maguo hingo yamo yakinya, mathangũ maguo namo matihohaga; nake, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũndũ o wothe egwĩka, nĩ ũgaacagĩra.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA: Gũkena-rĩ, nĩ mũndũ ũrĩa arĩĩhokaga o Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Arĩa aaganu matihaana ũguo; o matariĩ ta mũũngũ ũrĩa ũũmbũragwo </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ rũhuho. Amu Mwathani, 
nĩ njĩra ya arĩa </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>athingu oyaine nayo, nayo njĩra ya arĩa aaganu nĩ gũtoma ĩgatoma.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA: Gũkena-rĩ, nĩ mũndũ ũrĩa arĩĩhokaga o Mwathani.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ
1 Akorintho 15:12.16-20</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A KORINTHO MARĨA MA MBERE:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, ũhoro wa Kristũ ũngĩkorũo ũhunjagio atĩ nĩ </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kũriũkio aariũkirio-rĩ, kaĩ anyu amwe magĩcokaga kuuga </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>atĩ gũtirĩ kũriũka kwa arĩa akuũ atĩa? Amu korũo andũ arĩa akuũ </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>matiriũkagio-rĩ, Kristũ o nake ndakĩigana kũriũkio; na korũo </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kristũ ndaigana kũriũkio, gwĩtĩkia kwanyu gũtikĩrĩ kĩene; </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mehia manyu  o na rĩu mũgĩtũire o namo.  O na ningĩ andũ arĩa marĩkĩtie </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>gũkoma me thĩinĩ wa Kristũ-rĩ, 
o nao nĩ kũũra makĩũrĩte.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kũngĩgĩkorũo kwĩrĩgĩrĩĩra kũrĩa twĩrĩgĩrĩire Kristũ gũkoniĩ o muoyo</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũyũ tũtũire-rĩ, ithuĩ tũrĩ a kũũmĩrũo tha gũkĩra andũ arĩa angĩ othe. </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>No rĩrĩ, ũrĩa kũrĩ, nĩ atĩ Kristũ nĩ ariũkĩtio akoima kũrĩ arĩa akuũ, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>agagĩtuĩka mũtũrio wa andũ arĩa makomete.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI
Luk 6,23</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>	
Alleluya. Alleluya. Mwathani ekuuga ũũ: Kenai na mũtũhatũhe; </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ ũndũ-rĩ, igai rĩanyu nĩ rĩnene o Igũrũ. Alleluia</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI
Luka 6:17,20-26</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE LUKA:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hĩndĩ ĩo, Yesu, agĩikũrũka kĩrĩma nao, akĩrũgama handũ haaraganu,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>me na arutwo ake gĩkundi kĩnene,
na andũ aingĩ arĩa </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>moimĩte Judea guothe, na Jerusalemu, o na ndere-inĩ cia iria </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>rĩrĩa rĩnene  o kũrĩa Tiro na Sidone. Nake agĩtiirĩra 
arutwo ake maitho,</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akiuga atĩrĩ: Gũkena-rĩ, nĩ inyuĩ athĩni, nĩ gũkorũo Ũthamaki wa Ngai </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ wanyu. Gũkena-rĩ, nĩ inyuĩ mũhũtaga rĩu, nĩ gũkorũo nĩ</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mũgacoka kũhũnio. Gũkena-rĩ, nĩ onyuĩ  mũrĩraga rĩu, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ gũkorũo nĩ mũgacoka gũtheka.  Gũkena-rĩ, nĩ inyuĩ rĩrĩa andũ </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>makamũmena, na  meamũre kũrĩ inyuĩ, na mamũcambie, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na mathũkĩrĩrie rĩĩtwa rĩanyu nĩ ũndũ wa Mũrũ wa mũndũ.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mũthenya ũcio kenai na mũtũhatũhe; nĩ ũndũ-rĩ, igai </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>rĩanyu nĩ rĩnene o Igũrũ, nĩ gũkorũo ũguo noguo maithe mao mekaga Irori. </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>No rĩrĩ, kaĩ mũrĩ na haaro-ĩ, inyuĩ itonga, nĩ gũkorũo nĩ mũrĩkĩtie </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kuona kũnyamarũrũo kwanyu. Kaĩ mũrĩ na haaro-ĩ, inyuĩ </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mũhũnaga rĩu nĩ gũkorũo nĩ mũgacoka kũhũta.  Kaĩ mũrĩ na haaro-ĩ,</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>inyuĩ mũthekaga rĩu, nĩ gũkorũo nĩ mũgacoka gwĩthikĩra </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na kũrĩra. Kaĩ mũrĩ na haaro-ĩ, o inyuĩ, rĩrĩa andũ othe </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>makamũgathagĩrĩria, nĩ gũkorũo ũguo noguo maithe</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mao mekaga Irori cia maheni.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s></f>"}],
Text:"KIUMIA KIA ITHATHATU MWAKA C"},{Guid:"647pYJvl9UWzmij88Jx3QQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846>KIUMIA GIA IKUMI NA INYA KIA MWAKA C</s></f></u>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GITHOMO KIA MBERE
Isaia 66: 10- 14.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GUTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RIA KIRORI ISAIA :</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Inyuothe mwendaga Jerusalemu, 
kenanīrai hamwe narīo, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na mūcanjaműke 
ngoro nĩ ündũ warīo.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kenanīrai hamwe narīo inyuothe 
arīa műtüire mūrřiguagira </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kīeha; nĩ getha 
múikare ta mūkuonga</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maũndŭ marīa mega marīo, 
műkahünio nĩ maŭndŭ ma </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>úhoreri marīa monagwo 
ta moimite nyondo-inī ciarīo. </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Rekei nyondo ciarīo igaithie, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nīguo mükenio nĩ riri warĩo műingīĩ wa ürīa riikīrī-iruo, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tondű Mwathani ekuuga üű: Atīrīri, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ngarīrehithirie thayŭ o ta arī maaī riunithĩirio,</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nd</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>me riri wa ndūrirī ūtuike ta arĩ 
rüűï ruiyūru müno rūrītherereire, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>namo maündū macio nĩmo murīongaga. </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ti, i-itherű, nī műgaikara műhoreire ta 
mükuuītwo na ngoi, </s></f>"},{ID:17,Style:{Background:{BodyRect:"0,0,10000,9300"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na kana ta mūgūcüugacuūgio mwĩ ciero-ini. </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>O ta ürĩa mwana ahoragīrio nĩ nyina, </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>üguo noguo ngaműhoreria inyui;
na nĩ m</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>kahorerio kūu Jerusalemu o kühorerio. </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na nī mükeonera ühoro ūcio, 
nacio ngoro cianyu icanjaműke, </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>namo mahīndi manyu metire wega 
o ta ürīa nyeki njororo iīhandaga</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>irorete iguru naguo hinya wa guoko 
kwa Mwathani nĩ ükamenyeka nī ndungata ciake.</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>icio nicio ciugo cia mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>THABURI YA GUCOKERUO
Thaburi 66: 1-3a; 
4-5; 6-7a,; 16 na 20</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA :Anīrīrai Ngai na gīkeno, inyuí othe.</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Anirirai Ngai na gikeno, 
inyui mabūrūri mothe ma thĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Inerai mūrahe riri wa ritwa rīake;
gükumio gwake mūgītūme kūgīe riri. </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Irai Ngai atiri: Mawīko maku-rī, 
i matikirī na witigirinarīa munene</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA :Anīrīrai Ngai na gīkeno, inyuí othe.</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> 
Andu othe a thĩ nīwe makainamirira, </s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kūina makuinagīre magīkugoocaga; 
iini, ritwa riaku rio makiriinagire. </s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ükai, muone mawīko ma Ngai; </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maûndū marīa ekaga ciana cia kīrīndī
ni ma gitigirithanio kinene.</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA :Anīrīrai Ngai na gīkeno, inyuí othe.</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Iria riria inene, 
we nī aarīgarūrire ūrīa riatarii rigītuika thí niaru;
ruũi naruo, </s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kirindi gikīrūringa na magürū; </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kūu kūmūkenera tūgīkīmūkenera mūno. </s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tondū wa ūguo arī ūhoti, atūūraga e mwathani tene na tene.</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA :Anīrīrai Ngai na gīkeno, inyuí othe.</s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ukai, muigue, inyui inyuothe etigīri Ngai, </s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ ngūkiumbūra ūrīa aateithirie muoyo wakwa.</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ngai arokīgathwo, 
o we ūtaigana kūhūndūra ihoya rīakwa, </s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agīkiaga kūnjehereria ūtugi wake.</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA :Anīrīrai Ngai na gīkeno, inyuí othe.</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GITHOMO KIA IGĪRĪ
Agalatia 6: 14 - 18.</s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GUTHOMA MARUA iA MUTHURE PAUL KŪRĪ ANDU A GALATIA</s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ariŭ a Ithe witū, nī-rī, 
ndīroaga kwīgooca na ündű o wothe, </s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tiga o ndīigoocire nĩ ündū wa mũtharaba wa </s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani witű Yesu Kristü; </s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nī ündű waguo-rĩ, maündű ma gūkū thĩ nĩ maambitwo</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mūtī igūrű nīguo mathengere, </s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ni ngaambwo mūti igūrũ nĩguo ndīmathengere. </s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ni ündū-rī, ühoro wa kűrua nd</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>rĩ bata, </s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na kana wa kwaga kűrua, 
tiga o atī műndű agarūrūke, </s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>atuike mūndū ūüngī mwerũ. </s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nao andū arīa othe marīrümagia </s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ūhoro ūcio mīthiire-inī yao marogīa na
thayū na maroiguĩrūo tha, </s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na gwata Aisraeli arīa a Ngai.</s></f>"},{ID:59,
