Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika kitabu cha Mwanzo</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Siku ile: 
Bwana alimtokea Abrahamu kwenye mwaloni wa Mamre.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Abrahamu alikuwa amekaa mlangoni pa hema yake, saa joto la mchana. </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akainua mnacho, akaona </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Watu Watatu wamesimama mbele yake. </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alipowaona, alipiga mbio akatoka mlangoni: </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hema, akawakaribia, akainama mpaka chini. </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<i><fSegoe UI Black><s2769><cFFFFFF66><kFF00F200>Akasema,</k></c></s></f></i><fArial Black><s1846> </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFD8D800><kFFFF3F3F>“Bwana wangu, kama nimekupendeza machoni pako, </k></c></s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFD8D800><kFFFF3F3F>usinipite mtumishi:</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F> </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFD8D800><kFFFF3F3F>wako bila kushinda kwangu.</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F> </k></s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nitaamuru walete maji kidogo
mpate kuosha miguu, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kupumzika chini ya mti Nami
nitaleta mkate, mpate kuburudisha moyo, </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>halafu mtaendelea na
safari yenu, iliyowafikisha </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>karibu na mtumishi wenu.” 
Wakasema</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFD8D800><kFFFF3F3F>“Vema, fanya kama ulivyosemna!”</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Abrahamu akaenda kwa haraka hemani kwa Sara, akasema.       </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFD8D800><kFFFF3F3F>“Twaa upesi vipimo vitatu vya unga, uukande, ufanye mikate” </k></c></s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kisha Abrahamu akaenda mbio kwenye kundi la wanyama wake.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akachukua ndama mchanga aliye mzuri; akampa mtumishi, naye</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akafanya haraka kumwandaa. Akatwaa siagi, na maziwa, </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na yule ndama aliyemwandaa, akawaandikia vyote mbele yao: </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yeye akasimama karibu nao chini ya mti, nao wakala.</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>Halafu wakasema, </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFD8D800><kFFFF3F3F>“Sara, bibi yako yupo wapi?” </k></c></s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>Akajibu, 
</k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFD8D800><kFFFF3F3F>“Yumo hemani.</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F> 
Mgeni akamwambia,       </k></s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFD8D800><kFFFF3F3F>“Nitarudi kwako mwaka ujao
wakati huu huu; </k></c></s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFD8D800><kFFFF3F3F>na hapo mkeo Sara atakuwa na mtoto wa kiume.       </k></c></s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA
</s></f><u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF0000><kFFD8D800>Zaburi 15:2-5</k></c></s></f></u><u><fArial Black><s1846>                                             </s></f></u>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF0000><kFFF2F200>K.</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFD8D800><kFFFF3F3F> Ee Bwana, nani atakayekaa katika hema yako?</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ni mtu aendaye kwa ukamilifu,
atendaye haki,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>asemaye ukweli kutoka moyoni:
hasingizii kwa ulimi wake.                                                </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF0000><kFFF2F200>K.</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFD8D800><kFFFF3F3F> Ee Bwana, nani atakayekaa katika hema yako?</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846>                                        </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hamtendei mwenzake uovu,
wala hamsengenyi jirani yake;                  </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>machoni pake fisadi hudharauliwa.
bali huwaheshimu wamchao Bwana.                      </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF0000><kFFF2F200>K.</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFD8D800><kFFFF3F3F> Ee Bwana, nani atakayekaa katika hema yako?</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>                
Hakopeshi fedha yake kwa riba.
wala hapokei rushwa                                                                  </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>dhidi ya mtu asiye na kosa.
Anayefanya hayo, hatatikisika milele, 
 </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF0000><kFFF2F200>K. </k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFD8D800><kFFFF3F3F>Ee Bwana, nani atakayekaa katika hema yako?</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA PILI
</s></f><u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF0000><kFFD8D800>Wakolosai 1:24-28</k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika barua ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Wakolosai                           </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndugu zangu:
Sasa nafurahi kuvumilia mateso kwa ajili yenu. </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hivyo
ninatimiza katika mwili wangu yaliyopungua </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>katika mateso ya Kristo kwa ajili ya mwili wake, </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yaani Kanisa, ambalo mimi
nimefanywa mtumishi wake </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa kadiri ya agizo Mungu alilonipa
kwa ajili yenu, </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ili nilitimilize neno la Mungu, yaani fumbo lile
lililofichwa tangu milele kwa vizazi vyote.</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Sasa lakini limefunuliwa kwa 
watakatifu wake ambao ametaka</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kuwaonyesha utajiri wa utukufu 
wa fumbo </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>lenyewe kati ya watu
wa mataifa; </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yaani Kristo ndani yenu, matumaini ya utukufu.</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yeye tunamhubiri sisi, 
tukimwonya kila </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mtu na kumfundisha
kila mtu kwa hekima yote </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ili tuweze kumpeleka 
kila mmoja</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>angali amekamilika 
katika  Kristo.</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.                                                                   </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SHANGILIO LA INJILI 
</s></f><u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF0000><kFFD8D800>Luka 8:15</k></c></s></f></u><u><fArial Black><s1846>                                                          </s></f></u>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF0000><kFFD8D800>K. Aleluya.
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846>K. Heri watu wenye kulisikia neno</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na kulishika kwa moyo mzuri na mwema</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wakatoa mavuno kwa uvumilivu
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF0000><kFFD8D800>W Aleluya.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>INJILI
</s></f><u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF0000><kFFD8D800>Luka (10:38-42)</k></c></s></f></u><fArial Black><s1846>                           </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo la Injili takatifu 
ilivyoandikwa na Luka</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF0000><kFFD8D800>Wakati ule:
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846>Yesu alingia katika kijiji kimoja; huko mwanamke, jina lake.
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFD8D800><kFFFF0000>Martha, </k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846>                </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akamkaribisha nyumbani mwake.
Naye alikuwa na dada, </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>jina lake </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFD8D800><kFFFF0000>Maria</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000> aliyeketi 
miguuni pa Bwana</k></s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akisikiliza maneno yake.
Lakini </s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFD8D800><kFFFF0000>Martha</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846> akishughulikia </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>utumishi mwingi, 
akamwendea
akasema,                                     
                </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFD8D800><kFFFF3F3F>“Bwana, hujali kwamba dada yangu ameniacha nitumikie peke
yangu? Basi, umwambie anisaidie.”</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana akajibu akamwambia,</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFD8D800><kFFFF3F3F>“</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF0000><kFFD8D800>Martha,</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFD8D800><kFFFF3F3F> Martha, unajishughulisha na kujisumbua 
kwa mambo mengi. </k></c></s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFD8D800><kFFFF3F3F>Lakini kuna jambo 
moja tu lahitajika.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF0000><kFFD8D800>Maria</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFD8D800><kFFFF3F3F> 
amelichagua fungu lililo jema, nalo 
halitaondolewa kwake.”</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f>"}],
Text:"DOMINIKA YA KUMI NA SITA MWAKA C"},{Guid:"Ag0Yoaw8OEiBDcXpofRyqg",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>KIUMIA KIA MUCII MUTHERU MWAKA A</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE
Sirach 3: 2-6; 12-14</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA KUUMA GĨTABU KĨA SIRACH (“ŨGĨ WA JOSHUA BIN SIRA”)</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani nĩ akwenda ithe atĩĩo nĩ ciana; na 
akũnengera </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nyina kĩhooto igũrũ rĩa ciana ciake. Ũrĩa ũtĩaga ithe </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ arĩhaga mawĩhia; na ũrĩa ũkumagia nyina nĩ ta ũrĩa </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũnganagia mĩthithũ. Ũrĩa ũtĩaga ithe nĩ agakenio </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ ciana ciake we mwene, na rĩrĩa ahoyaga nĩ agwĩtĩkĩrio.  </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ũrĩa ũkumagia ithe nĩ akongererũo matukũ make; </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũrĩa wĩtĩkagia Mwathani nĩ agakenia nyina. Mwana wakwa, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>teithia  thoguo rĩrĩa akũrĩte;
na ndũkae kũmũiguithia </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũru kinya arĩ muoyo. O na angĩte gĩtaranio, ũmũiguĩre </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>tha na ndũkamũconokithie rĩrĩa wee ũrĩ na hinya. Amu </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>tha gwa thoguo  itikariganĩra, 
na igatarũo </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ithenya-inĩ rĩa thĩnjo ya mawĩhia.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO
Thaburi 128:1-2;3; 4-5</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA:Gũkena rĩ, nĩ mũndũ o wothe </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mwĩtigĩri Ngai, o ũrĩa ũgeraga njĩra ciake</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Gũkena-rĩ, nĩ mũndũ o wothe mwĩtigĩri Mwathani, o ũrĩa ũgeraga njĩra ciake.  </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kĩrĩa ũnogeire na moko maku-rĩ,
wee nĩ ũrĩkĩrĩaga, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>gũkena nĩwe ũrĩkenaga, na gũtũũra ũtũũre o na wega.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA:Gũkena rĩ, nĩ mũndũ o wothe </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mwĩtigĩri Ngai, o ũrĩa ũgeraga njĩra ciake</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mũtumia waku egũikara ta mũthabibũ </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũrĩa mũciari mũno e kuũ nyũmba yaku thĩinĩ; </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ciana ciaku nacio ituĩke ta
mĩtamaiyũ </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ya mũmerano ithiũrũrũkĩirie  metha yaku. </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA:Gũkena rĩ, nĩ mũndũ o wothe </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mwĩtigĩri Ngai, o ũrĩa ũgeraga njĩra ciake</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Onei, nĩ ta ũguo mũndũ 
arĩrathimagwo, ũrĩa mwĩtigĩri Mwathani.  </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani arokũrathima arĩ Sion, wonage wega wa Jerusalemu, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>matukũ maku mothe ma 
gũtũũra  muoyo.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA:Gũkena rĩ, nĩ mũndũ o wothe </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mwĩtigĩri Ngai, o ũrĩa ũgeraga njĩra ciake</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ
Akolosai 3:12-21</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A KOLOSI:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, kuona atĩ mũrĩ athure nĩ Ngai, mũgagĩtuĩka  </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>andũ atheru mendetwo nĩwe, wĩhumbei  mwĩhumbĩre  wa ngoro ũrĩa wa </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kũiguanĩra tha, na wa gũtugana, na kwĩnyihia, na kũhorera, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o na gũkirĩrĩria, mũgĩkiranagĩrĩria  na mũkĩohanagĩra o mũndũ na ũrĩa ũngĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>angĩkorũo nĩ harĩ mũndũ matetanĩtie na ũrĩa ũngĩ-rĩ; kĩohanagĩrei </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>inyuene o ta ũrĩa Mwathani nake 
aamũoheire inyuĩ.  </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ningĩ gũkĩra maũndũ macio  mothe-rĩ, gĩagai 
na wendani, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na nĩguo wohanagia  maũndũ mothe hamwe nĩguo maagĩrĩre kũna.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Rekei thayũ wa Kristũ ũteithũranage maũndũ mothe ngoro-inĩ  cianyu; </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na nĩguo mwetĩirũo mwathagwo  nĩguo, 
kuona atĩ mũrĩ a mwĩrĩ ũmwe; </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ningĩ mũgĩage na ngatho. Rekei Ũge Kristũ ũikarage ũngĩhĩte mũno thĩinĩ wanyu, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũkĩmũũhĩgagia na ũũgĩ wothe; na mũrutanage inyuĩ ene, mũgĩtaaranaga na thaburi,</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na nyĩmbo cia Ngai, o na nyĩmbo cia  kũguna maroho ma andũ, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mũkĩinagĩra Ngai mũrĩ na Wega wake thĩinĩ wa ngoro cianyu.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na ningĩ atĩrĩ: maũndũ marĩa mothe mũrĩĩkaga, mũkĩaria o na kana mũgĩĩka ũndũ o ũrĩkũ-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mekagei na rĩĩtwa rĩa Mwathani Yesu, mũgĩcokagĩria Ngai Ithe witũ ngatho </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na ũndũ wake. Inyuĩ atumia-rĩ, athĩkagĩrai athuri anyu o ta </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũrĩa kwagĩrĩire andũ arĩa 
maikaraga thĩinĩ wa Mwathani. </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na inyuĩ athuri-rĩ, endagai atumia anyu, na tigagai kũmakũũma.  </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>O na inyuĩ ciana, iguagai aciari anyu maũndũ-inĩ mothe, nĩ ũndũ ũguo nĩguo</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũkenagia Mwathani. Na inyuĩ maithe-rĩ, 
tigagai kũrakaria </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ciana cianyu, mũtigatũme igĩe na kĩnyiria.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI
Akolosai 3:15-16	</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>	
Alleluya. Alleluya. Thayũ wa Kristũ  ũikarage ngoro-inĩ cianyu; </s></f>"},{ID:18,
