Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA SAMŨELI WA MBERE: </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Agĩkĩgĩa nda agĩciara kaana ga kahĩĩ, agĩgatua Samũeli, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
