Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Arĩĩkia kũmũtigithia kuonga, akĩmũtwara Shilo, na agĩthiĩ </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na ndeegwa ya mĩaka ĩtatũ, na kiro ikũmi cia mũtu, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na mondo ĩmwe ya rũũa ĩiyũrĩĩte ndibei.  Agĩgĩtwara </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Samũeli, arĩ o mũnyiinyi, nyũmbainĩ ya Mwathani o kũu </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Shilo. Maarĩkia gũthĩnja ndeegwa ĩyo, magĩtwarĩra Eli </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mwana ũcio.  Hana akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ, “Mũthũũri ũyũ, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>tanjĩtĩkĩria.  No ũndirikane? Nĩ niĩ mũtumia ũrĩa warũũgamĩĩte </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>haaha akĩhooya Mwathani.  Ndamũhooire mwana ũyũ, naake </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akĩĩhe. Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, nĩndamwamũrĩra Mwathani.  </s></f>"},{ID:14,
