Malaki 3; 1-4</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani Ngai ekuuga ati: Atiriri, ni ngutuma murekio </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wakwa, nake athondekithirie king'aratua giakwa.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nake Mwathani ucio mutuire muuragiriria, 
ni akaguthuka </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na ihenya, atonye 
hekaruini yake thiini. </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>O na ningi, murekania uria muiguithania-wa-kirikaniro, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o we uria mukenagio niwe, ni agoka o nake.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Uguo niguo Mwathani munene wa Ita ekuuga.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>No riri muthenya uria agoka-ri, nuu ukahota kumwitiria?</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>O na riria akeonania-ri, nuu ukahota kwiumiriria?</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tondu-ri, ahana mwaki wa muturi, o na kana 
thabuni </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wa muthambia nguo. Ningi agaikara ta ari muturi wa betha,</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o na mutheria wacio, nake atherie ariu a alawi, amathambie </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mathere ta mari thahabu kana betha iria itheragio 
ithire </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nganga ciothe. Nao macoke kurutagira Mwathani mahaki ma uthingu.</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hindi iyo  Mwathani ni agakenio ni Mahaki ma Juda na</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Jerusalem, o ta uria akenagio nimo matuku </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ma tene, o miaka-ini iria yathirire tene.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:2,
