Luka 2: 22-40</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA INJIRI  YA MŨTHURE LUKA:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na matukũ mao na gũtherio thutha wa gũciara maahinga, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o ta ũrĩa gwaathanirũo nĩ Musa-rĩ (Maria na Joseph) </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>makĩambata Jerusalem magakanengere Mwathani,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
