Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũrĩa gũtuĩtwo Maandĩko-inĩ ma irĩra cia Mwathani atĩrĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nĩ ndirahũgĩ igĩrĩ, kana ndutura igĩrĩ. Na rĩrĩ, nĩ kwarĩ  </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mũndũ watũire Jerusalem wetagwo Simeoni; nake aarĩ mũthingu </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na mũigua- Ngai, na nĩ aatanyĩte hindĩ ĩrĩa Israeli </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>makanyamarũrũo: na Muoyo Mũtheru aarĩ hamwe nake.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na mũndũ ũcio nĩ aaguũrĩirio ni Muoyo Mũtheru atĩ ndagakua </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>atonete Kristũ ũrĩa wa Mwathani. Nake agĩtonya hekarũ ya Ngai  </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>arĩ na Muoyo Mũtheru: na rĩrĩa aciari a kaana kau, Yesu, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>maagatwarire hekarũ ya Ngai thĩinĩ, nĩ getha magageke </s></f>"},{ID:12,
