Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>agĩkaiyũkia moko-inĩ make,
akĩgatha Ngai akiuga atĩrĩ: “ Rĩu </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani nĩ hindĩ ũkũnjugĩra ũhoro, niĩ ngombo yaku, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>‘thiĩ na thayũ o ta ũrĩa wanjĩrire; nĩ gũkorũo maitho makwa nĩ monete </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũhonokio waku, ũrĩa wathondekire mbere ya irĩndĩ ciothe;</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩguo ũtheri wa kũguũrĩrio andũ a Ndũrĩrĩ, o na riri wa andũ aku </s></f>"},{ID:14,
