Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>marĩa maaririo nĩ ũndũ wake;
nake Simeoni akĩmarathima, </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akĩĩra Maria, nyina, Atĩrĩrĩ, kaana gaka nĩ gatuĩtwo ga kũgũithia o na </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>gũũkĩria andũ aingĩ a Israeli;
ningĩ gatuĩke kĩmenyithia kĩrĩa </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kĩrĩtendagwo; o na rĩrĩ, rũhiũ rũa mbaara nĩ rũgagũtũrĩkia ngoro </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wee mwene, nĩguo meciria ma ngoro nyingĩ maguũke.  </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na nĩ kwarĩ mũtumia mũnabii wetago Anna, mwarĩ wa Fanueli, </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wa mũhĩrĩga wa Asher, nake aarĩ mũkũrũ mũno; aaikarire na </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mũthuriwe mĩaka mũgwanja kuuma ahika, </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na nĩ aatũire arĩ wa  ndigwa mĩaka ĩngĩ mĩrongo ĩnana na ĩna; mũtumia </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũcio-rĩ, ndoimaga hekarũ, 
no aatũire aturagiria Ngai ndu </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akamũhoyaga ũtukũ na mũthenya akĩĩhingaga kũrĩa irio, </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na akĩmũthaithaga. Nake agĩkinya  oro hindĩ ĩo, akĩgatha Ngai, akĩheana </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũhoro wa kaana kau kũrĩ arĩa othe maatũire matanyaga hindĩ </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ĩrĩa Jerusalem gũgakũũrũo.
Nao maahingia maũndũ marĩa </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mothe maathanĩtwo irĩra-inĩ cia Mwathani, magĩcoka Galilea, </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>makĩinũka itũũra rĩao rĩa Nazareth.  Nako kaana kau gagĩkũra, gakĩgĩa </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na hinya , gakĩiyũrũo nĩ ũũgĩ; naguo Wega wa Ngai watũire nako.  </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Injiri theru ya Mwathani</s></f>"}],
Text:"GUTEGERWO HEKARU-INI KWA MWATHANI MWAKA C"},{Guid:"gxkpF+BeSky7YyjJhKQqMw",Verses:[{Style:{Background:{Image:"sky5.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>UBATITHIO WA MWATHANI MWAKA C</s></f>"},{ID:2,Style:{Background:{Image:"sky5.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE 
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>Isaiah. 40:1-5;9-11</s></f>"},{ID:2,Style:{Background:{Image:"sky5.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA MŨRATHI ISAIA:</s></f>"},{ID:3,Style:{Background:{Image:"sky5.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Atĩrĩrĩ, ta horanĩriai, mũhorerie andũ akwa; </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũguo nĩguo Ngai wanyu ekuuga. </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Arĩriai itũra rĩa Jerusalemu maũndũ ma kũrĩhoreria ngoro; </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>anĩrĩrai mũrĩĩre atĩrĩ, atĩ mbaara iria rĩrarĩ nayo nĩyathira, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na atĩ waganu warĩo nĩ wohanĩrũo; o na ningĩ atĩ nĩ rĩhũrĩtwo na guoko kwa Mwathani rĩgacokerithio maita</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> merĩ nĩ ũndũ wa mehia  marĩo mothe.  He mũgambo wa mũndũ ũkwanĩrĩra akoiga atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Thondekai njĩra ya Mwathani o kũu werũ-inĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>araganĩriai Ngai witũ njĩra ya gĩtwari o kũu rung’ũri-inĩ.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>  Mĩkuru nĩ ĩgathĩnjwo yambatĩre, o nacio irĩma ciothe, o na ithũngũri ciothe, inyihio ciaraganio; </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o nakuo kũrĩa kuogomu kũrũngario, nakuo kũrĩa gũtarĩ kwaraganu kwaraganio wega.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Naguo riri wa Mwathani nĩ ũkaguũranĩrio, nao andũ othe a gũkũ thĩ </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mawonanĩre me hamwe,</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> nĩ gũkorũo nĩ kanua ka Mwathani kaarĩtie ndeto icio.</s></f>"},{ID:11,Style:{Background:{BodyRect:"0,0,10000,9300"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Atĩrĩrĩ, wee ũheaga Sion ũhoro ũrĩa mwega-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:11,Style:{Background:{BodyRect:"0,0,10000,9300"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ta haica kĩrĩma kĩrĩa kĩraya igũrũ; wee ũheaga Jerusalemu ũhoro mwega rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ta haicia kayũ gaku na igũrũ na hinya mũno;</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> ta gĩkahaicie o na igũrũ na ũtige gwĩtigĩra, ĩra matũũra ma Juda atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ũyũ nĩwe Ngai wanyu! Atĩrĩrĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani Ngai agoka o ta njamba irĩ hinya mũno, </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na guoko gwake nĩkuo gũkamwathanagĩra;</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> atĩrĩrĩ, ũtungati wake e naguo, o na irĩhanĩria rĩake rĩrĩ o mbere yake. </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Mbũri cia rũũru rũake agacirĩithagia o ta mũrĩithi, </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>natuo tũgondu atuoyage na moko make,</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>atũkuuage tũrĩ gĩthũri-inĩ gĩake; nacio ng’ondu iria </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ikuongithia acitwarage o kahora.</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Thaburi: 
</s></f><fArial Black><s1076>(104; 1-2; 3-4; 24-25; 27-30)</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> ICOKIA:Ngoro yakwa gatha Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Jehova, Ngai wakwa,wee uri münene müno; 
wiguikite ütiiku,o na ukaru.</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ütüire wihumbite Ütheri ta nguo; 
wee niwe utamburukite igürü ta kiandarüa.</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA:Ngoro yakwa gatha Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nowe uria uigiriire migamba îrîa yakîrîiruo 
nyumba ciake cia ngoroba iguru ria mai;</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> 
nowe uria utuaga matu ngari yake ya kumukuua;</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nowe uria uthiaga agitwaragwo ni mathagu ma ruhuho;</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>O uria ningi utumaga huho ituike arekio ake, </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na mwaki uria uhenururukaga o naguo agatuma utuîke no atungati ake.</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA:Ngoro yakwa gatha Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>I Jehova, ni maingi atia mawîra maria ărutîte! </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o mothe umarutite na wara; 
thi ni kuiyura iiyure urimi waku.</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Rîria nirio iria, o uguo rinenehete na rikaarama; </s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>thiini wario kwi indo iria ciongoyaga itangîgereka; 
nyamu ii kuo nyinyi o na nene.</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA:Ngoro yakwa gatha Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio ciothe nowe iroragîriria,
niguo uciheage irio ciacio </s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o ihinda riacio riakinya.
O kiria wacihe nikio cioyaga;</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ăkumbatăragia guoko, igakihuna wega waku.</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA:Ngoro yakwa gatha Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ningi ukahitha uthiu, cio igagicanjama;</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>icokagira miheehu yacio, igakua, 
igacoka rukungu-ini gwacio.</s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>guituma utumaga roho waku, nacio igakigia;</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>uthiu wa thi ugakiwanakahia.</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA:Ngoro yakwa gatha Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Githomo gia keri: 
</s></f><fArial Black><s1384>(Tito 2: 11-14; 3; 4-7)</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Aruna akwa, Wega wa Ngai niwonekete,</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>üria üreheire andü othe ühonokio, </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>naguo niguo ütümenyagiria küregana </s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na maündü mothe maria mataiguaine </s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na uhoro wa kwiamürira Ngai, </s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na meririria maria moru ma gükü thi, </s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na tüikarage twi na üügi wa ngoro, 
na türi athingu, </s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na twiamüriire Ngai mahinda maya türi,</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tügitanyaga gükahingirio kiirigiriro kiria kii na kirathimo, </s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hindl iria gükaguüranirio riri wa Jesu Kristo, </s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>uria Wi Ngai witü münene na Mütühonokia, </s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake niwe werutire ni ündü witü,</s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nigetha atüküüre waganu-ini wothe, </s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na atherie andü a gütuika ake kiümbe, </s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>aria mari na kiyo gia gwikaga maündü mega. </s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Indi riria ütugi wa Ngai Mühonokia witü </s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>naguo wendani endete andü naguo ciaguükireri, </s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ni kühonokia aatuhonokirie, 
ti tondu wa ciiko </s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>iria twekaga ithuene cia gwitua athingu, </s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>no ni ündü wa tha ciake; 
ni gütuthambia o güthambio </s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>küria gütümaga mündü aciarüo ringi na erühio na Roho Mütheru.</s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na ni Roho ücio aatüitiriirie 
na ütana na ündü wa Jesu Kristo </s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mühonokia witü, ni getha tutuwo athingu ni ündü wa Wega Wake, </s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na agai gükagairüo muoyo üria ütagathira,</s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> 
küringana na üria tütüire tüwirigiriire.</s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nicio ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI 
</s></f><fArial Black><s1384>Luka 3:15-16,21-22</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA GĨCUNJĨ KĨA INJIRI YA MUTHURE LUKA:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hĩndĩ ĩo, tondũ ĩrĩa kĩrĩndĩ gĩatanyaga, gĩgĩthanganagia, nao andũ othe</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mageciragia ngoro-inĩ ciao ũhoro wa John,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kana hihi nĩwe Kristũ-rĩ, John agĩcokia akĩmera othe atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Niĩ-rĩ, ndĩmũbatithagia na maaĩ; no rĩrĩ,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> nĩ gũgoka ũngĩ wĩna hinya kũrĩ niĩ, nayo mĩkwa ya iratũ ciake, niĩ-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndiigaine wa kũmĩohora; </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũcio nĩwe ũkamũbatithagia na Muoyo Mũtheru o na mwaki.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na gũgĩkinya atĩrĩ, andũ othe maarĩkia kũbatithio, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o nake Yesu aarĩkia kũbatithio-rĩ, hĩndĩ ĩrĩa aahoyaga Ngai, Igũrũ rĩkĩhingũka, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nake Muoyo Mũtheru agĩikũrũka, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akĩũmba igũrũ rĩake arĩ na mwĩrĩ ũhaana ta wa ndutura, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>naguo mũgambo ũkiuma Igũrũ ũkiuga atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wee nĩwe Mũrũ wakwa nyendete mũno; nĩ ngenaga nĩ ũndũ waku.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s></f>"}],Style:{Background:{Image:"sky5.jpg"}},
Text:"UBATITHIO WA MWATHANI MWAKA C"},{Guid:"WRCP8HC2CEqI2QOnamX9BQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846>KUMIA KIA IGIRI KIA MWAKA C</s></f></u>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE 
Isaya. 62:1-5</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA MŨRATHI ISAIA: </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Atĩrĩrĩ, ha ũhoro wa kũrũĩrĩra Sion, 
ndigatumia kanua,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o na kana 
ndigithĩrie gũtetera Jerusalem,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o nginya hĩndĩ ĩrĩa ũhoro wakuo </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wa ũthingu ũkoimbũka ware o ta ũtheri,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o naguo ũhoro wakuo wa kũhonokania </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>woneke o ta tawa ũrĩa wakanaga mũno.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nacio ndũrĩrĩ nĩ ikona ũthingu waku, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o nao athamaki othe mone riri waku; </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wee nawe ũcoke gwĩtwo rĩĩtwa rĩngĩ</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>rĩkagwetwo na kanua ka Mwathani.  
Ningĩ ũgatuĩka ta tanji ya ũthaka </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũnyitĩtwo na guoko kwa Mwathani,</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na ũhaane ta thũmbĩ ya ũthamaki </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ĩnyitĩtwo na guoko kwa Ngai waku.  </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wee nawe-rĩ, ndũgacoka gwĩtwo Mũtirike, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o na kana bũrũri waku wĩtwo Mũkiru Ihooru;</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na rĩrĩ, ũrĩĩtagwo Hefiziba, 
o naguo bũrũri waku </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wĩtagwo Beula;
nĩ gũkorũo Mwathani nĩ akenagio nĩwe, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o naguo bũrũri waku ũgatuĩka o ta mũhiki ũrĩa ũhikĩtio.  </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nĩ gũkorũo o ta ũrĩa mwanake ahikagia mũirĩtu,</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũguo noguo aanake aku magakũhikia,</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ningĩ o ta ũrĩa mũhikania ekenagĩra nĩ mũhiki wake-rĩ,</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o ũguo noguo Ngai waku arĩĩkenagĩra nĩwe.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO
Thaburi 96:
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>1-2a,2b-3;7-8;9-10</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA	
Ganai ũhoro wa riri wake ndũrĩrĩ-inĩ</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ĩ itĩkai kũinĩra Mwathani rũĩmbo
rũerũ! 
Mũinĩre Mwathani,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>inyuĩ andũ othe a thĩ.  
Inĩrai Mwathani, gathai rĩĩtwa rĩake.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA	
Ganai ũhoro wa riri wake ndũrĩrĩ-inĩ</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hunjagiai ũhoro wa ũhonokania wake mũthenya o mũthenya.  </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ganai ũhoro wa riri wake ndũrĩrĩ-inĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mawĩko make ma magegania </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mũkĩmaganĩre iruka ciothe cia andũ.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA
Ganai ũhoro wa riri wake ndũrĩrĩ-inĩ</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Rahai Mwathani, inyuĩ mĩhĩrĩga yothe ya irĩndĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>rahai  Mwathani atĩ nĩwe wĩ riri na e na hinya. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Rahai Mwathani nĩ kũgwetaga riri wa rĩĩtwa rĩake: </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũkai na ihaki, mũgĩtonye nja-inĩ ciake.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA	
Ganai ũhoro wa riri wake ndũrĩrĩ-inĩ</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ĩ gĩthathaiyei Mwathani mũgemete ũgemu ũrĩa wa ũtheru; </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>tetemekai  mwĩ mbere yake, inyuĩ andũ othe a thĩ. </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ugai ndũrĩrĩ-inĩ atĩrĩ: Nĩ hĩndĩ Mwathani agwatĩte gũthamaka; </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>arĩciragĩra irĩndĩ ciakuo o ũrĩa kwerekereire.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA	
Ganai ũhoro wa riri wake ndũrĩrĩ-inĩ</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>1 Akorintho 12:4-11</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE  PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A KORINTHO MARĨA MA MBERE:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, iheo iria iheanagwo 
ciumanĩte na Wega wa Ngai</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ mĩthemba-mĩthemba, no rĩrĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Muoyo mwene cio no ũmwe.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mĩtungatĩre o nayo nĩ mĩthemba-mĩthemba, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na Mwathani mwene yo no ũmwe.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>O nayo mĩĩkĩre ya maũndũ nĩ ĩtiganĩte mĩthemba,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ĩndĩ Ngai no ũmwe, ũcio wĩkithagia </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>maũndũ macio mothethĩinĩ wa andũ  othe. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>No rĩrĩ, mũndũ o mũndũ aheagwo ũndũ wake ũrĩa</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wonanagia atĩ arĩ na Muoyo nĩ getha </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũndũ ũcio ũgune andũ othe.  
Tondũ wa kũheo nĩ Muoyo-rĩ,</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mũndũ ũmwe agĩaga na ũhoro wa kwaria ũrĩ ũũgĩ; </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũngĩ akagĩa na ũhoro ũrĩ ũmenyi mũkinyanĩru</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>werekanĩrĩire na wa Muoyo  o ro ũcio; 
nake ũngĩ akaheo wĩtĩkio , </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ ũndũ wa Muoyo o oro ũcio; 
ũngĩ akaheo ũhoti wa</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kũhonania mĩrimũ, no ũndũ wa Muoyo o ũcio  ũmwe;</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũngĩ nake akaheo ũhoti wa kũringa ciama,</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> ũngĩ ũrathi, ũngĩ ũhoti wa gũkũũrana mioyo;</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũngĩ gũthioma thiomi,
na ũngĩ ũtaũri </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ahote gũtaũra thiomi icio.  </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>No rĩrĩ, maũndũ macio mothe 
no wĩra wa Muoyo o ro ũcio ũmwe,</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akĩgayagĩra andũ o ta ũrĩa ekwenda, 
o mũndũ mwanya, o mũndũ mwanya.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI
John 2:11</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Alleluya. Alleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Yesu nĩ ekire ũguo kũu Kana ya Galilea, </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akĩambĩrĩria ciama ciake,
agĩkĩonania ũnene wake; </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nao arutwo ake makĩya kũmwĩhoka.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Alleluia</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI 
John 2:1-12</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE JOHN:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Gũkĩgĩa kĩhikanio kũndũ gwĩtagwo Kana ya Galilea, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nake nyina wa Yesu aarĩ ho.  </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>O na Yesu nake nĩ etirũo, na arutwo ake, mathiĩ kĩhikanio kĩu. </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nayo njohi yaaga kũmaigana,
nyina wa Yesu akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ:</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Matirĩ na njohi.  Nake Yesu akĩmwĩra: </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mũtumia ũyũ, ũhoro nĩ ũrĩkũ witũ na we? </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ihinda rĩakwa rĩtirĩ rĩrakinya.  
Nyina agĩkĩĩra ndungata atĩrĩrĩ:</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>O ũrĩa ekũmwĩra, ĩkai guo. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na rĩrĩ, kwarĩ ndigithũ cia mahiga ciagĩtwo </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kuo nĩ ũndũ wa mĩtugo ya Ayahudi ya gwĩtheria, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ĩmwe no gũthirĩra maaĩ ma mũtũngi 
ũrĩa mũnene maita merĩ kana matatũ. </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nake Yesu akĩmera atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Iyũriai ndigithũ icio maaĩ.  
Magĩgĩciiyũria  o riita.  </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Agĩcoka akĩmera atĩrĩ:</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Rĩu tahiai,mũtwarĩre mũtabania  wa iruga.  </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nao makĩmũtwarĩra.  
Mũtabania wa iruga nake aacama maaĩ macio matuikĩte njohi, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na ndamenye harĩa yumĩte ĩndĩ ndungata iria ciatahĩte maaĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>cio nĩ ciamenyaga ũcio mũtabania wa iruga agĩĩta mũhikania, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: 
Mũndũ aambaga kũruta njohi ĩrĩa njega;</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> na andũ maarĩkia kũnyua mũno, 
akaruta ĩrĩa ĩtarĩ njega mũno; </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wee-rĩ, ũkũigĩte njohi ĩrĩa njega ũkamĩruta rĩu.  </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Yesu nĩ ekire ũguo kũu Kana ya Galilea, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akĩambĩrĩria ciama ciake, agĩkĩonania ũnene wake; </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nao arutwo ake makĩ ya kũmwĩhoka.</s></f>"},{ID:12,Style:{Background:{BodyRect:"0,0,10000,9300"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>INIJIRI THERU YA MWATHANI</s></f>"}],Style:{Background:{Image:"sunsea2.jpg"}},
Text:"KUMIA KIA IGIRI KIA MWAKA C"},{Guid:"uvGImn/EDEKyt69XiGi7EA",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE			             	         Isaia 43:16-21</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA KUUMA MURATHI ISAIA: </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani ekuuga ũũ: O we ũrĩa ũtemaga njĩra irĩa-inĩ, o na agatema gacĩra kũndũ kũrĩa kũrĩ maaĩ me hinya,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> na akoimagarithia ngari cia ita, o na mbarathi, o na mbũtũ cia ita hamwe  na anene a cio, ekuuga ũũ: </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hĩ! Magakoma othe hamwe, na maticoke kwarahoka; nĩ macingimanĩtio makahora ta rũtambĩ rũa ũguta.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> No rĩrĩ, tigai kũririkana maũndũ marĩa mahĩtũkĩte, o na kana mwĩcũranie maũndũ ma tene.  Atĩrĩrĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ ngwĩka ũndũ ũngĩ mwerũ, naguo ũgũkunũka o ro rĩu; githĩ mũtirĩkĩũmenya? Ũrĩa ngwĩka nĩguo ũũ, atĩ nĩ ngatema njĩra werũ-inĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o naguo rũng’ũrĩ-inĩ ndũme kũgĩe na njũĩ. Nyamũ cia gĩthaka ta mbwe, na nyaga, nĩ ikanjĩkĩrĩra,</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> nĩ gũkorũo kũu werũ-inĩ nĩ ngatũma kũgĩe na maaĩ, o na ndũme o kũu rũng’ũrĩ-inĩ kũgĩe na njũĩ, nĩ getha andũ akwa manyuage maaĩ kuo, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o andũ arĩa akwa  athure; nao nĩo andũ arĩa ndeyũmbĩire, nĩ getha maheanage ũhoro wa ũrĩa njagĩrĩirũo nĩ gũkumagio. </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                           Thaburi 126:1-2a,2b-3;4-5;6</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA	
Ĩĩni, maũndũ manene Mwathani atwĩkĩire.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Rĩrĩa Mwathani aagarũrire a Sion arĩa atahe akĩmainũkia-rĩ, twahaanire ta andũ mekũrota.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>  Tũnua twitũ hĩndĩ ĩo tũkĩiyũra mĩtheko, nĩmĩ ciitũ igakĩiyũra mĩkũngũiyo.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA	
Ĩĩni, maũndũ manene Mwathani atwĩkĩire.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hĩndĩ ĩo ndũrĩrĩ-inĩ  gũgĩkĩĩranwo atĩrĩ: Mwathani nĩ ekĩĩre andũ aya maũndũ manene! Ĩĩ-ni, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ maũndũ manene Mwathani aatwĩkĩire, na ithuĩ nĩ tũgũkena nĩ ũndũ wamo.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA	
Ĩĩni, maũndũ manene Mwathani atwĩkĩire.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ĩ Mwathani, kĩrĩkie kũgarũra atahwo aitũ mainũke, ta ũrĩa njũĩ cia Guthini icokaga kũiyũra. </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Arĩa marahanda na maithori makagetha  magĩkũngũyagia.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA	
Ĩĩni, maũndũ manene Mwathani atwĩkĩire.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mũndũ o na angĩthiĩ akĩrĩraga akuuĩte mbegũ agĩcihandaga, gũcoka agacoka agĩkũngũyagia, e na itĩa ciake cia ngano.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA	
Ĩĩni, maũndũ manene Mwathani atwĩkĩire.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ					          Afilipi 3:8-14</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A FILIPI:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, ĩĩ-ni, o na maũndũ mothe-rĩ ndĩmatuaga ma tũhũ,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> kuona atĩ rĩu nĩ menyete Yesu Kristũ Mwathani wakwa na ũmenyi ũrĩa ũkĩrĩte kũna maũndũ macio mangĩ mothe.  Nĩ tondũ wake ndorĩirũo nĩ indo ciothe, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na ngacitua o ta mahuti ma gũteo, nĩ getha ndĩigĩĩre na Kristũ na ngoragwo ndĩ thĩinĩ wake, itakĩrĩ na ũthingu wakwa mwene, o wa mũthemba ũcio uumanaga na watho,</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> tiga o ũrĩa uumanaga na ũhoro wa gwĩtĩkia Kristũ, o ũthingu ũrĩa uumaga kũrĩ Ngai nĩ ũndũ wa gwĩtĩkia. Na ningĩ nĩ getha ndĩmũmenye we,</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> o na menye hinya ũrĩa uumanaga na kũriũka gwake, na tũgwatanĩre nake mĩnyamaro yake, na haananio nake ũhoro-inĩ wake wa gũkua, nĩguo atĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kũngĩkĩhoteka, ngakinyĩrĩra ũhoro wa kũriũkio nyume kũrĩ arĩa akuũ. Ngiuga ũguo-rĩ, ti ta kuuga atĩ nĩ ndĩkĩtie gũkinya hau, o na kana ngarĩkia kwagĩrĩra kũna:</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> ĩndĩ nĩ kwĩrutanĩria ndĩĩrutanagĩria gũthiĩ na mbere, nĩguo atĩ, kwahoteka, ndĩĩnyitĩre ũndũ o ũrĩa ndanyitĩirũo nĩ Kristũ Yesu. </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, ndikwĩona ta ndĩkĩtie kũũnyita:</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> no ũndũ ũrĩa njĩkaga no ũmwe, atĩrĩ, nĩ ndiganĩirũo nĩ maũndũ marĩa ndigĩte na thutha, ngatambũrũka ‘nyite maũndũ marĩa  marĩ mbere yakwa-rĩ,</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> ngerutanĩria gũthiĩ o na mbere, nĩ getha ngakinya handũ harĩa hakinyagwo, na ngaheo kĩheo kĩrĩa kĩheanagwo,</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> nakĩo nĩkio gwĩtwo nĩ Ngai thĩinĩ wa Kristũ Yesu, nĩguo ‘thiĩ Igũrũ.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI				                              Ezekieli 33,11</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>	
Niĩ ndũũraga muoyo-rĩ, ndikenaga nĩ ũndũ wa gĩkuũ kĩa mũndũ mwaganu;</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> no rĩrĩ, nĩ kaba mũndũ ũcio mwaganu agarũrũke atigane na mĩthiĩre ĩo yake nĩguo atũũre muoyo.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			                John 8:1-11</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE JOHN:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hĩndĩ ĩo Yesu agĩthiĩ kĩrĩma kĩa Mĩtamaiyũ.  Ningĩ rũcinĩ tene agĩcoka o hekarũ-inĩ, na andũ othe magĩthiĩ kũrĩ we; nake agĩikara thĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akĩgwata kũmaruta ũhoro.  Nao aandĩki-marũa ma Afarisei makĩrehe mũtumia wanyitirũo agĩtharia,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> na maarĩkia kũmũrũgamia gatatĩ-ini, makĩmwĩra atĩrĩrĩ: Mũrutani, mũndũ mũka ũyũ aanyitwo o agĩtharia. Rĩu-rĩ, watho-inĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Musa aatwĩrire tũhũre aka ta acio na mahiga nyuguto tũmorage; wee ũgũkiuga atĩa ũhoro wake?  Na moigire ũguo mamũgerie, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mone ũndũ wa kũmũthitakĩra.  Nake Yesu akĩinamĩrĩra, akĩgwata kwandĩka thĩ na kĩara.  Ningĩ maakĩrũmanĩria kũmũũria, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>agĩĩtiira, akĩmera atĩrĩ: Inyuĩ ũrĩa ũtarĩ ehia-rĩ, nĩ akĩambe amũikĩrie ihiga.  Agĩcoka o kũĩnamĩrĩra, akĩandĩka thĩ na kĩara. </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Nao, maaigua ũguo, makĩgwata kuuma ũmwe ũmwe, marutĩtie harĩ arĩa akũrũ, o nginya ũrĩa wa kũrigĩrĩria; Yesu agĩtigwo wiki,</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> na mũtumia arũngiĩ o hau gatagatĩ.  Nake Yesu agĩĩtiira, akĩmũũria atĩrĩ:  Me ha, mũtumia ũyũ? Anga gũtirĩ mũndũ wagũtuĩra? </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nake akiuga: Gũtirĩ, Mwathani.  Nake Yesu akiuga atĩrĩ: Na niĩ ndigũgũtuĩra; thiĩ, thutha ũyũ ndũkanacoke kwĩhia.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s></f>"}],
Text:"KIUMIA GIA ITHANO KIA KWADRAJESMA MWAKA C"},{Guid:"jiPh82LQKEu1CM4jSWhM5w",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>KIUMIA KIA MUGWANJA KIA IRIUKIRO</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GITHOMO KIA MBERE
Atumwo 
7: 55 - 60.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŪTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RIA ATŪMWO :</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Matukū-inī macio, Stefano nĩ aakorirūo aiyūrītwo nī Muoyo Mūtheru, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agīcūthĩrīria lgūrū akīona riri wa Ngai, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na Yesu arūgamte guoko-ini kwa ürīo kwa Ngai. </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Agikiuga: Atīrī, ndĩ kuona Igūrū rīhingūkīte, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na Mūrũ wa Mūndũ arūgamīte guoko-inī kwa ūrĩo kwa Ngai. </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>No andū acio makīgūūth</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>ūka
na mūgambo mūnene, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>makīhinga matū mao, makīműguthükīra marī na ngoro o ro imwe; </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>makīmūthinīkania nja ya itūüra, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ma kīmūhūra na mahiga: </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nao aira makiiga nguo ciao thĩ magūrū - inī ma
mwanake wetagwo Saulo. </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Magīkīhūra Stefano na mahiga, 
o agīkayagīra Mwathani akiugaga atīrī :</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani Yesu, oya muoyo wakwa. 
Agīturia ndu, akīanīrira na m</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>gambo münene atīrīĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani,
ndūkamorie riihia riri. </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na aarīkia kuuga üguo agīkoma toro. Icio nĩcio ciugo cia Mwathani,</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>THABURI YA GÜCOKERUO</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Thaburi 
97:1 na 2b; 6 na 7b;9.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA : Utūhotithie, Mwathani, twone ükumio waku.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nihindī Mwathani agwatīte gūthamaka; 
thĩ ta ni îcanjamūke; </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mabūrūri maria ma iria-ini o namo
ni magīkene o ūguo maingīhīte. </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Giti gīake kia ūnene,
gitina kirīa gīkartire, nī ūthingu o na kīhooto</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA : Utūhotithie, Mwathani, twone ükumio waku.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Igūrū nĩ riraanirīra ūthingu wake, riri wake nī mūoneku ni irīhdī ciothe cia thĩ,</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Inyuî ngai ici ri, mūinamîrīrei we, inyuothe.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA : Utūhotithie, Mwathani, twone ükumio waku.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩgūkoruo wee, Mwathani, 
nowe wī igūrū m</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>no igūrū ria thĩ yothe ;</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wee ūrī mūtuūgiru muno gūkira ngai ciothe,</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĪTHOMO KĪA IGIRI</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kuguuririo 
22: 12-14. 16-17. 20.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŪTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RIA KUGU</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>Ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>RĪRIO KWA JOHN :</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>NiI John ngīigwa mūgambo mũnene Ukīnjīra: </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>One nii nĩ ngūüka o narua; naguo űtungati wakwa</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndī o naguo, ngahe o mūndū kūringana na ürĩa wīra wake ütari. </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ nii Alfa o na Omega, ūrīa wa
mbere o na wa kūrigīrīria, </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ningī kīambīrīria o na kīrīkīro. </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Gükena-rī, nĩ arīa a gūkorűo mathambītie
nguo ciao, </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nīguo magīe rūtha makinye mūtī-inī ürīa wa muoyo, </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na matonyere na mĩromo makinye
itūüra rīu thĩinī.</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nii Yesu nĩ ndeketie mūraika wakwa aműhe </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>inyuī üira wa maūndű macio nĩ ündű wa makanitha.</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ nii thuuna iria ya Davide,o we ürīa wa rűciaro rűake, </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nīĩ niĩ njata theru, rīa ya rūcinī tene.</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake Muoyo o nake mühiki mekuuga: </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Üka Nake ürīa üküigua nĩ oige: Üka Nake ūrīa ūnyotiī, nĩ oke;</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o ürīa ükwenda, ni aaműkīre maaī marīa ma muoyo, atekūgüra.</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Müheani uira wa maündü macio ekuuga: </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ii, nīguo, ngűüka o narua. Amen: no giúke, Mwathani Yesu. </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wega wa Mwathani Yesu ürogīa na andű arĩa aamūre. Amen.</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nĩcio ciugo cia Mwathani,</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GITHOMO KIA INJIRI
John 17: 20-26.</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MUTHURE JOHN :</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hīndī io Yesu akiinamūra matho akiuga : </s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Awa műtheru, ti aya oike ndirahoera; </s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndahoera arīa marīkoragwo meīhokete nī ündũ wa ciugo ciao; </s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>atī othe matuīke ümwe ki; o ta ūguo wee, 
Awa, </s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wī thīinī wakwa, na niĩ ndī thĩinī waku, </s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o nao magīe thīinī witūũ, nĩ getha kīrīndī gīa gūkü</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>thĩ gīītīkie atī niwe wandekirie. </s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na nīī, riri üria üheete, nĩ ndīmaheete o nao, </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>atī nīguo matuīke umwe ki, o ta üguo ithuī tũri ümwe; </s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nīi thĩinĩ wao, nawe thĩinī wakwa, nīguo marīkīiririe gūtuika</s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ümwe o wega; nĩ getha kīrindi kīmenye atī nīwe wandekirie, </s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ati acionĩ ümendete, o ta ürīa nyendete nii. </s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Awa, arīa üheete, nĩ ngwenda atī, o harīa ndī, </s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o nao magīage o ho hamwe na niī; 
niguo monage riri wakwa ürīa üheete; </s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>amu nīi nĩ wanyendaga o na tene thi itaanombwo. </s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Awa mūthingu, kīrindī gīa gūkū thĩ gītiakűmenyire, </s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>no nii nĩ ndakūūi; o na aya nĩ maamenyire at</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ỉ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> nīwe wandekirie; </s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na nīĩ ngimamenyithia rīitwa rīaku, 
na no ndimamenyithagia rĩo; </s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ getha wendani ūria ünyendete naguo üikarage thĩinī wao, </s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na ni njikaraga thĩinī wao.</s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nīcio ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"}],
Text:"KIUMIA KIA MUGWANJA KIA IRIUKIRO MWAKA C"},{Guid:"/iHlKL2Q5EidBo47ZNjWEQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>KIUMIA KIA MUGWANJA MWAKA C</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE
1 Samueli 26:2,7-9,12-13,22-23</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA MBERE RIA SAMUELI: </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Matukũ-inĩ macio, Saulo agĩgĩũkĩra, agĩikũrũka kũu werũ-inĩ wa Zifu </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>arĩ na Aisraeli ngiri ithatũ athure, magacarie Davide kuo.  </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tondũ ũcio Davide na Abisai magĩgĩkinya harĩ andũ a Saulo </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũtukũ; na atĩrĩrĩ: Saulo agĩkorũo akomete handũ hau harigicĩrie </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na ngari, narĩo itimũ rĩake rĩkahandwo mũtwe-inĩ wake; </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nake Abner, na andũ arĩa angĩ, magakoma mamũrigicĩirie </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na mĩena yothe.  Hĩndĩ ĩo Abisai agĩkĩĩra Davide atĩrĩ: Ngai </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ arekereirie thũ yaku akamĩneana guoko-inĩ gwaku ũmũthĩ;</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>tondũ ũcio, ta reka ndĩmĩthece na itimũ rĩrĩ, ndĩmĩthecethanie</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na thĩ o itheca rĩmwe, na ndimĩtheca rĩa kerĩ.  Nake Davide </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>agĩkĩĩra Abisai atĩrĩ: Menya ũmũũrage; no ũndũ-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nũ ũngĩkĩhota gũtambũrũkia guoko okĩrĩre mũitĩrĩrio maguta </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wa Mwathani, na onwo ta atehĩtie? Davide agĩgĩcokia akiuga ũũ: </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Itimũ nĩ wa rĩrĩ, mũthamaki ũyũ; mũndũ ũmwe wa aanake acio nĩ </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>aringe arĩiyĩre.  Mwathani nĩwe ũrĩĩkaga mũndũ maũndũ o ta </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũrĩa ũthingu wake, na wĩhokeki wake, itariĩ; nĩ ũndũ Mwathani nĩ </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>egũkũneanĩte guoko-inĩ gwakwa ũmũthĩ, na ndinetĩkĩra </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>gũtambũrũkia guoko gwakwa njũkĩrĩre mũitĩrĩrio maguta wa Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                                   Thaburi 103:1-2;3-4 8 na 10;12-13</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA: Mwathani nĩ wa matha maingĩ, na nĩ muuma andũ mũno</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ngoro yakwa, gatha Mwathani; gwata kĩrĩa o gĩothe gĩĩ </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>thĩinĩ wakwa nĩ kĩgathe 
rĩĩtwa rĩake rĩamũre. </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ngoro yakwa, kĩgathe Mwathani, na ndũkariganĩrũo </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ wega o na ũmwe marĩa agwĩkaga. </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA:Mwathani nĩ wa matha maingĩ, na nĩ muuma andũ mũno</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Arĩ we ũkuohagĩra waganu waku wothe, ndũari ciaku ciothe o nacio </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nowe mũkũhonia; o we mũkũũri muoyo waku harĩ irima rĩa gĩkuũ,</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na nowe mũgwĩki maũndũ ma ũtugi na ma matha maingĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ta arĩ thũmbĩ aragwĩkĩra ya ũnene.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA:Mwathani nĩ wa matha maingĩ, na nĩ muuma andũ mũno</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani nĩ wa matha maingĩ nĩ muuma-andũ mũno; </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ndahiũhaga kũrakara, na e na ũtugi mũingĩ.  Ndatwĩkĩte ta ũrĩa </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mahĩtia maitũ maagĩrĩirũo, kana agatũcokeria </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kũringana na ũrĩa waganu witũ ũigana.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA:Mwathani nĩ wa matha maingĩ, na nĩ muuma andũ mũno</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>O ta ũrĩa irathĩro kũraihanĩrĩirie na ithũĩro, no taguo atũthengeirie </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mehia maitũ matũraihĩrĩrie.  
O ũrĩa mũthuri aiguagĩra </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ciana ciake tha, noguo Mwathani aiguagĩra arĩa mamwĩtigĩrĩte.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA:Mwathani nĩ wa matha maingĩ, na nĩ muuma andũ mũno</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ
1 Akorintho 15:45-49</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A KORINTHO MARĨA MA MBERE:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, mũndũ ũrĩa wa mbere wetagwo Adamu aatuĩkire </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mũndũ wĩ muoyo. Nake Adamu ũrĩa wa kũrigĩrĩria-rĩ, nĩ muoyo wa </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>gwĩkanagĩra muoyo.  No rĩrĩ, mwĩrĩ ũcio wa muoyo tiguo ũgĩaga mbere,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>no nĩ ũrĩa wa ndũire; na thutha waguo gũgoka ũcio wa muoyo.  </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mũndũ wa mbere nĩ wa na thĩ ĩno, 
o wa tĩri-inĩ; </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ĩndĩ mũndũ wa kerĩ nĩ wa na Igũrũ.  O ta ũguo ũcio wa tĩri aatariĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>noguo arĩa a tĩri nao matariĩ; 
na ta ũguo ũcio wa Igũrũ atariĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>noguo arĩa a Igũrũ nao matariĩ.  Na ta ũrĩa twagĩire na mũhianĩre wa ũcio </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wa tĩri-rĩ, no taguo tũkagĩa na mũhianĩre wa ũcio wa Igũrũ o naguo.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI
John 13,34</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Alleluya. Alleluya. Mwathani ekuuga ũũ: Ngũmũhe rĩathani rĩerũ, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ atĩ mwendane,o ta ũguo niĩ ndĩmwendete.
Alleluia</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI			                Luka 6:27-38</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE LUKA:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hĩndĩ ĩo Yesu erire arũmĩrĩri ake: ngũmwĩra atĩrĩ inyuĩ mũrathikĩrĩria: endagai thũ cianyu,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> na mwĩkage wega arĩa mamũnenaga, na ningĩ mũrathimage arĩa mamũrumaga, na mũhoyagĩre arĩa mamũcambagia. </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Na rĩrĩ, mũndũ wa gũkũringa rũthĩa rũmwe, mũhũgũkĩrie rũrĩa rũngĩ naruo: na ũrĩa wa gũgũtunya nguo yaku ya igũrũ,</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> ndũkamũgirie athiĩ na nguo ĩrĩa ya thĩinĩ o nayo.  O mũndũ ũrĩa wothe ũgũkũhoya kĩndũ, mũhe; </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na ũrĩa ũngĩgũtunya indo ciaku, ndũkamũrandũre.  Na rĩrĩ, o ũrĩa mwendaga gwĩkwo nĩ andũ, mekagei o ũguo.  Rĩu-rĩ,</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> mũngĩkorũo mwendaga  o arĩa mamwendaga inyuĩ, mũkĩrĩ na ngatho ĩrĩkũ? Nĩ gũkorũo ehia nao nĩ mendaga andũ arĩa mamendaga.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>  Na ningĩ, mũngĩkorũo mwĩkaga wega inyuĩ, mũkĩrĩ na ngatho ĩrĩkũ? Nĩ gũkorũo ehia nao nĩ mekaga o ũguo. </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Ningĩ mũngĩkorũo muohoragĩra o arĩa mwĩhokete atĩ nĩ makamũrĩha, mũkĩrĩ na ngatho ĩrĩkũ?</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Nĩ gũkorũo o na andũ ehia nĩ mohoragĩra ehia angĩ, nĩ getha
Magacokagĩrio indo ciiganaine na iria maarutire. </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> No rĩrĩ, endagai thũ cianyu, na mũciĩkage wega, o na mũohoranagĩre, mũtegwĩkũũĩra mũndũ,</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> na igai rĩanyu rĩgatuĩka rĩnene, na nĩ mũgatuĩka ariũ a Ũrĩa-wĩ-Igũrũ-mũno: nĩ gũkorũo we nĩ atugaga arĩa matacokagia ngatho, o na arĩa oru.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>  Iguanagĩrai tha o ta ũrĩa Ithe wanyu nake aiguanagĩra tha.  Ningĩ mũtikanekũũanĩre,</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> na inyuĩ ene mũtikanekũũĩrũo: mũtikanatuanĩre, na mũtikanatuĩrũo: ohanagĩrai na nĩ mũkoherũo:</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> heanagai, na nĩ mũkaheo; mũgererũo na kĩgeri kĩrĩa kĩega, o kĩrĩa gĩkindĩrĩtwo na gĩthukathukĩtwo, </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na kĩrĩa kĩhũmbĩrĩirũo o kinya irio igaitĩka thĩ, nokĩo mũkaheo nakĩo na kiunĩrũo nguo-inĩ cianyu. </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Nĩ gũkorũo o kĩgeri kĩrĩa mũgeranagĩra nakĩo, nĩkĩo mũgacoka kũgeragĩrũo nakĩo.</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s></f>"}],Style:{Background:{Image:"flower4.jpg"}},
