Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>DOMINIKA YA NNE YA KWARESMA MWAKA C</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SOMO LA KWANZA
Yoshua 5:9a, 10-12</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Somo katika kitabu cha Yoshua</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Siku zile: Bwana alimwambia Yoshua: \"Siku hii ya leo </s></f>"},{ID:4,
