Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wamepiga kambi yao huko Gilgali, jioni ya siku ya kumi na nne </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ya mwezi, waliadhimisha Sikukuu ya Pasaka </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>katika tambarare za Yeriko. Nao wakala mazao ya nchi siku ya </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>pili baada ya Sikukuu ya Pasaka yaani, mikate isiyotiwa </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>chachu na bisi siku ile. Walipokula mazao ya nchi ile, siku ya pili </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>yake, mana ikakoma; kwa vile sasa waliweza kula mazao ya nchi ile. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kwa kuwa Waisraeli hawakuwa na mana tena wakajilisha </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mazao ya nchi ya Kanaani tangu wakati huo.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA
Zaburi 34:2-3, 4-5, 6-7, 8-9 </s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>KIITIKIO: Onjeni, mwone jinsi Bwana alivyo mwema.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nitamtukuza Bwana kila wakati sifa zake zi kinywani mwangu daima.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nafsi yangu itajisifu katika Bwana Wanyonge wasikie na kufurahi. </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>KIITIKIO: Onjeni, mwone jinsi Bwana alivyo mwema.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mtukuzeni Bwana pamoja nami, tuliadhimishe jina lake pamoja.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nilimkimbilia Bwana, akanisikiliza, akaniopoa katika hofu zangu zote. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>KIITIKIO: Onjeni, mwone jinsi Bwana alivyo mwema.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mtazameni Mungu mkafurahiwe na nyuso zenu zisihuzunike.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mnyonge huyu alilia, naye Bwana akamsikiliza, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akamwokoa katika shida zake zote. </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>KIITIKIO: Onjeni, mwone jinsi Bwana alivyo mwema.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Malaika wa Bwana ameweka kambi kwao, kuwazungukia wale </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wamchao Mungu na kuwaokoa. Onjeni, mwone jinsi Bwana </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>alivyo mwema heri mtu yule anayemkimbilia. </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>KIITIKIO: Onjeni, mwone jinsi Bwana alivyo mwema.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SOMO LA PILI
2 Wakorintho 5:17-21</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Somo katika barua ya pili ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Wakorintho</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ndugu zangu: Mtu akiwa katika Kristo ni kiumbe </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kipya. Ya kale yamepita, mapya yamefika.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hayo yote yanatoka kwa Mungu. Yeye ametupatanisha naye </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kwa ujumbe wa Kristo, akatukabidhi sisi kazi ya upatanisho.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Yaani, Mungu ameipatanisha dunia naye katika Kristo, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kusudi asiwahesabie watu tena makosa yao.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Akaliweka neno la upatanisho ndani yetu. Basi, tumekuwa</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wajumbe mahali pa Kristo, kwa maana ni Mungu anayeonya</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kwa huduma yetu. Na ombi tunalotoa kwa jina la </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kristo ndilo mpatanishwe na Mungu. Yeye amemfanya yule </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>asiyejua dhambi kuwa dhambi kwa ajili yetu, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ili na sisi tuwe uadilifu 
wa Mungu katika yeye.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
