Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na wana wawili, mdogo akamwambia baba yake, \"Baba,</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nipe sehemu ya mali iliyo haki yangu.’ Basi baba akawagawia mali.  </s></f>"},{ID:7,
