alikotapanya mali yake kwa </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kuishi maisha ya uasherati. 
Alipomaliza vyote, njaa kali </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>iliingia nchi ile, naye pia akaanza kupatwa na shida. Basi akaenda </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kujiunga na mwenyenji wa huko 
aliyemtuma shambani kwake </s></f>"},{ID:12,
