'Upesi leteni joho maridadi, </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mkamvike, mtieni pete kidoleni na viatu miguuni. Tena mleteni ndama </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mnono, mkamchinje. Kisha tule na kufanya sherehe, </s></f>"},{ID:16,
