Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kisha wakaanza kufanya shangwe. Sasa mzaliwa wake wa kwanza </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>alikuwa bado shambani, na aliporudi na kuikaribia nyumba, </s></f>"},{ID:18,
