nĩguo wa atĩ Ngai aarĩ thĩinĩ wa</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kristũ, agaikara akĩiguithanagĩria kĩrĩndĩ gĩa thĩ nake we mwene,</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>agĩtigaga gũtarĩra andu mahĩtia mao, na atĩ ũhoro ũcio wa ũiguithanio </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ aũigĩte kũrĩ ithuĩ tũũheanage.  
Tondũ wa ũguo, tũkĩrĩ arekio </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mareketio a kwarĩrĩria Kristũ, o ta arĩ Ngai ũrathaithana </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na tũnua twitũ; twamũthaitha ithenya rĩa Kristũ atĩrĩ:</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ĩtĩkĩrai kũiguithanio  na Ngai.  Ngai nĩ aatũmire ũcio ũtarĩ hingo </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>aamenyire wĩhia atuĩke o wĩhĩa arĩ we ithenya riitũ,</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ getha ithuĩ, nĩ ũndũ wa ũrĩa twĩ thĩinĩ wake, tũtuĩke o ũthingu wa Ngai.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI
Luka 15,18</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>	
Nĩ ngũũkĩra ‘thiĩ kũrĩ Awa, ngamwĩre atĩrĩ: Awa, nĩ njĩhĩtie Igũrũ, o na ngakwĩhia wee.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI
Luka 15:1-3, 11-32</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE LUKA:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hĩndĩ ĩo etia mbia cia igoti o na ehia nĩ maathengereire othe Yesu,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ getha mamũigue.  Nao Afarisei na aandĩki-marũa makĩng’ong’ora </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>makĩĩranaga atĩrĩ: Mũndũ ũyũ nĩ aamũkagĩra ehia akarĩanĩra nao. </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nake akĩmera ngerekano ĩno, akiuga atĩrĩ: Mũndũ ũmwe aarĩ  </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na ariũ eerĩ: nake ũrĩa 
mũnyinyi  akĩĩra ithe atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Awa, ngaĩra indo o iria ingĩgatuĩka  ciakwa.  Nake ithe akĩmagayania indo </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ciake ciothe. Na matukũ manyinyi maathira, mũriũ ũcio </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mũnyinyi akĩũngania indo ciake ciothe, akĩgwata njĩra,</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>agĩthiĩ bũrũri warĩ kũraya;
agĩitanga indo ciake </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ciothe kũu na mĩtũũrĩre ya ũmaramari.  
Nake aanina</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>indo ciake ciothe, gũkĩgĩa ng’aragu nene mũno bũrũri ũcio; nake agĩitĩka </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kũhũta na gũthĩna. Agĩthiĩ,
akĩĩiguithania na mũndũ</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wa bũrũri  ũcio; nake mũndũ ũcio akĩmũrekia akariithie ngũrũe</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>gĩthaka-inĩ gĩake.  Nake nĩ endaga mũno kwĩhũnia  na makoro ma maciaro</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ma mũtĩ wa mũkarabi, 
marĩa maarĩagwo nĩ ngũrũe;</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na gũtirĩ mũndũ wamũheire kĩndũ.  
Na rĩrĩa ecokerire,</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akiuga atĩrĩ: Hĩ! Nĩ ndungata ciigana atĩa cia awa irĩ na irio cia gũciigana, </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na igatigara, na niĩ nĩ ngũkuĩra gũkũ nĩ ng’aragu! Nĩ ngũũkĩra ‘thiĩ kũrĩ </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>awa, ngamwĩra atĩrĩ: Awa, nĩ njĩhĩtie Igũrũ, o na ngakwĩhia wee:</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ndiagĩrĩirwo nĩ gũcoka gwĩtagwo mũrũguo: ndua ta ndungata </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ĩmwe yaku. Nake agĩũkĩra agĩthiĩ kũrĩ ithe.  No rĩrĩ, hĩndĩ ĩrĩa aarĩ o haraya,</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ithe akĩmuona, akĩringwo nĩ tha, 
akĩhanyũka</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akĩmũhĩmbĩria ngingo, akĩmũmumunya mũno. </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nake mũriũ akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Awa, nĩ njĩhĩtie Igũrũ, o na </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ngakwĩhia wee, na ndiagĩrĩirũo nĩ gũcoka 
gwĩtagwo </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mũrũguo. No ithe akĩĩra ndungata ciake atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Thiĩi narua, mũgĩre nguo ĩrĩa njega mũmũhumbe; na mũmwĩkĩre gĩcũhĩ</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kĩara na iratũ magũrũ;
ningĩ mũcoke mũrehe</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>njaũ ya gĩcegũ ĩrĩa noru mũmĩthĩnje,
tũrĩe na tũcanjamũke,</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ gũkorũo mũriũ ũyũ wakwa ararĩ mũkuũ, na nĩ mũriũku; ningĩ </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ arorĩte, na nĩ acokete kuoneka.  Nao magĩitĩka gũcanjamũka. </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na rĩrĩ, mũriũ  ũrĩa mũkũrũ aatindĩte mũgũnda: na rĩrĩa aainũkaga,</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>aakuhĩhĩria nyũmba-rĩ, akĩigua mĩtũrirũ ĩkĩhuhwo, gũkĩinagwo rũĩmbo.  </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Agĩgĩĩta ndungata ĩmwe ya mũciĩ, akĩmĩũria gĩtũmi kĩa maũndũ macio.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nayo ĩkĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Mũrũ wa nyũkwa nĩ okĩte; nake thoguo </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ athĩnjĩte njaũ ya gĩcegũ ĩrĩa noru, nĩ ũndũ nĩ 
aamũcokerera</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>arĩ mũgima. Nake akĩrkara, akĩrega gũtonya nyũmba, ĩndĩ ithe akiuma </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nja akĩmũthaitha atonye.  Nowe agĩcokia akĩĩra ithe atĩrĩ:</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ndanakũrutĩra wĩra mĩaka mĩingĩ, na ndirĩ ndagarara rĩathani rĩaku </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o rĩothe; no ndũrĩ wa’he o na kori tũthĩnje, tũcanjamũke </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na arata akwa: no rĩrĩ, mũrũguo oka, ũcio waninire indo ciaku ciothe </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na aka a maraya, nĩ wamũthĩnjĩra njaũ ya gĩcegũ ĩrĩa noru.  </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nake ithe akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Wee nĩ ũtũũraga na niĩ hĩndĩ ciothe,</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nacio indo iria ciothe ndĩ nacio nĩ ciaku.  No rĩrĩ, nĩ kwagĩrĩire</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>tũcanjamũke na tũkene; nĩ gũkorũo ũcio mũrũ wa nyũkwa ararĩ </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mũkuũ, na nĩ mũriũku; ningĩ nĩ arorĩte, na nĩ acokete kuoneka.</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s></f>"}],
Text:"KIUMIA KIA INYA KIA WINYEREKIA MWAKA C"},{Guid:"hojcQ60L9EaKDDpkRgQ/Xw",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>DOMINIKA YA TANO MWAKA C</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SOMO LA KWANZA
Isaya 6:1-2a. 3-8</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Somo katika kitabu cha Nabii Isaya</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwaka ule alipokufa Mfalme Uzia, nilimwona Bwana amekaa </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>katika kiti cha enzı kilichoinuka: 
mapindo ya</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>vazi lake yamejaza hekalu. Maserafi walisimama juu yake: </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kila mmoja alikuwa na mbawa sita: wakaitana, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kila mmoja na mwenzake, wakisema:
\"Mtakatifu, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mtakatifu, Mtakatifu, Bwana Mungu wa ulimwengu</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>dunia nzima imejaa utukufu wake.” Na misingi ya vizingiti </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ikatikisika kama sauti ya wenye kulia, nalo hekalu </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>likajaa moshi. Nami nikasema, \"Ole wangu, nimeangamia!.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Maana mimi ni mtu mwenye midomo michafu, makao yangu ni kati ya </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>taifa lenye midomo michafu, na macho yangu yamemwona Mfalme, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Bwana wa majeshi!” Hapo mmoja wa maserafi akaruka upande </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wangu, akishika mkononi kaa la moto, alilotwaa altareni kwa koleo. </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Akanigusa kinywa kwa kaa hilo, akasema, \"Tazama, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>hili limegusa midomo yako, uovu wako umeondolewa, </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na dhambi yako imesamehewa.\" Kisha </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nikasikia sauti ya Bwana, akisema: Nimtume nani? Nani atakayekuwa </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mjumbe wetu? Nikaitika, \"Mimi hapa, unitume mimi!</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA
Zaburi 138:1-2a, 2bc-3, 4-5.7c-8 (K. 1c)</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kiitikio: 
Mbele ya malaika nitakuimbia sifa, ee Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nitakushukuru, ee BWANA, kwa moyo wangu wote; mbele ya malaika </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nitakuimbia sifa.
Nitakusujudu nikilielekea hekalu lako takatifu. </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kiitikio:
Mbele ya malaika nitakuimbia sifa, ee Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nitalishukuru jina lako
Kwa ajili ya wema na uaminifu wako</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kwa maana umekuza kuliko yote jina lako na ahadi yako</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Siku nilipokuomba ulinisikiliza; uliifariji nafsi yangu kwa kunitia nguvu.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kiitikio:
Mbele ya malaika nitakuimbia sifa, ee Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wafalme wote wa dunia watakutukuza, ee Bwana, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Watakapoyasikia maneno ya kinywa chako, Wataziimbia </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>njia za Bwana: “Kwani utukufu wa Bwana ni mkuu!” </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kiitikio:
Mbele ya malaika nitakuimbia sifa, ee Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mkono wako wa kulia unanisalimisha; Bwana </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>atatimiliza kwangu mpango wake, Ee Bwana, wema </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wako ni wa milele, usiziache kazi ya mikono yako! </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kiitikio:
Mbele ya malaika nitakuimbia sifa, ee Bwana.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SOMO LA PILI
1 Wakorintho 15:1-11</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Somo katika barua ya kwanza ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Wakorintho</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ndugu nawakumbusha Injili niliyowahubiria. </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mmeipokea na kuthibitika ndani yake. Na kwa nguvu yake </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mnaokolewa mkilishikilia neno nililowahubiria. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Msipolishikilia,mlisadiki
bure. Hasa niliwakabidhi </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>niliyopokea mwenyewe, yaani: Kristo alikufa kwa ajili ya dhambi zetu, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kama ilivyoandikwa, tena alizikwa, akafufuliwa </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>siku ya tatu, kama Maandiko yasemavyo Akamtokea Kefa, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na baadaye wale Kumi na Wawili. Halafu akawatokea </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ndugu zaidi ya mia tano pamoja, ambao wengi wao wanaishi hata sasa,</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ila baadhi yao wameaga dunia. Baadaye akamtokea </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Yakobo, halafu mitume wote. Kisha, baada ya wote,</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akanitokea hata mimi, kama mtu aliyezaliwa nje ya wakati </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wake. Maana mimi ni mdogo kuliko mitume wote. Sistahili </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kuitwa mtume, kwa sababu nililitesa Kanisa la Mungu</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Lakini kwa neema ya Mungu nimekuwa kama nilivyo, na neema </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>yake haikuwa ya bure ndani yangu. Bali nilijitahidi zaidi ya </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wengine wote, kwa kweli si mimi, ila neema ya Mungu pamoja nami. </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Basi mahubiri yangu na yao ni sawa, nayo mmeyasadiki.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Neno la Bwana</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SHANGILIO LA INJILI
John 15:16  				                             </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Aleluya, Aleluya.
Njoni mnifuate, asema Bwana; nami </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nitawafanya kuwa wavuvi wa watu.
Aleluya.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>INJILI
Luka 5:1-11</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Luka</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wakati ule: Watu wengi walipomsonga [Yesu] wapate kulisikiliza </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>neno la Mungu, yeye alikuwa 
amesimama kando ya Ziwa </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>la Genesareti. Akaona vyombo viwili vimepwelewa pwani wavuvi </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wameshuka, wanaosha nyavu. 
Akapanda chombo kimoja, ndicho </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>cha Simoni, akamwomba akitenge kidogo na pwani. Akaketi. </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akawafundisha makutano toka chomboni. Baada ya mafundisho, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akamwambia Simoni,
“Rudisha chombo baharini, shusheni </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nyavu zenu kwa kuvua samaki.”  Simoni akajibu, akamwambia, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>\"Bwana, tumejitahidi sana usiku mzima tusipate kitu, lakini </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kwa neno lako nitashusha nyavu.”
Walipofanya hivyo, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>walinasa samaki wengi mno hata nyavu zao zikaanza kukatika.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wakawaashiria wenzao waliokuwako katika chombo kingine </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>waje kuwasaidia. Wakaja, 
wakajaza vyombo vyote viwili hata karibu ya </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kuzama. Simoni Petro alipoona hayo, alimwangukia Yesu magotini </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>pake, akasema \"Ondoka kwangu, ewe Bwana, kwa maana mimi ni mtu </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mkosefu.” Maana mshangao ulimshika yeye na wote waliokuwa </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>pamoja naye kwa sababu ya 
wingi wa samaki </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>waliowanasa, kadhalika Yakobo na Yohane, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wana wa Zebedayo, walikuwa washiriki wa Simoni.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Yesu akamwambia Simoni, Usiogope; tangu sasa utakuwa </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mvuvi wa watu. Walipoviegesha vyombo pwani, </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wakaacha vyote, wakamfuata.</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f>"}],
Text:"DOMINIKA YA TANO MWAKA C"},{Guid:"NA9xnHdd/kidzzgglKroWQ",Verses:[{Style:{Body:{FontStyle:{Fill:{Color:"FFFFFF00"},Stroke:{Color:"FFFFD700"},ShadowColor:"FFFFFFFF"}}},
Text:"<s1076></s><u><fArial Black><s2769>DOMINIKA YA TATU 
YA MWAKA C</s></f></u>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>SOMO LA KWANZA
Nehemia 
8:2-4a, 5-6, 8-10</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Somo katika kitabu cha Nehemia</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Siku zile: Ezra kuhani akaileta Torati mbele ya mkutano uliojaa</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>wanawake na wanaume na wengine wote waliofahamu, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>katika siku ya kwanza ya mwezi wa saba. Akiwa amesimama</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>upande mmoja wa mahali pa wazi, akikabili Lango la Maji,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Ezra alisoma
kutoka humo kitabuni tokea alfajiri hadi adhuhuri, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>mbele ya wanaume na wanawake, na watoto walio wakubwa kuelewa;</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769> na watu wote walisikiliza kwa makini, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>yote yaliyosomwa kutoka kitabu cha Torati. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Naye Ezra kuhani akasimama juu ya jukwaa la miti </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>iliyojengwa kwa kusudi hilo.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Ezra alifungua kitabu mbele ya macho ya watu wote, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>maana alisimama mahali pa juu zaidi kuliko watu wote.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Watu hao wakasimama wima mara tu alipokifunua kitabu. </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Ezra akamtukuza Bwana, Mungu mkuu,</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769> na watu wote huku wakiwa wameinua mikono yao juu, wakaitikia, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>\"Amina, amina!\" Halafu wakainama chini na kumsujudu Bwana kifudifudi. </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Naye Ezra akasoma kutoka kitabu cha Sheria ya Mungu, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>akiitafsiri ili watu waweze kuelewa kilichosomwa. </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Halafu Nehemia, yaani gavana, na Ezra kuhani-mwandishi </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>na Walawi waliokuwa wakifahamika na watu waliwaambia watu wote.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>\"Leo ni siku takatifu kwa Bwana Mungu wetu. Hivyo msiwe na  </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>huzuni na wala msilie\" - maana watu wote walikuwa wanalia, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>walipoyasikia maneno ya sheria. Akaendelea, \"Nendeni mkale </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>chakula bora na vinywaji vitamu,
na kutenga sehemu kwa wale </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>watu ambao hawakutayarisha chochote; kwani leo ni siku takatifu kwa Bwana wetu.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769> Msisikitike leo, kwa kuwa furaha ya Bwana ndiyo nguvu yenu!\"</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA 
Zaburi 
19:8, 9, 10, 15 </s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>(K) Maneno yako, ee Bwana, ni roho pia ni uzima.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Sheria ya Bwana ni kamilifu,
yautuliza moyo.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Maagizo ya Bwana ni imara,
yamletea mjinga hekima,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>(K) Maneno yako, ee Bwana, ni roho pia ni uzima.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Amri za Bwana ni za haki,
zaufurahisha moyo,</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>agizo la Bwana ni safi,
layatia macho mwangaza.(K)</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>(K) Maneno yako, ee Bwana, ni roho pia ni uzima.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Uchaji wa Bwana ni safi,
hudumu hata milele.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Hukumu za Bwana ni kweli,
zote ni za haki kamili. (K)</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>(K) Maneno yako, ee Bwana, ni roho pia ni uzima.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Maneno ya Kinywa changu yakupendeze wewe,</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>nayo mawazo ya moyo wangu,</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>yaliyo mbele yako, ee Bwana,
mwamba wangu na Mkombozi wangu. </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>(K) Maneno yako, ee Bwana, ni roho pia ni uzima.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769> SOMO LA PILI
Wakorintho 12:12-30</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Somo katika barua ya kwanza ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Wakorintho </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Ndugu zangu: Kristo ni kama mwili: mwili ni mmoja wenye </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>viungo vingi. Lakini viungo vyote vya mwili huo, ijapo ni vingi,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>huunda mwili mmoja. Kwa maana sisi sote tumebatizwa </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>kwa Roho mmoja kuwa mwili mmoja bila tofauti baina ya </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Wayahudi na Wagiriki,au baina ya watumwa na watu huru. </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Nasi sote tumenyweshwa 
Roho mmoja. Basi, mwili si </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>kiungo kimoja, bali ni viungo vingi. Kama mguu ungesema, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>\"Mimi si mkono, basi si sehemu ya mwili,\" je, hivyo mguu </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>ungeacha kuwa sehemu ya mwili?</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Na kama sikio lingesema, \"Mimi si jicho, basi si sehemu ya mwili.”</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>je, hivyo lingeacha 
kuwa sehemu ya mwili? </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Kama mwili wote ungekuwa jicho, ungewezaje kusikika?</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769> Na Kama mwili wote ungekuwa sikio, ungewezaje Kunusa? </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Kumbe Mungu ameweka viungo hivyo vyote na </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>kila kimoja Katika mwili kwa kadiri ya azimio lake.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Kama vyote 
vingekuwa kiungo kimoja tu, 
mwill ungepatikanaje? </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Basi, viungo ni vingi, 
lakini mwili ni mmoja. </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Hapo Jicho haliwezi 
kuuambia mkono, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>\"Sikuhitaji,\" wala kichwa hakiwezi kuiambia miguu, \"Siwahitaji ninyi.\" </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Zaidi ya hayo, viungo vya mwili vinavyoonekana </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>kuwa vinyonge vinahitajika zaidi. </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Tena tunazidi kuvihifadhi viungo vile vya mwili </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>vinavyoonekana machoni mwetu kuwa hafifu.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Hivyo viungo vyetu vya haya huvishwa kwa njia isiyotakiwa na viungo vyetu maalum.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769> Katika kupanga mwili, Mungu amevijalia zaidi viungo hafifu,</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>ili kuepusha mabishano mwilini na kuviwezesha </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>viungo vyote kuitikiana vizuri.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769> Basi, kiungo kimoja kikiumwa, viungo vyote huvumiliana nacho, na </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>kiungo kimoja kikitukuzwa,
viungo vyote hufurahi pamoja nacho. </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Lakini ni ninyi mlio mwili wa Kristo na viungo vyake kiungo kwa kiungo.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769> Na wengine Mungu amewaweka katika Kanisa kuwa mitume </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>mahali pa kwanza; manabii, mahali pa pili; walimu,</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769> mahali pa tatu, na baada ya hao wafanya miujiza, </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>tena wenye kipaji cha kuponya, wasaidizi,</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>viongozi, na wenye kusema lugha za kiroho. </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Je, hao wote ni mitume? Au wote ni manabii? Au wote ni walimu? </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Au wote ni wafanya 
miujiza? Je, hao wote wana kipaji cha kuponya? </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Au wote wamejaliwa kusema lugha za kiroho? Au wote waweza kufafanua lugha hizo? </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Aleluya. 
Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Bwana amenituma niwahubirie  maskini habari njema, </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>kuwatangazia wafungwa kufunguliwa.</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Aleluya.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>INJILI 
Luka 
1:1-4; 4:14-21</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Luka</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Kwa kuwa watu wengi wamejaribu kuyaratibisha </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>masimulizi ya mambo yaliyotendeka kati yetu, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>kama walivyoyapokea 
kwa wale 
waliokuwa mashahidi </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>wa macho na watumishi wa neno tokea mwanzo, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>sasa nami naona afadhali, baada ya uchunguzi</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>makini wa mambo hayo yote, toka mwanzo, nikuandikie wewe, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>mheshimiwa Theofilo, habari zake hatua kwa hatua, upate </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>kujua ya kuwa mafundisho uliyoyapata yana msingi thabiti.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>wakati ule: 
Katika nguvu ya Roho, 
Yesu alirudi Galilaya na sifa  yake </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>ikaenea katika nchi yote ya jirani. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Alifundisha katika masinagogi naye akasifiwa na watu wote.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Akaenda Nazareti, ndiko alikolelewa, na siku ya Sabato akaingia </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>katika sinagogi kama ilivyokuwa desturi yake.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769> Akasimama asome, wakampa kitabu cha nabii Isaya, akakifungua, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>akakuta mahali palipoandikwa:
\"Roho wa Bwana yu juu yangu, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>kwa maana amenipaka mafuta niwahubirie maskini habari njema. </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Amenituma kuwatangazia wafungwa kufunguliwa, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>vipofu kuona tena, kuwaletea wafungwa uhuru, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>na kutangaza mwaka uliokubalika kwa Bwana.\"</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Akakifunga kitabu, akamrudishia mtumishi, akaketi,</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769> na macho ya wote katika sinagogi yakamkazia. </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Akaanza kuwaambia, 
\"Leo andiko hili limetimia masikioni mwenu.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1076></s><fArial Black><s2769>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f>"}],Style:{Background:{Image:"Bible.jpg",Luminosity:-30}},
Text:"DOMINIKA YA TATU YA MWAKA C"},{Guid:"JGWoKna5E06Q9tMCaKMvdw",Verses:[{Style:{Background:{Luminosity:-35}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>KIUMIA KIA ITHATU KIA MWAKA C</s></f>"},{ID:2,Style:{Background:{Luminosity:-35}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE
Nehemia 8:2-4a, 5-6,8-10</s></f>"},{ID:2,Style:{Background:{Image:"Blue Sky over Field.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA NEHEMIA: </s></f>"},{ID:3,Style:{Background:{Image:"Blue Sky over Field.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Matukũ-inĩ macio, Esdra mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai, aatwarire ibuku </s></f>"},{ID:4,Style:{Background:{Image:"Blue Sky over Field.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>rĩu rĩa watho harĩ kĩrĩndĩ kĩu kĩa andũ acio monganĩte, arũme o na </s></f>"},{ID:5,Style:{Background:{Image:"Blue Sky over Field.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>andũ-a-nja, o na andũ othe arĩa maahotaga kũigua gĩtũmi kĩa </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>watho ũcio. Nake agĩthoma mohoro marĩa maarĩ thĩinĩ warĩo arĩ </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o handũ hau haariĩ haarĩ mbere ya Kĩhingo kĩu kĩa Maĩ,</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kuuma o rũcinĩ gwakĩa nginya a 
mĩaraho, andũ acio othe, arũme </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na andũ-a-nja, o na andũ arĩa othe maahotaga kũigua gĩtũmi </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kĩamo, marĩ ho. Nao andũ acio othe magĩtega matũ mao maigue ũhoro </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wa ibuku  rĩu rĩa watho.  Nake Esdra, 
ũcio mwandĩki-marũa, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akĩrũgama handũ hokĩrĩirie haakĩtwo na mĩtĩ nĩ ũndũ wa ũhoro ũcio kĩũmbe.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake Esdra agĩkũnjũra ibuku rĩu andũ 
othe makĩonaga; </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ ũndũ aarũgamĩte handũ igũrũ agatũũgĩra gũkĩra andũ arĩa angĩ</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>othe; na hĩndĩ ĩrĩa aarĩkũnjũrire, andũ othe makĩrũgama; </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nake Ezra akĩgooca Mwathani, Ngai ũrĩa Mũnene. </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nao andũ othe magĩcokia atĩrĩ: Amen, Amen, moete moko mao </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na igũrũ; nao makĩinamia mĩtwe yao, 
makĩhoya Mwathani </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maturumithĩtie mothiũ  mao thĩ.  
Nao magĩthoma  ciugo iria cia </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>watho ũcio wa Ngai ciarĩ ibuku-inĩ rĩu,
magĩcitaũranĩra na </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mũgambo mũnene, nĩguo andũ mamenye wega gĩtũmi  gĩacio.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake Nehemia, barũthi, na Esra, mũthĩnjĩri Ngai ũrĩa mwandĩki marũa, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na Alawii arĩa maarutaga andũ maũndũ, makĩĩra andũ othe atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mũthenya wa ũmũthĩ nĩ mwamũrĩre 
Mwathani Ngai  wanyu; </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>menyai mũgĩe na kĩeha, o na kana mũrĩre. 
Nĩ gũkorũo andũ </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>othe nĩ maarĩrire rĩrĩa maaiguire ciugo icio cia watho wa Ngai.  </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake agĩkĩmera atĩrĩ: Wĩthiĩrei mukarĩe nyama noru, na mũkanyue </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>indo irĩ mũrĩo, o nake mũndũ ũrĩa ũtarĩ 
kĩndũ aigĩirũo </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mũmũgaĩre rũgai rũake; nĩ gũkorũo mũthenya wa ũmũthĩ nĩ </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mwamũrĩre Mwathani  witũ; o na ningĩ tigai kũigua ũũru, </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ gũkenera Mwathani nĩkuo hinya wanyu.</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                                         Thaburi 19:7;8;9;14</s></f></u>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
Ciugo ciaku, Mwathani, nĩ cio muoyo na ũtũũro</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kĩrĩra kĩa Mwathani nĩ gĩkinyanĩru,
gĩthondekaga muoyo wa mũndũ;</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũira wa Mwathani  nĩ mwĩhokeku, ũũhĩgagia ũrĩa ũtarĩ mũũgĩ.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
Ciugo ciaku, Mwathani, nĩ cio muoyo na ũtũũro</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mataaro ma Mwathani nĩ merekereru, makenagia mũndũ ngoro,</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>watho wa Mwathani nĩ mũkembu, wĩkagĩra maitho  ũtheri.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
Ciugo ciaku, Mwathani, nĩ cio muoyo na ũtũũro</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Gwĩtigĩra  Mwathani nĩ ũndũ mũtheru, ũtũũraga tene na tene;</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>matua ma Mwathani no ma ma, nĩ ma kĩhooto kũna.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
Ciugo ciaku, Mwathani, nĩ cio muoyo na ũtũũro</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia kanua gakwa , o na mwĩrurumio wa ngoro, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ĩroetĩkĩrĩka mbere yaku, wee Mwathani, o wee ndũmba yakwa </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ya ihiga,o na ningĩ mũngũũri.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
Ciugo ciaku, Mwathani, nĩ cio muoyo na ũtũũro</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ
1 Akorintho 12:12-31</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE  PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A KORINTHO MARĨA MA MBERE:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, o ta ũrĩa mwĩrĩ wa mũndũ ũrĩ na ciĩga nyingĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na mwĩrĩ ũcio no ũmwe, nacio ciĩga ciothe ciaguo, o na </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ciatuĩka nĩ nyingĩ, no mwĩrĩ o ũmwe-rĩ, ũguo no taguo ũhoro wa Kristũ ũtariĩ. </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ gũkorũo ithuĩ twabatithirio ithuothe  nĩ ũndũ wa Muoyo </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o ũmwe tũtuĩke mwĩrĩ o ũmwe, tũrĩ Ayahudi, kana tũrĩ Ayunani, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na kana twĩ ngombo kana tũtarĩ ngombo; na ithuothe </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tũgĩkĩnyuithio Muoyo o ũmwe. Amu mwĩrĩ ti wa kĩĩga kĩmwe, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ wa ciĩga nyingĩ. Kũgũrũ kũngiuga: Tondũ ti niĩ guoko-rĩ,</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>niĩ ndikĩrĩ wa mwĩrĩ ũyũ, ũguo ndũngĩtũma kwage gũtuĩka kwaguo.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nakuo gũtũ kũngiuga: Na niĩ, tondũ ti niĩ riitho-rĩ, niĩ ndikĩrĩ wa mwĩrĩ  </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũyũ, ũguo ndũngĩtũma kwage gũtuĩka kwaguo.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwĩrĩ wothe ũngĩtuĩka na riitho itheri, kũigua twakĩiguaga na kĩ? </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ningĩ mwĩrĩ wothe ũngĩtuĩka no gũtũ gũtheri gwa kũigua nakuo-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ĩ kũnungĩra twakĩnungagĩra na kĩ? No rĩrĩ, 
ũrĩa kũrĩ nĩ atĩ </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ngai nĩ ekĩrire o kĩĩga thĩinĩ wa mwĩrĩ o harĩa endete gĩikare.  </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na rĩrĩ, ciothe ingĩtuĩka no kĩĩga kĩmwe-rĩ,
mwĩrĩ naguo </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wakĩgĩa ha? No ũrĩa kũrĩ, nĩ atĩ ciĩga nĩ nyingĩ, 
no  mwĩrĩ nĩ ũmwe.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Narĩo riitho rĩtingĩhota kwĩra guoko atĩrĩ: 
Niĩ ndirĩ na bata </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nawe; kana mũtwe naguo wĩre magũrũ, 
Niĩ ndirĩ na bata </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na inyuĩ. No makĩria mũno, ciĩga cia mwĩrĩ iria cionagũo ii njacu kũrĩ iria </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ingĩ-rĩ, nĩcio itangĩtigĩka; na mĩĩrĩ iitũ kũrĩa tuonaga na gũtarĩ </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gwa gũtĩwo mũno, kũu nĩkuo tũheaga gĩtĩo kĩnene makĩria,</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>harĩa honagwo ta harĩ thoni hagagĩtuwo haagĩrĩru gũkĩra </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kũrĩa kũngĩ; ĩndĩ harĩa hathaka hatirĩ ũndũ habataire gwĩkwo. </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwĩrĩ-rĩ, Ngai nĩ kũũiguithania aũiguithanĩtie, harĩa </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hatingiarĩtie agakĩhahe gĩtĩo makĩria ma harĩa hangĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:17,Style:{Background:{Transition:0}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ getha mwĩrĩ ndũkagĩe na ũndũ ũngĩwamũkania, </s></f>"},{ID:18,Style:{Background:{Transition:0}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>no atĩ ciĩga ciaguo imenyanagĩrĩre, 
o kĩĩga na kĩrĩa kĩngĩ.</s></f>"},{ID:19,Style:{Background:{Transition:0}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na kĩĩga kĩmwe kĩngĩkorũo gĩkĩnyarirĩka, 
ciĩga iria ingĩ </s></f>"},{ID:20,Style:{Background:{Transition:0}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ciothe nĩ inyarirĩkaga hamwe nakĩo.
Na kĩĩga kĩmwe </s></f>"},{ID:21,Style:{Background:{Transition:0}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kĩngĩkorũo kĩheetwo gĩtĩo-rĩ, ciĩga iria ingĩ ciothe igagĩkenanĩra </s></f>"},{ID:22,Style:{Background:{Transition:2}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hamwe nakĩo. Rĩu-rĩ, inyuĩ nĩ inyuĩ mwĩrĩ wa Kristũ, </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nake mũndũ o mũndũ wanyu nĩ kĩĩga kĩaguo.
O na thĩinĩ wa kanitha, </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ngai nĩ ekĩrĩte andũ amwe matuĩke o mbere atũmwo, a kerĩ anabii, </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>a gatatũ arutani; na thutha wa ũguo kũgĩe na ũringi wa ciama,</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ningĩ iheo cia ũhonokia wa mĩrimũ, na maũndũ ma ũteithania, </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ma ũtabarĩri, o na ũhoro wa gũthioma thiomi. </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>No anga andũ othe marĩ atũmwo? No anga othe marĩ anabii? </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>No anga othe marĩ arutani? Othe nĩ aringi a ciama?</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Othe nĩ ahe iheo cia ũhonania? Othe nĩ magĩthiomaga thiomi? </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Othe nĩ makĩhotaga gũtaũranĩra thiomi icio? </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>No rĩrĩ, wĩriragĩriei kũheo iheo ciumanĩte na Wega </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wa Ngai iria ikĩrĩte iria ingĩ. Na hamwe na ũguo-rĩ, nĩ ngũcoka </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kũmuonia njĩra ĩngĩ, ĩrĩa njega makĩria. </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI
Luka 4,18</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>	
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani nĩ andũmĩte ‘hunjagĩrie arĩa athĩĩni </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ũhoro-ũrĩa-Mwega, na njohorithie arĩa mahinyĩrĩirio.</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alleluia</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI
Luka 1:1-4; 4:14-21</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE LUKA:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kuona atĩ andũ aingĩ maanagwata kwandĩka marũa ma maũndũ marĩa tũhingĩirio, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o ta ũrĩa twaheirũo ũhoro wamo nĩ aira arĩa mameoneire,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kuuma o hĩndĩ ĩrĩa maambĩrĩirie gwĩkĩka; nao nĩo maarĩ </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndungata cia ũhoro ũcio; kuona ũguo-rĩ, niĩ o na niĩ-rĩ,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ ũndũ nĩ nduĩrĩtie wega maũndũ macio kuuma o rĩrĩa maambĩrĩirie gwĩkwo, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ nyonete arĩ wega ngwandĩkĩre marũa, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wee Theofilo, mũnene mũgathe, ma gũthingatania </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maũndũ macio wega o ta ũrĩa mekĩkire, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ getha ũmenye na ma maũndũ marĩa warutirũo.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hĩndĩ ĩo, Yesu agĩcoka arĩ na hinya wa Muoyo, agĩthiĩ Galilea: </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nayo ngumo yake ĩgĩtambũka ng’ongo ciothe cia kũu. </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake akarutanaga thinagoga-inĩ mũthenya wa thabatũ andũ othe.  </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake agĩkinya Nazareth, o kũrĩa aarereirũo: </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agĩtonya thinagoga mũthenya wa thabatũ, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o ta ũrĩa aamenyerete gwĩkaga, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akĩrũgama athome.  Nake akĩheo ibuku rĩa Isaia ũrĩa mũrathi. </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akĩrĩkũnjũra, agĩcaria harĩa ũhoro wandĩkĩtwo ũũ: </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Muoyo wa Mwathani arĩ igũrũ rĩakwa,</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ ũndũ nĩ aanjitĩrĩirie maguta hunjagĩrie </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>arĩa athĩni Ũhoro-
ũrĩa-Mwega: </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ andũmĩte menyithanie atĩ arĩa mohetwo nĩ mohorũo,</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na atĩ arĩa atumumu nĩ megũcoka kuona; </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na njohorithie arĩa mahinyĩrĩirio, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ningĩ hunjanagĩrie ũhoro wa mwaka wa Mwathani,</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o ũrĩa wĩtĩkĩrĩtwo.  Agĩcoka agĩkũnja ibuku, akĩrĩcokeria ndungata, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agĩikara thĩ; nao andũ othe arĩa maarĩ thinagoga </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>makĩmũkũũrĩra maitho.  Nake akĩrika kũmera atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ũhoro ũcio wandĩkĩtwo nĩ wahingio </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o ũmũthĩ mweiguĩra na matũ manyu.</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s></f>"}],Style:{Background:{Image:"Bible.jpg",Transition:3,Luminosity:-40}},
Text:"KIUMIA KIA ITHATU KIA MWAKA C"},{Guid:"H3B1LeeMZkCmNvRfAxEVYg",Verses:[],
Text:"DOMIKA YA TATU YA MWAKA C SOMO FUPI"},{Guid:"TsLlU25QqkyrOegxec9YGw",Verses:[{Style:{Body:{FontName:"Arial Black",FontSize:150,Wrap:1}},
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1384>DOMINIKA YA KUMI NA NNE YA MWAKA C</s></f></u><u><s923> </s></u>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA KWANZA</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika kitabu cha Nabii Isaya</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Shangilieni pamoja na Yerusalemu:
Pigeni vigelegele kwa ajili yake.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>enyi nyote mnaomlilia:
furahini, furahini pamoja naye</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ninyi nyote mlioomboleza kwa ajili yake.
lli mpate kunyonya na kushibishwa maziwa ya </s></f>"},{ID:6,Style:{Body:{Wrap:1}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>faraja vake
na kufurahishwa kwa maziwa yake matukufu.</s></f>"},{ID:6,Style:{Body:{Wrap:0}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Maana, Bwana asema hivi:
Nitatiririsha amani na 
utulivu pande zote kama mto;</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nao utukufu wa mataifa kama kijito kifurikacho.
Nanyi mtapata kunyonya,</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mtabebwva kifuani,.
na kubembelezwa juu ya magoti yake:</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mfano wa mwana anayefarijiwa na mama yake,
ndivyo nami nitawafariji;</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nanyi mtafarijiwa moyo katika Yerusalemu.
Kwa kuona hayo,
mioyo yenu itafurahi.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na mifupa yenu itasitawi mfano wa majani mabichi:</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na mkono wa Bwana utajulikana kwa watumishi wake.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Zaburi 66:-3a, 4 5,6 
7a. l6 na 20(&. 1</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Mshangilieni Mungu kwa furaha, ee nchi yote.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mshangilieni Mungu kwa furaha, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ee nchi yote;
liimbieni jina lake tukufu;</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mtoleeni sifa na heshima.
Mwambieni Mungu, 
\"Matendo yako ni ya ajabu sana!\" </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Mshangilieni Mungu kwa furaha, ee nchi yote.</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Dunia nzima ikuabudu na 
kukuimbia ilimbie jina lako!</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Njoni, tazameni matendo ya Mungu.</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ametanya mambo ya kutisha kati va wanadamu </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>k Mshangilieni Mungu kwa furaha, ee nchi yote.</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Aligeuza bahari kuwa nchi kavu:
katika mto walivuka kwa miguu.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hape ndipo tunamfurahia,
anatawala kwa enzi yake hata milele.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> K Mshangilieni Mungu kwa furaha, ee nchi yote.</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Njoni. sikieni ninyi nyote mnao mcha Mungu,
nami nitawaeleza makuu alivonitendea.</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Asifiwe Mungu asiyekataa maombi yangu,
wala kuniondolea fadhili zake nilizoomba. </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K Mshangilieni Mungu kwa furaha, ee nchi yote.</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA PILI
Somo katika barua ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Wagalatia</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndugu zangu: 
Mimi sipendi kujisifia kitu </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>isipokuwa msalaba wa
Bwana wetu Yesu Kristo.</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa msalaba huo ulimwengu 
umesulibiwa kwangu, nami</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nimesulibiwa kwa ulimwengu. 
Kutahiriwa au kutotahiriwa si kitu:</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kilicho muhimu ni kuwa kiumbe kipya.
Amani na huruma ziwe na wenye </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kuifuata kanuni hiyo na kwa
Israeli wa Mungu. </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kutoka sasa mtu asinisumbue tena, 
kwani ninazo alama za Yesu mwilini mwangu.</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neema ya Bwana wetu Yesu 
Kristo iwe na roho zenu, ndugu zangu.</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Amina.</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SHANGILIO LA INJILI</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakolosai 
3:15a 16a</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Aleluya.
W. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Acheni amani ya Kristo itawale mioyoni mwenu,</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Kristo likae ndani yenu kwa wingi.</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>W. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>INIILI</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Luka 12:32-4</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>INJILI
Luka 10:12,17</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>
Somo la Injili takatifu kama lilivyoandikwa na Luka (10:1–12, 17–20)</s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>Wakati ule: Bwana aliweka wengine sabini na wawili, akawatuma wawili wawili wamtangulie katika kila mji na kijiji alikokusudia kwenda mwenyewe.</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>Akawaambia, “Mavuno ni mengi, lakini watenda kazi ni wachache; basi mwombeni Bwana wa mavuno, apeleke watenda kazi katika mavuno yake. Nendeni; angalieni, nawatuma kama wana-kondoo kati ya mbwamwitu.</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>Msichukue mfuko wa fedha, wala mkoba, wala viatu; wala msimsalimie mtu njiani. Na nyumba yoyote mtakayoingia, semeni kwanza: ‘Amani iwemo nyumbani humu.’ Na ikiwa yumo mwana wa amani, amani yenu itatua juu yake; la sivyo, itarudi kwenu.</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>Kaeni katika nyumba hiyo, mkila na kunywa wanavyowapa, maana mtenda kazi anastahili mshahara wake. Msiende toka nyumba hata nyumba. Na katika mji wowote mtakaopokelewa, kuleni mlivyowekewa. Waponeni wagonjwa waliomo, waambieni, ‘Ufalme wa Mungu umekaribia.’</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>Lakini katika mji wo wote msipopokelewa, tokeni katika barabara zake mseme: ‘Hata mavumbi ya mji wenu yaliyoshikamana na miguu yetu tunayakung’uta juu yenu. Lakini jueni haya: Ufalme wa Mungu umekaribia.’</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>Nawaambieni, siku ile Sodoma itapata nafuu kuliko mji huo.”</s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>Wale sabini na wawili walirudi kwa furaha, wakisema, “Bwana, hata pepo wanatutii kwa jina lako.”</s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>Akawaambia, “Nilimwona Shetani akianguka kutoka mbinguni kama umeme wa radi. Tazameni, nimewapa uwezo wa kukanyaga nyoka na nge, na nguvu zote za adui; wala hakuna kitu kitakachowadhuru.</s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>Walakini, msifurahi kwa sababu pepo wanawatii, bali furahini kwa sababu majina yenu yameandikwa mbinguni.”</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f>"}],Style:{Body:{FontName:"Arial Black",FontSize:150}},
