Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>pamoja mara uvumi  ulitoka mbinguni kama upepo mkali,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> ukaijaza nyumba yote walimokaa. </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na ndimi kama za moto zikawatokea  </s></f>"},{ID:5,
