Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Roho Mtakatifu  alivyowajalia kunena,</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>huko Yerusalemu walikaa Wayahudi, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>watu wacha mungu wa kila taifa lililoko ingu.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
