Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hao wote wanaosema si Wagalilaya?</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Kwa namna gani kila mmoja  anaisikia lugha aliyozaliwa nayo? </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Sisi Waparthi, Wamedia,</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Waelami, nasi tukaao Mesopotamia, Yudea, na </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kapadokia, Ponto, na Asia, Firigia na Pamfilia, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Misri na wilaya za Libia kuelekea Kirene, pia </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wageni walioitoka Roma, Wayahudi na waongofu,</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Wakrete na Waarabu, sote lunawasikia wakisema kwa </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>lugha zetu, matendo makuu ya Mungu.' </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ZABURI 
104: 1. 24; 29,30; 31. 34</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Bwana, umtume roho wako na uufanye upya uso wa nchi. </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Umsifu Bwana, ee nafsi Yangu!
Ee Bwana, Mungu wangu u mkuu sana!</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Ee Bwana, jinsi gani zilivyo nyingi kazi zako! dunia imejaa viumbe vyako. K.</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ukiondoa pumzi yao, wanakufa, na kuyarudia mavumbi yao.</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Ukimtuma roho wako wanaumbwa, na unafanya upya uso wa nchi. K</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Utukufu wa Bwana na udumu milele; Bwana na afurahie kazi zake!</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tafakari Yangu na impendeze Mungu; nami nitafurahi katika Bwana. K.</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Utukufu wa Bwana na udumu milele; Bwana na afurahie kazi zake!</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA PILI</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Warumi 8:8-17</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika barua ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Warumi</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndugu zangu: Wote walio wafuasi wa mwili hawawezi kumpendeza
Mungu. </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ninyi, lakini, si wafuasi wa mwili, bali wa Roho, ikiwa</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Roho wa Mungu amekaa kweli ndani yenu. Kama mtu hana Roho</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wa Kristo, basi si mtu wake. Tena Kristo akiwa ndani yenu, miili</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>imekufa kwa sababu ya dhambi, lakini roho ni uzima kwa sababu</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ya uadilifu. Lakini Roho yake yeye aliyemfufua Yesu katika wafu</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akikaa ndani yenu, basi yeye aliyemfufua Kristo Yesu katika wafu</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ataiokoa pia miili yenu katika hali ya kufa na kuitilia uzima kwa</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nguvu ya Roho anayekaa ndani yenu.</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Basi, ndugu, tuna wajibu wetu, lakini si kwa mwili tuishi kama mwili</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>unavyotamani. Maana mkiishi kama mwili unavyotamani, mtakufa.</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bali mkiyafisha mazoea maovu ya mwili kwa nguvu ya Roho,</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mtaishi. Kwani wote wanaoongozwa na Roho wa Mungu ni wana</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wa Mungu. Kwa maana hamkupata roho ya utumwa mwogope tena,</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>bali mmempokea roho anayewafanya kuwa wana wa Mungu na</s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kuita, Abba! Baba!\" Roho mwenyewe hushuhudia roho zetu ya</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kuwa sisi ni watoto wa Mungu. Basi, tukiwa wana, tu warithi pia,</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yaani warithi wa Mungu wanaorithi pamoja na Kristo, tukiwa</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tunavumilia mateso pamoja na Kristo, tupate kutukuzwa pamoja</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>naye.</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana</s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SHANGILIO LA INJILI</s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Aleluya.
W. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:48,
