washa moto wa mapendo ndani yao.</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Aleluya
Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>INJILI     </s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yohane 14:15-16, 23b 26</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Yohane</s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakati ule: Yesu aliwaambia wafuasi wake,</s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Mkinipenda,mtashika amri zangu.</s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nami nitamwomba Baba,
naye atawapa </s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Msaidizi mwingine,
ili awepo kwenu hata milele.</s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mtu akinipenda, atashika neno langu,
na Baba yangu atampenda,</s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nasi tutakuja kwake na kufanya makao kwake.</s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Asiyenipenda hayashiki maneno yangu;</s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na neno mnalolisikia si langu,
bali ni la Baba aliyenituma.</s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hayo nimewaambia nilipokaa kwenu.
Lakini Msaidizi, ndiye Roho Mtakatifu,</s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ambaye Baba atamtuma kwa jina langu,
atawafundisha </s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yote na atawakumbusha
yote niliyowaambia mimi.\"</s></f>"},{ID:64,
