Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Atakuwa kama kichaka mbugani, 
hataona </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>heri hata kidogo; atakaa mahali pa joto, jangwani, katika nchi </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ya chumvi isiyokaliwa na watu. Heri mtu anayemtegemea </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Bwana; aliyeweka matumaini yake katika Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Atakuwa kama mti uliopandwa kando ya maji, uenezao mizizi </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>yake penye mto; wala hauogopi wakati wa hari unapofika,</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nayo majani yake yanazidi kuwa mabichi; wala hauhangaiki </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>katika mwaka wa ukavu, wala hauachi kuzaa matunda.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA
Zaburi 1:1-2, 3, 4 na 6</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>KIITIKIO: Heri mtu aliyemfanya Bwana kuwa tumaini lake.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Heri mtu yule
asiyefuata shauri la waovu,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>asiyesimama katika njia ya wakosefu,wala kukaa </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>katika baraza la wenye mzaha. Bali, furaha yake ni katika sheria </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ya Bwana, na kuitafakari sheria yake mchana na usiku. </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>KIITIKIO: Heri mtu aliyemfanya Bwana kuwa tumaini lake.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Naye ni kama mti uliopandwa kandokando ya vijito vya maji,</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>unaozaa matunda kwa wakati wake; wala jani lake </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>halinyauki; kila wafanyalo linafanikiwa. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>KIITIKIO: Heri mtu aliyemfanya Bwana kuwa tumaini lake.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Sivyo walivyo waovu!
