Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>makapi yapeperushwayo na upepo.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Maana Bwana anatunza njia yao waadilifu,</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>lakini njia ya waovu itapotea. </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>KIITIKIO: Heri mtu aliyemfanya Bwana kuwa tumaini lake.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SOMO LA PILI
1 Wakorintho 15:12, 16-20</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Somo katika barua ya kwanza ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Wakorintho</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ndugu zangu: Kristo akihubiriwa ya kuwa amefufuka kutoka wafu, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mbona baadhi yenu husema kwamba hakuna ufufuko wa wafu?</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Maana kama wafu hawafufuliwi, hata Kristo hakufufuliwa. </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na kama Kristo hakufufuka, imani yenu ni ya bure,</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na mnakaa bado katika dhambi zenu. Hapo hata </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wale waliofariki katika Kristo wamepotea.
Tukimtumaini </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kristo katika maisha haya tu, sisi ni maskini kupita watu wote.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Lakini Kristo amefufuka katika wafu kama </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>malimbuko ya wenye kulala.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SHANGILIO LA INJILI
Luka 6.23ab</s></f>"},{ID:11,
