Furahini na kupiga vigelegele, asema </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Bwana. Tazama, thawabu yenu ni kubwa mbinguni.
Aleluya.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>LUKA 
6:17,20-26</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Somo  la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Luka</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wakati ule Yesu alishuka pamoja na [mitume kumi na wawili],mitume kumi na </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wawili akasimama mahali tambarare pamoja na wafuasi wake wengi,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na umati mkubwa wa watu waliotoka Yudea </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>yote na Yerusalemu, na pwani ya Tiro na Sidoni; </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>walikuja kumsikiliza na kuponywa magonjwa yao. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Akainua macho yake, akawatazama wafuasi wake,</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akasema, Heri ninyi mlio maskini, kwa 
maana ufalme </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wa Mungu ni wenu. Heri ninyi mlio na njaa sasa, kwa maana </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mtashibishwa. Heri ninyi mliao machozi sasa, kwa maana </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mtacheka. Heri ninyi ikiwa watu wanawachukia na kuwatenga,</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na kuwatukana, na kutupa nje jina lenu 
kama neno baya </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kwa ajili ya Mwana wa Mtu. Furahini siku ile na kupiga vigelegele! </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tazama thawabu yenu ni kubwa mbinguni. Ndivyo baba zao </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>walivyowatenda manabii. Lakini ole wenu ninyi matajiri, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kwa maana mmekwisha kupata faraja yenu. Ole wenu </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ninyi mshibao sasa, kwa maana mtaona njaa. Ole wenu ninyi </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mchekao sasa, kwa maana mtasikitika na kulia machozi.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ole wenu, ikiwa watu wote wanawasifu, ndivyo baba zao </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>walivyowatendea manabii wa uongo.\"</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f>"}],
Text:"DOMINIKA YA SITA MWAKA C"},{Guid:"+FhUp4gpbEaBp/VZObHTOg",Verses:[{Style:{Background:{Image:"Bible.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Atũmwo 5:27-32.40-41</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA ATŨMWO:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Matukũ-inĩ macio, mũthĩnjĩri-Ngai ũrĩa mũnene akĩmoria atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Githĩ tũtiramũkaanirie  o kũmũkaania </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mũtikae kũrutana na rĩĩtwa rĩu? </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na rĩu-rĩ, nĩ mũiyũrĩte Jerusalem </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>guothe ũrutani wanyu, mũkenda gũtũma </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>thakame ya mũndũ ũcio itũcokerere arĩ ithuĩ.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nowe Petro me na atũmwo arĩa angĩ 
makĩmacokeria makiuga atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ kwagĩrĩire tũigue Ngai kũrĩ kũigua andũ. </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ngai wa maithe maitũ nĩ ariũkirie Yesu, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o ũcio inyuĩ mworagithirie na kũmũcuurithia mũtĩ igũrũ. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ũcio nĩwe Ngai aatũũgĩririe aikare 
guoko-inĩ gwake </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa ũrĩo atuĩke Mũnene na Mũhonokia,</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> nĩ getha atũme Aisraeli merire na moherũo mehia mao.  </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na ithuĩ-rĩ, nĩ ithuĩ aira a mohoro macio; </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nake Muoyo Mũtheru no mũira, 
o we </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ngai aheete arĩa mamũiguaga. 
Nao magĩĩtĩkania nake, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na maarĩkia gwĩta atũmwo macoke harĩ o, makĩmahũrithia, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>makĩmakaania matikae gũcoka 
kwaria ũhoro o na </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũrĩkũ na rĩĩtwa rĩa Yesu, makĩmarekia mathiĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>magĩkiuma kĩama-inĩ makenete nĩ ũndũ wa ũrĩa </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maatuĩtwo aagĩrĩru a kũmenererio  nĩ ũndũ wa Rĩĩtwa rĩa Yesu.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO </s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>Thaburi 30:1 na 
3; 4-5;10.11a na 12b</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
Nĩ ndĩkũinagĩra Mwathani, tondũ nĩ wahonia </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ ngũgĩkũgooca ngũtũũgĩrie, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wee Mwathani; tondũ nĩ ũngucĩtie na igũrũ, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũgakĩaga kũreka thũ ciakwa ingenerere. </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Ĩ Mwathani, ngoro yakwa nĩ ũmĩrutĩte thĩ o kwa ngoma;</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ ũnjikairie na muoyo, ndige gũtonyerera irima.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
Nĩ ndĩkũinagĩra Mwathani, tondũ nĩ wahonia </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Inĩrai Mwathani mũmũgooce, 
inyuĩ mũrĩ ũiguano nake, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>rĩĩtwa rĩu rĩake rĩamũre mũkĩrĩcokerie ngatho. </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Amu marakara make no ma kahinda kanini,</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ĩndĩ mĩtuganĩre yake nĩ ya gũtũũria  mũndũ muoyo: </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kĩrĩro no gũũka kũraarĩrĩra hwaĩ-inĩ na rũcinĩ gũkaroka ngemi.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
Nĩ ndĩkũinagĩra Mwathani, tondũ nĩ wahonia </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani, igua, ũkĩnginyĩrie  wega waku: </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ĩ Mwathani, itĩkĩra gũtuĩka mũndeithia, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>rĩu nĩ ũngarũranĩirie mũcayo ũcio ndĩrarĩ naguo</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũgatuĩka ndũrũhĩ. Ĩ Mwathani, Ngai wakwa-ĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ngũgĩtũũra ngũcokagĩria ngatho nginya mĩndĩ na mĩndĩ.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA	
Nĩ ndĩkũinagĩra Mwathani, tondũ nĩ wahonia </s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kũguũrĩrio 5:11-14</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA KŨGUŨRĨRIO:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Niĩ John ngĩcoka ngĩrora, 
ngĩigua mũgambo wa araika aingĩ </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mathiũrũrũkĩirie gĩtĩ kĩrĩa gĩa ũthamaki na </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ciũmbe icio ii muoyo o na athuri, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ũrĩa maaiganaga nĩ ngiri ikũmi, 
na ngiri cia ngiri; </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>makoigaga atĩrĩ na mũgambo mũnene,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Gatũrũme karĩa gaathĩnjirũo nĩwe mwagĩrĩru wa kũgwata ũhoti, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na ũtonga, na ũũgĩ, na hinya, 
na gĩtĩo, na riri o na kĩrathimo.  </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na kĩndũ kĩũmbe o gĩothe, kĩrĩa kĩĩ Igũrũ, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kĩrĩa kĩrĩ thĩ, na kĩrĩa kĩrĩ ruungu rũa thĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kĩrĩa kĩrĩ iria rĩrĩa inene igũrũ, 
o na indo ciothe iria irĩ kuo, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ngĩigua ikiuga atĩrĩ: Ũcio ũikarĩire gĩtĩ gĩa ũthamaki, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o nake Gatũrũme, marotũũra na kĩrathimo, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na gĩtĩo, na riri, o na wathani, nginya tene na tene.  </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nacio ciũmbe icio inya ii muoyo ikiuga: 
Amen.  </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nao athuri makĩĩgũithia thĩ magĩthathaiya.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alleluya, Alleluya			   </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kristũ nĩ ariũkĩte We ũrĩa  wombire thĩ </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ahonokirie andũ thĩinĩ wa tha ciake.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alleluya</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>John 21:1-19</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE JOHN: </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hĩndĩ-ĩo Yesu nĩ eonithirie arutwo ake rĩngĩ iria-inĩ rĩa Tiberiade; </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ũrĩa eonithanirie nĩ ũũ: Simone Petro,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> na Thomas ũrĩa wetagwo Didimo, 
na Nathanaeli wa na kũrĩa Kana ya </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Galilea, na ariũ a Zebedei, o na arutwo angĩ ake erĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>andũ acio maarĩ hamwe.  
Nake Simone Petro akĩmera atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Niĩ ndathiĩ gũtega ciũngũyũ.  
Makĩmwĩra: O na ithuĩ nĩ tũgũthiĩ nawe.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Magĩkiumagara magĩtonya marikabu; 
na ũtukũ ũcio matiigana kũgwatia kĩndũ.  </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na rũcinĩ gũgĩkĩa Yesu agĩkorũo arũngiĩ rũtere-inĩ rũa iria;</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nao arutwo matiamenyaga nĩwe Yesu. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake Yesu agĩkĩmoria atĩrĩ: 
ciana, mwĩ na kanyamũ ga kũrĩa? </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Makĩmũcokeria:</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Aca, tũtirĩ.  
Akĩmera: Ikiai rũgara mwena wa ũrĩo wa marikabu na nĩ mũkuona. </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Magĩgĩikia, na hĩndĩ ĩo rũkĩrema kũgucĩka nĩ ũrĩa ciũngũyũ ciingĩhĩte. </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Tondũ ũcio mũrutwo ũrĩa wendetwo nĩ Yesu akĩĩra Petro atĩrĩ: 
Nĩ Mwathani.  </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Simone Petro aakĩigua atĩ nĩ Mwathani, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akĩĩoha nguo yake, tondũ aarĩ ũtheri, akĩrũũga maaĩ-inĩ.  </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nao arutwo arĩa angĩ magĩũka na macua ĩrĩa nyinyi,</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tondũ matiarĩ haraya na rũtere, 
no ta itĩĩna rĩa makinya igana, magĩũka, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>makĩgucagia rũgara rũiyũire ciũngũyũ.  
Maakĩrĩkia kuumĩra rũteere-inĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>makĩona mwaki wa Makara wakĩtio ho, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ciũngũyũ ii njĩkĩre riiko, o na mũgate.  </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake Yesu akĩmera; Rehei ciũngũyũ imwe icio mwanyita.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake Simone Petro agĩkĩhaica  macua akĩgucia </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>rũgara akĩruumĩria rũtere rũiyũire ciũngũyũ iria nene, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>igana rĩa mĩrongo ĩtano na ciũngũyũ ithatũ; </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ningĩ o na harĩa ciarĩ  nyingĩ ũũ, 
rũgara rũtiigana gũtuĩka.  </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake Yesu akĩmera: 
Ũkai mwĩgagũre.  </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nao arutwo gũtirĩ wetire kũmũũria: Nĩwe ũ?,</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> nĩ kũmenya nĩwe Mwathani.  
Nake Yesu agĩthiĩ, akĩoya mũgate, akĩmahe, </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na ciũngũyũ nacio.  
Rĩu nĩrĩo rĩa gatatũ Yesu eonithirie arutwo ake, </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>arĩkĩtie kũriũka akoima  kwĩ arĩa akuũ.  </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ningĩ maakĩrĩkia  kwĩgagũra, 
Yesu akĩũria Simone Petro  atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Simone wa Jona, wee-rĩ, nĩ ũnyendete kũrĩ aya angĩ?</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akĩmwĩra: Ĩĩ-nĩ, Mwathani, 
wee nĩ ũũĩ nĩ ngwendete. </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake akĩmwĩra atĩrĩrĩ: Heaga tũgondu twakwa gĩa kũrĩa.  
Akĩmũũria rĩngĩ hingo ya kerĩ, atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Simone wa Jona, nĩ ũnyendete? 
Akĩmwĩra: Ĩĩ-ni, </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani, wee nĩ ũũĩ nĩ ngwendete.  
Nake akĩmwĩra atĩrĩrĩ:  
Rĩithagia ng’ondu ciakwa. </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Agĩcoka akĩmũũria  hingo ya gatatũ, atĩrĩ:  </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Simone wa Jona, nĩ ũnyendete? 
Nake Petro </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akĩigua ũũru nĩ ũndũ aamũria hingo ya gatatũ: </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ ũnyendete? Agĩkĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Mwathani, </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wee nĩ ũũĩ maũndũ mothe; no ũkuona atĩ nĩ ngwendete.  </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake Yesu akĩmwĩra atĩrĩrĩ: Heaga ng’ondu ciakwa gĩa kũrĩa. </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndakwĩra atĩrĩ, o ma, ma; Rĩrĩa warĩ mũnyinyi, </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ weohaga, ũgetwara o handũ wendaga gũthiĩ; </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>rĩrĩa ũgakũra-rĩ, ũgatambũrũkia moko,</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> mũndũ ũngĩ akuohe, agũtware handũ ũtangĩenda gũthiĩ.  </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na rĩrĩ, oigire ũguo akĩorota  
gũkua kũrĩa ũcio agakua  agoocithie </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ngai nakuo.  
Na aarĩkia kuuga ũguo agĩcoka akĩmwĩra: Nũmĩrĩra.</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s></f>"}],Style:{Background:{Image:"Bible.jpg",Luminosity:-25}},
Text:"KIUMIA GIA ITHATU KIA IRIUKIRO MWAKA C"},{Guid:"OfOIj9SstUSZJyNnlhnrQQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>DOMINIKA YA TATU YA KWARESMA MWAKA C</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SOMO LA KWANZA
Kutoka 3:1-8, 13-15</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Somo katika kitabu cha Kutoka</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Siku zile: Musa alikuwa akichunga kondoo wa Yethro </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mkwewe aliye kuhani wa Midiani; 
aliwapitisha </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>jangwani, akafika 
kwenye mlima wa Mungu, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ndio Horebu. Malaika wa BWANA akamtokea katika </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>sura ya moto uliowaka katikati ya kichaka. </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Musa akatazama: kumbe kile kichaka kinawaka moto Iakini hakiteketei. </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hapo Musa akasema, \"Nitajongea nipate kuona jambo hili la </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ajabu, nione kwa nini kichaka hicho hakiteketei.” BWANA </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akamwona anakaribia apate kutazama vema, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>naye Mungu akamwita kutoka katikati ya kichaka: \"Musa, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Musa!\" Akaitikia,  \"Mimi hapa.\" Hapo BWANA akasema: </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>\"Usikaribie hapa. Vua viatu vyako miguuni mwako, kwa maana </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mahali hapo unaposimama ni nchi takatifu.\" Tena Mungu akasema:</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>\"Mimi ni Mungu wa baba yako, Mungu wa Abrahamu, Mungu wa Isaka, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na Mungu wa Yakobo.\"
Basi Musa akajifunika uso,</s></f>"},{ID:9,
