Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kwa kutikisa chekecheke, huonekana pumba;</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ndivyo ionekanavyo takataka ya mtu katika usemi  wake.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tanuri hujaribu vyombo vya udongo; na kujaribiwa </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kwa mtu ni katika mazungumzo yake.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tunda la mti huonyesha ulimaji wake; hali kadhalika </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>neno hisia ya moyo wa mtu.
Usimsifu mtu kabla hajasema,</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>maana ndivyo anavyo jaribiwa mtu.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA
Zaburi 92:2-3, 13-14, 15-16 </s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kiitikio: Ni vema kukushukuru, ee Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ni vema kumshukuru Bwana, na kuliimbia jina lako,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ewe Uliye juu, ni vema kutangaza wema wako </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>asubuhi, na uaminifu wako nyakati za usiku. </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kiitikio: Ni vema kukushukuru, ee Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwenye haki atastawi kama mtende,
atakua kama </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mwerezi wa Lebanoni. Waliopandwa katika nyumba </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ya Bwana, watastawi katika nyua za Mungu wetu. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kiitikio: Ni vema kukushukuru, ee Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hata katika uzee watazaa matunda,
watakuwa </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na utomvu na ubichi,
ili watangaze, \"Bwana </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ni mwadilifu; Mwamba wangu, asiye na uovu ndani yake.\" </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kiitikio: Ni vema kukushukuru, ee Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SOMO LA PILI
1 Wakorintho 15:54-58</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Somo katika barua ya kwanza ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Wakorintho</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ndugu zangu: Kama hali hii ya kuharibika imevaa hali </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>isiyo haribika, na hali ya kufa imevaa hali ya kuto kufa, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ndipo litakapo timia neno lililo andikwa:
\"Mauti </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>imemezwa na ushindi. Ewe mauti, ukowapi ushindi wako?</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ewe mauti, ukowapi uchungu wako?\"
Lakini </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>uchungu wa mauti ni dhambi, na dhambi imepata </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nguvu katika sheria. 
Basi tumshukuru Mungu aliye tupa </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ushindi kwa nguvu ya Bwana wetu Yesu Kristo.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kwa hiyo, ndugu zangu wapendwa, muwe thabiti na imara.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Endeleeni kufanya kazi ya Bwana siku zote mkijua </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>yakuwa taabu yenu katika Bwana si bure.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SHANGILIO LA INJILI
Wafilipi 2:15d-16a</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Aleluya. Aleluya. Mng'ae kama mianga katika ulimwengu,</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mkilishikilia neno la  uzima. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>INJILI
Luka 6:39-45</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyo andikwa na Luka</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wakati ule: Yesu aliwaambia wafuasi wake[wafuasi wake] mfano,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>\"Je, kipofu aweza kumwongoza kipofu njiani?</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Hawa tatumbukia shimoni wote wawili? Mwanafunzi hampiti </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mwalimu wake; lakini aliye maliza kujifunza, atakuwa sawa na  </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mwalimu wake. Mbona unakiona kibanzi kilichomo jichoni mwa </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ndugu yo, lakini boriti iliyomo jichoni mwako huiangalii?</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wawezaje kumwambia ndugu yako, 'Ndugu, nipe </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nafasi ni ondoe kibanzi katika jicho lako,’ ungali mwenyewe </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>huoni boriti katika jicho lako? Wanafiki ninyi!
Toa boriti </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>iliyo ndani ya jicho lako kwanza; ndipo utafute nafasi </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>yakukitoa kibanzi katika jicho la ndugu yako.
Hakuna mti mzuri </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>uzaao matunda mabaya,
wala mti  mbaya uzaao matunda </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mazuri. Kwa maana kila mti hutambulikana   kwa matunda yake.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Maana katika: miiba hawachumitini,  wala katika </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>michongoma hawachumi zabibu. Mtu mwema hutoa mema  </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>latika hazina njema ya moyo wake, na mtu mwovu hutoa maovu katika </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>hazina mbovu ya moyo wake. Kwa maana kutoka kinywa </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>chake hunena yafurikayo moyoni.”</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f>"}],
