Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>GŪTHOMA INJIRI YA MUTHURE LUKA :</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Hĩndī io arīithi magīthiï mahiűhīte, magīkora Maria na Joseph,</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076> o erī,o na gakenge kau gakometio műharatī- inī. </s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Na maakona, makīheana űhoro wa ciugo iria maarīirio ündű wa kaana kau.</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076> Nao andu othe arīa maaűiguire makīgega nĩ ündű wa maündũ marīa maarīirio nĩ arīithi acio. </s></f>"},{ID:34,
