akamacűranagia na ngoro yake.</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076> Nao arīithi acio makīhũndüka, makīgoocaga Ngai na makīműkumagia </s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>nĩ ūndū wa maūndű marīa metho maaiguire na marīa monire, o ta ürīa merītwo. </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>Na matukũ.manana maahinga ma küruithia kaana kau,</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s3076>gagītwo Yesu
o rīitwa rīrĩa gaatuirűo nĩ müraika o mbere, gatarī karagīwo ihu.</s></f>"},{ID:39,
