Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani witũ Yesu Kristũ! Hakĩrĩ ũguo, ariũ a Baba arĩa nyenda mũno-rĩ,</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ikaragai mwĩrũmĩtie, mũtegũgĩthengeka, na mũtũũre </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>hingo ciothe mũrutaga wĩra wa Mwathani mũgakĩrĩrĩria,</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ ũndũ wa kũmenya atĩ wĩra ũrĩa mwĩnogagia naguo </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ti wa tũhũ mũkĩũrutaga mũnyitaine na Mwathani. </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI
Atumwo 16,14</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>	
Alleluya. Alleluya. Mwathani hingũra ngoro iitũ,</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na tũkamenya mĩgambo ya Mwana waku. Alleluia</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI
Luka 6:39-45</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE LUKA:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hĩndĩ ĩo, Yesu erire arũmĩrĩri ake ngerekano ĩno:</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kaĩ mũndũ mũtumumu angĩkĩhota kuonereria  </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mũndũ ũngĩ mũtumumu njĩra?
Githĩ o erĩ </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>matingĩgũa irima-inĩ?
Mũrutwo ti mũnene kũrĩ mũmũruti:</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>no rĩrĩ, mũndũ o wothe rĩrĩa akaigania, nĩ agatuĩka</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o ta mũmũruti. Na rĩrĩ, nĩ kĩ gĩtũmaga ũrore kĩhuti kĩrĩa kĩĩ riitho rĩa mũrũ </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wa thoguo, na ndũkũũria  mũgogo ũrĩa wĩ riitho rĩaku mwene?</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kana wakĩhota atĩa kwĩra mũrũ wa thoguo atĩrĩ: Mũrũ wa awa, tareke </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ngũrute kĩhuti kĩu kĩĩ riitho rĩaku, 
ũtakĩonete wee mwene mũgogo</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũrĩa wĩ riitho rĩaku mwene? Wee, hinga ĩno, amba ũrute mũgogo</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũrĩa wĩ riitho rĩaku mwene,
na hĩndĩ ĩo nĩ ũkuona</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wega ũrute kĩhuti kĩu kĩĩ ritho rĩa mũrũ wa thoguo. Nĩ gũkorũo gũtirĩ mũtĩ </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mwega ũciaraga maciaro mathũku;
na ningĩ gũtirĩ mũtĩ mũthũku ũciaraga </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>maciaro mega. Tondũ o mũtĩ o mũtĩ ũmenyekaga nĩ ũndũ wa </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>maciaro maguo mwene.  Nĩ ũndũ-rĩ, andũ matituaga ngũyũ ciigua-inĩ,</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o na kana magatua thabibũ mĩtare-inĩ.  Mũndũ ũrĩa mwega arutaga kĩrĩa kĩega </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mũthithũ-inĩ ũrĩa mwega wa ngoro yake;
nake ũrĩa mũũru </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>arutaga kĩrĩa kĩũru 
mũthithũ-inĩ ũrĩa mũũru: nĩ gũkorũo kanua </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>gake kaaragia o maũndũ marĩa maiyũire ngoro. </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s></f>"}],
Text:"KIUMIA KIA INYANYA MWAKA C"},{Guid:"nrtpzjaXbUi/XOjTRftugA",Verses:[{
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>KIUMIA GİA IKÜMI NA KENDA KÍA MWAKA C</k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>GiTHOMO KIA MBERE
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846>Uugi (Wisdom) 
18: 3, 6 - 9.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GUTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RIA UŪGI :</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Waruta kirindī gīaku ükombo-inī 
nĩ wakīheire kīmūrī gīakanu kīa mwaki </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gīa kūmatongoria rūgendoinī 
rüao rüra matamenyete.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kimūrī kīu kīhiana riūa rīega 
rīakūmamürīkīra </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>thĩinī wa thama 
iyo ya kügegearithia. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Otukū ūcio nĩ ürīa 
werīirūo maithe maitű </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ getha maikarage 
makīwiriragiria </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mena mwīhoko 
thĩinĩ wa ci</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>ranīro irīĩa merīirūo. </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kīrīndī gīaku gīetagīrīra ühonokia nī ündü 
wa andü a </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mītugo mīega na küninwo gwa th</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>ũ ciakīo. </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na ta ürīa wahotithirie thũ ũguo </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ ütükumithtie ügītwīta hari  we. </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciana cia arīa a mītugo mĩega 
nĩ ciarutaga magongona </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na hitho na iKirikanira 
na ngoro </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>îmwe kühingia rīathana rīrī rīa Ongai: </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>atī aria a mītugo mīega nĩmakagayana 
ündü ümwe mawega na mogwati </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>makiinaga mbere nyīmbo 
cia ngatho cia maithe mao.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nīcio ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>THABURI YA GŪCOKERUO
</k></c></s></f></u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>Thaburi 33: 1,12; 18-19; 20,22.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>ICOKIA: Gükena, nĩ rüri rüria Mwathani ari We Ngai waruo.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>1.Inyui athingu, kūngūiyai nī ündū mwĩ na Mwathani;</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>andū aria arūngiriru nio maagiriirūoni kūmakumia.</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Gükena, nĩ rūrīrī rūria Mwathani arī we Ngai waruo,</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o kīo kirindi kirīa ethurīire gīgatuīka igai rīake</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>ICOKIA: Gükena, nĩ rüri rüria Mwathani ari We Ngai waruo.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>2. Atiririi, rütho rīa Mwathani rierekeire harī ariā amwitigiri, </s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>rīgakīerekera hari andũ arīa merigagirira o ütugi wake; </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>niguo ateithūrage mioyo yao gikuū-ini, 
gwata hingo ya ng’araga maikaragie na muoyo.</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>I</k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>COKIA: Gükena, nĩ rüri rüria Mwathani ari We Ngai waruo.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>2.Mĩoyo iitū-ri, īkirirīirie yetereire o Mwathani:</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>we nowe ūteithio witū o na ngo itū, Ütugi waku, </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani, tũma ūikarage na ithuĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>k</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>ringana o na ūrīa ttūtűire tūkwirīgirīire.</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>ICOKIA: Gükena, nĩ rüri rüria Mwathani ari We Ngai waruo.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>GITHOMO KIA IGIRI</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846> 
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>Aheberea 
11: 1 - 2. 8- 19</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GUTHOMA 
MARUA MARIA MAANDĪKĪIRUO KŪRI ANDU A HEBEREA :</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ariŭ a lthe witū, wītikia nīguo ümenyithanagia </s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>atī maűndū marīa 
merīgīrīirūo nĩ ma ma, </s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na nīguo wĩ kīhooto gīa kūmenyithania </s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>atī maūndű marĩa matonekaga marī ho. </s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Amu-rī, nĩ ündũ waguo athuri arīa 
a tene n</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> maagīire na ngumo njega.</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ ũndū wa gwītikia, Abraham, 
rīrīa etirűo, agīītika, </s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akiuma kwao athiï kũndű kürīa 
akaheo thutha gūtuike igai rīake; </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agīkiuma küu atoï kürĩa egüthii, 
Nĩ ündũ wa witīkia agīikara būrűüri ürīa</s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>weranīirűo e műgeni, ta arĩ mūthamīri kuo,
agatüüraga </s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mahema-inī me hamwe na Isaaka na Jakobu, </s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o arīa maarī a kūgaīrűo hamwe nake kiiranīro o ro kīu. </s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tondű n</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> aatanyīite kuona itūüra rīrīa rīakītwo gītina kīrümu, </s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o rīo mwaki warīĩo na mūthondeki nîi Ngai, 
Ni ündű wa wītikia, </s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o nake Sara akīheo hinya wa kwīgwatīra </s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ihu rīrīa hĩndĩ yake ya gūciara yathirīte, </s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ gūkorūo nĩ aatuīte ati Üria wamwīrīire 
üguo nĩ wa kwīhokwo, na tondū wa üguo, </s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>güīciarūo nĩ mūndū ūmwe, 
nake no ta arī műndũ műkuũ, </s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>andũ maingīhīte O ta njata cia igür</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>ũ, 
o na ta </s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mūthanga ūrīa ütangītarīka wĩ hügūrūrű-inī cia iria.</s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>( Icio nĩcio ciugo cia Mwathani ).</s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Short Form: 
</k></c></s></f></u><fArial Black><s1846>11: 1-2, 8-12</s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Andū acio othe-rĩ, 
maakuire marűmītie ühoro ücio wa gwitīkia, </s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na matarī maahingīrio ciîranīro; 
Indī nĩ </s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maacionaga irī küraya magaciküngüira, </s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>makiumbūraga atī no ageni na agendi gūkū
thi, </s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na rĩrī, andũ arīa maaragiå maündŭ </s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ta macio nī monanagia wega atī nĩ gūcaria maracaria
bürüri üngītuika wao ene. </s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na mangiatüire maririkanaga 
bürüri ūrīa moimīte mawirirīrie-rī, </s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ mangīonire hīndī ya gücoka kuo.
Indī rĩu, </s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>üra meriragīria kuona nĩ bürüri mwega kürī ücio, </s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>naguo nĩ bürüri wa lgürü, 
na nikīo Ngai atangīconoka nĩ gwītwo Ngai wao, </s></f>"},{ID:70,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ ündū nĩ amathonde
keire itūüra. Nĩ ündű wa gwitikia, </s></f>"},{ID:71,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Abraham, aagerio, nĩ aarutire 
Isaka atuiīke wa igongona; </s></f>"},{ID:72,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ücio waamükīrīite ciīranīro icio-ī, 
agīgīkorűo akīruta </s></f>"},{ID:73,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o mwana wake wa mūmwe atuîke wa igongona;</s></f>"},{ID:74,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o we werītwo ühoro wake atī, 
thiinī wa Isaka nĩ ho mbeü irī irña îrītanagio nawe, </s></f>"},{ID:75,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake nigütua
aatuīte na ngoro atī Ngai aahota küriükia műndü, </s></f>"},{ID:76,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na arī mükuű; naguo ühoro ücio ükigerekanio, </s></f>"},{ID:77,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ gūcokerio aacokeirio mūriű ta oimīte kürī arīa akuü.</s></f>"},{ID:78,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nīcio ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:79,
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>GĪTHOMO KĪA INJIRI
</k></c></s></f></u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>Luka l2: 32 - 48</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:80,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŪTHOMA INJIRI YA MŪTHURE LUKA :</s></f>"},{ID:81,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>No rirī, caragiai ūthamaki wa Ngai, 
nacio indo icio nĩ mūgakīrīrīrio. </s></f>"},{ID:82,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Inyuī a karūüru gaka kanini,tigagai gwītigira, </s></f>"},{ID:83,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ gükorūo Ithe wanyu nĩ eyendeire kūmūhe ūthamaki ücio. </s></f>"},{ID:84,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Endiai indo iria mūrī 
nacio, mūcoke 
mūciheanage na tha; </s></f>"},{ID:85,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mwītumĩre tūmondo twa mbia tūrīa tütaküraga, </s></f>"},{ID:86,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ getha műkagīa na ūtonga ürīa ütathiraga o lgürű, </s></f>"},{ID:87,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kürīa gūtarī mūici ūthengagīrīra, 
o na kürīa memenyi itaninaga indo. </s></f>"},{ID:88,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ gūkorūo o kūrīa ütonga wanyu ürī,
nīkuo ngoro cianyu nacio ikoragwo irī.</s></f>"},{ID:89,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ikaragai mwīhotorete, na 
mūrī na matawa 
manyu magīakanaga; </s></f>"},{ID:90,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na inyuī ene mūtuñke ta andũ
metereire mwathani wao, </s></f>"},{ID:91,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agīcoka oimīte iruga-inī rĩa kīhikanio; 
nĩ getha, </s></f>"},{ID:92,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>rīrīa agakinya aringaringe mūrango, </s></f>"},{ID:93,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mamūhingūrīre o rīmwe. Gükena-rī, 
nĩ ndungata </s></f>"},{ID:94,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>iria igakorüo ciīiguīte rīrīa mwathani
wacio agakinya: </s></f>"},{ID:95,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ngümwīra na ma atī nĩ-akehotora 
aciikarie metha-inī irie, </s></f>"},{ID:96,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nake oke acirehere irio. 
Nake angīkinya ta ūtukű gatagatī, </s></f>"},{ID:97,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kana ta thaa kenda, acikore ciiguīte 
üguo, gükena -rī, nĩ ndungata icio, </s></f>"},{ID:98,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>No rĩrī, menyai üű, 
atī korűo mwene nyūmba nĩ </s></f>"},{ID:99,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>aamenyaga thaa îrīa müici egūüka,
nĩ angīakorirūo eiguīte, </s></f>"},{ID:100,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ndareke nyūmba yake yenjwo. </s></f>"},{ID:101,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>O na inyuī ikaragai mwihaaririe: 
Nĩgükotwo Mūrű wa mūndū nĩ agoka o thaa irīa mūtegereirie.</s></f>"},{ID:102,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>( Injiri thetu ya Mwathani ).</s></f>"},{ID:103,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>Short form 12: 35- 40,</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:104,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>[ Nake Petro akīműüria atīrīĩ: 
Mwathani, </s></f>"},{ID:105,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ ithuĩ wera ngerekano io,
kana nĩ andű othe? </s></f>"},{ID:106,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake Mwathani akīmūűria atīrī: 
Rĩurī, </s></f>"},{ID:107,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mürori indo ürĩa ūngī îhokeka na műügí-rī, </s></f>"},{ID:108,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o ürĩa ügatuwo hĩ mwathani wake 
wa kūramataga </s></f>"},{ID:109,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nyūmba yake yothe, 
na aheage andű irio </s></f>"},{ID:110,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ciao o hĩndī yakinya, nĩ ürikū? </s></f>"},{ID:111,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Gükena-rī, nĩ ndungata io, 
ingīkorūo </s></f>"},{ID:112,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>igiīka ūguo mwathani wao aakinya. </s></f>"},{ID:113,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ti-itherű ngũmwīra atīrī: 
atī nĩ </s></f>"},{ID:114,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akamītua ya kūramataga indo ciake ciothe. </s></f>"},{ID:115,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>indī ndungata io ingīkorūo îirītena ngoro atīrī: </s></f>"},{ID:116,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani wakwa ndehiüha gūűka; </s></f>"},{ID:117,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na titīke kūhűra ndungata 
iria cia arűme na cia andü-a-nja, </s></f>"},{ID:118,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kūrīa na künyua, 
na kūrīwo-rī, </s></f>"},{ID:119,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mwathani wandungata ĩo nĩ 
agakinya mūthenya ürīa itegereirie, </s></f>"},{ID:120,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na thaa īrīa 
itoï, na amihüre mūno, </s></f>"},{ID:121,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na amītuīre cira o ta ürīa gütuagīrűo arīa matehokekete. </s></f>"},{ID:122,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nayo ndungata irĩa 
yamenyete ürīa mwathani wayo endaga, </s></f>"},{ID:123,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ndigana kwīhaarīria, 
kana gwiīka ürĩa endaga-rī, nĩ 
ikah</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>ürūo mĩtunda miingī. </s></f>"},{ID:124,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>No irĩa itaa menyete-rī, 
na īginka maundü </s></f>"},{ID:125,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ma gūtüma ihūrűo, 
io nĩ  ikahürūo mītunda itarī miingī. </s></f>"},{ID:126,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na rīrī, mūndū ürīa üheetwo indo nyingī,
 nīwe ügetio nyingī; </s></f>"},{ID:127,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ürĩa ühithītio indo nyingĩ nĩ andū,
nīwe ügacoka gwītio nyingī makīria.</s></f>"},{ID:128,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>( Injiri thetu ya Mwathani </s></f>"}],
Text:"KIUMIA GİA IKÜMI NA KENDA KÍA MWAKA C
"},{Guid:"WF9PEJ8Ark6pW9d1lijqSw",Verses:[{
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>DOMINIKA YA ISHIRINI 
MWAKA C</k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:2,Style:{Background:{Luminosity:-50}},
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>SOMO LA KWANZA
</k></c></s></f></u><fArial Black><s1846>Yeremia 
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF0000><kFFF2F200>38:4 6, 8-10</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika kitabu cha Nabii Yeremia</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Siku zile:
Wakubwa walimwambia mfalme,</s></f>"},{ID:5,Style:{Background:{Transition:16}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yeremia auawe.
Maana kwa maneno yake</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>anavunja mioyo ya askari waliobaki mjini,</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na wa watu wote pia kwa kuyasema hayo;</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwani mtu huyu hawatafutií watu haa wokovu,</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>bali upotevu wao.”
Mfalme Zedekia akajibu,</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>“Vema, yumo mikonowni mwenu,” </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maana mfalme hangewazuia.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Basi wakamkamata Yeremia,
wakamtupa </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>katika kisima cha mwana wa mfalme Malkiya,</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kilicho katika boma la walinzi,
wakamshusha </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yeremia kwa msaada wa kamba.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na mle kisimani hamkuwa na maji, ila matope tu,</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>naye Yeremia akazama katika matope.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ebedmeleki akaenda katika jumba la mfalme,
akamwambia mfalme,</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>“Ee bwana wangu, mfalme,
watu hawa wamefanya vibaya</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>katika mambo yote waliyomtendea Yeremia nabi.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wamemtupa katika kisima ambamo atakufa kwa njaa akiwa ndani,</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa kuwa hakuna tena mkate mjini.”</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndipo mfalme akamwamuru Ebedmeleki, Mkushi:</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>“Chukua watu watatu pamoja nawe kutoka hapa,</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ukamtoe Yeremia nabii kutoka kisimani kabla hajafa.”</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA
</k></c></s></f></u><fArial Black><s1846>Zaburi 
</s></f><fArial Black><s1384><cFFFF0000><kFFF2F200>40:2, 3.4. 18 (K. 14b)</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>K.</k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Ee Bwana, fanya haraka kunisaidia!</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>1.Nalimngojea Bwana kwa subira;
akanielekea na kukisikia kilio changu. K.</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K.</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Ee Bwana, fanya haraka kunisaidia!</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>2.Akaniopoa katika shimo la upotevu,
katika matope ya kisima kirefu,</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akasimamisha miguu yangu juu ya mwamba,
akaimarisha hatua zangu. K.</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K.</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Ee Bwana, fanya haraka kunisaidia!</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>3.Akaweka wimbo mpya kinywani mwangu,
sifa za Mungu wetu.</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wengi wataona na kushikwa na woga,
watamwamini Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K.</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Ee Bwana, fanya haraka kunisaidia!</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nami ni maskini na mhitaji,
unikumbuke, ee Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndiwe msaada wangu na mwokozi wangu; ee Mungu, wangu, usikawie. K.</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>K.</k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Ee Bwana, fanya haraka kunisaidia!</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>SOMO LA PILI
</k></c></s></f></u><fArial Black><s1846>Waebrania 
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF0000><kFFF2F200>12:1-4</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika barua kwa Waebrania</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndugu zangu: 
Sisi tumezungukwa 
na wingu la mashahidi.</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa hiyo tuondoe yote yanayotutatíza, 
hasa dhambi inayoshikamana nasi.</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tupige mbio kwa uthabiti katika 
mashindano yaliyowekwa mbele yetu. </s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tumkazie macho Yesu, maana ni yeye </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>aliyeanzisha
imani yetu, naye ataikamilisha. </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa ajili ya furaha ya baadaye,</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>aliustahimili msalaba, 
asiiangalie aibu yake, </s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>naye amekaa kulia kwa
kiti cha enzi cha Mungu.</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Haya, kumbukeni jinsi alivyovumilia mapingamizi makubwa
kutoka kwa wakosefu, </s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ili msichoke na kukata tamaa mioyoni
mwenu.</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> 
Katika kupigana na dhambi ninyi hamjapigana mpaka
kiasi cha kumwaga damu yenu.</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>SHANGILIO LA INJILI
</k></c></s></f></u><fArial Black><s1846>Yohane 
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF0000><kFFF2F200>10:27</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Aleluya.
Kondoo wangu huisikia sauti yangu,
asema Bwana;</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nami nawajua, nao wanifuata.
W. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>INJILI
</k></c></s></f></u><fArial Black><s1846>Luka 
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF0000><kFFF2F200>12:49-53</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Luka</s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakati ule:
Yesu aliwaambia wafuasi wake, </s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>“Nimekuja kuleta moto duniani
tena </s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>natamani sana uanze kuwaka! 
Kuna ubatizo nitakaobatizwa</s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ninasongwa kama nini hata utimizwe!</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Watagawanyika baba dhidi ya mwanawe,</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Je, mwadhani nimekuja kuleta amani duniani?</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nawaambieni Sivyo, bali mgawanyiko. 
Kwa maana, </s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>toka sasa wakazi watano wa nyumba moja watagawanyika, </s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>watatu dhidi ya wawili, wawili dhidi 
ya watatu.</s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Watagawanyika baba dhidhi ya 
mwanawe na mwana dhidi ya babaye,</s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mama dhidi ya binti yake, na binti dhidi ya mamaye,</s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mkwe mtu dhidi ya mkwewe, mkwewe dhidi ya mkwe mtu.”</s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Bwana. </s></f>"}],Style:{Background:{Transition:6,Duration:976}},
Text:"DOMINIKA YA ISHIRINI MWAKA C
"},{Guid:"+jCmgcNC+kObIvmxdCUQ4Q",Verses:[{
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>KIUMIA KĨA MÍRONGO IRI KIA MWAKA C</k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:2,Style:{Background:{BodyRect:"0,0,10000,9300"}},
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>GITHOMO KIA MBERE
</k></c></s></f></u><fArial Black><s1846>Jeremia 
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>38:4-6.8-10.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GUTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RIA KIRORI JEREMIA :</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mīthenya-inī io, anene magīkiira müthamaki atīrī: </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Twagüthaitha ūreke mūndū ūyūoragwo, kuona atī </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>no küguoyohia araguoyohia andü a ita arīa matigarīte itüüra-inī rīiri,</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> hamwe na 
andū arīa
angī othe, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ ündü wa üria amaaragīria mohoro ta macio; </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ ündū mūndū </s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>yũ ndegūcarīria andū aya wega tiga o üūru. </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake Zedekia műthamaki akiuga ūű: To we ücio. </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>E moko-inī manyu,
amu mūthamaki ndangīīka ündū mūtekwenda. </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hīndī io makīnyita Jeremia, 
makīmūikia irima-inī</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>rīenjetwo rīa maaī ria Malikia mürü wa müthamaki, </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kūu kīhingo-inī kia arangīri; magīikürükia
Jeremia irima-inī rīu na mīhĩndo. </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nakuo kūu irima-inī gūtiarī maai, tiga o mūtondo mūtheri; </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nake Jeremia agīgītonyerera műtondo-inī ücio. </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ebed-Meleku ücio akiumagara akiuma kūu nyūmba ya mūthamaki, </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agīthiī akīaria na müthamaki, akīmwīra atīri: </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathi wakwa müthamaki witū, andü
acio mihetie nī ūndũ </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wa maūndü maya mothe mekīte Jeremia münabii, </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o ücio maikītie irima; nake hihi ti-itherű nī egükuīra handű hau arī nĩ ündü wa ng’aragu: </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ ündü gükū itüüra-inī riri
gütiri irio riu. </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hindī io müthamaki agīatha Ebed-Meleku, ücio wari Mükushi, </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akimwīra atīrí:
Oya andūmĩrongo îtatū műkarute </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Jeremia ücio münabiii kūu irima riu atanakua.</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nĩcio ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>THABURI YA GUCOKERŪO
</k></c></s></f></u><fArial Black><s1846>Thaburi 
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>40:1;2;3;17.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA: </s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Mwathani hiűha gükīndeithia.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>1.weterera ndetereire Mwathani o ngiriririe, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nake agikīi’hūgürira akīnjerekera, agitīkīra kūigua kiriro giakwa,</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA: </s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Mwathani hiűha gükīndeithia.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>2.Akinduta thiini wa irima riuru riĩ mūūro, o thinī wa itomboya. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kūu mũtoro-inī, agīkinyithia
magūrū </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>makwa ihiga igūrū, 
mikinyīre yakwa agikimirūmia,</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>ICOKIA: </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Mwathani hiűha gükīndeithia.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>3.Agigiikira kanua gakwa ruimbo rueru uguo, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o rūa īgooci, ngoocage Ngai witū naruo: </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>and</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> aingi magetigīra, magwate kwihoka Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA: </s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Mwathani hiűha gükīndeithia.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>4.Na nii ndi mūndu mūthiniki, mũndū mwagi; </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>no Mwathani ni andirikanaga; wee nīwe ūteithio</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wakwa o na nowe mu’hatūri: wee Ngai wakwa-ī, ndūgakīgonderere,</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>ICOKIA: </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Mwathani hiűha gükīndeithia.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>GITHOMO KIA IGĪRI
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846>Aheberea 
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F>12:1-4,</c></s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GUTHOMA 
MARUA MARIA MAANDiKiIRŪO 
KŪRĪ ANDU A HEBEREA</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ariü a Ithe witū, hakīrī üguo-rī, 
kuona atī nĩ tüthiürürüktirio nĩ aira aingī üü, </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mahaana ta itu
rīnene, o na ithuī nĩ twīaüre kīrīa gīothe gītūritühīire, </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na wihia üria ütürigicaga mūüno, tügīteng’ere </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kīhītahītano-ini kīrīa tūigiirūo mbere iitü tūkirīriirie, </s></f>"},{ID:19,Style:{Background:{BodyRect:"0,0,10000,9300"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o tūcüthīriirie Yesu, ürīa wĩ mwambirīria </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na mühingia wa wītikio ürīa twitikītie. </s></f>"},{ID:21,Style:{Background:{BodyRect:"0,0,10000,9300"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>We-rī, nĩ ündū wa gīkeno kiria aigīirüo mbere yake,</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ akirīrīirie ühoro wa kwambwo mūtharaba-inī, </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>atekūüria güconorūo, na rĩu nĩ aikaire thĩ mwena </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wa ürĩo wa gīti-gīa-ūthamaki kīrīa kĩa Ngai. </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Rīu-rī, nĩ getha mūtikae künoga kana kūürűo nĩ hinya ngoro-inī, </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>cüraniai ühoro wa ücio wakirīriirie ngarari nyingi uu cia ehia magīkararania nake. </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Inyui- rī, mütiri műrarűa o nginya mükoira thakame mükigianaga na mehia.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nicio ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>RUIMBO RÚA INJIRI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>Atūmwo 16, 14.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alleluya, Alleluya. </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani, hingüra ngoro ciitü nīguo
tűhote </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>küigua mīgambo ya Mwana waku.
Alleluya</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<b><u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>GiTHOMO KĪA INJIRI
</k></c></s></f></u></b><fArial Black><s1846>Luka </s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F>(12:49-57.)</c></s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŪTHOMA INJIRI YA MŪTHURE LUKA :</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hindi io, Yesu nĩ erire arümiriiri ake: Njükīte güikia mwaki thĩ; </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ngūcoka kwenda kī, üngīkorūo nĩ ürikītie gwakio? </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>No rirī, ndii na übatithio ndimbatithio naguo; </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kühinyīrīrio ndiühinya
girīrio atĩa ügigakinya. </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Anga műkwīgereria atī njükīte kūrehe thayū gükü thi? </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ngümwira atīri:
Tiguo, no makīria nĩ nduikano: </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tondü kuuma rīu, nĩ kürīkoragwo andü atano a nyümba imwe matuīkanīte: </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>atatū magakararia erī, nao erĩ makararie atatü. </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nao magakorūo matuikanīte ūu :
műthuri na műriũ, o na mūriŭ na ithe; </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ningri mütumia na mwarī, o na müirītu na nyina; </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ningi nyaciara na műtumia wa mũriű, ningī mütumia wa műriű na nyaciarawe.</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake akira andű a kirīndī nao atirui: </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Riria muonaga itu rikīambata, riumiīte na kürīa ithüiro,</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hĩndī io muugaga atirī: Nĩ gükügīa mbura; na gűgatuîka üguo.</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na rīrīa muonaga rũhuho rūkīhurutana ruumīte o kūria gūthini, muugaga atīrī: </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ gūkūgia üru.
garī mūnene; na gūgatuīka üguo. 
Inyuī hinga ici. </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ mū</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>i gūküürana ürīa kürīhaana gūkū thi.</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na matu-inī; no rīrī, nĩ kĩ gītümaga mwage gũ kűürana ühoro wa ihinda rīrī? </s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na mwagaga inyuï ene gwītuīra ūhoro ūrīa wagīriire nĩ ündū kĩ ?</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nĩcio ciugo cia Mwathani,</s></f>"}],
Text:"KIUMIA KĨA MÍRONGO IRI KIA MWAKA C
"},{Guid:"m17N4pDnWE2bNSlP5W7WCQ",Verses:[{Style:{Body:{FontStyle:{Fill:{Color:"FFFFFF00"},Stroke:{Color:"FF225BA1"},ShadowColor:"FF8C8C8C",ShadowRadius:33,ShadowDirection:-45,ShadowDepth:21}}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846></s></f><u><fArial Black><s1846>DOMINIKA YA KUMI NA TANO MWAKA C</s></f></u>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA KWANZA</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kumbukumbu la Torati 30:10</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika kitabu cha Kumbukumbu la Torati</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Musa alinena na watu akawaambia: </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"itini sauti ya Bwana
mungu wenu, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kushika amri zake na maagizo yake, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yaliyoandikwa
moyo wenu wote na kwa roho yenu yote.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa maana amri hii ninayokuamuru leo haipiti nguvu zako
usiiweze. </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Haiko angani hata useme, 'Nani atakayepanda kwa ajili</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>vetu huko angani akatuletee tupate kusikia na kuitenda? </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hiko mbali ng'ambo ya bahari hata useme, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>'Nani atakaye kwenda huko ng'ambo ya bahari akatutafutie tupate kuisikia 
na kuitenda?</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa kuwa neno lipo karibu nawe, lipo kinywani mwako, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>lipo kinywani 
mwako kusudi ulitimize kwa matendo.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:17,Style:{Body:{FontStyle:{Fill:{Color:"FFF2F200"},Stroke:{Color:"FFFFD700"}}}},
Text:"<b><u><fArial Black><s2769>ZABURI YA 
KUITIKIZANA</s></f></u></b>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Zaburi 
69:14 na 17.30-37</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Enyi wanyonge, mtafuteni Mungu,
na mioyo yetu itahuishwa.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Sala yangu inakuelekea, ee Bwana,
wakati wa neema yako.</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ee Mungu, unisikilize kwa wema wako mkubwa,</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa uaminifu wako wenye kuniokoa.</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ee Bwana, unisikilize, maana fadhili zako ni bora;</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa wingi wa rehema zako uniangalie. </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Enyi wanyonge, mtafuteni Mungu,
na mioyo yetu itahuishwa.</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nami, niliye mnyonge na mgonjwa;</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ee Mungu, wokovu wako unilinde,</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nitalisifu jina la Mungu kwa wimbo,</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nitamtukuza kwa kumtolea shukrani.</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Enyi wanyonge, mtafuteni Mungu,
na mioyo yetu itahuishwa.</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Enyi Wanyonge, lazarmeni, furahini:</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Enyi mtafutao mungu mioyo yenu ihuishwe!</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mwana wa Bwana huwasikia wahitaii.</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wala hawadharau wafungwa wake.</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Enyi wanyonge, mtafuteni Mungu,
na mioyo yetu itahuishwa.</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Maana Mungu atasalimisha Sioni.
ataijenga upya miji ya Yuda.</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na wazao wa watumishi wake watairithi:</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na wenye kulipenda jina lake watakaa humo.</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Enyi wanyonge, mtafuteni Mungu,
na mioyo yetu itahuishwa.</s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>(AU)</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<i><fArial Black><s1846>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA</s></f></i>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Zaburi 
19 k 9. 10.11 K. a</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Amri za Bwana ni za haki
zafurahisha moyo.</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Sheria ya Bwana ni kamilifu, yautuliza moyo.</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Maagizo ya Bwana ni imara,
yamletea mjinga hekima.</s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Amri za Bwana ni za haki
zafurahisha moyo</s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Maagizo ya Bwanani ya haki, yaufurahisha moyo,</s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agizo la Bwana ni safi.
layatia macho mwangaza.</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Amri za Bwana ni za haki
zafurahisha moyo</s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Uchaji wa Bwana ni safi, hudumu hata milele.</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hukumu za Bwana ni kweli,
zote ni za haki kamili. </s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Amri za Bwana ni za haki
zafurahisha moyo</s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA PILI</s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakolosai 
1:15-20</s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika barua ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Wakolosai</s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kristo Yesu ndiye mfano wa Mungu asiyeonekana, 
mzaliwa wakwanza wa viumbe vyote.</s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa maana katika yeye vitu vyote vimeumbwa vilivyomo </s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mbinguni na duniani, vionekanavyo na visivyoonekana. </s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wenye enzi wenye utawala wenye ukuu na wenye mamlaka </s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>vyote vimeumbwa kwa nguvu yake yeye na kwa ajili yake. </s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Naye alikuwako kabla Yeye mwenyewe ni kichwa cha mwili, 
yaani Kanisa. </s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yeye ni mwanzo, ní mzaliwa wa kwanza katika wafu ili awe, 
wa kwanza katika yote. </s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa maana Mungu alipenda utimilifu wote ukae ndani yake </s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na kwa ajili yake amepatanisha naye vyote 
vilivyoko duniani na mbinguni, </s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwani ameleta amani kwa damu ya msalaba wake </s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SHANGILIO LA INJILI
Yohane 6.63c, 6</s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Maneno yako, ee Bwana,
ni roho, pia ni uzima;</s></f>"},{ID:70,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wewe unayo maneno ya uzima wa milele.</s></f>"},{ID:71,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>W. Aleluya.
W. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:72,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>INJILI
Luka 10:25-37</s></f>"},{ID:73,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Luka</s></f>"},{ID:74,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakati ule:
Mwanasheria mmoja alisimama amjaribu Yesu, akasema,</s></f>"},{ID:75,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Mwalimu, nifanye nini nipate kuurithi uzima wa milele?\"</s></f>"},{ID:76,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu akamwambia, \"Imeandikwa nini katika Sheria? Wasomaje?\"</s></f>"},{ID:77,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Umpende Bwana, Mungu wako, kwa moyo wako wote, </s></f>"},{ID:78,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kwa roho yako yote, na kwa nguvu zako zote, na kwa akili zako zote,</s></f>"},{ID:79,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na jirani yako kama unavyojipenda mwenyewe.</s></f>"},{ID:80,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akamwambia, \"Umejibu sawasawa: fanva hivyo na utaishi.</s></f>"},{ID:81,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yeye lakini akitaka kujidai haki, akamwuliza Yesu,
\"Na jirani yanguni nani?\"</s></f>"},{ID:82,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu akajibu akisema, \"Mtu mmoja alishuka toka Yerusalemu</s></f>"},{ID:83,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwenda Yeriko akakutana na wanyang'anyi. Nao wakamvua nguo,</s></f>"},{ID:84,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kamtia majeraha, wakaenda zao wakimwacha karibu ya kufa.</s></f>"},{ID:85,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa bahati kuhani alishuka kwa njia ile, alipomwona, alipitia
kando.</s></f>"},{ID:86,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kadhalika Mlawi alifika mahali pale, alipomwona, akapitia kando.</s></f>"},{ID:87,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>lakini Msamaria mmoja alikuwa akisafiri, na alipofika mahali
pale. </s></f>"},{ID:88,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akamwona, akashikwa na huruma. Akamkaribia, akamfunga</s></f>"},{ID:89,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>majeraha yake, akayatia mafuta na divai. </s></f>"},{ID:90,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kisha akamweka juu ya mnyama wake </s></f>"},{ID:91,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akampeleka katika nyumba ya wageni, akamwuguza.</s></f>"},{ID:92,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Siku ya pili akatoa dinari mbili, akampa mwenye 
nyumba, akisema,mtunze, </s></f>"},{ID:93,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na yote utakayotumia zaidi nitakulipa nitakaporudi.</s></f>"},{ID:94,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Waonaje? Katika hao watatu ni nani aliyekuwa </s></f>"},{ID:95,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>jirani wa yule
aliyeshambuliwa na wanyang'anyi?\" </s></f>"},{ID:96,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akajibu,
\"Ndiye aliyemfanyia huruma.\"</s></f>"},{ID:97,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu akanwambia, \"Nenda, kafanye vivyo hivyo.\"</s></f>"},{ID:98,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f>"}],
Text:"DOMINIKA KA KUMI NA TANO YA MWAKA C"},{Guid:"b7dzeOw0CECfCTt2L+WNOA",Verses:[{Style:{Body:{FontStyle:{Fill:{Color:"FFF2F200"},Stroke:{Color:"00FFFFFF"},ShadowColor:"FF00FF00",ShadowRadius:42}}},
Text:"<i><u><fArial Black><s1384><kFFFFFFFF>KIUMIA GIA IKUMI NA ITHANO KIA MWAKA C</k></s></f></u></i>"},{ID:2,Style:{Body:{FontStyle:{Fill:{Color:"FFF2F200"},Stroke:{Color:"00FFFFFF"},ShadowColor:"FF00FF00",ShadowRadius:42}}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GiTHOMO KIA MBERE</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Gucokerithia Maathani 
30: 10 - 14.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GÜTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RIA GUCOKERITHIA MAATHANI :</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<kFFFFFFFF></k><fArial Black><s1846>Musa agīgīita kirīndī na akīmera atīrī: </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>üngīkorūo nĩ ürīathīkagīra uuge wa Mwathani Ngai waku,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ümenyagīrīre maathani make, na irīra cia watho wake wa </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kürümīrīrüo iria ciandīkītwo ibuku-inī rīri rīa watho; </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na ükorūo nĩ ükühūgūkīra Mwathani </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ngoro yaku yothe, o na muoyo waku wothe. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tondü-rī, rīathani rīī ngügwatha ümüthĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>rītikügītřire hinya, kana rīgaküraihīrīria. </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Rītirī igūrű matu-int marĩa mairü, ati hihi nīguo uuge atīrī:</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nū ügütwambatīra matu-inī arīgīre atūrehere, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na atüiguithie ühoro warīo nīguo türīkage? </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ningī ritirī mbarī iria îngi ya iria, nī getha hihi uuge atīri</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nũ ügütürinīra iria, arīgīre atūrehere, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na atūiguithie ühoro warĩo nīguo tūrikage ?</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>No rīri, uuge ücio wĩ hakuhī nawe, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o kanua-inī gaku, na ngoro-inī yaku, nĩ getha ūtwīkage.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nīcio ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>THABURI YA GUCOKERŪO</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Thaburi 
69: 13 na 16;-36</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA : Mwathani nĩ akuhīrīirie arīa mamwethaga.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>No atiri, ni, nowe Mwathani ndikahoya, hingo ya gwītikirika; </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wee Ngai, tondū wa üria ūtugi waku wī mtingī,</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>njokeria kūringana o na wihokeki wa ūhonokania waku. </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani,nyamūkîria, amu ūtugi waku nī mwega mūno: </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wiihūgūrire ūkinjerekere kūringana na uria mathamaku maingīhīte.</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA : Mwathani nĩ akuhīrīirie arīa mamwethaga.</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>No nirirī, ndĩ mūthĩnīku, na ngarīo nĩ kīeha, reka ūhonokio waku, </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ngai ūnjige handū haraya na igūrū, </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Rīitwa rīa Ngai ngūrīkumia na rūimbo, </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kūnenehia ndīkīmūnenehie na ngatho iria ngūmūcokeria.</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA : Mwathani nĩ akuhīrīirie arīa mamwethaga.</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Andu aria ahoreri mona ūguo, no makene: </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>inyui mūrongoretie Ngai, ngoro cianyu ta ni iřiuke.</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Amu andū arīa aagi, Mwathani no amaiguaga;</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>arīa ake othe ndangimaagira bata.</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA : Mwathani nĩ akuhīrīirie arīa mamwethaga.</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Amu Ngai ni akahonokia Sion, na nake matūūra ma Juda, </s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na kūgaya ni mbeũ ya ndungata ciake îgakūgaya; </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>arīa menda rīmtwa rīake, nĩo magatūüraga kuo.</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA : Mwathani nĩ akuhīrīirie arīa mamwethaga.</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĪTHOMO KIA IGIRI</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akolosai 1: 15 - 20.  </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> 
GUTHOMA MARUA MA MŪTHURE PAUL KŪRĪ ANDŪ A KOLOSAI:</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kristū  Yesu nīwe mūhianīre wa ürīa Ngai ahaana, </s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o we ütonekaga, na nīwe waambire kurigithathwo indo ciothe itaanombwo. </s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tondü rirī, indo iothe ikīümbwo nĩ ciombirüo na ündü wake, </s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>iria irī Igūrũ, o nacio iria irī thĩ; iria cionekaga o na iria itonekaga; </s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na ciatuīka nĩ itī cia ünene kana ene wathani, kana mothamaki, </s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na kana mahinya, ciothe-rĩ, nĩ kūümbwo</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ciombirüo na ūndū wake, nīguo ituike ciake. </s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake we nīwe ūtūire o ho mbere indo ciothe itaanagīa, </s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nacio ciothe itūūraga inyitanītio nīwe. </s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ningī nīwe Mūtwe wa mwirī, arī guo kanitha: nake nīwe wa kiambīrīria, </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na nīwe irigithathi rĩa andü arīa maanakua; </s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nī getha maūndū-inī mothe atuīke nowe wa mbere.  </s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ gūkorūo ūiyũru wothe wa Ngai nī wetīkīrire gūtūűra thĩinĩ wake; </s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nīguo atī na ündū wake maūndũ mothe macoke kūiguithanio na Ngai, </s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ ündū wa ürīa aarehire thayū na ündū wa </s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>thakame īrīa yaitirūo mūtharaba-inī wake;. </s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mo mothe-rī, maiguithanio na Ngai no ūndũ wake,</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na magītuīka nĩ ma gūkū thĩ,o na kana ma lgūrü.</s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nīcio ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>RUIMBO RUA INJIRI
John 13, 34.</s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alleluya, Alleluya. </s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani ekuuga atī : Niĩ nĩ ngũmühe rĩathani rīerū, </s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ ati mwandane; o ta üguo niĩ ndīmwendete. </s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GİTHOMO KIA INJIRI
Luka 10: 25 - 37.</s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GUTHOMA INJIRI YA MÜTHURE LUKA :</s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hīndi io, mūrutani ūmwe wa watho </s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akīrügama akīmügeria, akīmüüria atīrī: </s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mürutani, ngwīka atīa nī getha ngagaīrūo muoyo ūtagathira? </s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake Yesu akīmūűria atīirī: 
Kwandikītwo </s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>atīa watho-inī wa Ngai ? Othomaga atīa ? </s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake akīműcokeria akiuga atīrĩ: Enda </s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani Ngai waku na ngoro yaku yothe, </s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na muoyo waku wothe, o na hinya waku wothe,</s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na gwīciria gwaku guothe; </s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ningī enda mūndū wa itūüra rīanyu, </s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o ta ürĩa wīendete wee mwene. </s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake akīmwīra atirī: Nĩ wacokia ūhoro o wega: </s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ikaga o üguo na nĩ ügūtūüra muoyo, </s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake mūndū ücio, akīenda gwītua </s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mwega, agīcoka akīüria Yesu atīrī: </s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mündü ürīa wītagwo üũ, Mündū wa itūūra riitū,nĩta ürīkü? </s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake Yesu akīmūcokeria akiuga atīrī : </s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwarī mündū wathereraga athiī Jariko,</s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>oimīte Jerusalemu; nake agīkorūo nĩ atunyani, </s></f>"},{ID:70,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nao makīmüruta nguo ciake na makīmūhūra, makīmūtiga atigairie hanini atumbükane. </s></f>"},{ID:71,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na gūgītuika atīrī: atī nĩ kwarĩ mūthĩnjīri-Ngai </s></f>"},{ID:72,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wathereraga, akīgera njīra io: </s></f>"},{ID:72,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nake ona mūndū ūcio, akīhītūkīra o mükīra-inī ürīa üngt wa njīra. </s></f>"},{ID:73,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>O üguo taguo Mülawii ümwe nake agīkinya </s></f>"},{ID:74,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o handū hau, nake aamuona, </s></f>"},{ID:74,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akīhītükīra o mūkīra-inī ürīa ūngī wa njīra. </s></f>"},{ID:75,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>No rirī, Müsamaria ümwe agīthii ügeni agīkinya o hau aarī: </s></f>"},{ID:76,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nake aamuona, akīringwo nī tia, agīthii harī we, </s></f>"},{ID:77,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akīmuoha kürīa aatihangītio, agīgüitīrīria maguta na njohi; </s></f>"},{ID:78,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agīcoka akīmūhaicia ndigiri  igürű rīa nyamū yake mwene, </s></f>"},{ID:79,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akīmūtwara o kinya nyūmba ya ageni, akīmūmenyerera. </s></f>"},{ID:80,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na m</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>thenya üyū üngī akīruta mbia </s></f>"},{ID:81,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>igīrī akīnengera mwene nyūmba io ya ageni, </s></f>"},{ID:82,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akīmwīra atīrī: Mūmenyagīrīre; na rīrī, </s></f>"},{ID:83,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o kīndü kirīa kīngī üngīruta nī ündū wake, </s></f>"},{ID:84,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ ngakūrīha rīrīa ngacoka, Rīu-rī,andü acio atatü-ri, </s></f>"},{ID:85,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ügwīciria nĩ ürīkü wao wekire mũndū ūcio wakorirūo nĩ atunyani o ta ūrīa</s></f>"},{ID:86,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mündű angīkwo nĩ műndü wa itütüra rīao ? 
Nake mürutani ūcio wa watho akīmūcokeria atīrī:</s></f>"},{ID:87,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ni ücio wamūiguīrīire tha. Nake Yesu akīmwīra atīrī: Thiĩ, ügekanageo ta üguo.</s></f>"},{ID:88,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nīcio ciugo cia Mwath ani.</s></f>"}],Style:{Body:{FontStyle:{Fill:{Color:"FFFFFFFF"},Stroke:{Color:"FF000000"},ShadowColor:"FFFFFFFF"}}},
Text:"KIUMIA GIA IKUMI NA ITHANO KIA MWAKA  C"},{Guid:"lMrmaOp9W0OfATFv+M8JYw",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>KIUMIA KIA IGIRI KIA WINYEREKIA MWAKA C</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KIA MBERE 
Kĩambĩrĩria 15:5-12. 17-18</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA KĨAMBĨRĨRIA: </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Matukũ-inĩ macio Ngai agĩcoka akiumia nja Abraham na akiuga </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>atĩrĩ: Rĩu ta tiira maitho, ũbare igũrũ, ũtare njata, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>okorũo wakĩhota gũcitara; ningĩ akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ:</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ũguo noguo mbeũ yaku ĩkaigana. Nake akĩĩhoka Mwathani; </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>naguo ũndũũcio Mwathani akĩmũtuĩra ta arĩ ũthingu e naguo.  </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Agĩcoka akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Niĩ nĩ niĩ Mwathani ũrĩa wakũrutire bũrũri </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wa Ur wa Akaldei, nĩ getha ngũhe bũrũri ũyũ ũtuĩke igai rĩaku.  </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nake akĩũria atĩrĩ: Mwathani Ngai, ngũmenyithio nĩ kĩ atĩ nĩ ũgatuĩka</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>igai rĩakwa? Nake akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Ta njoera mori ya mĩaka ĩtatũ,</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na harika ya mĩaka ĩtatũ, na ndũrũme ya mĩaka ĩtatũ,</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na ndirahugi na kĩana kĩa ndutura.  Nake agĩkĩmũoera icio </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ciothe,  agĩciatũranga na gatagatĩ njatũ igĩrĩ igĩrĩ,</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nacio njatũ icio agĩciara mĩhari, akĩringanagia a rũatũ </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na rũrĩa rũngĩ; no rĩrĩ, nyamũ icio cia njoya ndaigana gũciatũranga.  </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nacio nderi igĩitĩka gũcuhũkĩra nyamũ icio thĩnje, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nake Abraham agaciũmbũra.  Na rĩrĩa riũa rĩatuire gũthũa, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Abraham akĩgwatwo nĩ toro mũnene; na atĩrĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>agĩtebeba nĩ ũndũ wa gũtũmanĩrũo nĩ nduma nene.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na gũgĩkinya atĩrĩ, atĩ  riũa rĩathũa, na kwagĩa nduma-rĩ, atĩrĩrĩ,</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>gũkĩgĩa na kĩmwaki kĩnene gũgũtoga ndogo,</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> o na gĩcinga gĩkũrĩrĩmbũka, nakĩo gĩkĩhĩtũkĩra gatagatĩ-inĩ </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ka njatũ icio cia nyama. Na rĩrĩ, mũthenya o ro ũcio Mwathani agĩĩkĩra</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kĩrĩkanĩro na Abraham,
akiuga atĩrĩ: Bũrũri ũyũ-rĩ,</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ ‘heete mbeũ yaku, warũma rũũĩ rũa Misri o nginya </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>rũũĩ rũrĩa rũnene
rũĩtagwo Eufrate.</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO
Thaburi 27:1;7-8;9ab;13-14</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA: Mwathani nĩwe ũtheri wakwa na ũhonokio wakwa</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani nĩwe ũtheri wakwa, o gwata ũhonokio wakwa;</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ingĩgĩĩtigĩra ũ? Mwathani nĩwe hinya ũrĩa </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũgitĩire muoyo wakwa; ũrĩa ũngĩ’makia nũ?</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA: Mwathani nĩwe ũtheri wakwa na ũhonokio wakwa</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> 
Ĩ Mwathani, igua mũgambo wakwa ngĩkaya; kĩnginyĩrie wega waku,</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũnyamũkĩrie. Harĩa woigire, rongoriani ũthiũ wakwa-rĩ, ngoro yakwa ĩkwĩrĩte</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũũ: Ũthiũ  waku, Mwathani, nĩ ndĩrĩũrongoragia.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA: Mwathani nĩwe ũtheri wakwa na ũhonokio wakwa</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tiga kwĩĩ’hithĩra ũthiũ; tiga gũkĩingata ndungata yaku </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na marakara: nĩwe ũtũire ũndeithagia.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA: Mwathani nĩwe ũtheri wakwa na ũhonokio wakwa</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Gũca njĩtĩkĩtie atĩ nĩ ngeyonera wega wa Mwathani ndĩ bũrũri wa </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>arĩa me muoyo, ingĩrĩ kũhooteka. Eterera O Mwathani gĩa na hinya, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na wĩũmĩrĩrie ngoro; ĩĩ-ni, no gĩeterere Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA: Mwathani nĩwe ũtheri wakwa na ũhonokio wakwa</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ
Afilipi 3:17-4,1</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A FILIPI:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, wĩgerekanagiei na niĩ, ningĩ mũbarage wega </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>andũ arĩa mathiaga na mĩthiĩre o ĩrĩa twamũonagĩrĩria. </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tondũ nĩ kũrĩ andũ aingĩ mathiaga na mĩthiĩre ya kũonania </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>atĩ nĩ thũ cia Mũtharaba wa Kristũ, o arĩa ndanamwĩra</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũhoro wao kaingĩ, o na rĩu ngũmwĩra ũhoro wao ngĩitaga maithori. </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Andũ acio-rĩ, kũrigĩrĩria kwao nĩ gũtoma magatoma;</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ngai yao nĩyo nda; naguo ũndũ ũrĩa wa kũmaconora, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩguo megoocaga nĩ ũndũ waguo; ningĩ metaranagia maũndũ</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o ma gũkũ thĩ. Nĩ gũkorũo bũrũri ũrĩa tũrĩ aguo kĩũmbe nĩ kũrĩa Igũrũ, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na twetagĩrĩra  Mũhonokia ũrĩa ũkoima kuo, nĩwe Mwathani Yesu </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kristũ, ũrĩa ũkagarũra mwĩrĩ ũyũ witũ ũhinyaraga,</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũhaananio na mwĩrĩ wake wĩna riri, nĩ ũndũ wa hinya ũrĩa arĩ </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>naguo wa gũtũma o maũndũ mothe maathĩkage nĩwe.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hakĩrĩ ũguo, ariũ a Ithe witũ-rĩ, inyuĩ nyendete na ngamwĩriragĩria, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o inyuĩ mũhaana ta gĩkeno gĩakwa o na thũmbĩ yakwa-rĩ, ikaragai mũrũmĩte</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wega, endwa akwa, thĩinĩ wa Mwathani. </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI
Marko 9:7
	</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Rũgoco na gĩtĩo gwaku, Mwathani Yesu.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Thĩinĩ wa itu gũkiuma mũgambo wa Ithe: </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>“Ũyũ nĩwe Mũrũ wakwa nyendete mũno: mũiguagei”.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Rũgoco na gĩtĩo gwaku, Mwathani Yesu.</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI
Luka 9:28-36</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE LUKA:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hĩndĩ ĩo Yesu agĩtwarana na Petro, na John, na Jacob, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akĩambata kĩrĩma nao, ahoere Ngai kuo. </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na akĩhoyaga-rĩ, ũthiũ wake ũkĩgarũrũka ũrĩa wahaanaga, nacio </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nguo ciake ikĩerũha, igĩkenga mũno.  
Na rĩrĩ, hagĩkorũo athuri erĩ makĩaria nake, nĩo </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Musa na Elia; makĩmoimĩrĩra me na riri, makĩaria ũhoro wa ikua </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>rĩake rĩrĩa akiriĩ gũkuĩra Jerusalem. Nake Petro, na arĩa maarĩ hamwe nake, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>magĩkorũo mahĩtĩtwo nĩ toro; no rĩrĩa maarahũkire,</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>makĩigua, makĩona riri wake, 
o na makĩona athuri acio erĩ </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>marũgamĩte hamwe nake.  Na gũgĩkinya  atĩrĩ, hĩndĩ ĩrĩa andũ acio maatiganaga</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nake, mathiĩ, Petro akĩĩra Yesu atĩrĩ: Mũnene witũ, nĩ twagĩrĩirũo </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ gũikara gũkũ: reka twake ithũnũ ithatũ, 
kĩmwe gĩaku,</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na kĩmwe kĩa Musa, na kĩmwe kĩa Elia: nake ndoĩ ũrĩa oigaga.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na akĩaragia maũndũ macio-rĩ, 
gũgĩũka itu rĩkĩmahumbĩra; </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nao magĩĩtigĩra nĩ ũndũ wa kũhumbĩrũo nĩrĩo.  Na mũgambo </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>uumĩte itu-inĩ rĩu ũkiuga atĩrĩ: Ũyũ nĩwe Mũrũ wakwa, o ũrĩa ndĩĩthurĩire:</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mũiguagei. Na hĩndĩ ĩrĩa mũgambo ũcio waiguirũo, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Yesu agĩcoka kũonwo arĩ wiki.  Nao magĩkĩra, na matierire mũndũ </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o na ũmwe matukũ macio ũndũ o wothe wa maũndũ macio monire.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> </s></f>"}],
Text:"KIUMIA KIA IGIRI KIA WINYEREKIA MWAKA C
"},{Guid:"V12f568wWku5HhYUlPkcHQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>DOMINIKA YA PILI YA KWARESIMA MWAKA C</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SOMO LA KWANZA
Mwanzo 15:5-12, 17-18</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Somo katika kitabu cha Mwanzo</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wakati ule: Bwana alimleta Abramu nje, akasema:</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>“Tazama mbinguni, hesabu nyota, kama waweza kuzihesabu.”</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Akamwambia: \"Ndivyo uzao wako utakavyokuwa.” </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Abramu akamwamini Bwana, naye Bwana </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akamhesabia jambo hilo kuwa haki. Akamwambia: </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>\"Mimi ndimi Bwana niliyekutoa toka Uru wa Wakaldayo, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nikupe nchi hii iwe yako.\" Abramu akamwambia, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>\"Ee Bwana, nitajuaje ya kuwa nitapewa  iwe yangu?\"</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Akamwambia: Unipatie ndama wa miaka mitatu, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mbuzi jike wa miaka mitatu, kondoo dume wa miaka mitatu, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>hua na mwana njiwa. Abramu akamletea wanyama hao wote, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akawapasua katikati, akaweka kila kipande kuelekeana</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na kingine; lakini ndege hakuwapasua. Na tai wakaishukia </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ile mizoga, lakini Abramu akawafukuza. </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Jua lilipokuwa likishuka, usingizi mzito ukamshika Abramu, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na hofu na giza vikamwangukia. Jua lilipokwisha kushuka, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na giza kuenea, tanuri ya moshi na mwenge wa moto vikapita </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kati ya vipande vile vya nyama. Siku ile Bwana akafanya agano </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na Abramu akisema:
“Nimeupatia uzao wako nchi hii, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kutoka mto wa Misri, mpaka mto mkubwa, Mto Eufrate.\"</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA                                      Zaburi 27:1,7-8, 9abc,3-14(K 1a)</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kiitikio: Bwana ni mwanga wangu na wokovu wangu.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Bwana ni mwanga wangu na wokovu wangu;nimwogope nani?</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Bwana ni kinga ya uzima wangu,
nimhofu nani? </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kiitikio: Bwana ni mwanga wangu na wokovu wangu.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ee Bwana, usikie sauti yangu ninapokulilia; unihurumie, unijibu.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Moyo wangu unasema, \"Njoo utafute uso wake Mungu.” </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nitautafuta uso wako, ee Bwana! </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kiitikio: Bwana ni mwanga wangu na wokovu wangu.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Usinifiche uso wako; usimkatae kwa hasira mtumishi wako.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wewe ndiwe msaada wangu;
usinitupe; </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wala usiniache Mwokozi wangu! (K)</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kiitikio; Bwana ni mwanga wangu na wokovu wangu.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Naamini ya kuwa nitauona wema wa Bwana katika nchi ya walio hai.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Umngoje Bwana, uwe hodari;
ujipe moyo, naam, umngoje Bwana! </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kiitikio: Bwana ni mwanga wangu na wokovu wangu.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SOMO LA PILI
Wafilipi 3:17-4:1</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Somo katika barua ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Wafilipi</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ndugu, mniige mimi!
Waangalieni wale wanaopanga </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mwenendo wao kadiri ya mfano tuliowapeni. </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Maana wengi - nimewaambieni mara nyingi, na sasa </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nawaambia kwa machozi - huishi kama adui wa msalaba wa Kristo.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwisho wao ni uharibifu; mungu wao ni tumbo; hujisifia aibu yao, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akili zao ni kwenye mambo ya dunia. Bali kwetu ni mbinguni;</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na kutoka mbinguni atakuja Mwokozi, Bwana Yesu Kristo, tunayemtazamia. </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Naye ataubadili mwili wetu wa unyonge, upate kufanana na mwili </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wake wa utukufu. Atafanya hayo kwa enzi ile </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>inayomwezesha kuuweka ulimwengu wote chini ya </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mamlaka yake. Basi, ndugu zangu wapendwa niwatunukao sana, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mlio furaha yangu na taji langu, simameni </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>imara katika Bwana, enyi wapendwa.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SHANGILIO LA INJILI</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Sifa na utukufu kwako, ee Kristo.</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Sauti ya Baba ikatoka katika wingu lile jeupe ikisema, </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Huyu ni mwanangu mpendwa, msikilizeni yeye.</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Sifa na utukufu kwako, ee Kristo.</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>INJILI
Luka 9:28b-36</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Luka</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wakati ule Yesu aliwachukua Petro na Yohane na Yakobo,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akapanda mlimani ili asali. Alipokuwa akisali, sura ya uso </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wake ikageuka, mavazi yake yakawa meupe na kung'aa. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mara watu wawili walikuwa wakizungumza naye, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ndio Musa na Eliya, walionekana katika utukufu, wakanena </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>juu ya kutoka kwake atakakotimiza Yerusalemu.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Petro na wenzake walikuwa wameshikwa na usingizi,</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>lakini walipoamka, waliona utukufu wake na wale watu 
wawili wakisimama </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>naye. Nao walipotaka kuagana naye, Petro alimwambia Yesu, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>“Mwalimu, ni vizuri kwetu kukaa hapa; tutanjenga vibanda vitatu,</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kimoja chako, kimoja cha Musa na kimoja cha Eliya.” Lakini </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>hakujua alilosema.
Aliposema hayo, likatokea wingu likawatia uvuli, nao </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wakaogopa walipoingia katika wingu hilo.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kisha sauti ikatoka katika wingu ikisema, “Huyu ni mwanangu </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mpendwa, msikilizeni yeye.” Sauti ilipomaliza </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kusema, Yesu alionekana peke yake. Nao wakashika </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>siri juu ya mambo hayo waliyoyaona, wala </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>hawakumwambia mtu wakati ule.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f>"}],
Text:"DOMINIKA YA PILI YA KWARESIMA MWAKA C"},{Guid:"jYyjkPRvdUqp96r8vLEbnA",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĪTHOMO KĨA MBERE
Atumwo 5: 12-16.</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŪTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA ATUMWO:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na rīrī, ciama nyingi ikīringwo, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na morirű maingi magiīkwo andű na moko ma atűmwo: </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nao othe maaikaraga githaku-inī kīrĩa gietagwo </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Githaku gĩa Salomone, marī na ngoro o ro îmwe. </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na andũ arĩa angĩ- rĩ, gūtirī wao ũigana gweta gūthi thiritű nao. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Indī kīrīndĩ nĩ kiamakumagia, na andű aría metikītie </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>makïongerereka o makīria kūrī Mwathani, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>itutu cia arūme na andű-a-nja, o nginya makīya </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gűkuua andű aría arŭaru, makīmaiga </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ing'aratua-inī makomeire itanda o na ibarĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ getha, rĩrĩa Petro ekühïtūka, </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>naarī hihi kīīruru gĩake kīringe amwe ao. </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nakĩo kīrīndī gīkīūngana kiumīte matűüra-inī marïa </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mathiürürükïirie Jerusalemu, </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gîkarehage andű aría arŭaru na aría maanyamaragio ni ngoma thűku; </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nao othe makihonio.</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nicio ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>THABURI YA GŪCOKERÑO
Thaburi 118: 2-4; 22-24; 25-27a.</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA: Wee Ngai, nĩ tūtaranītie magegania ma rűendo rũaku.</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>1. A Israeli ta nī moige ūguo, atī ūtugi wake ni wa tene na tene. </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nyumba ya Haaron, ta ni moige
üguo, </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>atī ūtugi wake ni wa tene na tene. </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Andu aría etigiri Mwathani-rī ni makiuge üguo, </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ati ūtugi wake ni wa tene na tene.</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA: Wee Ngai, nĩ tūtaranītie magegania ma rűendo rũaku.</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>lhiga rīrīa riaregiruo nî aaki nīrio rītuîkīte </s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o rīrīa inene ría koine. </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Undū īcio uumete kwî Mwathani, </s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na nì ügütügegia tūkīwona. </s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Müthenya üyü ni Mwathani ütümite ügie; </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nī tūcanjamūkei tūkīūkenagīra.</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA: Wee Ngai, nĩ tūtaranītie magegania ma rűendo rũaku.</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>I Mwathani, twaguthaitha, tühonokagie! I Mwathani, </s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>twagūthaitha, tūma tütüüre o tūgaaciire!</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Műrathimwo-rī, ni ūrīa wa güūka na riitwa rĩa Mwathani! </s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Twī gūkū nyümba ya Mwathani, inyuī
ni twamürathima, </s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani nowe Mürungu, na ni agītuonetie ütheri.</s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA: Wee Ngai, nĩ tūtaranītie magegania ma rűendo rũaku.</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GITHOMO KIA IGĪRĪ
Kuguuririo 1: 9-11. 12-13, 17-19.</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GUTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA KŪGUŪRĪRIO :</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Niĩ John, műrű wa ithe wanyu na mügwatanıīri </s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na inyuī mīnyamaro na üthamaki na ūkirīrīria, </s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>iria ii na Yesu, ndakorirüo ndĩ githama kīrĩa giitagwo </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Patmos nĩ ũndű wa ühoro wa Ngai na ũira wa Yesu.</s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ngikorão ndĩ thĩini wa Muoyo müthenya wa Mwathani, </s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ngõigua műgambo műnene na thutha wakwa, </s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o ta wa coro, ūkiuga atīrī: Oria ūkuona-rī, </s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>andīka mbuku-inī, ücoke ütümïre makanitha maria műgwanja. </s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ngīkihügüra nyone mügambo ūcio wanjarīria. </s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndehűgūra, ngĩona mītī műgwanja ya kühangīrũo matawa, ya thahabu; </s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na miti- inï ïo ya kühangiruo matawa gatagatĩ </s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ngĩona kūrĩ wĩ ho ahaana ta műrű wa mündü, </s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ekīrīte nguo imūkinyîte o nyarīrī, na akeoha mücibi wa thahabu gîthüri-inī. </s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndamuona, ngĩgũa magűrű-inī make ngõikara ta műndű műkuű. </s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake akinjigīrīra guoko kwa ūrio, akiuga: </s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tiga gwitigīra; nĩ nii wa mbere o na wa kūrigīrīria, </s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ nii Orĩa-wi-muoyo; na nĩ ndakuïte,</s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na nĩ nii ũyũ, ngũtüüra muoyo kinya o tene na tene, </s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nacio ihingũro nĩ nĩi ndĩ nacio cia gīkuũ na cia kwa-ngoma. </s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hakīrī ūguo-rī, kïandīke maūndű macio wona, </s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o namo maũndű marĩa me kuo rĩu, na marĩa magakinya thutha.</s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nicio ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>RŪĪMBO RUA INJIRI
John 20, 29.</s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alleluya, Alleluya. </s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wee, Thomas, tondū nĩ űnyonete, nikio wītīkītie;</s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gükena-rī, nĩ arĩa matonete na no metīkītie.</s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:70,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GITHOMO KIA INJIRI
John 20: 19-31.</s></f>"},{ID:71,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GUTHOMA INJIRI YA MUTHURE JOHN :</s></f>"},{ID:72,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Muthenya o ūcio wa kwambīrīria kiumia, </s></f>"},{ID:73,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gūkinyîte hwaï- inĩ, na mīrango īkahingwo küu arutwo ma
arĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:74,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ ũndū wa gwītigīra Ayahudi, </s></f>"},{ID:75,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu agīūka akīrūgama gatagatī- inī, akīmera atīrī: </s></f>"},{ID:76,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Giai na thayo.</s></f>"},{ID:77,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na aarīkia kuuga ūguo, akīmonia hĩ ciake o na mbaru. </s></f>"},{ID:78,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nao arutwo mona Mwathani magīkena. </s></f>"},{ID:79,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu agikīmera ringi atīrī: Giai na thayũ; </s></f>"},{ID:80,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o ta ürĩa Ithe witü aandekirie nii, noguo ndaműrekia inyuĩ. </s></f>"},{ID:81,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na aarīkia kuuga űguo akimahecherera, akīmera: </s></f>"},{ID:82,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>lyűkiai Muoyo Mütheru; </s></f>"},{ID:83,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>andü arïa othe mwarekera mehia mao, nĩ maarekeruo; </s></f>"},{ID:84,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>arĩa othe mwarega kűrekera mehia mao, megüikara matarekeiruo.</s></f>"},{ID:85,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na rīrī, űmwe wa arïa ikūmi na erĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:86,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na nĩ Thomas ūrīa wetagwo Didimo (Wamahatha), </s></f>"},{ID:87,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ücio ndaarī nao hindi io Yesu okire. </s></f>"},{ID:88,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tondű ücio arutwo arĩa angī makīmwīra: Nĩ tuonete Mwathani. </s></f>"},{ID:89,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake akīmera atīrī: Itonete irema cia mícumarĩ hĩ ciake, </s></f>"},{ID:90,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ngatonyia kïara gĩakwa irema-inī icio cia mīcumarĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:91,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ngatonyia guoko gwakwa mbaru-inī ciake-rī, </s></f>"},{ID:92,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndingīītīkia o na hanini.</s></f>"},{ID:93,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ningi matukű maathira anana, </s></f>"},{ID:94,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>arutwo ake maarī kuo rĩngĩ kũu nyũmba thĩinī, </s></f>"},{ID:95,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na maarĩ na Thomas. </s></f>"},{ID:96,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake Yesu agīūka, mirango īrī mīhinge, </s></f>"},{ID:97,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akīrūgama gatagatī- inī, akiuga : Gĩai na thayũ. </s></f>"},{ID:98,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Agĩcoka akira Thomas atīrī: Rehe kiara gĩaku haha, </s></f>"},{ID:99,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ürore hĩ ciakwa; na űrehe guoko gwaku, </s></f>"},{ID:100,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ütonyie mbaru-inī ciakwa; na ütige gūtuîka wa kűrega gwītīkia, </s></f>"},{ID:101,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>űtuïke wa gwītīkia. Thomas agīcokia akimwira atīrī: </s></f>"},{ID:102,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani wakwa, Ngai wakwa! Nake Yesu akimwīra atīrīrī: </s></f>"},{ID:103,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wee tondū nī ūnyonete, nĩkĩo wītīkītie; gūkena-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:104,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ arĩa matonete, na no metīkītie. </s></f>"},{ID:105,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Gwi ciama ingĩ nyingĩ Yesu ekire arutwo me ho, </s></f>"},{ID:106,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>itaandîkîtwo mbuku îno; </s></f>"},{ID:107,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>no icio nĩ ciandīkītwo ni getha mwītīkie ati Yesu niwe Kristű, </s></f>"},{ID:108,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Műrű wa Ngai; </s></f>"},{ID:109,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na tondű wa gwītīkia műgie na muoyo na ũndű wa riitwa riake.</s></f>"},{ID:110,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nicio ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"}],
Text:"KIUMIA KĨA IGĪRĪ KĨA IRIŰKĪRO
 MWAKA C"},{Guid:"h9K7a+ydaUWHQqo5NJsUPA",Verses:[{
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>DOMINIKA YA KUMI NA SABA </k></c></s></f></u><u><fArial Black><s1846><cFF00F200><kFFFF0000>MWAKA C</k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1384>SOMO LA KWANZA</s></f></u><fArial Black><s1846> 
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFD8D800>Mwanzo 
18:20-32</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika kitabu cha Mwanzo</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Siku zile: Bwana alisema: </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mlio uliotoka Sodoma na Gomora</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ni mkubwa na dhambi yao ni kubwa mno! Nitashuka nione kama</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wametenda ama hawakutenda yote wanayoshtakiwa na </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mlío uliopanda hata kwangu; 
nitajua tu. Basi hao watu </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wawili wakaondoka pale, wakaenda Sodoma.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana akabaki bado amesimama mbele ya Abrahamu.
 </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>Abrahamu akamkaribia, akasema, </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>\"Je, utampoteza mwenye haki pamoja na
mwovu?</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000> </k></s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Labda kunapatikana wenye haki hamsini kati Kweli, utauharibu, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wala hutausamehe mji ule kwa ajili ya wale wanyofu hamsini waliomo? </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Sivyo, huwezi kutenda jambo hilo, 
na kumwua 
mtu mnyofu pamoja na mwovu, </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hata mtu mwenye haki
atendewe sawa na mwovu.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Usitende hivyo hata kidogo. </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Je, yule anayehukumu dunia nzima</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>angeacha kushika yaliyo haki?\" </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>Bwana akajibu: </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Nikiwapata mjini </k></c></s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F></k></c><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Sodoma wenye haki hamsini, nitauhurumia mji wote kwa ajili yao.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Abrahamu akasema tena, 
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200>\"Nathubutu kusema na </c></s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<cFFF2F200></c><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200>Bwana wangu,
mimi niliye mavumbi na majivu.</c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846> </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200>Lakini labda katika watu hamsini
wakipunguka watano; </c></s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<cFFF2F200></c><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200>je, sababu ya watano
hao utaharibu mji wote?*</c></s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>Akasema: </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Sitaharibu 
mji nikiwapata 
wale arobaini na watano.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Abrahamu akazidi kusema naye, akamwambia, </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>\"Labda watapatikana
humo arobaini tu?\" </k></c></s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana akajibu: 
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Sitafanya hayo, kwa ajili Ya
wale arobaini. </k></c></s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Abrahamu akasema, 
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>\"Bwana wangu asikasirike,
kama nasema tena: </k></c></s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F></k></c><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Labda watapatikana thelathini?\" </k></c></s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana akajibu:
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Sita fanya hayo, 
kama ninakuta 
humo thelathini. </k></c></s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Abrahamu akasema,</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>\"Nathubutu kusema tena na 
Bwana wangu? </k></c></s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Labda watapatikana
humo ishirini?\" </k></c></s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana akajibu: 
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Sitaharibu mji, 
kwa ajili ya wale
ishirini. </k></c></s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Abrahamu akasema, </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>\"Bwana wangu asikasirike, nikisema
tena mara moja tu. </k></c></s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Labda watapatikana humu kumi?\" </k></c></s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana akajibu:
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Sitaharibu m</k></c></s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>j</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>i, kwa ajili ya wale kumi.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA</k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Zaburi  138:
</s></f><fArial Black><s1076><cFFFF0000>1-2a. 2bc-3, 6-7ab, 7c-8 (K. 3a)</c></s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF0000><kFFF2F200>K</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF3F3F>. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Siku nilipokuomba, ulinisikiliza, ee Bwana.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>1.Nitakushukuru, ee Bwana, kwa moyo wangu wote;</s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>umesikiliza maneno ya kinywa changu. </s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mbele ya malaika nitakuimbia sifa.
Nitakusujudu </s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nikilielekea hekalu lako takatifu. K.</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF0000><kFFF2F200>K</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846>. </s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Siku nilipokuomba, ulinisikiliza, ee Bwana.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>2.Nitalishukuru jina lako kwa ajili ya wema na uaminifu wako.</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa maana umekuza kuliko yote jina lako na ahadi yako. </s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Siku nilipokuomba ulinisikiliza;
uliifariji nafsi yangu kwa kunitia nguvu.</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF0000><kFFF2F200>K</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>. Siku nilipokuomba, ulinisikiliza, ee Bwana.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>3. Ingawa Bwana yuko juu, anamwangalia mnyonge,</s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>anamjua mwenye kujivuna tokea mbali.</s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nijapokwenda kati ya taabu, wewe unanihuisha,</s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>unanyosha mkono wako dhidi ya hasira ya adui zangu. K.</s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF0000><kFFF2F200>K</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>. Siku nilipokuomba, ulinisikiliza, ee Bwana.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>4. Mkono wako wa kulia unanisalimisha; </s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana atatimiliza kwangu mpango wake.</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ee Bwana, wema wako ni wa milele,
usiziache kazi ya mikono yako! K.</s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>K. Siku nilipokuomba, ulinisikiliza, ee Bwana.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>SOMO LA PILI 
</k></c></s></f></u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF0000><kFFF2F200>Wakolosai 2:12-14</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika barua ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Wakolosai</s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndugu zangu: Pamoja na Kristo mlizikwa kwa ubatizo</s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>pamoja naye pia mmefufuliwa kwa kuiamini nguvu ya Mungu</s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>aliyemtufua Kristo katika wafu. Nanyi mkiwa wafu </s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa dhambi zenu
na kwa kutotahiriwa mwilini. </s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Lakini Mungu amewafanya wazima
pamoja naye, </s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa kuwasamehe makosa yote. </s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ameifuta ile hati ya msalabani. deni iliyotushtaki </s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na iliyotukinza. 
Ameiondoa kati yetu akipigilia</s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>SHANGlLIO LA INJILI
</k></c></s></f></u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFD8D800>Warumi 8:15be</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Aleluya.
W. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Mmempokea roho anayewafanya kuwa wana wa Mungu</s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kuita, </s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFD8D800>“Abba! Baba!\"
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846>W. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF6666>INJILI
</k></c></s></f></u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF6666><kFFF2F200>Luka 11:1-13</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Luka</s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu alipokuwa mahali 
fulani akisali, </s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na alipomaliza mmoja wa
wafuasi wake </s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>alimwambia, 
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>\"Bwana, utufundishe kusali kama</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Yohane alivyowafundisha wanafunzi wake.\"</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akawaambia, 
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>\"Wakati mnaposali semeni: </k></c></s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Baba, jina lako
litukuzwe, ufalme wako ufike. </k></c></s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F></k></c><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>Utupe mkate wetu wa kila siku,
utusamehe dhambi zetu, </k></c></s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F></k></c><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>kwa maana sisi 
pia tunawasamehe wote</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>waliotukosea, na usitutie katika kishawishi.\"</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akawaambia, 
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>“Ikiwa mmoja wenu ana rafiki anayemwendea</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>kati ya usiku, akamwambia, 'Rafiki, nikopeshe mikate mitatu.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:69,
