Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake akiuga atīri: Ndatiga gwīka ündü ücio nī ündũ wa acio mĩrongo īna. </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akiuga atiri: Mwathani ta nĩ atige kürakara-ī, </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>njoke njarie. i hihi küngikorüo kwī mĩrongo itatü? </s></f>"},{ID:16,
