Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ningi akiuga atīrī: Riu-rī, no ngweta kwarīria Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Atīriri, i hihi küngĩoneka mĩrongo iirï? Nake akiuga atīrī: </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndatiga kuriunuha nĩ ũndű wa acio mĩrongo iri. </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ningī akiuga atīrī: Mwathani ta nĩ atige kürakara-i, </s></f>"},{ID:19,
