Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŪTHOMA INJIRI YA MŪTHURE LUKA :</s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na gügīkinya atīrī, hĩndī iria aari handü hana akīhoya </s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ngai-rī, aarīkia, mürutwo ümwe wake </s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akĩmwīra atīrī: Mwathani, tũrute o na ithui kühoya Ngai, </s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o ta ūrīa John nake aarutire arutwo ake.</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake akīmera atīrī: Rīria műkühoya Ngai, ugagai atīrī :</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Baba witü ürĩ lgürü, Rīītwa raku rīroigwo, Ünene waku üroka. </s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tüheage o mūthenya irio ciitű
cia gütüigana, </s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ütuohere mehia maitü, nĩ gükorűo o na ithuĩ nĩ tuohagīra </s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o mündū ürīa wĩ na
thirī na ithuī, na ndūgatūtware ühītithia-ini.</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake akĩmera atīri: Nĩ mündü ürikü wanyu üngīkorūo </s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>arī na műratawe, nake aathii gwake o .
utukű gatagatī, </s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>amwīre atīrĩ: Mürata wakwa, njohorera mĩgate itatü; </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ gükorűo ndĩ na murata
wakwa ūükīte ügeni, </s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ndirī na irio cia kūmühe; nake ūcio arī nyűmba thĩ inī amücokerie </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>amwīre atīrī: Tiga kündanga: rigī nī itiirie, na tūri ürīriĩ </s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hamwe na twana twakwa; ndihota güükīra ngūnengere? Ngũmwīra atīrī: </s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na atangiükīra amünengere nĩ ündü nĩ müratawe, indi nĩ</s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ündű wa ürīa aramūringīrīria mũno, nĩ egūükīra amühe </s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o iria iműbatairie. Na niĩ ngümwĩra atīrĩ: Hoyai, na nĩ mūküheo; </s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mathai, na nĩ mükuona; ringaringai mürango, na nĩ mükühingũrirũo, Nĩ ũndü </s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o mũndũ ürīa ühoyaga, nĩ aheagwo; na ürīa ümathaga, </s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ onaga; na ürīa üringaringaga, nĩ ahingüragīrüo. </s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na riri, nĩ ürīkü wanyu wĩ ithe wa mündü, na mürű wake angīmwītia mügate, </s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>aamüne ihiga? Kana angīmwītia kīüngüyũ , amüne nyamű-ya-thī handü ha kīüngūyű ?</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ningī angīmwītia itumbī, aamüne kang’aurü? </s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nīguo-rī, mwagīkorūo inyuī, na mürī oru, nĩ mü</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>i kūheaga ciana cianyu iheo njega, </s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>i Ithe wanyu wĩ lgūrü angīkīria atīa kühe </s></f>"},{ID:53,
