Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mühunjia űcio ekuuga; 
i, ti-itherű mothe nī ma tūh</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>m</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>theri, mothe nĩ tüh</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> biũ. 
Ni ündű-ri, he műndű </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ürutaga wīra na üügī, 
o na ümenyi maündü, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ohīgīriire maündũ make mūno; 
no riri, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akaűtigīra műnd</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> ütaűnogeire, űtuñke igai rīake. </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>O naguo ündū ücio no wa tūhũ, na nĩ müüru müno. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ gūkorűo gwītungumania küria aanetungumania </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gükū thĩ 
kwaraga riūa, 
o na gwīthĩnia </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kūrīa 
aanethīnia 
ngoro-rī, 
küműgunīte atīa? </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tondű matukű make mothe no ma thĩna, mĩtangīko yake nĩ ya kümüreherere kīeha; </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>I, ti-itherű, o na ütukū ngoro yake ndīkindagīria. O naguo ündű ūcio, no wa tűhũ.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nīcio ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846></s></f><u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFD8D800><kFFFF0000>THABURI YA GŪCOKERŪO
</k></c></s></f></u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF0000><kFFF2F200>Thaburi 95: 1-2; 6-7; 8-9</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFD8D800><kFFFF0000>ICOKIA</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000> : Tühotithie Mwathani küigwa mügambo waku.</k></s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>1.Ükani, tũkūngūiye Mwathani tukenete, 
tükīanirire ndumba iitü ya ihiga, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yo nyene ūhonokio witü, 
Nĩ tūkinye </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ūthiū-inī wake twī na ngatho, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tũmwanirire na gīkeno 
toktinaga nyimbo cia thaburi.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>ICOKIA</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846> : Tühotithie Mwathani küigwa mügambo waku.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>2.Gīükeni, tũmūthathaiye, tũmūinamirīre; </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nī tūturīrie Mwathani ndu, o ūcio Mūtūūmbi. </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ g</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>korūo we nīwe Ngai witū, 
na nî ithui kirīndī gīake kwīrīthīria, </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nī ithuĩ ng'ondu iria atungataga na guoko gwake.</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFD8D800><kFFFF0000>ICOKIA</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000> : Tühotithie Mwathani küigwa mügambo waku.</k></s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>3.Ümūthī, na arikoruo mwītikira küigua mūgambo wake! </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tigai kūũmia ngoro cianyu, ta üria mwekire kūu Meriba, </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mūthĩ ta ūrīa mwarī Masa, kūu werū-ini; 
hindi irīa </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maithe manyu maangeririe, 
makīndoria, na magīkīona wīko wakwa.</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFD8D800><kFFFF0000>ICOKIA</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000> : Tühotithie Mwathani küigwa mügambo waku.</k></s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFD8D800><kFFFF0000>GĪTHOMO KĪA IGĪRĪ
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF0000><kFFF2F200>Akolosai 
3: 1 - 5. 9- 11</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFF2F200>.</k></s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA MARŪA MA MŪTHURE PAUL KŪRI ANDU A KOLOSI :</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ariŭ a Ithe witū, mūngīkorūo nĩ mwariűkirio hamwe na Kristū, </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>no kīmathagei maündű maria marī Igūrū, </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kūrīa Kristū arī, aikaire guoko-inī kwa ürīo kwa Ngai. </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Rümbűyagiai maűndű marīa marī lgūürū, </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na mūtigage k</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>ũrūmbūyia marīa marī thĩ. </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ni ünd</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> nĩ mwakuire, naguo muoyo wanyu nĩ mūhithe hamwe na Kristū thĩini wa Ngai. </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na rĩrīa Kristũ, o we űri muoyo witű, akona nio, hĩndī îo o na inyuī nĩ mūkonanio hamwe nake mwī na riri. </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ ündū űcio, tuagai ciiga cianyu iria irī gükü thĩ ta ikuīte; </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nacio nĩ ici, atīrī, űmaraya, na meciria mathūku, </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na thuti njūru, nakwīrirīria maūndū moru, 
na gūcumikīra, </s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nakuo no 
ündū ümwe na 
küinamirīra 
mihianano kūmîhoya. </s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tigagai kühenania na 
kanua o műndű na ürĩa üngī, </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kuona atī nĩ mwiaűrīte műndü ürīa wa tene, </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na ciīko ciake, 
na műkehumba mündū üngī mwerū, </s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ürīa werűhagio o nginya agīe na ūmenyo, </s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agakīgīa na műhianīre wa ürīa wamūümbire. </s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na ühoro-inī ücio-rī, 
gūtingīgia na Müyunani kana Mūyahudi; </s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mūndű űruīte käna mūndū ütaruīte; </s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mündű műcenji 
kana Mūthithia; 
o na ngombo kana </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mũndū 
űtarī ngombo; 
no Kristű wiki na nīwe ūiyüire guothe.</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nīcio ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846></s></f><u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF3F3F>RUIMBO RUA INJIRI
</k></c></s></f></u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF0000><kFFF2F200>Marko 1, 15.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alleluya, Alleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Othamaki wa Ngai nĩ űkuhīrīirie : 
wrirei na mwītikie Injiri, </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846></s></f><u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFD8D800><kFFFF0000>GiTHOMO KIA INJIRI
</k></c></s></f></u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF0000><kFFF2F200>Luka 12 : 13 - 21</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFF2F200>.</k></s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GUTHOMA INJIRI YA MŪTHURE LUKA:</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hĩndī io, mündü ümwe wa kīrīndī kīrīa kīarīĩ ho </s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akīmwīra atīrī: 
tūgayane nake igai riitū, </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nowe akímwīra atīrī: 
Mündű űyűũ, </s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nũ ũnduïte mūcirirīri, 
kana mūgayania wa indo cianyu? </s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Agīkīmera atīrī: 
Wimenyagīrīrei nīguo </s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mütikanagīe na riitho rīraya o
atīa: </s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ ündū muoyo wa műndű 
nduonekaga ni ündű </s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wa ürīa indo 
ciingīhīte iria arī nacio.</s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akīmagerekanīria ngerekano akiuga atīri: 
Mügünda wa műndű </s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mūna warī gītonga nī waciarire
mūno:</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> nake akīira na ngoro atīrī: Ngügīka atīa, nĩ ündü ndirĩ na handũ ha kūgethera magetha makwa ? </s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Agīcoka akiuga atirī: Ngwika ūű: nĩ ngūtharithia makümbī makwa, njoke njakithie mangī manene kürĩ mo;</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na nĩ ngaita irio ciakwa ciothe thĩinī wamo, o na indo ciakwa ciothe ndīciige kuo. </s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na ndiīre na ngoro yakwa atīri: 
Ngoro îno, </s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wi na indo nyingi 
njige cia kūigana miaka mĩingī; </s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hurüka, ürīage, na ünyuage, na ücanjamükage. </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>No riri, Ngai akimwira atīiri: 
Wee, kīrimū gīkī, </s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ütukū o üyũ nĩ ugwītio ngoro yaku; 
nacio indo icio wihaiire-ri, igagituika cia ū? </s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na rīrī, o üguo noguo 
mūndũ atariï ürīa wīigagīra </s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>müthithű wa indo we mwene, 
na ndatongete na Uhoro wa Ngai.</s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injiri theru ya Mwathani.</s></f>"}],
Text:"KIUMIA GİA IKÜMI NA INYANYA KIA MWAKA  C"},{Guid:"raivyNMitkqWXLq7Aa4plQ",Verses:[],
Text:"DOMINIKA YA KUMI NA TISA MWAKA C"},{Guid:"TzUZhLi+pkChXJW8QuI+rw",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846></s></f><u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>KIUMIA KIA 
MIRONGO IRI NA IMWE 
KIA MWAKA C</k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>GITHOMO KIA MBERE
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFD80000><kFFF2F200>Isaia 66: 18 - 21.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŪTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RIA MURATHI ISAIA :</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani Ngai ekuuga üű : 
nĩ njüi mawira mao marīa marutaga, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na meciria mao; na riri, 
ihinda nĩ rigūűka riria ngacokanirīria </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndūrirī ciothe hamwe o na andū a miario yothe, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nao nĩ magoka meyonere ürīa riri wakwa ütarii. </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na nii nĩ ngaiga kīmenyithia gatagatīinī kao, 
nao andu arīa makahonoka thĩinī wao </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndīmaharaganīrie ndūrīri-inī; 
nao nĩ makoimbūranīra ndūrīrī- inī</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ūhoro wa ürīa riri ücio wakwa ūtarii, 
Nao nĩ makarehe ariü a Ithe wanyu </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>othe moime ndūrīrī-inī ciothe, 
matuike ta marī igongona rĩa kürutīrūo Mwathani; </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nao magoka mahaicīte mbarathi, 
o na ngari cia ita, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na moke makuuītwo na itanda cia gücuhio, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na nyūmbű, o na ngamīra iria ithiaga
na ihenya, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>makinyio kirīma-inī gīakwa kirīa kīamüre o kūu </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Jerusalemu; 
üguo nīguo Mwathani ekuuga. </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nao makarehwo o ta ürīa cianá cia lsraeli 
itwaraga kindü giacio gia küruta igongona </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gīkuuïtwo na kīndū gītheru gigatwarūo </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nyūmba ya Mwathani.
O naho harī andū acio-rī, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ ho ngeamūrira andū matuike athinjĩri-Ngai, 
o na matuike alawi.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nīcio ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>THABURI YA GŪCOKERUO
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFD80000><kFFF2F200>Thaburi 117: 1; 2.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFD80000><kFFF2F200>ICOKIA: </k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Ndüriri ciothe ikügoocage We Mwathani.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>1. Kigoocei Mwathani, inyui ndūriri, mũri inyuothe;</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kuraha mümūrahe, inyuī andū a iruka ciothe</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFD80000><kFFF2F200>ICOKIA: </k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Ndüriri ciothe ikügoocage We Mwathani</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>2.Tondū ūtugi wake nĩ kūneneha ūtūnenehagira; 
naguo ühoro wa Mwathani, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o ūguo ũri wa
ma, nī wa tene na tene.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFD80000><kFFF2F200>ICOKIA: </k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Ndüriri ciothe ikügoocage We Mwathani</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>GITHOMO KIA IGIRI
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFD80000><kFFF2F200>Aheberea 12: 5 - 7. 11 - 13</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GUTHOMA MARUA MARIA MAANDĪKĪIRUO AHEBEREA</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ariū a Ithe witū, 
nĩ müriganīirūo nĩ uhoro wa kūmūhatirīria </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>üria mütaaragwo naguo ta 
Mwi ciana, műkerūo atirī: </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mürü wakwa, menya gükaira iherithia rīa </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani, 
kana ūürũo nĩ hinya warüithio nīwe. </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ gükorūo ürīa Mwathani endete, 
nīwe aherithagia, </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na akah</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>ra mwana o
wothe ūria etīkagira. </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Inyuï nĩ mūkiragirīria ni getha mūrutagwo o mūkīherithagio; </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ngai amwikaga o ta mūrī ciana ciake: 
nĩ ündű-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ mwana ürīkũ ütaherithagio akirutwo nĩ Ithe ?</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Küherithio o guothe kuonagwo 
o ihinda rīakuo ta gūtari gikeno, tiga o kieha: </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>no riri, thuthaini nĩ kürehagīre andü arīa mamenyeretio nakuo mnaciaro me na thayū, </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>marĩa moimanīte na üthingu. 
Nĩ ündü ücio-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tambūrükiai moko marīa macunjurīte, </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na maru maria maregerete na mwirũngarīrie njīra cia makinya manyu, </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nī getha kīrīa gīthuaga gītikagonyorūo, no kaba kīhonio.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icío nĩcio ciugo cia Mwathani,</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>RUIMBO RUA INJIRI
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFD80000><kFFF2F200>Luka 13, 29.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alleluya, Alleluya, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Andū othe nī magoka moimīte 
kūrīa irathīro na itherero, </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na maikare thi
ūthamaki-inī wa Ngai, </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alleluya. Alleluya</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>GITHOMO KIA INJIRI
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFD80000><kFFF2F200>Luka 13: 22 - 30.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GUTHOMA INJIRI YA MUTHURE LUKA :</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hĩndī īo Yesu agīthianga, 
akīhunguraga matūüüra na mĩcii, </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akīrutanaga ühoro, erekeire Jerusalem.</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na mũndū ümwe akīmūüria atīrī: 
Mwathani, </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>andű arīa mekühonokio-ī, anga nĩ anyinyi ?</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake akīmera atīrīĩ: 
Geragiai na hinya mūtonyere </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mūromo ūrīa mūceke; 
nĩ gūkorūo ngūmwīra
atiri: </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ ündü aingī magacaria ürīa mangītonya, na matihote. </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hĩndī iria mwene nyūmba agakorüo okirite, 
na arīkitie kūhinga műrango-rī, </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mügaitīka kūrügama o nja mūkīringaringaga mürango, mūkiugaga atīrī: </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani, tūhingūrīre; 
nake nī akamūcokeria amwīre atīrī: </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndimüüi kürīa muumite. 
Hindī io nĩ mügaitika kuuga atīrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ twarīaga na tūkanyua wee ūrī 
o ho, o nawe nĩ warutanaga ing’aratua-inī ciitű; </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nake nī akoiga atīrī: Ngümwĩra atīrī, ndikīūï kūrīa muumīte; </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>umai kūrī niĩ inyuĩ othe mwikaga waganu. </s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na kūu nīkuo gūükagīa kīrīro na kühagarania magego, </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>rirīa mükona Abraham na Isaaka na Jakobu, na anabii othe, marī üthamaki-inī wa</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ngai, na inyui ene mügakorüo müikanītio na nja. </s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nao andü nĩ magoka moimīte kürīa irathīro
na kürīa ithüiro, </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na gathigathini na gūthini, na maikare thĩ üthamaki-inī wa Ngai. </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na rirī, nĩ kūri andū a thutha magatuika a mbere, </s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na nĩ kürī andü a mbere magatuīka a thutha.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nīcio ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"}],
Text:"KIUMIA KIA MIRONGO IRI NA IMWE KIA MWAKA C
"},{Guid:"4eH1dC8tck2EK5ZhCdP0tg",Verses:[{
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>DOMINIKA YA ISHIRINI NA MOJA MWAKA C</k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>SOMO LAKWANZA
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>Isaya 66:18-21</k></c></s></f>",IsDisplayed:0},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika kitabu cha Nabii Isaya</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Bwana asema hivi:
Nami nayajua matendo yao na mnawazo yao,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nami nimekuja kuwakusanya watu wa lugha zote;
watakuja kuuona utukufu wangu.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nitaweka ishara, kati yao wale waliookoka,
nitawatuma kwa mataifa ya Tarshishi,</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Puti, Ludi, Mosoki, Tubali, Yavani
na nchi za </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>pwani za mbali zisizosikia bado habari zangu</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wala kuona utukufu wangu;
nao watawahubiria mataifa utukufu wangu.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na kutoka mataifa yote, wataleta matoleo kwa Bwana,</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>watawarudisha ndugu zenu wote: juu ya farasi, katika magari,</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na machela, juu ya nyumbu au juu ya ngamia,</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mpaka mlima wangu mtakatifu pale Yerusalemu, asema Bwana,</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kama wana wa Israeli wanavyotolea hekaluni kwa Bwana,
matoleo yao katika vyombo safi.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na baadhi yao nitawatwaa wawe makuhani na Walawi,
asema Bwana.</s></f>",IsDisplayed:0},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>Zaburi 117:1, 2</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFF2F200> (
</k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846>K. Marko 16:15)</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K, </s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Nendeni duniani kote, mkaihubiri injili.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>1.Msifuni Bwana, enyi mataifa yote!
Mtukuzeni Bwana, enyi watu wote! K.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K, </s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Nendeni duniani kote, mkaihubiri injili.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>2.Maana wema wake kwetu sisi ni mkuu,
na uaminifu wa Bwana ni wa milele. K.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K, </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Nendeni duniani kote, mkaihubiri injili.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>SOMO LA PILI
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>Waebrania 12:5-7. 1-1</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika barua kwa Waebrania</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndugu zangu:
Tayari mmeyasahau yale maonyo yasemayo </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nanyí kama kusema
na wana, yaani: </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>“Mwanangu, usiyadharau adhabu ya Bwana, wala</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>usikate tamaa anapokurekebisha. Kwaní Bwana akimpenda mtu</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>humpa nidhamu, humwadhibu kila amkubaliye kuwa mwanawe</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Vumilieni adhabu kwani ní fundisho”.
Mungu huwatendea kama wana.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Je, kuna “mwana” gani asiyeadhibiwa na baba yake?</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kila adhabu yaonekana wakati wake kuleta huzuni, si furaha</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Lakini baadaye itawapatia 
wenye kuizoea </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mavuno ya amani na
uadilifu. </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa hiyo imarisheni mikono milegevu na magoti dhaifu</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Isawazishieni miguu yenu njia, ili kilicho kiwete kisiteguke, bali
kipone.</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>SHANGILIO LA INJILI
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846>Yohane 14-6</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Aleluya.</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000> W. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Aleluya.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mimi ndimi njia na ukweli na uzima asema bwana </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<kFFF2F200></k><fArial Black><s1846>Hakuna ajaye kwa Baba, ila kwa njia yangu mimi.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>W. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Aleluya.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>INJILI
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>Luka 13:22-30</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Luka</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakati ule:
Katika safari yake ya kwenda Yerusalemu, [Yesu] alipita katika</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>miji na vijiji akifundisha. Mtu mmoja akamwuliza
Bwana, wenye kuokoka ni wachache tu?”</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akawajibu,
Fanyeni bidii kuingia kwa kupitia mlango mwembamba, kwa</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maana nawaambieni, wengi watajaribu kuingia wasiweze. Mwenye</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nyumba atakapokuwa amesimama na kufunga mlango, mtaanza</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kusimama nje na kubisha mlangoni na kuita, Bwana, utufungulie.”</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Naye atajibu na kuwaambia, ‘Sijui mlikotoka.</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndipo mtakapoanza kusema, Tulikula na kunywa mbele yako,</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ulifundisha katika barabara zetu. Naye atasema, ‘Sijui mmetoka
wapi. </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ondokeni kwangu, ninyi nyote mtendao maovu!’”</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndipo kutakuwa kulia machozi na kusaga meno, mtakapomwona</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Abrahamu, na Isaka, na Yakobo, na manabii wote katika ufalme wa</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mungu, nanyi wenyewe mmetupwa nje.</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Watu watakuja toka mashariki na magharibi, na toka kaskazini na
kusini, </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kukaa mezani katika ufalme wa Mungu.</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tazama, walio wa mnwisho watakuwa wa kwanza, na walio wa
kwanza watakuwa wa mwisho.”</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f>"}],
Text:"DOMINIKA YA ISHIRINI NA MOJA MWAKA C"},{Guid:"l0Dn3wZnz0G87NVsIAzerQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846></s></f><u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>KIUMIA KIA 
MIRONGO IRÍ 
NA IGIRI KIA 
MWAKA C</k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>GITHOMO KIA MBERE
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>Sirach 3: 17-18. 20. 28 - 29 .</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GUTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RIA SIRACH</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwana wakwa, tuika mūndü mwīnyihia rīrīa ükūruta mawīra maku, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na nī ūkwendwo nī mūndū
mwendeke nĩ Ngai.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ona üngīkorūo üri mūnene atīa üguo noguo </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ūbataire gükorūo ūrī mūndū mwīnyihia, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na nĩ ürīonekaga ürī mwendekanu maitho-inī ma Mwathani; </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ amu 
enyihia nĩ o mamūkumithagia</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ngoro ya mūndū muügī Tooranagia no ngerekano cia ūügī, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gūtũ kwa mūndū mūthikīriria wa maündū wendagwo nī mündű mūügī</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Maaī nī mahoragia mwaki mwakanu, kūguna andū nī kwiherithia mawīhia,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nīcio ciugo cia Mwathani,.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>THABURI YA GUCOKERŪO
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>Thaburi 68: 3; 4a,c; 5-6a; 9-10.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>ICOKIA: Wee Mwathani, nīwe Ithe wa arīa ahoreri.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>1.Aria athingu marokena, gūkenūka ni makenīke, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>me mbere-inĩ ya Ngai: ini, o na
nî makengeūke.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>ICOKIA: Wee Mwathani, nīwe Ithe wa arīa ahoreri.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Inirai Ngai, inai mūkumie riitwa riake, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Riitwa rīake-rī, nĩ Mwathani; gikenürürūkei
mbere-ini yake.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>ICOKIA: Wee Mwathani, nīwe Ithe wa arīa ahoreri.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>2.Nĩwe ithe wa ciana cia ngoriai, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na hari atumia a ndigwa nī mūümatuiri cira na kihooto, </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o wee
Ngai, kūu aikaraga, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gitüüro giake githeru, </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ngai-ī, arīa et</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>ria-githũnũ atūmaga magie na micii</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>andū aria ohe 
amarutaga korokoro 
akamoimiria 
wega-inī.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>ICOKIA: Wee Mwathani, nīwe Ithe wa arīa ahoreri.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>3.Wee  Ngai, nĩ waminjaminjaga mbura ya ütana, </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kűnogora nĩ wanogoraga igai rīaku riria rianoga</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Thamna yaku igikīgīa na Gikaro; </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tondű wa wega waku, Ngai, ugikībatūra athini acio.</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>ICOKIA: Wee Mwathani, nīwe Ithe wa arīa ahoreri.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>GiTHOM0 KIA IGIRĪ
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>Aheberea 12: 18- 19, 22 - 24.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŪTHOMA MARUA MARIA MAANDIKIIRŪO KŪRĪ ANDŪ AHEBEREA :</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ariū a Ithe witū, inyuī mūtikinyīte </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kīrīma-inī kīrīa kīngīhutīika na gīakanīte mwaki, </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kana mügakinya kūrīa kwī na itu rīthimbu, na ,</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kīhuhūkanio, na 
mügambīre wa coro, o na mügambo ükiaria. </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Naguo arīa naaūiguire-rī, magīthaithana atī </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>matigacoke kūheo ühoro üngi o na ümwe. </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Indī inyui- rī, mükinyīte kīrima-inī kīria gĩa Sion, </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o itüūra-inī ria Ngai üria ūtäire muoyo, </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>narīo nirío Jerusalem, itüüra o riria ría igürü, </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mūgakinya küria kwī araika ngiri itangīgeraka</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>marürünganīte kīüngano kīnene, </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na gwī kanitha wa marigithathi arīa maandkītwo kūria Igūrū,</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ningi kūrī Ngai mūtuīri andū othe cira, </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na kūrī mīoyo ya andū athingu arīa matuīkīte aagiriru kūna,</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na kūrĩ Yesu, műiguithania wa kīrikanīro kīrĩa kīerū, </s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na thakame ya kūminjaminijanírio rīa îheanaga mohoro mega kūrī irīa ya Habel.</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nicio ciugo cia Mwathani,</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>RUIMBO RUA INJIRI
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>Luka 4, 18.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alleluya, Alleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani nĩ aanjitīrīirie maguta “hunjagirie arīa athĩni Ohoro  urīa  mwega,</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o nao arĩa mohutwo korokoro-inī ndimere atī nĩ mahingüriirūo, </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alleluya, Alleluya</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>GITHOMO KĪA INJIRI
</k></c></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFFF3F3F><kFFF2F200>Luka 14: 1, 7- 14.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:26,
