Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake akīira arīa metītwo ngerekano, </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ona üria maathuraga itī cia mbere maikarīre cio; </s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agīkīmera atiri: </s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Rīrĩa ügwītwo nĩ mũndű üthii iruga-inī rĩa kīhikanio, </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndūgaikarīre gitī kīrīa kia 
mbere :</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gütigatuike hihi atī nĩ harĩ mündū üngī mūtie kūrī we, </s></f>"},{ID:35,
