Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ūcio 
umwīitite inyuerī oka, akwire atirī: </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ta eheherera mūndū űyū; na hĩndī io ūcoke 
güikarao </s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gatung’a ka arīa angī othe, üconokete. No rirīa wītītwo-rī, </s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>thi</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> üikare o gatűng’a ka arīa angī; </s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ getha ürīa ügwītīte oka, akwīre atīrī: Wathiomo, </s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ta hītüka na harīa mbere: na hīĩndī io ügĩe na </s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gĩtio mbere ya aria othe müikarainie nao, </s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ gükorūo o mūndü ürīa wītüügagīria nĩ </s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akanyihio
nake ürīa winyihagia-rī, nīwe ügatūügīrio,</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Agīcoka akīīra mündū ürīa wamwītīte atīrī: </s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Waruga iruga ria mūthenya, kana rīa hwaī- inī, </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tigaga
gwīta o arata aku, kana ariū a nyūkwa, </s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kana andū anyu, o na kana itonga cia kwanyu; </s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gūtigatuï‘ke atī andū acio nao nĩ magacoka gūgwīta o nawe maruga-inī mao, </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nawe űthukīrűo. No rirī, waruga iruga-i, itaga ngīa, na cionje, na ithua, </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na atumumu: nawe nĩ ükarathimwo; 
nĩ gükorūo matirī na kīndū gīa gūgüthukīra nakīo: </s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>amu nīĩ ügathukīrüo hĩndĩ îria andű arīa athingu makariükio.</s></f>"},{ID:36,
