Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake tene ndaarī na kīene harī wee,</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>no riu nĩ mũndū wĩ na kīene harī wee o na harī niī, </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake niwe üy</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> ndamūcokia kürī wee, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na nota gūtūma ndagūtūmīra ngoro yakwa mwene.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na nĩ ingīendete tüikare nake, </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ getha andungatagīre ithenya rīaku</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kīoho-inī gīikī njohetwo nī ündū wa Uhoro-üria-Mwega. </s></f>"},{ID:19,
