mwende müno. </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na iri, akorüo rĩ mündű mwende müno nĩ nii-ri, </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>githti ndaagīrīirüo nĩ kwendwo nīwe müno makīria ühoro-inī wa mwiri,</s></f>"},{ID:28,
