mūtí wake wa kwambĩrūo anūmīrīre, </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndangīhota gūtuika mūrutwo wakwa. </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ ündū-ī, nĩ mūndū  uriku wanyu, </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akīenda gwaka nyumba ndaya na igūrū, ūtangīamba gūikara thĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agatare mbia iria cia kumiakithia, amenye kana </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>arī na cia kūigana cia kümīrikia? </s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ekaga üguo, gūtikae gūtiīka ati,
aarikia gwaka </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gītina kiayo na aremwo nĩ kümīrīkia, </s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>andū arīa othe marīmīonaga maitīke kümūthekorera. </s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>makiugaga atīrī : </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kai mündu üyũ nĩ aambĩrīirie </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gwaka nyūmba, akīremwo ni kūmīrikia I . </s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kana nĩ műthamaki ūrīkü, </s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hĩndī îrīa angīthii kürūa ita na mūthamaki üngī, </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ütangīamba güikara thĩ macokanie ndundu na andü ake, </s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>amenye kana aahota kürüa na m</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>thamaki üria </s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ügüüka e na andŭ a ita ngiri mirongo irī, </s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nake we mwene akīri o na ngiri ikümi ? </s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake angīona ati ndangīho ta üguo, </s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hĩndī io, ūcio ūngī arī o küraya, </s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>amürekerie arekio, makamüürie ürīa angihakwo kügīe na thayū. </s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hakīrī üguo-rī, mūndū o wothe wanyu ütangīrekia indo ciothe iria ari</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nacio, ndangīhota gūtuīka műrutwo wakwa.</s></f>"},{ID:46,
