Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Isaya 
40:1- 5, 9-11</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Somo katika kitabu cha Nabii Isaya</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Watulizeni, wapeni tulizo watu wangu,asema Mungu wenu.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Semeni na moyo wa Yerusalemu,utangazieni ya kwamba:</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>huduma yake ngumu imekwisha, dhambi yake imeondolewa, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>maana kwa mkono wa Bwana amepokea</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>adhabu maradufu kwa maovu yake yote.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mtu analia:
tengenezeni jangwani njia ya Bwana!</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nyosheni nyikani barabara kwa Mungu wetu! Kila bonde lifukiwe,</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> kila mlima na kilima kishushwe, Njia zenye kupotoka zinyoshwe,</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na njia zenye mashimo zisawazishwe.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Hapo utukufu wa Bwana utafunuliwa,</s></f>"},{ID:9,
