Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Yerusalemu habari njema! Paza sauti, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>usiogope!  Sema kwa miji ya Yuda:</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tazama, Mungu wenu! Yupo hapa Bwana Mungu: </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>anakuja kwa uwezo, na mkono wake utatawala;</s></f>"},{ID:11,
