 27- 28, 29-30 </s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>K;Umsifu Bwana, ee roho yangu:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ee Bwana, Mungu wangu u mkuu sana!</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Umejivika fahari na adhama,
umejivika mwanga kama vazi.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Umetandaza anga kama hema. </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>K;Umsifu Bwana, ee roho yangu:</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Umeweka nguzo za ghorofa zake juu ya maji.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Umefanya mawingu kuwa gari lako,</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>umekwenda juu ya mbawa za upepo.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Umefanya pepo kuwa wajumbe wako,</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na ndimi za moto, kuwa watumishi wako. </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>K;Umsifu Bwana, ee roho yangu:</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ee Bwana, jinsi gani zilivyo nyingi kazi zako!
 </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Zote umezifanya kwa hekima,
dunia imejaa viumbe vyako.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Bahari iko kule, kubwa na pana sana!</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ndimo mlimo viendavyo bila idadi,</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>viumbe hai vidogo na vikubwa. </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>K;Umsifu Bwana, ee roho yangu:</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hao wote hukutazamia wewe</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>uwape chakula chao kwa wakati wake.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wewe huwapa, nao wanakiokota;</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wewe unakunjua mkono wako, nao wanashiba mema. </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>K;Umsifu Bwana, ee roho yangu:</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ukiuficha uso wako, wanafadhaika.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ukiondoa pumzi yao, wanakufa,</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na kuyarudia mavumbi yao.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ukiipeleka roho yako wanaumbwa,</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na unafanya upya uso wa nchi.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>K;Umsifu Bwana, ee roho yangu:</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SOMO 2</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tito 2:1114</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Somo katika barua ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Tito</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mpendwa: Neema ya Mungu imetokea kwa kuwaokoa watu wote.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nayo inatuongoza kuzuia yasiyo ya Mungu,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na kupinga tamaa za kidunia, tupate kuishi duniani hapa kwa kiasi,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
