Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> mfano wa njiwa. Tena sauti ikatoka mbinguni ikinena, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>\"Wewe ndiwe Mwanangu mpendwa,  nimependezwa nawe.\"</s></f>"},{ID:8,
