Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nikupe nchi hii iwe yako.\" Abramu akamwambia, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>\"Ee Bwana, nitajuaje ya kuwa nitapewa  iwe yangu?\"</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Akamwambia: Unipatie ndama wa miaka mitatu, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mbuzi jike wa miaka mitatu, kondoo dume wa miaka mitatu, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>hua na mwana njiwa. Abramu akamletea wanyama hao wote, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akawapasua katikati, akaweka kila kipande kuelekeana</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na kingine; lakini ndege hakuwapasua. Na tai wakaishukia </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ile mizoga, lakini Abramu akawafukuza. </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Jua lilipokuwa likishuka, usingizi mzito ukamshika Abramu, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na hofu na giza vikamwangukia. Jua lilipokwisha kushuka, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na giza kuenea, tanuri ya moshi na mwenge wa moto vikapita </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kati ya vipande vile vya nyama. Siku ile Bwana akafanya agano </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na Abramu akisema:
“Nimeupatia uzao wako nchi hii, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kutoka mto wa Misri, mpaka mto mkubwa, Mto Eufrate.\"</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA                                      Zaburi 27:1,7-8, 9abc,3-14(K 1a)</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kiitikio: Bwana ni mwanga wangu na wokovu wangu.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Bwana ni mwanga wangu na wokovu wangu;nimwogope nani?</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Bwana ni kinga ya uzima wangu,
nimhofu nani? </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kiitikio: Bwana ni mwanga wangu na wokovu wangu.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ee Bwana, usikie sauti yangu ninapokulilia; unihurumie, unijibu.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Moyo wangu unasema, \"Njoo utafute uso wake Mungu.” </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nitautafuta uso wako, ee Bwana! </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kiitikio: Bwana ni mwanga wangu na wokovu wangu.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Usinifiche uso wako; usimkatae kwa hasira mtumishi wako.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wewe ndiwe msaada wangu;
usinitupe; </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wala usiniache Mwokozi wangu! (K)</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kiitikio; Bwana ni mwanga wangu na wokovu wangu.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Naamini ya kuwa nitauona wema wa Bwana katika nchi ya walio hai.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Umngoje Bwana, uwe hodari;
ujipe moyo, naam, umngoje Bwana! </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kiitikio: Bwana ni mwanga wangu na wokovu wangu.</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SOMO LA PILI
Wafilipi 3:17-4:1</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Somo katika barua ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Wafilipi</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ndugu, mniige mimi!
Waangalieni wale wanaopanga </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mwenendo wao kadiri ya mfano tuliowapeni. </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Maana wengi - nimewaambieni mara nyingi, na sasa </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nawaambia kwa machozi - huishi kama adui wa msalaba wa Kristo.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwisho wao ni uharibifu; mungu wao ni tumbo; hujisifia aibu yao, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akili zao ni kwenye mambo ya dunia. Bali kwetu ni mbinguni;</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na kutoka mbinguni atakuja Mwokozi, Bwana Yesu Kristo, tunayemtazamia. </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Naye ataubadili mwili wetu wa unyonge, upate kufanana na mwili </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wake wa utukufu. Atafanya hayo kwa enzi ile </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>inayomwezesha kuuweka ulimwengu wote chini ya </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mamlaka yake. Basi, ndugu zangu wapendwa niwatunukao sana, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mlio furaha yangu na taji langu, simameni </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>imara katika Bwana, enyi wapendwa.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SHANGILIO LA INJILI</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Sifa na utukufu kwako, ee Kristo.</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Sauti ya Baba ikatoka katika wingu lile jeupe ikisema, </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Huyu ni mwanangu mpendwa, msikilizeni yeye.</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Sifa na utukufu kwako, ee Kristo.</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>INJILI
Luka 9:28b-36</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Luka</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wakati ule Yesu aliwachukua Petro na Yohane na Yakobo,</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akapanda mlimani ili asali. Alipokuwa akisali, sura ya uso </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wake ikageuka, mavazi yake yakawa meupe na kung'aa. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mara watu wawili walikuwa wakizungumza naye, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ndio Musa na Eliya, walionekana katika utukufu, wakanena </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>juu ya kutoka kwake atakakotimiza Yerusalemu.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Petro na wenzake walikuwa wameshikwa na usingizi,</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>lakini walipoamka, waliona utukufu wake na wale watu 
wawili wakisimama </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>naye. Nao walipotaka kuagana naye, Petro alimwambia Yesu, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>“Mwalimu, ni vizuri kwetu kukaa hapa; tutanjenga vibanda vitatu,</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kimoja chako, kimoja cha Musa na kimoja cha Eliya.” Lakini </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>hakujua alilosema.
Aliposema hayo, likatokea wingu likawatia uvuli, nao </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wakaogopa walipoingia katika wingu hilo.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kisha sauti ikatoka katika wingu ikisema, “Huyu ni mwanangu </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mpendwa, msikilizeni yeye.” Sauti ilipomaliza </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kusema, Yesu alionekana peke yake. Nao wakashika </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>siri juu ya mambo hayo waliyoyaona, wala </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>hawakumwambia mtu wakati ule.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f>"}],
Text:"DOMINIKA YA PILI YA KWARESIMA MWAKA C"},{Guid:"g7+F95ePNk6j3eKi2jqRjw",Verses:[{Style:{Background:{Image:"sunsea5.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GĨTHOMO KĨA MBERE 
Isaya. 62:1-5</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA MŨRATHI ISAIA: </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Atĩrĩrĩ, ha ũhoro wa kũrũĩrĩra Sion, ndigatumia kanua, o na kana ndigithĩrie gũtetera Jerusalem, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o nginya hĩndĩ ĩrĩa ũhoro wakuo wa ũthingu ũkoimbũka ware o ta ũtheri,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o naguo ũhoro wakuo wa kũhonokania woneke o ta tawa ũrĩa </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wakanaga mũno. Nacio ndũrĩrĩ nĩ ikona ũthingu waku, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o nao athamaki othe mone riri waku; </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wee nawe ũcoke gwĩtwo rĩĩtwa rĩngĩ rĩkagwetwo na kanua ka Mwathani.  </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ningĩ ũgatuĩka ta tanji ya ũthaka ũnyitĩtwo na guoko kwa Mwathani,</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ũhaane ta thũmbĩ ya ũthamaki ĩnyitĩtwo na guoko kwa Ngai waku.  </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wee nawe-rĩ, ndũgacoka gwĩtwo Mũtirike, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na kana bũrũri waku wĩtwo Mũkiru Ihooru; na rĩrĩ, ũrĩĩtagwo Hefiziba, o </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>naguo bũrũri waku wĩtagwo Beula; nĩ gũkorũo Mwathani nĩ akenagio nĩwe, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o naguo bũrũri waku ũgatuĩka o ta mũhiki ũrĩa ũhikĩtio.  Nĩ gũkorũo o ta </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũrĩa mwanake ahikagia mũirĩtu, ũguo noguo aanake aku magakũhikia,</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> ningĩ o ta ũrĩa mũhikania ekenagĩra nĩ mũhiki wake-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o ũguo noguo Ngai waku arĩĩkenagĩra nĩwe.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO
Thaburi 96:1 na 3;4-5;7-8;9-10</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA 
 Rahai Mwathani atĩ nĩwe wĩ riri na ena hinya</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ĩ itĩkai kũinĩra Mwathani rũĩmbo rũerũ! Mũinĩre Mwathani, inyuĩ andũ othe a thĩ. </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ganai ũhoro wa riri wake ndũrĩrĩ-inĩ, mawĩko make ma magegania</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mũkĩmaganĩre iruka ciothe cia andũ.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA 
 Rahai Mwathani atĩ nĩwe wĩ riri na ena hinya</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ ũndũ Mwathani nĩ mũnene, na nĩ wa kũgoocwo mũno: we nĩ wa gwĩtigĩrũo gũkĩra ngai ciothe.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Thima-rĩ, ngai icio ciothe cia irĩndĩ no indo itarĩ kĩene, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ĩndĩ Mwathani nĩwe wombire igũrũ.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA 
Rahai Mwathani atĩ nĩwe wĩ riri na ena hinya</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Rahai Mwathani, inyuĩ mĩhĩrĩga yothe ya irĩndĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>rahai Mwathani atĩ nĩwe wĩ riri na e na hinya.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Rahai Mwathani nĩ kũgwetaga riri wa rĩĩtwa rĩake: </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũkai na ihaki, mũgĩtonye nja-inĩ ciake.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA 
Rahai Mwathani atĩ nĩwe wĩ riri na ena hinya</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tetemekai mwĩ mbere yake, inyuĩ andũ othe a thĩ. Ugai ndũrĩrĩ-inĩ atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ hĩndĩ Mwathani agwatĩte gũthamaka; ĩĩ-ni, thĩ nĩ kũrũmio ĩrũmĩtio, ũndũ</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> ĩtangĩenyenyeka; arĩciragĩra irĩndĩ ciakuo o ũrĩa kwerekereire.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA 
Rahai Mwathani atĩ nĩwe wĩ riri na ena hinya</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1384>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ
1 Akorintho 12:4-11</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE  PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A KORINTHO MARĨA MA MBERE:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, iheo iria iheanagwo ciumanĩte na Wega wa Ngai nĩ mĩthemba-mĩthemba, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>no rĩrĩ, Muoyo mwene cio no ũmwe.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>  Mĩtungatĩre o nayo nĩ mĩthemba-mĩthemba, na Mwathani mwene yo no ũmwe.  </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>O nayo mĩĩkĩre ya maũndũ nĩ ĩtiganĩte mĩthemba,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> ĩndĩ Ngai no ũmwe, ũcio wĩkithagia maũndũ macio mothe thĩinĩ wa andũ  othe. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> No rĩrĩ, mũndũ o mũndũ aheagwo ũndũ wake ũrĩa wonanagia atĩ arĩ na Muoyo nĩ getha </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũndũ ũcio ũgune andũ othe.  Tondũ wa kũheo nĩ Muoyo-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mũndũ ũmwe agĩaga na ũhoro wa kwaria ũrĩ ũũgĩ; </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũngĩ akagĩa na ũhoro ũrĩ ũmenyi mũkinyanĩru werekanĩrĩire </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na wa Muoyo  oro ũcio; nake ũngĩ akaheo wĩtĩkio , </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ ũndũ wa Muoyo o oro ũcio; ũngĩ akaheo ũhoti wa </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kũhonania mĩrimũ, no ũndũ wa Muoyo o ũcio  ũmwe; </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ũngĩ nake akaheo ũhoti wa kũringa ciama,</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> ũngĩ ũrathi, ũngĩ ũhoti wa gũkũũrana mioyo; ũngĩ gũthioma thiomi, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ũngĩ ũtaũri ahote gũtaũra thiomi icio.  No rĩrĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maũndũ macio mothe no wĩra wa Muoyo o ro ũcio ũmwe, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akĩgayagĩra andũ o ta ũrĩa ekwenda, o mũndũ mwanya, o mũndũ mwanya.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI
John 2:11</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>	
Alleluya. Alleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu nĩ ekire ũguo kũu Kana ya Galilea, </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akĩambĩrĩria ciama ciake, agĩkĩonania ũnene wake; </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nao arutwo ake makĩya kũmwĩhoka.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alleluia</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>INJIRI
JOHANA 2;1-11</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ningi muthenya wagatatu gukigia na kihikanio kundu </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gwitagwo Kana ya Galili, nake nyina wa Jesu aari ho;</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> o naJesunakenietiruo, naarutwoake, mathiikihikaniokiu.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nayondibeiyaagakumaigana, nyina wa Jesu akimwira atiri, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Matiri na ndibei.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Nake Jesu akimwira, Mutu mia uyu, uhoro niu riku witu nawe? </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ihinda riakwa ritiri rirakinya. Nyina agikiir andu ngata atiriri, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>O uria ekumwira, ikaiguo.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Na riri kwari ndigithu ithathatu cia mahiga ciaigitwo kuo niundu wamitugo ya Ayahudi yagwitheria,</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> imwe no guthirira mai ma mutungi uria munene maita meri kana matatu. </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake Jesu akimera atiri, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Iyuria indigithu icio mai. Magigiciiyuria o riita. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Agicoka akimera atiri, Riu tahiai, mutwarire mutabania wa iruga.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Nao makimutwarira. Mutabania wairuga nake aacama mai macio </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>matuikite ndibei, nandamenye haia yumite [indindungata iria ciatahite mai, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>cio nicia menyaga ucio mutabania wairuga agiita muhikania, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akimwira atiri, Mundu aambaga kuruta ndibei iria njega;</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> na andu maarikia kunyua muno, akaruta iria itari njega muno; </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wee-ri, ukuigite ndibei iria njega ukamiruta riu.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Jesu niekire uguo kuu Kana ya Galili, akiambiriria ciama ciake, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agikionania unene wake; nao arutwo akemaki yakumwihoka.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
