Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika barua ya kwanza ya Mtakatifu Paulo
kwa Wakorintho</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndugu zangu: Niliyowakabidhi ninyi ndiyo niliyoyapokea mimi kwa Bwana,</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yaani usiku ule aliposalitiwa, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu alitwaa mkate, akashukuru,
akaumega, akasema,</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Huu ndio mwili wangu unaotolewa kwa ajili yenu: </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>fanyeni hivi
katika ukumbusho wangu.\"</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kadhalika akatwaa kikombe baada va kula, akasema,</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Kikombe
hiki ni agano jipya katika damu yangu. </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kila mnapokinywea
fanyeni hivi katika ukumbusho wangu.\"</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Maana kila mnapoula mkate huo na kukinywea kikombe,</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mnatangaza kifo cha Bwana hata atakapokuja.</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana..</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SEKWENSIA</s></f>"},{ID:36,
