Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mkombozi na Mwalimu apitaye kila sifa,</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa nyimbo na shangwe kuu,</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>itokayo kwa watu,
Nia yetu ya kusifu,</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Iishe hili walipewa,
hasa mkate Mtakatifu, </s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wale kumi na wawili, uletao uzima,</s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Karamuni mwa mwisho.</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Shangilio la rohoni,
Iipendeze liwe zuri,</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Sifa tele livune, ipo leo siku kubwa,</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa kumbusho la kuwekwa,</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwanza ile karamu.
Muda ule umekwisha,</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ipo meza ya mfalme, Na sheria mpya, </s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tumepata mapya yote. Nuru, sio nusu giza,</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwanga sio usiku.
Tendo lake karamuni, </s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kristo ametuamuru, 
utende tumkumbuke,</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wafuata amri yake, 
ukitoa hii sadaka,</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa mkate na divai.
Mkate wageuka</s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na divai ikawa damu
Kanuni kwa Wakristo,</s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>huelewi huioni, kweli hio; hukubali,</s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Maana ni muujiza mkuu unaota tu maumbo,</s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ni alama zifumbazo,
Utukufu wenyewe,</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ule mwili unywe damu,
Kila umbo linafumba,</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu mzima halisi-
Ukipewa tu kimego,</s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Umempata Yesu mzima, si sehemu yake tu,</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Moja hula, elfu hula,
Wote hupokea sawa,</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na mpokewa hakomi.
Hula wema na wabaya,</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa bahati mbali mbali,
Kifo au uzima,</s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Basi, mkate Mtakatifu,
Huwa sumu kwa Wabaya,</s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Dawa bora kwa wema.
Ikimegwa sakramenti,</s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Usisite, uamini, huwa ndani ya kipande,</s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwili wote wa Yesu,
Mwili wake haumegwi,</s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ni alama ivunjwayo,
Hali yake pia kimo cha, </s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mwenyewe ni sawa. kumbe mkate wa malaika</s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>huwlisha wasafiri kweli mkate wa wana,</s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>usitupwe	kwa mbwa,
hii mifano ya zamani,</s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hutolewa mwana Isaka,
na kondoo kuchinjwa pasaka,</s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Pia mana ya jangwani.
Ee Mchungaji wetu mwema,</s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu utuhurumie,
utuchunge utulinde,</s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ee Mchungaji wetu mwema, uonyeshe </s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mema yako, huko kwenye wazima.</s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ee Mchungaji wetu mwema, Ee Mwenyezi na Mjuaji,</s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwenye kutuchunga hapa, tujalie pia huko,</s></f>"},{ID:62,
