aulaye mkate huu ataishi milele.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>W. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>INJILI</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Luka 9:11b 17</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Luka</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakati ule:
Yesu alisema na watu juu ya ufalme wa Mungu, na akawaponya</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>waliohitaji kuponywa. Kulipokuchwa, wale Kumi na Wawili</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wakamwendea, wakamwambia, Waage watu waende katika</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>vijiji vya jirani na kwa wakulima wa mashambani wapate mahali pa</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kulala na vyakula, maana hapa tulipo ni mahali pa ukiwa.\"[Yesu]</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akawaambia, \"Wapeni ninyi chakula.\" Wakajibu,</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Hatuna zaidi ya mikate mitano na samaki wawili, labda twende</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kuwanunulia watu hawa wote chakula.\"
akawaambia,</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Sasa wanaume peke yao walikuwa kadiri ya elfu tano.</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kisha akawaambia wafuasi wake,</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Waketisheni watu vikundi vya hamsini hamsini.\"</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakafanya hivyo wakawaketisha wote.</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Akaitwaa mikate mitano na samaki wawili,</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akatazama juu mbinguni, akaibariki, akaimega,</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akawapa wafuasi wake wawaandalie watu wa umati.</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wote wakala, wakashiba. Na vipande walivyoviokota vilijaza</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>vikapu kumi na viwili.</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f>"}],
