Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ngai Mũrungu Urīa wi- lgūr</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>-Müno, agīkīműrathima, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akiuga atīrī: Abraham arorathimwo nĩ Mürungu üria wi igūũrũ mũno, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o we mwene igūrũ na thĩ; ningī Mūrungu üria wi lgürü mũno arogathwo, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o we ūria ūrekeirie thũ ciaku agacineana moko-inī maku. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake Abraham akīműgaïra gicunji gīa ikūmi kīa indo ciothe cia ndaho.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
