Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Thaburi l10: 1;2;3;4.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA : Mwathani, Wee wĩ Műsacerdoti o nginya tene.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani nî erire mwathani wakwa atiīī: </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ikara th</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ỉ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> guoko-inī gwakwa kwa ūrio, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kinya ngatūma thũ ciaku ituike gaturūa ka'makinya maku.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA : Mwathani, Wee wĩ Műsacerdoti o nginya tene.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mūthigi wa hinya waku, Mwathani nī akaūtambūrūkia wĩ</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Sion wee ri athanaga uri o gatagati ga thu ciaku</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA : Mwathani, Wee wĩ Műsacerdoti o nginya tene.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mūthenya wa ita ciaku kirindi giaku gikerehage mwiendero, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kii na ugemu ūria wa ūtheru:</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>aanake aku wi nao mahaana ta ireera, </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o uria rioima nda ya rucini ruoro ruatema,</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA : Mwathani, Wee wĩ Műsacerdoti o nginya tene.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani nī ehītīte, na ndangiiricükwo, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akoiga: Wee wīi mūthinjri-Ngai o nginya teneo ta
üria Melkisedeck aatarii.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA : Mwathani, Wee wĩ Műsacerdoti o nginya tene.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
