Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>1 Akorintho 11: 23 - 26,</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GUTHOMA MARUA MA MUTHURE PAUL KŪRI ANDÜ A KORINTHO</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ariŭ a Ithe witū, nĩ gūkorűo niï nĩ ndamenyithirio nĩ </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani űhoro o ürīa ndamūkinyirie inyuī: </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>atĩ Mwathani Yesu, o ütukű üria aakunyanīirűo, </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>oire műgate, na aarīkia gűcokeria Ngai</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ngatho, akīwenyūra, akiuga atīrī: </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>uyũ nĩguo mwirí wakwa ūheanītwo ni ündũ wanyu: </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ikagai üü niĩ getha mündirikanage. </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ningī, o ündũ ūmwe, irio ciarīkia kürīo, </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akīoya gīkombe, akiuga atirī :</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Gīkombe dikī nikĪo gã kĩrikaníro kīrīa kīerũ thĩinī wa thakame yakwa: </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ikagai ū</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> h</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>ndĩ ciothe rīria mürĩkĩnyuagī ra, </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ getha műndirikanage. </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ gükorűo rĩrña rīothe mūkürĩa mūgate ücio, </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na mūkanyuīra gĩkombe kĩu-ī, nĩ kuumbűra müküumbūra </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ühoro wa gūkua kwa Mwathani.
O nginya hĩndĩ iria agoka.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nīcio ciugo cia Mwathani,</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SEQUENCE</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>1. Sion kumia Muhonokia Muthamaki na Murïithi na thaburi 
na nyïmbo.</s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>2. Mukumie ta urïa wahota Nïakïrïte ukumio wothe, 
Ndungïmukumia kuigana.</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>3. Umuthï nï tuinïre muno, Mugate urï muoyo, Na urï na ugima.</s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>4. Urïa kõuna Yesu aheire Atume ikumi na erï Irio-inï cia muthia.</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>5. ukumio muhingu uiguo, Wa okeni na Wï riri, ucanjamure 
ngoro.</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>6. Amu umuthï gwï thigukuu nene, Ya kuririkana, Ekaristi 
ya mbere, Irio-inï cia muthia.</s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>7. Metha-inï ya Muthamaki mweru, Paska njeru ya watho mweru, 
Yanina Paska ya tene.</s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>8. Undu mweru weheria mukuru, Kïrïa kïa ma, kïeheria muhianano, Utheri weheria nduma.</s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>9. Urïa Kristu ekire tene, Agïtwatha twïkage guo 
Tukïmuririkana.</s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>10. Turutïtwo nï Kanitha, Turutaga igongona. Mugate na dibai.</s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>11. Wïtïkia wa Akristu nï uyu, Mugate utuïkaga Mwïrï Na dibai 
Thakame.</s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>12. Tutekuona kana kuhutia, Nïtwïtïkie na hinya, Kïama gïkï 
kïnene.</s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>13. Nï tuonaga muhuanire, Wa mugate na dibai No nï Yesu 
urï ho.</s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>14. Mwïrï nï irio, Thakame gïa kunyua No Kristu eho 
mugima O thïinï wa o kïmwe.</s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>15. Ndangïnyiha nï kurïo Ndegaika nï kwenyuruo Amukïruo 
e mugima.</s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>16. Arïo nï umwe kana ngiri, Othe marïe undu umwe Na Yesu 
ndangïthira.</s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>17. Marïaga ega na oru, No maciaro ti undu umwe Gïkuu kana 
ugima.</s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>18. Gïkuu kurï oru ugima kurï ega, No wone marïa undu umwe 
No matigana atïa.</s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>19. O na hostia yenyuruo, Ndukae kugïa na nganja, Ririkana 
Yesu eho Kenyu-inï e mugima.</s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>20. Yesu ndagayukanagio, No muhuanire guo wiki, Na uhingu 
na muigana, Wa Yesu ndunyihaga.</s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>21. Oneni mugate wa Araika, utuïkïte irio cia agendi Kuna 
mugate wa ciana Ndukanaheo ngui.</s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>22. Mugate warathiruo tene, rïrïa Isaaka arutagwo igon gona, </s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na ndurume ya Paska ïgïthïnjwo Na manna ma weru-
inï.</s></f>"},{ID:70,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>23. Murïithi mwega, mugate wa ma, Yesu utuiguïre tha, Wee 
turïithie no tugitïre,</s></f>"},{ID:71,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Wee tuma tukona wega, Bururi wa 
Ikenero.</s></f>"},{ID:72,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>24.Wee mwene uugï, na uhoti wothe, uturïithagia ithuï andu, 
utwïte kuu gwaku muciï,</s></f>"},{ID:73,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ututue agai na aikari, A muciï wa 
Atheru. Nï gutuïke guo. Alleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:74,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>RUIMBO RWA ALLELUYA 
John 6,51</s></f>"},{ID:75,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alleluya, Alleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:76,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwathani ekuuga atïrï, \"Niï ndï mugate urï 
muoyo urïa woimire iguru;</s></f>"},{ID:76,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> mundu urïa ungïrïa mugate uyu nï 
agatuura mïndï na mïndï, Alleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GUTHOMA INJIRI YA MUTHURE LUKA:</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hindī io Yesu akiira kirīndi na akīaragîria ühoro wa </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Unene wa Ngai na nĩ ahonagia arīa mabataraga nī </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kūhonio, akīmahonia Narīo riüa rigītwa g</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>th</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>a; </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nao arīa ikūmi na erī magiuka kūri we makīmwira atīrī: </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ira andü a kiründi mathii, makinye mīcīi-inī, </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na ng'ongo iria irī hakuhī, makaraare kuo, na mamathe i:</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nī gūkorũo haha tũri no werũ. </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nowe akīmera atirī: Mahei irio arī inyu. </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nao makīmwira atirirī na kīndü, tiga mīgate îtano na ciüngūyũ igīrī; </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>no anga tūthiire tūkagūrīre andü aya othe irio. </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Amu nī haarī arüme ta ngiri ithano. </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake akiira arutwo ake atīri: 
Merei maikare thĩ kundi andũ mĩrongo îtano, </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ītano. Nao magīika ūguo, makīmaikaria thĩ othe. </s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nake akīoya mioate io itano na ciũng</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>yũ icio igīrī, </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agīcoka akīrora lgūrű, agīcirathima, agīcienyūranga, </s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akīnengera arutwo matwarīre andű a kirīndī. </s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nao makīrīa makīhüna othe : gügicoka gūkĩoyo cienyū iria ciatigarire </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ciondo ikümi na igīrī</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nicio ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"}],
Text:"THIGUKU YA MWIRI NA THAKAME YA KRISTU MWAKA C"}],IsCompressed:0,Guid:"uf/h0wxFWkSrxneJr6CDbQ",
Text:"MATHOMO MA MWAKA C"}